"untuk membuat tindakan yang dapat memperbarui deskripsi tugas, tindakan "
"*Jalankan Kode* dapat dibuat dengan kode berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:119
msgid ""
"To function correctly, `content` **must** be defined as an argument in "
"tool's *Usage* tab."
msgstr ""
"Agar berfungsi dengan benar, `content` **harus** didefinisikan sebagai "
"argumen di tab *Penggunaan* alat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:122
msgid ":ref:`Server Actions <reference/actions/server>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Tindakan Server <reference/actions/server>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:125
msgid "Common issues"
msgstr "Masalah umum"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:128
msgid "Why is the Tools field empty?"
msgstr "Mengapa kolom Alat kosong?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:130
msgid ""
"Confirm that at least one server action has :guilabel:`Use in AI` enabled."
msgstr ""
"Konfirmasi bahwa setidaknya satu tindakan server memiliki :guilabel:`Gunakan "
"di AI` yang diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:131
msgid ""
"Confirm that at least one tool is assigned to the same "
"model :guilabel:`Model` as the server action."
msgstr ""
"Konfirmasi bahwa setidaknya satu alat ditetapkan ke model yang "
"sama :guilabel:`Model` dengan tindakan server."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:135
msgid "Why did the tool run but nothing happened?"
msgstr "Mengapa alat berjalan tetapi tidak terjadi apa-apa?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:137
msgid "The Python code exited without changes."
msgstr "Kode Python keluar tanpa perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:138
msgid "Required arguments were missing or empty."
msgstr "Argumen yang diperlukan hilang atau kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:139
msgid "Business conditions were not implemented in the tool logic."
msgstr "Kondisi bisnis tidak diimplementasikan dalam logika alat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:142
msgid "Why did the AI choose an unexpected tool?"
msgstr "Mengapa AI memilih alat yang tidak terduga?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:144
msgid "The prompt lacked sufficient context."
msgstr "Prompt tidak memiliki konteks yang cukup."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:145
msgid "Multiple tools matched the same intent."
msgstr "Beberapa alat cocok dengan maksud yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:146
msgid "No constraints were enforced at the tool level."
msgstr "Tidak ada batasan yang diterapkan di tingkat alat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:3
msgid "AI in support workflows"
msgstr "AI dalam alur kerja dukungan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:7
msgid ""
"Utilizing Odoo's |AI| features in the **Helpdesk** app assists support "
"agents with their tasks, rather than replacing existing workflows. The goal "
"is to reduce repetitive tasks, accelerate ticket handling, and improve "
"consistency by allowing |AI| to analyze ticket content and suggest or "
"execute actions automatically."
msgstr ""
"Memanfaatkan fitur |AI| Odoo di aplikasi **Pusat Bantuan** membantu agen "
"dukungan dengan tugas-tugas mereka, bukan menggantikan alur kerja yang ada. "
"Tujuannya adalah untuk mengurangi tugas berulang, mempercepat penanganan "
"tiket, dan meningkatkan konsistensi dengan memungkinkan |AI| menganalisis "
"konten tiket dan menyarankan atau menjalankan tindakan secara otomatis."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:12
msgid ""
"Instead of manually categorizing, prioritizing, and responding to every "
"request, support teams can rely on |AI| to interpret incoming information "
"and perform preliminary processing. Agents remain in control of decisions "
"and customer communication, while |AI| handles repetitive analysis and "
"drafting."
msgstr ""
"Alih-alih secara manual mengkategorikan, memprioritaskan, dan merespons "
"setiap permintaan, tim dukungan dapat mengandalkan |AI| untuk "
"menginterpretasikan informasi yang masuk dan melakukan pemrosesan awal. Agen "
"tetap mengontrol keputusan dan komunikasi pelanggan, sementara |AI| "
"menangani analisis dan penyusunan yang berulang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:18
msgid "How AI works in Helpdesk"
msgstr "Bagaimana AI bekerja di Pusat Bantuan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:20
msgid "|AI| capabilities in **Helpdesk** are built around three core ideas:"
msgstr ""
"Kemampuan |AI| di **Pusat Bantuan** dibangun berdasarkan tiga ide inti:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:22
msgid ""
"|AI| agents that interact with users or agents and generate responses based "
"on knowledge sources."
msgstr ""
"Agen |AI| yang berinteraksi dengan pengguna atau agen dan menghasilkan "
"respons berdasarkan sumber pengetahuan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:23
msgid ""
"|AI| automations that update tickets automatically when records are created "
"or modified."
msgstr ""
"Otomasi |AI| yang memperbarui tiket secara otomatis ketika rekaman dibuat "
"atau dimodifikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:24
msgid ""
"|AI| enabled fields that generate structured information, such as summaries, "
"from unstructured text."
msgstr ""
"Bidang yang diaktifkan |AI| yang menghasilkan informasi terstruktur, seperti "
"ringkasan, dari teks tidak terstruktur."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:30
msgid ""
"An |AI| agent is a configurable assistant that operates using prompts and "
"contextual knowledge. The agent itself does not contain business logic; "
"instead, it follows instructions defined by users and relies on provided "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Agen |AI| adalah asisten yang dapat dikonfigurasi yang beroperasi "
"menggunakan prompt dan pengetahuan kontekstual. Agen itu sendiri tidak "
"mengandung logika bisnis; sebaliknya, ia mengikuti instruksi yang ditentukan "
"oleh pengguna dan bergantung pada dokumentasi yang disediakan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:34
msgid ""
"When an agent receives a request, it combines its system :ref:`prompt <ai/"
"agents/prompts-in-odoo>`, the current record context (such as a ticket), and "
"its knowledge :ref:`sources <ai/sources>`."
msgstr ""
"Ketika agen menerima permintaan, ia menggabungkan :ref:`prompt <ai/agents/"
"prompts-in-odoo>` sistemnya, konteks rekaman saat ini (seperti tiket), "
"dan :ref:`sumber <ai/sources>` pengetahuannya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:37
msgid ""
"This allows the agent to provide responses grounded in internal "
"documentation rather than generic language model output."
msgstr ""
"Ini memungkinkan agen memberikan respons yang didasarkan pada dokumentasi "
"internal daripada keluaran model bahasa generik."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:40
msgid ""
"Agents can be restricted to specific sources or granted permissions to "
"perform actions using topics. This ensures that support assistants behave "
"predictably and remain aligned with organizational rules."
msgstr ""
"Agen dapat dibatasi pada sumber tertentu atau diberikan izin untuk melakukan "
"tindakan menggunakan topik. Ini memastikan bahwa asisten dukungan "
"berperilaku dapat diprediksi dan tetap selaras dengan aturan organisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:45
msgid "AI automations"
msgstr "Otomasi AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:47
msgid ""
"Automation rules allow |AI| to act during record lifecycle events. Instead "
"of waiting for an agent to categorize or prioritize tickets, |AI| can "
"perform these tasks automatically as soon as a ticket is created."
msgstr ""
"Aturan otomasi memungkinkan |AI| bertindak selama peristiwa siklus hidup "
"rekaman. Alih-alih menunggu agen untuk mengkategorikan atau memprioritaskan "
"tiket, |AI| dapat melakukan tugas-tugas ini secara otomatis segera setelah "
"tiket dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:51
msgid ""
"The key principle is that |AI| does not understand Odoo models directly. It "
"receives text extracted from fields and produces an output based on prompt "
"instructions. Users guide |AI| behavior through clear prompting and "
"carefully selected input fields."
msgstr ""
"Prinsip utamanya adalah |AI| tidak memahami model Odoo secara langsung. Ia "
"menerima teks yang diekstrak dari field dan menghasilkan keluaran "
"berdasarkan instruksi prompt. Pengguna memandu perilaku |AI| melalui prompt "
"yang jelas dan field input yang dipilih dengan hati-hati."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:58
msgid ""
"|AI| enabled fields extend standard Odoo fields by allowing their values to "
"be generated automatically through prompts."
msgstr ""
"Field yang diaktifkan |AI| memperluas field Odoo standar dengan memungkinkan "
"nilai mereka dihasilkan secara otomatis melalui prompt."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:61
msgid ""
"These fields are useful when large amounts of text need to be condensed into "
"actionable information. For example, a long customer message can "
"automatically be summarized into a short list of key points, allowing agents "
"to understand issues quickly without reading full descriptions."
msgstr ""
"Field ini berguna ketika sejumlah besar teks perlu dipadatkan menjadi "
"informasi yang dapat ditindaklanjuti. Misalnya, pesan pelanggan yang panjang "
"dapat secara otomatis diringkas menjadi daftar singkat poin-poin kunci, "
"memungkinkan agen memahami masalah dengan cepat tanpa membaca deskripsi "
"lengkap."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:69
msgid "Configuring an AI agent for support"
msgstr "Mengonfigurasi agen AI untuk dukungan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:71
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`agents <agents>` are configured in the **AI** application. To "
"configure an existing agent, navigate to :menuselection:`AI app` and click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon, then "
"click :guilabel:`Configuration` on the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`agen <agents>` dikonfigurasi di aplikasi **AI**. Untuk "
"mengonfigurasi agen yang ada, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`aplikasi AI` "
"dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(elipsis vertikal)`, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Konfigurasi` pada menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:75
msgid ""
"Configuring begins by selecting a language model and defining a system "
"prompt describing how the agent should behave. The prompt determines tone, "
"scope, and responsibility. A support-focused agent might be instructed to "
"analyze issues and provide concise technical responses."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi dimulai dengan memilih model bahasa dan mendefinisikan prompt "
"sistem yang menjelaskan bagaimana agen harus berperilaku. Prompt menentukan "
"nada, cakupan, dan tanggung jawab. Agen yang berfokus pada dukungan mungkin "
"diinstruksikan untuk menganalisis masalah dan memberikan respons teknis yang "
"ringkas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:79
msgid ""
"The next step is defining the agent's *sources*. These :ref:`sources <ai/"
"sources>` form the agent's memory and should contain trusted documentation "
"such as product guides or FAQs. The quality of these sources directly "
"impacts the quality of AI responses."
msgstr ""
"Langkah selanjutnya adalah mendefinisikan *sumber* agen. :ref:`Sumber <ai/"
"sources>` ini membentuk memori agen dan harus berisi dokumentasi tepercaya "
"seperti panduan produk atau FAQ. Kualitas sumber ini secara langsung "
"memengaruhi kualitas respons AI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:84
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Restrict to Sources` to require the agent to **only** base "
"their responses on the supplied resources."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Batasi ke Sumber` untuk mengharuskan agen **hanya** "
"mendasarkan respons mereka pada sumber daya yang disediakan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:87
msgid ""
"Users may also define *topics*, which grant the agent permission to perform "
"specific actions. :ref:`Topics <ai/topics>` allow advanced scenarios such as "
"record creation or automation triggers."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna juga dapat mendefinisikan *topik*, yang memberikan izin kepada agen "
"untuk melakukan tindakan tertentu. :ref:`Topik <ai/topics>` memungkinkan "
"skenario lanjutan seperti pembuatan rekaman atau pemicu otomasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:None
msgid "An example support AI agent."
msgstr "Contoh agen AI dukungan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:93
msgid ""
"Once an agent exists, *default prompts* can be used to initiate a "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Setelah agen ada, *prompt default* dapat digunakan untuk memulai percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:95
msgid ""
"A default prompt defines where and when the |AI| appears inside Odoo. In the "
"**Helpdesk** app, this typically means allowing the |AI| button to appear on "
"ticket records. The default prompt specifies the model where it is "
"available, which agent is called, and additional contextual instructions."
msgstr ""
"Prompt default mendefinisikan di mana dan kapan |AI| muncul di dalam Odoo. "
"Di aplikasi **Pusat Bantuan**, ini biasanya berarti mengizinkan tombol |AI| "
"muncul pada rekaman tiket. Prompt default menentukan model di mana ia "
"tersedia, agen mana yang dipanggil, dan instruksi kontekstual tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:None
msgid "A list of default prompts assigned to the Support Agent."
msgstr "Daftar prompt default yang ditetapkan ke Agen Dukungan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:102
msgid ""
"These instructions act as a second layer on top of the agent prompt, "
"adapting the agent's behavior to **Helpdesk** scenarios."
msgstr ""
"Instruksi ini bertindak sebagai lapisan kedua di atas prompt agen, "
"menyesuaikan perilaku agen dengan skenario **Pusat Bantuan**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:106
msgid "Configuring AI automations"
msgstr "Mengonfigurasi otomasi AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:108
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`server actions <server-actions>` are configured using standard "
"automated actions, with |AI| used as the update mechanism."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`tindakan server <server-actions>` dikonfigurasi menggunakan "
"tindakan otomatis standar, dengan |AI| digunakan sebagai mekanisme pembaruan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:111
msgid ""
"When defining a server action, users specify when the action should run, "
"such as when a new ticket is created. The |AI| prompt then explains how the "
"ticket should be interpreted and which field should be updated."
msgstr ""
"Při definování serverové akce uživatelé určují, kdy má akce běžet, například "
"při vytvoření nového tiketu. Výzva |AI| pak vysvětluje, jak má být tiket "
"interpretován a které pole by mělo být aktualizováno."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:115
msgid ""
"This approach keeps automation predictable while allowing |AI| to make "
"contextual decisions."
msgstr ""
"Tento přístup udržuje automatizaci předvídatelnou a zároveň umožňuje |AI| "
"činit kontextová rozhodnutí."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:118
msgid "Configuring AI fields"
msgstr "Konfigurace AI polí"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:120
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`fields <fields>` are configured by enabling the |AI| option on a "
"custom or property field and providing a prompt describing the expected "
"result. Once configured, the field updates automatically when the record "
"changes, giving agents instant access to structured information."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`pole <fields>` se konfigurují povolením možnosti |AI| na vlastním "
"poli nebo poli vlastností a poskytnutím výzvy popisující očekávaný výsledek. "
"Po konfiguraci se pole automaticky aktualizuje při změně záznamu, což "
"agentům poskytuje okamžitý přístup ke strukturovaným informacím."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:125
msgid ""
"|AI| fields can be added to a record through the **Studio** app or property "
"field. :ref:`Installing Studio <general/install>` may impact the current "
"pricing plan for a database."
msgstr ""
"|AI| pole lze do záznamu přidat prostřednictvím aplikace **Studio** nebo "
"pole vlastností. :ref:`Instalace Studio <general/install>` může mít vliv na "
"aktuální cenový plán pro database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:128
msgid ""
"For more information, refer to `Odoo's pricing page <https://www.odoo.com/"
"pricing-plan>`_ or contact your account manager."
msgstr ""
"Pro více informací se podívejte na `cenovou stránku Odoo <https://"
"www.odoo.com/pricing-plan>`_ nebo kontaktujte svého account managera."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:132
msgid ":doc:`AI Fields <fields>`"
msgstr ":doc:`AI pole <fields>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:134
msgid ":doc:`AI Server Actions <server-actions>`"
msgstr ":doc:`AI serverové akce <server-actions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:3
msgid "AI voice transcription"
msgstr "Transkripsi suara AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo |AI| can transcribe spoken audio into text and generate summaries from "
"that transcript. This feature supports both meeting recordings and real-time "
"dictation, making it easier to capture notes, decisions, and action items "
"without manual typing."
msgstr ""
"Odoo |AI| dapat menyalin audio lisan menjadi teks dan menghasilkan ringkasan "
"dari transkrip tersebut. Fitur ini mendukung rekaman rapat dan dikte waktu "
"nyata, sehingga memudahkan untuk menangkap catatan, keputusan, dan item "
"tindakan tanpa pengetikan manual."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:11
msgid ""
"Voice transcription converts spoken audio into a written transcript. Once a "
"transcript is available, Odoo |AI| can generate a summary that highlights "
"key information, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Transkripsi suara mengonversi audio lisan menjadi transkrip tertulis. "
"Setelah transkrip tersedia, Odoo |AI| dapat menghasilkan ringkasan yang "
"menyoroti informasi kunci, seperti:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:14
msgid "key discussion points"
msgstr "poin diskusi kunci"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:15
msgid "decisions"
msgstr "keputusan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:16
msgid "action items"
msgstr "item tindakan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:17
msgid "next steps"
msgstr "langkah berikutnya"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:19
msgid ""
"Transcription and summarization can be used for meetings, calls, quick "
"dictations, and internal notes."
msgstr ""
"Transkripsi dan peringkasan dapat digunakan untuk rapat, panggilan, dikte "
"cepat, dan catatan internal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:23
msgid ""
"Voice transcripts can be created in the *Description* and *Notes* fields of "
"most records, as well as in **Knowledge** articles."
msgstr ""
"Transkrip suara dapat dibuat di bidang *Deskripsi* dan *Catatan* pada "
"sebagian besar rekaman, serta dalam artikel **Pengetahuan**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:0
msgid "The powerbox in the description tab of a task in the Projects app."
msgstr "Kotak daya di tab deskripsi tugas dalam aplikasi Projects."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:29
msgid ""
"Voice transcription works by temporarily recording audio during the session, "
"replaying it for transcription, and generating a written transcript and "
"summary. Once the transcription process is complete, the audio recording is "
"automatically discarded. The recorded audio is not stored, replayable, or "
"accessible from the database."
msgstr ""
"Transkripsi suara bekerja dengan merekam audio sementara selama sesi, "
"memutarnya kembali untuk transkripsi, dan menghasilkan transkrip tertulis "
"serta ringkasan. Setelah proses transkripsi selesai, rekaman audio secara "
"otomatis dihapus. Audio yang direkam tidak disimpan, tidak dapat diputar "
"ulang, atau diakses dari database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:35
msgid "Transcribe a meeting"
msgstr "Transkripsi rapat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:37
msgid ""
"To create a voice transcript, type `/` to open the :ref:`powerbox "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`. Select :guilabel:`Voice Transcript` from "
"the drop-down list. This creates a new text block. Click :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`Notes` to add notes and details regarding the meeting. This "
"is where information, such as a meeting agenda and attendees, can be added. "
"Click :icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`Transcript` to switch to a live view "
"of the transcript being created in real-time."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat transkrip suara, ketik `/` untuk membuka :ref:`kotak daya "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`. Pilih :guilabel:`Voice Transcript` dari "
"daftar drop-down. Ini akan membuat blok teks baru. Klik :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`Notes` untuk menambahkan catatan dan detail mengenai rapat. "
"Di sinilah informasi seperti agenda rapat dan peserta dapat ditambahkan. "
"Klik :icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`Transcript` untuk beralih ke tampilan "
"langsung transkrip yang dibuat secara real-time."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:44
msgid ""
"When the meeting is ready to begin, click :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start "
"Recording`."
msgstr ""
"Ketika rapat siap dimulai, klik :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start "
"Recording`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:47
msgid ""
"Clicking :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start Recording` may cause a pop-up in "
"the browser, requesting access to a microphone. If permission is not given, "
"the recording stops, and an error message appears. To combat this error, "
"refresh the page and allow Odoo access to the microphone."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start Recording` mungkin menyebabkan "
"pop-up di browser, meminta akses ke mikrofon. Jika izin tidak diberikan, "
"perekaman berhenti dan muncul pesan kesalahan. Untuk mengatasi kesalahan "
"ini, segarkan halaman dan izinkan Odoo mengakses mikrofon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:51
msgid ""
"When the meeting has ended, click :icon:`fa-stop` :guilabel:`Stop "
"Recording`. The recorded audio is then processed to generate a transcript "
"and an |AI| summary. Once processing is complete, the audio recording is "
"automatically discarded, leaving only the transcript and summary available."
msgstr ""
"Ketika rapat telah berakhir, klik :icon:`fa-stop` :guilabel:`Stop "
"Recording`. Audio yang direkam kemudian diproses untuk menghasilkan "
"transkrip dan ringkasan |AI|. Setelah pemrosesan selesai, rekaman audio "
"secara otomatis dihapus, hanya menyisakan transkrip dan ringkasan yang "
"tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:None
msgid "The AI summary of a meeting transctipt."
msgstr "Ringkasan AI dari transkrip rapat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:58
msgid ""
"The |AI| summary can be manually edited to provide additional insight, such "
"as identifying meeting attendees by name, or specifying key points. The "
"meeting notes can then be converted into an email recap, or shared directly "
"via email by clicking the :guilabel:`Share by email` button."
msgstr ""
"Ringkasan |AI| dapat diedit secara manual untuk memberikan wawasan tambahan, "
"seperti mengidentifikasi peserta rapat berdasarkan nama, atau menentukan "
"poin-poin penting. Catatan rapat kemudian dapat dikonversi menjadi rekap "
"email, atau dibagikan langsung melalui email dengan mengklik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Share by email`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:6
msgid "Appointments"
msgstr "Appointment"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:8
msgid ""
"Odoo's **Appointments** app is a self-service scheduling app that simplifies "
"the process of booking meetings, consultations, or services. Integrated with "
"Odoo's suite of business apps, it allows companies to automate appointment "
"scheduling, reduce manual coordination, and provide a seamless experience "
"for clients. Appointments can be linked to calendars, **CRM** opportunities, "
"employee schedules, and more, making it an ideal tool for service-based "
"businesses seeking efficiency and organization."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Appointment** dari Odoo adalah aplikasi penjadwalan layanan "
"mandiri yang menyederhanakan proses pemesanan meeting, konsultasi, atau "
"layanan. Terintegrasi dengan rangkaian aplikasi bisnis Odoo, aplikasi ini "
"memungkinkan perusahaan mengotomatiskan penjadwalan appointment, mengurangi "
"koordinasi manual, dan memberikan pengalaman yang lancar bagi klien. "
"Appointment dapat ditautkan ke kalender, peluang **CRM**, jadwal karyawan, "
"dan lainnya, menjadikannya alat yang ideal bagi bisnis berbasis layanan yang "
"mencari efisiensi dan organisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:18
msgid ""
"The **Appointments** app allows for new appointments to be scheduled based "
"on the availability of users, or the availability of *resources*, such as "
"meeting rooms or seating areas. To create a new resource, or manage existing "
"resources, navigate to :menuselection:`Appointments --> Configuration --> "
"Resources`. This opens a list of the available resources in the database, as "
"well as their individual capacity."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Appointment** memungkinkan appointment baru dijadwalkan "
"berdasarkan ketersediaan user, atau ketersediaan *resource*, seperti ruangan "
"meeting atau area tempat duduk. Untuk membuat resource baru, atau mengelola "
"resource yang ada, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Appointment --> "
"Configuration --> Resources`. Ini membuka daftar resource yang tersedia "
"dalam database, serta kapasitas masing-masing."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:27
msgid "Resources"
msgstr "Sumber Daya"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new resource. On the blank record, enter "
"a :guilabel:`Name` for the new resource. In the :guilabel:`Capacity` field, "
"enter the maximum number of people the resource can accommodate. Then, "
"confirm the :guilabel:`Timezone` for this resource."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`New` untuk membuat resource baru. Pada record kosong, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Name` untuk resource baru. Dalam "
"field :guilabel:`Capacity`, masukkan jumlah maksimum orang yang dapat "
"ditampung resource. Kemudian, konfirmasi :guilabel:`Timezone` untuk resource "
"ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:33
msgid ""
"If desired, select one or more :guilabel:`Linked Resource` from the drop-"
"down. This option designates one or more resources that can be used in "
"combination to handled a bigger demand."
msgstr ""
"Jika diinginkan, pilih satu atau lebih :guilabel:`Linked Resource` dari drop-"
"down. Opsi ini menunjuk satu atau lebih resource yang dapat digunakan secara "
"kombinasi untuk menangani permintaan yang lebih besar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:37
msgid ""
"*Linked resources* are only used when using the :ref:`auto-assign "
"<appointments/configure>` :guilabel:`Assignment Method`."
msgstr ""
"*Resource yang ditautkan* hanya digunakan saat menggunakan :ref:`auto-assign "
"<appointments/configure>` :guilabel:`Assignment Method`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:40
msgid ""
"Lastly, add a :guilabel:`Description` for this resource. The contents of "
"the :guilabel:`Description` tab are visible to customers when booking an "
"appointment online."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, tambahkan :guilabel:`Description` untuk sumber daya ini. Konten "
"tab :guilabel:`Description` terlihat oleh pelanggan saat memesan janji temu "
"secara online."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:44
msgid "Resource capacity"
msgstr "Kapasitas sumber daya"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:46
msgid ""
"When booking an appointment based on resource availability, the website only "
"displays capacity up to `12`. This occurs even if the resource has a higher "
"capacity. To avoid this, a new *System Parameter* needs to be added to the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Saat memesan janji temu berdasarkan ketersediaan sumber daya, website hanya "
"menampilkan kapasitas hingga `12`. Hal ini terjadi bahkan jika sumber daya "
"memiliki kapasitas yang lebih tinggi. Untuk menghindari hal ini, *Parameter "
"Sistem* baru perlu ditambahkan ke database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:50
msgid ""
"First, ensure that :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` is enabled. Then, "
"navigate to the :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Parameters --"
"> System Parameters`. Click :guilabel:`New` to add a new parameter."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pastikan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>` diaktifkan. "
"Kemudian, navigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengaturan --> Teknis --> "
"Parameter --> Parameter Sistem`. Klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk menambahkan "
"parameter baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:54
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Key` field, enter "
"`appointment.resource_max_capacity_allowed`. In the :guilabel:`Value` field, "
"enter the maximum capacity that should be allowed. Click :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Di kolom :guilabel:`Key`, masukkan "
"`appointment.resource_max_capacity_allowed`. Di kolom :guilabel:`Value`, "
"masukkan kapasitas maksimum yang harus diizinkan. Klik :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Simpan secara manual)` setelah selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:None
msgid "The new system parameter for capacity limits."
msgstr "Parameter sistem baru untuk batas kapasitas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:64
msgid "Appointment type configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi tipe appointment"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:66
msgid ""
"Before appointments can be scheduled or booked, an appointment type must be "
"created. Navigate to the :menuselection:`Appointments` app dashboard and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. On the new blank record, enter "
"an :guilabel:`Appointment Title`, then set a :guilabel:`Duration` for this "
"appointment type."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum appointment dapat dijadwalkan atau dipesan, tipe appointment harus "
"dibuat. Navigasikan ke dashboard aplikasi :menuselection:`Appointment` dan "
"klik :guilabel:`New`. Pada record kosong baru, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Appointment Title`, kemudian "
"tetapkan :guilabel:`Duration` untuk tipe appointment ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:70
msgid ""
"Next, set a :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time`. This is the minimum amount of time "
"between when an appointment can be booked and when the appointment can "
"begin. If the :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time` is `1` hour, appointments must be "
"booked *at least* `1` hour in advance."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, tetapkan :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time`. Ini adalah jumlah waktu "
"minimum antara saat appointment dapat dipesan dan saat appointment dapat "
"dimulai. Jika :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time` adalah `1` jam, appointment harus "
"dipesan *setidaknya* `1` jam sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:75
msgid ""
"An appointment type is created for `Tennis Courts`, with "
"a :guilabel:`Duration` of `1` hour, and a :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time` of "
"`1` hour. At `02:00` PM, a customer attempts to book an appointment for the "
"same day at `02:45` pm. The first available time is `04:00` pm."
msgstr ""
"Tipe appointment dibuat untuk `Tennis Courts`, dengan :guilabel:`Duration` "
"`1` jam, dan :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time` `1` jam. Pada pukul `02:00` siang, "
"pelanggan mencoba memesan appointment untuk hari yang sama pada pukul "
"`02:45` siang. Waktu pertama yang tersedia adalah pukul `04:00` sore."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the booking calendar showing available times."
msgstr "Contoh kalender pemesanan yang menampilkan waktu yang tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:82
msgid "Select a :guilabel:`Scheduling Window`:"
msgstr "Pilih :guilabel:`Scheduling Window`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:84
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Available now` to allow customers to book an appointment "
"immediately. Use the :guilabel:`Up to X days into the future` field to "
"define how far in advance customers can schedule appointments. For example, "
"if `14` is entered, customers cannot book anything more than 14 days from "
"the current date."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Available now` untuk memungkinkan pelanggan memesan "
"appointment segera. Gunakan field :guilabel:`Up to X days into the future` "
"untuk menentukan seberapa jauh pelanggan dapat menjadwalkan appointment. "
"Misalnya, jika `14` dimasukkan, pelanggan tidak dapat memesan apa pun lebih "
"dari 14 hari dari tanggal saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:88
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Within a date range` to limit bookings to a specific range "
"of dates. After selecting this option, click the :guilabel:`From` "
"and :guilabel:`to` fields, and use the calendar pop-up window to customize "
"the date and time range."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Within a date range` untuk membatasi pemesanan pada rentang "
"tanggal tertentu. Setelah memilih opsi ini, klik field :guilabel:`From` "
"dan :guilabel:`to`, dan gunakan jendela pop-up kalender untuk menyesuaikan "
"rentang tanggal dan waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:92
msgid ""
"Update the :guilabel:`Allow Cancelling` field to limit the amount of time "
"before an appointment where a customer can cancel. If this setting is "
"enabled, customers are unable to cancel within the designated time frame."
msgstr ""
"Perbarui field :guilabel:`Allow Cancelling` untuk membatasi jumlah waktu "
"sebelum appointment di mana pelanggan dapat membatalkan. Jika pengaturan ini "
"diaktifkan, pelanggan tidak dapat membatalkan dalam jangka waktu yang "
"ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:97
msgid ""
"If a customer does try to cancel within the time frame, they receive an "
"error message with contact information. If the appointment is for a "
"resource, the contact details are for the user that created the appointment "
"type. If the appointment is for a user, the contact details are for the user "
"the appointment is with."
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan mencoba membatalkan dalam jangka waktu tersebut, mereka "
"menerima pesan error dengan informasi kontak. Jika appointment untuk "
"resource, detail kontak adalah untuk user yang membuat tipe appointment. "
"Jika appointment untuk user, detail kontak adalah untuk user yang akan "
"melakukan appointment."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the message a customer sees when cancelling."
msgstr "Contoh pesan yang dilihat pelanggan saat membatalkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:105
msgid ""
"Next, designate whether this appointment type is based on :guilabel:`Users` "
"or :guilabel:`Resources`, by selecting the appropriate radio button. If it "
"is based on users, select one or more :guilabel:`Users` in the drop-down. If "
"it is based on :ref:`resources <appointments/resources>`, select one or "
"more :guilabel:`Resources` in the drop-down."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, tentukan apakah tipe appointment ini "
"berdasarkan :guilabel:`Users` atau :guilabel:`Resources`, dengan memilih "
"tombol radio yang sesuai. Jika berdasarkan user, pilih satu atau "
"lebih :guilabel:`Users` dalam drop-down. Jika berdasarkan :ref:`resource "
"<appointments/resources>`, pilih satu atau lebih :guilabel:`Resources` dalam "
"drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:111
msgid ""
"User-based appointment types can be used for scheduling sales meetings and "
"demos, as well as recruiting interviews."
msgstr ""
"Tipe appointment berbasis user dapat digunakan untuk menjadwalkan meeting "
"dan demo penjualan, serta wawancara perekrutan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:114
msgid ""
"Resource-based appointment types can be used for scheduling time in specific "
"rooms or locations."
msgstr ""
"Tipe appointment berbasis resource dapat digunakan untuk menjadwalkan waktu "
"di ruangan atau lokasi tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:116
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Resources` in the :guilabel:`Availability on` field "
"reveals the :guilabel:`Manage Capacities` option. If selected, the "
"appointment limits the number of participants based on the capacity of the "
"resources selected."
msgstr ""
"Memilih :guilabel:`Resources` dalam field :guilabel:`Availability on` "
"mengungkapkan opsi :guilabel:`Manage Capacities`. Jika dipilih, appointment "
"membatasi jumlah peserta berdasarkan kapasitas resource yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:120
msgid ""
"Choose an :guilabel:`Assignment Method` by selecting the appropriate radio "
"button:"
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Metode Penugasan` dengan memilih tombol radio yang sesuai:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pick User/Resource then Time`: customers select from a list of "
"available users/resources, then select an open time slot."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pilih User/Resource lalu Waktu`: pelanggan memilih dari daftar "
"user/resource yang tersedia, lalu memilih slot waktu yang terbuka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Time then User/Resource`: customers choose a date and "
"time, then select from the list of available users/resources."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pilih Waktu lalu User/Resource`: pelanggan memilih tanggal dan "
"waktu, lalu memilih dari daftar user/resource yang tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Time then auto-assign`: customers select a time slot and "
"are automatically assigned a user/resource."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pilih Waktu lalu tetapkan otomatis`: pelanggan memilih slot waktu "
"dan secara otomatis ditugaskan ke user/resource."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:130
msgid "Schedule tab"
msgstr "Tab Jadwal"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:132
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Schedule` tab is used to outline when this appointment type "
"is to be made available. The settings define the time slots shown on the "
"booking page."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Jadwal` digunakan untuk menguraikan kapan tipe appointment "
"ini tersedia. Pengaturan menentukan slot waktu yang ditampilkan di halaman "
"booking."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:135
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to create a new time frame. Select a day of the "
"week from the :guilabel:`Every` drop-down menu, then update the times in "
"the :guilabel:`From` and :guilabel:`To` fields. Click the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon to delete an entry. Multiple entries can be "
"included for a single day."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Tambah baris` untuk membuat kerangka waktu baru. Pilih hari "
"dalam seminggu dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`Setiap`, lalu perbarui waktu "
"di kolom :guilabel:`Dari` dan :guilabel:`Hingga`. Klik ikon :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(tempat sampah)` untuk menghapus entri. Beberapa entri dapat "
"disertakan untuk satu hari."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:141
msgid ""
"If an appointment should not be available at specific times, such as when "
"users are taking lunch, include time slots before and after."
msgstr ""
"Jika appointment tidak boleh tersedia pada waktu tertentu, seperti ketika "
"user sedang makan siang, sertakan slot waktu sebelum dan sesudahnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the Schedule tab in an appointment."
msgstr "Contoh tab Jadwal dalam appointment."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:234
msgid "Options tab"
msgstr "Tab Options"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:150
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Options` tab is used to customize the display options for "
"this appointment, as well as notification settings for customers and users."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Opsi` digunakan untuk menyesuaikan opsi tampilan untuk "
"appointment ini, serta pengaturan notifikasi untuk pelanggan dan user."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:153
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Front-End Display` field determines how the appointment is "
"presented on the website to customers. Select the :guilabel:`Show Pictures` "
"radio button to publish the default pictures of the user or resources for "
"this appointment on the website."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Tampilan Front-End` menentukan bagaimana appointment "
"ditampilkan di website kepada pelanggan. Pilih tombol "
"radio :guilabel:`Tampilkan Gambar` untuk mempublikasikan gambar default user "
"atau resource untuk appointment ini di website."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:157
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Timezone` and :guilabel:`Location` fields automatically "
"populate for resource appointments, based on where the resource is located. "
"For user-based appointments, the :guilabel:`Location` field defaults to an "
"`Online Meeting`, with a :guilabel:`Videoconference Link` automatically "
"generated. If this should not be an online meeting, select a different "
"option in the :guilabel:`Location` field."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Zona Waktu` dan :guilabel:`Lokasi` secara otomatis terisi "
"untuk appointment resource, berdasarkan lokasi resource tersebut. Untuk "
"appointment berbasis user, kolom :guilabel:`Lokasi` default ke `Rapat "
"Online`, dengan :guilabel:`Link Videoconference` dihasilkan secara otomatis. "
"Jika ini bukan rapat online, pilih opsi lain di kolom :guilabel:`Lokasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:163
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Manual Confirmation` checkbox to require approval before "
"a meeting is accepted. If this feature is enabled, the appointment time slot "
"is still considered *reserved* until it is confirmed or rejected. Leave this "
"checkbox blank to automatically accept meetings created from this "
"appointment."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak :guilabel:`Konfirmasi Manual` untuk memerlukan persetujuan "
"sebelum rapat diterima. Jika fitur ini diaktifkan, slot waktu appointment "
"masih dianggap *dipesan* hingga dikonfirmasi atau ditolak. Biarkan kotak ini "
"kosong untuk menerima rapat secara otomatis yang dibuat dari appointment ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:168
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Create Opportunities <appointments/create-opps>` feature adds an "
"opportunity to the **CRM** app for each scheduled appointment, which is "
"assigned to the responsible user. Tick the :guilabel:`Create Opportunities` "
"checkbox to enable this option."
msgstr ""
"Fitur :doc:`Buat Peluang <appointments/create-opps>` menambahkan peluang ke "
"aplikasi **CRM** untuk setiap appointment yang dijadwalkan, yang ditugaskan "
"ke user yang bertanggung jawab. Centang kotak :guilabel:`Buat Peluang` untuk "
"mengaktifkan opsi ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:173
msgid ""
"This field is only visible if the **CRM** app is installed on the database."
msgstr "Kolom ini hanya terlihat jika aplikasi **CRM** diinstal di database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:175
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Reminders` field is used to set how customers are to be "
"contacted before the appointment time. Select one or more options from the "
"drop-down, based on the communication method, and the time frame."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Pengingat` digunakan untuk mengatur bagaimana pelanggan "
"akan dihubungi sebelum waktu appointment. Pilih satu atau lebih opsi dari "
"drop-down, berdasarkan metode komunikasi dan kerangka waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:179
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Allow Guests` checkbox to grant customers the ability to "
"add additional guests when registering for an appointment."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak :guilabel:`Izinkan Tamu` untuk memberikan kemampuan kepada "
"pelanggan menambahkan tamu tambahan saat mendaftar appointment."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:185
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:204
msgid "Questions tab"
msgstr "Tab Pertanyaan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:187
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Questions` tab can be used to prompt customers for additional "
"information while they are booking an appointment. Click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` to add a new question."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Pertanyaan` dapat digunakan untuk meminta informasi tambahan "
"dari pelanggan saat mereka memesan appointment. Klik :guilabel:`Tambah "
"baris` untuk menambahkan pertanyaan baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:190
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Questions` pop-up window, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Question`, then choose an :guilabel:`Answer Type`."
msgstr ""
"Pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Create Questions`, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Question`, kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Answer Type`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:193
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Mandatory Answer` checkbox to require customers to "
"answer this question before they are allowed to book an appointment. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save & New` to add another question, or :guilabel:`Save & "
"Close` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak :guilabel:`Mandatory Answer` untuk mengharuskan pelanggan "
"menjawab pertanyaan ini sebelum mereka diizinkan untuk memesan appointment. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Save & New` untuk menambahkan pertanyaan lain, "
"atau :guilabel:`Save & Close` setelah selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:198
msgid "Messages tab"
msgstr "Tab Pesan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:200
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Messages` tab is used by the business to provide additional "
"information to customers regarding this appointment type."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Messages` digunakan oleh bisnis untuk memberikan informasi "
"tambahan kepada pelanggan mengenai jenis appointment ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:204
msgid ""
"The content in the :guilabel:`Messages` tab is visible to customers and "
"website visitors."
msgstr ""
"Konten dalam tab :guilabel:`Messages` dapat dilihat oleh pelanggan dan "
"pengunjung website."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:206
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Introduction Message` field, add a short description of "
"the appointment type. This can include the topic of the appointment, a "
"meeting agenda, or an introduction to the users responsible for the meeting."
msgstr ""
"Pada kolom :guilabel:`Introduction Message`, tambahkan deskripsi singkat "
"tentang jenis appointment. Ini dapat mencakup topik appointment, agenda "
"pertemuan, atau pengenalan kepada pengguna yang bertanggung jawab atas "
"pertemuan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:210
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Extra Message on Confirmation` is displayed to a customer "
"after they have booked a meeting. Add any additional information here that "
"the customer should be aware of. This can include parking information, last "
"minute rules, or additional instructions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Extra Message on Confirmation` ditampilkan kepada pelanggan "
"setelah mereka memesan pertemuan. Tambahkan informasi tambahan di sini yang "
"perlu diketahui pelanggan. Ini dapat mencakup informasi parkir, aturan menit "
"terakhir, atau instruksi tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:215
msgid "Publishing an appointment"
msgstr "Menerbitkan appointment"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:217
msgid ""
"When an appointment is ready to publish, click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` "
"smart button at the top of the record. Then, slide the :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"off` :guilabel:`Unpublished` icon to :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"on` :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"Ketika appointment siap diterbitkan, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Go to "
"Website` di bagian atas record. Kemudian, geser ikon :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"off` :guilabel:`Unpublished` ke :icon:`fa-toggle-on` :guilabel:`Published`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:3
msgid "Create opportunities from appointments"
msgstr "Membuat peluang dari appointment"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:5
msgid ""
"When creating a new appointment type in the **Appointments** application, "
"users have the option to create new *opportunities* with information from "
"new bookings. This option captures information from scheduled appointments "
"and creates opportunities in the **CRM** app."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat jenis appointment baru di aplikasi **Appointment**, pengguna "
"memiliki opsi untuk membuat *peluang* baru dengan informasi dari pemesanan "
"baru. Opsi ini menangkap informasi dari appointment yang dijadwalkan dan "
"membuat peluang di aplikasi **CRM**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:10
msgid ""
"This option is only available if the **CRM** application is installed on the "
"database."
msgstr "Opsi ini hanya tersedia jika aplikasi **CRM** diinstal pada database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:15
msgid ""
"Navigate to the **Appointments** app dashboard. Click :guilabel:`New` "
"to :doc:`create a new appointment type <../appointments>`. To edit an "
"existing appointment type, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Action` at the "
"far-right of the appointment line, to open the drop-down menu, then "
"click :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Buka Dashboard aplikasi **Appointment**. Klik :guilabel:`New` "
"untuk :doc:`membuat jenis appointment baru <../appointments>`. Untuk "
"mengedit jenis appointment yang ada, klik :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Action` "
"di ujung kanan baris appointment untuk membuka menu drop-down, kemudian "
"klik :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid "The edit button on an appointment type record."
msgstr "Tombol edit pada record jenis appointment."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:23
msgid ""
"On the appointment type record, click the :guilabel:`Options` tab, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Create Opportunities` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Pada record jenis appointment, klik tab :guilabel:`Options`, dan centang "
"kotak :guilabel:`Create Opportunities`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid "The options tab on an appointment type form."
msgstr "Tab opsi pada formulir jenis appointment."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:30
msgid "Add questions"
msgstr "Menambahkan pertanyaan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:32
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Questions` tab allows users to :ref:`add questions "
"<appointments/questions>` to the appointment booking page. When customers "
"are booking an appointment slot, they are prompted to answer these "
"questions. The information provided by customers is available in "
"the :ref:`new opportunity <appointments/new-opp>`. Adding questions to the "
"appointment type is optional. However, the additional information captured "
"by the questions can be useful later in the sales pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Questions` memungkinkan pengguna untuk :ref:`menambahkan "
"pertanyaan <appointments/questions>` ke halaman pemesanan appointment. "
"Ketika pelanggan memesan slot appointment, mereka diminta untuk menjawab "
"pertanyaan ini. Informasi yang diberikan oleh pelanggan tersedia "
"di :ref:`peluang baru <appointments/new-opp>`. Menambahkan pertanyaan ke "
"jenis appointment bersifat opsional. Namun, informasi tambahan yang "
"ditangkap oleh pertanyaan dapat berguna di kemudian hari dalam pipeline "
"penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:39
msgid ""
"A furniture company creates a new appointment type for sales demos. "
"Customers reserve time with salespeople to discuss their furniture and "
"design needs. However, because the time is limited to only thirty minute "
"increments, salespeople do not have the time to show all of the available "
"furniture styles in every call. They add questions to the appointment type "
"to prompt customers to provide additional information about the products and "
"services they are interested in. Not only does this help when preparing for "
"the demo, it also provides clarity further along in the sales process."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan furnitur membuat jenis appointment baru untuk demo "
"penjualan. Pelanggan memesan waktu dengan tenaga penjualan untuk membahas "
"kebutuhan furnitur dan desain mereka. Namun, karena waktunya terbatas hanya "
"tiga puluh menit, tenaga penjualan tidak memiliki waktu untuk menunjukkan "
"semua gaya furnitur yang tersedia di setiap panggilan. Mereka menambahkan "
"pertanyaan ke jenis appointment untuk meminta pelanggan memberikan informasi "
"tambahan tentang produk dan layanan yang mereka minati. Ini tidak hanya "
"membantu saat mempersiapkan demo, tetapi juga memberikan kejelasan lebih "
"lanjut dalam proses penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:0
msgid "An appointment booking form with custom questions."
msgstr "Formulir pemesanan appointment dengan pertanyaan khusus."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:53
msgid "Viewing the new opportunity"
msgstr "Melihat peluang baru"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:55
msgid ""
"To view opportunities created from appointments, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`CRM` app dashboard. If necessary, remove any filters "
"from the search bar. Then, click the Kanban card for the appropriate "
"opportunity to open it."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat peluang yang dibuat dari appointment, navigasikan ke dashboard "
"aplikasi :menuselection:`CRM`. Jika perlu, hapus filter apa pun dari bilah "
"pencarian. Kemudian, klik kartu Kanban untuk peluang yang sesuai untuk "
"membukanya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:59
msgid ""
"The contact information from the appointment is added to the opportunity "
"record. The answers the customer provided to the optional questions are "
"included in the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` tab. The scheduled appointment is "
"listed in the *Chatter* of the record, and can be edited from there."
msgstr ""
"Informasi kontak dari appointment ditambahkan ke catatan peluang. Jawaban "
"yang diberikan pelanggan terhadap pertanyaan opsional disertakan dalam "
"tab :guilabel:`Catatan Internal`. Appointment yang dijadwalkan terdaftar di "
"*Chatter* dari catatan, dan dapat diedit dari sana."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid ""
"The chatter of an opportunity in the CRM with the scheduled appointment "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Chatter dari peluang di CRM dengan informasi appointment yang dijadwalkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:67
msgid ""
"If an opportunity is created from a :ref:`resource based <appointments/"
"resources>` appointment type, the user who created the appointment type is "
"listed as the :guilabel:`Salesperson` for the opportunity. If it is created "
"from a user based appointment, the user the appointment is scheduled with is "
"assigned as the :guilabel:`Salesperson`."
msgstr ""
"Jika peluang dibuat dari tipe appointment :ref:`berbasis resource "
"<appointments/resources>`, user yang membuat tipe appointment terdaftar "
"sebagai :guilabel:`Salesperson` untuk peluang tersebut. Jika dibuat dari "
"appointment berbasis user, user yang dijadwalkan dengan appointment tersebut "
"ditugaskan sebagai :guilabel:`Salesperson`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:3
msgid "Google reserve integration"
msgstr "Integrasi Google Reserve"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:5
msgid ""
"Google Reserve lets customers book appointments directly from Google Search, "
"Google Maps, and the Google Assistant. By connecting Odoo **Appointments** "
"to Google Reserve, bookings are added directly into Odoo without customers "
"needing to visit the company website."
msgstr ""
"Google Reserve memungkinkan pelanggan memesan appointment langsung dari "
"Google Search, Google Maps, dan Google Assistant. Dengan menghubungkan "
"**Appointment** Odoo ke Google Reserve, pemesanan ditambahkan langsung ke "
"Odoo tanpa pelanggan perlu mengunjungi website perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:14
msgid ""
"First, navigate to the :guilabel:`Apps` application. Then, remove "
"the :guilabel:`Apps` filter from the search bar and type in `Google`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Install` on the :guilabel:`Appointment Google Reserve` "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, navigasikan ke aplikasi :guilabel:`Apps`. Kemudian, hapus "
"filter :guilabel:`Apps` dari bilah pencarian dan ketik `Google`. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Install` pada modul :guilabel:`Appointment Google Reserve`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:None
msgid "The Google Reserve module in the Odoo apps application."
msgstr "Modul Google Reserve dalam aplikasi apps Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:21
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to the :menuselection:`Appointments` application. Open an "
"existing appointment type, or click :guilabel:`New` to :ref:`create a new "
"one <appointments/configure>`. Then click the :guilabel:`Google Bookings` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, navigasikan ke aplikasi :menuselection:`Appointment`. Buka tipe "
"appointment yang ada, atau klik :guilabel:`New` untuk :ref:`membuat yang "
"baru <appointments/configure>`. Kemudian klik tab :guilabel:`Google "
"Bookings`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Google Reserve Merchant` field, and select an option "
"from the drop-down, or click :guilabel:`Create` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Create Google Reserve Merchant` form."
msgstr ""
"Klik field :guilabel:`Google Reserve Merchant`, dan pilih opsi dari drop-"
"down, atau klik :guilabel:`Create` untuk membuka formulir :guilabel:`Create "
"Google Reserve Merchant`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:28
msgid ""
"On the form, enter all required information. The business address **must** "
"match exactly what appears on Google Maps. Click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir, masukkan semua informasi yang diperlukan. Alamat bisnis "
"**harus** sesuai persis dengan yang muncul di Google Maps. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Save & Close`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:None
msgid "A create new google merchant form in the Appointments app."
msgstr "Formulir create new google merchant dalam aplikasi Appointment."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once the new merchant has been created, click :guilabel:`Synchronize with "
"Google Reserve`. The initial synchronization can take up to 24 hours to "
"propagate to Google's systems."
msgstr ""
"Setelah merchant baru dibuat, klik :guilabel:`Synchronize with Google "
"Reserve`. Sinkronisasi awal dapat memakan waktu hingga 24 jam untuk "
"dipropagasi ke sistem Google."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:38
msgid ""
"Ensure that the business address matches the Google Maps listing precisely, "
"including formatting and unit numbers. Mismatches may cause synchronization "
"to fail or prevent the listing from appearing on Google."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan alamat bisnis sesuai persis dengan listing Google Maps, termasuk "
"format dan nomor unit. Ketidakcocokan dapat menyebabkan sinkronisasi gagal "
"atau mencegah listing muncul di Google."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:5
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Kalender"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Calendar** is a scheduling app that allows users to integrate a "
"company's business flow into a single management platform. By integrating "
"with the other apps in Odoo's ecosystem, **Calendar** allows users to "
"schedule and organize meetings, schedule events, plan employee appraisals, "
"coordinate projects, and more."
msgstr ""
"**Kalender** Odoo adalah aplikasi penjadwalan yang memungkinkan user "
"mengintegrasikan alur bisnis perusahaan ke dalam satu platform manajemen. "
"Dengan integrasi dengan aplikasi lain dalam ekosistem Odoo, **Kalender** "
"memungkinkan user untuk menjadwalkan dan mengatur rapat, menjadwalkan acara, "
"merencanakan penilaian karyawan, mengoordinasikan project, dan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:12
msgid ""
"Upon opening the :menuselection:`Calendar app`, users have an overview of "
"their current meetings. The selected view option appears as "
"a :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, or :guilabel:`Year` "
"drop-down menu. Under the view options drop-down menu, users can also enable "
"or disable :guilabel:`Show weekends`."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuka :menuselection:`aplikasi Kalender`, user memiliki gambaran umum "
"tentang pertemuan mereka saat ini. Opsi tampilan yang dipilih muncul sebagai "
"menu drop-down :guilabel:`Hari`, :guilabel:`Minggu`, :guilabel:`Bulan`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Tahun`. Di bawah menu drop-down opsi tampilan, user juga "
"dapat mengaktifkan atau menonaktifkan :guilabel:`Tampilkan akhir pekan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Overview of Calendar app."
msgstr "Gambaran umum aplikasi Kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:21
msgid ""
"Depending on the selected view option, users can click the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"left` :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(left or right arrow)` buttons to "
"switch between days, weeks, etc., and switch back to the current day with "
"the :guilabel:`Today` button."
msgstr ""
"Bergantung pada opsi tampilan yang dipilih, user dapat mengklik "
"tombol :icon:`oi-arrow-left` :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(panah kiri "
"atau kanan)` untuk beralih antara hari, minggu, dll., dan beralih kembali ke "
"hari saat ini dengan tombol :guilabel:`Hari Ini`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:26
msgid "Sync third-party calendars"
msgstr "Sinkronkan kalender pihak ketiga"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:28
msgid ""
"Users can sync Odoo with existing :doc:`Outlook <calendar/outlook>` and/"
"or :doc:`Google <calendar/google>` calendars, by heading "
"to :menuselection:`Calendar app --> Configuration --> Settings`. From here, "
"enter :guilabel:`Client ID` and :guilabel:`Client Secret`. There is also an "
"option to pause synchronization by ticking the checkbox, or automating "
"synchronization by keeping it blank."
msgstr ""
"User dapat menyinkronkan Odoo dengan kalender :doc:`Outlook <calendar/"
"outlook>` dan/atau :doc:`Google <calendar/google>` yang ada, dengan menuju "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Kalender --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. Dari "
"sini, masukkan :guilabel:`ID Klien` dan :guilabel:`Rahasia Klien`. Ada juga "
"opsi untuk menjeda sinkronisasi dengan mencentang kotak centang, atau "
"mengotomatiskan sinkronisasi dengan membiarkannya kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once the desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save` before "
"moving on."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, klik :guilabel:`Save` sebelum "
"melanjutkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:36
msgid ""
"Events created in synced calendars automatically appear across the "
"integrated platforms."
msgstr ""
"Acara yang dibuat di kalender yang disinkronkan secara otomatis muncul di "
"semua platform yang terintegrasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:39
msgid ":doc:`Synchronize Outlook calendar with Odoo <calendar/outlook>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Sinkronkan kalender Outlook dengan Odoo <calendar/outlook>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:40
msgid ":doc:`Synchronize Google calendar with Odoo <calendar/google>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Sinkronkan kalender Google dengan Odoo <calendar/google>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:43
msgid "Create activities from chatter"
msgstr "Buat aktivitas dari chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:45
msgid ""
"Instantly create new meetings anywhere in Odoo through an individual "
"record's chatter, like in a **CRM** opportunity card or task in the "
"**Project** app."
msgstr ""
"Buat rapat baru secara instan di mana saja di Odoo melalui chatter record "
"individual, seperti di kartu peluang **CRM** atau task di aplikasi "
"**Project**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:48
msgid ""
"From the chatter, click on the :guilabel:`Activity` button. In "
"the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up window, select the "
"desired :guilabel:`Activity Type`, which populates a set of buttons, "
"depending on the activity."
msgstr ""
"Dari chatter, klik tombol :guilabel:`Activity`. Di jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Schedule Activity`, pilih :guilabel:`Activity Type` yang "
"diinginkan, yang akan menampilkan satu set tombol, tergantung pada "
"aktivitasnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:52
msgid ""
"Activities that involve other schedules, like :guilabel:`Meeting` "
"or :guilabel:`Call for Demo`, link to the **Calendar** app. Select one of "
"these activities to link to the **Calendar** app, then "
"hit :guilabel:`Schedule` to navigate back to the app."
msgstr ""
"Aktivitas yang melibatkan jadwal lain, seperti :guilabel:`Meeting` "
"atau :guilabel:`Call for Demo`, terhubung ke aplikasi **Kalender**. Pilih "
"salah satu aktivitas ini untuk terhubung ke aplikasi **Kalender**, lalu "
"tekan :guilabel:`Schedule` untuk kembali ke aplikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:57
msgid ":doc:`Schedule activities in Odoo <../essentials/activities>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Jadwalkan aktivitas di Odoo <../essentials/activities>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:60
msgid "Plan an event"
msgstr "Rencanakan acara"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:62
msgid ""
"To put an event on the calendar, open the :menuselection:`Calendar app`, and "
"click into the target date. On the :guilabel:`New Event` pop-up window that "
"appears, start by adding the event title."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menempatkan acara di kalender, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Kalender`, dan klik tanggal target. Pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Acara "
"Baru` yang muncul, mulai dengan menambahkan judul acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Schedule an event window on Calendar app."
msgstr "Jendela jadwal acara di aplikasi Kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:68
msgid ""
"The target date auto-populates in the :guilabel:`Start` field. This can be "
"changed by clicking into the date section, and selecting a date from the "
"calendar. For multi-day events, select the end date in the second field, "
"then click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr ""
"Tanggal target secara otomatis terisi di kolom :guilabel:`Mulai`. Ini dapat "
"diubah dengan mengklik bagian tanggal, dan memilih tanggal dari kalender. "
"Untuk acara multi-hari, pilih tanggal akhir di kolom kedua, kemudian "
"klik :guilabel:`Terapkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:72
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`All Day` checkbox if there is no specific start or end "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak centang :guilabel:`Sepanjang Hari` jika tidak ada waktu mulai "
"atau akhir tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:74
msgid ""
"For events with specific start and stop times, ensure the :guilabel:`All "
"Day` checkbox is unticked to enable time selection. With the :guilabel:`All "
"Day` checkbox unticked, time selections appear in the :guilabel:`Start` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk acara dengan waktu mulai dan berhenti yang spesifik, pastikan kotak "
"centang :guilabel:`All Day` tidak dicentang untuk mengaktifkan pemilihan "
"waktu. Dengan kotak centang :guilabel:`All Day` tidak dicentang, pilihan "
"waktu muncul di kolom :guilabel:`Start`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:78
msgid ""
"The signed-in user auto-populates as the first attendee. "
"Additional :guilabel:`Attendees` can be added or created from here, as well."
msgstr ""
"User yang masuk secara otomatis terisi sebagai peserta "
"pertama. :guilabel:`Attendees` tambahan dapat ditambahkan atau dibuat dari "
"sini juga."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:81
msgid ""
"For virtual meetings, copy and paste the URL into the space provided in "
"the :guilabel:`Videocall URL` field. Or, click :icon:`fa-"
"plus` :guilabel:`Video` to create a link."
msgstr ""
"Untuk rapat virtual, salin dan tempel URL ke dalam ruang yang disediakan di "
"field :guilabel:`Videocall URL`. Atau, klik :icon:`fa-"
"plus` :guilabel:`Video` untuk membuat link."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:84
msgid ""
"Next, either create the event by clicking :guilabel:`Save & Close`, or "
"select :guilabel:`More Options` to further configure the event."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, buat acara dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Save & Close`, atau "
"pilih :guilabel:`More Options` untuk mengonfigurasi acara lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:88
msgid ""
"Once the event is created, users can click into the virtual meeting directly "
"from the calendar event to access more configuration options."
msgstr ""
"Setelah acara dibuat, user dapat mengklik langsung ke pertemuan virtual dari "
"acara kalender untuk mengakses lebih banyak opsi konfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "The full event form for a new calendar event."
msgstr "Formulir acara lengkap untuk acara kalender baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:94
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Description` field allows users to add additional information "
"and details about the meeting."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Description` memungkinkan user menambahkan informasi dan "
"detail tambahan tentang pertemuan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:97
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`More Options` to navigate to the meeting form, which "
"provides additional configurations for the event:"
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`More Options` untuk membuka formulir pertemuan, yang "
"menyediakan konfigurasi tambahan untuk acara:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:100
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duration`: Define the length of the meeting in :guilabel:`hours`, "
"or toggle the :guilabel:`All Day` switch."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Duration`: Tentukan durasi pertemuan dalam :guilabel:`hours`, "
"atau aktifkan tombol :guilabel:`All Day`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Organizer`: This is defaulted to the current Odoo user. Select a "
"new one from existing users, or create and edit a new user."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Organizer`: Ini default ke user Odoo saat ini. Pilih yang baru "
"dari user yang ada, atau buat dan edit user baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Add tags to the event, like `Customer Meeting` or "
"`Internal Meeting`. These can be searched and filtered in the **Calendar** "
"app when organizing multiple events."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Tambahkan tag ke acara, seperti `Customer Meeting` atau "
"`Internal Meeting`. Ini dapat dicari dan difilter di aplikasi **Kalender** "
"saat mengatur beberapa acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Calendar description`: Add additional information or details "
"about the meeting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Calendar description`: Tambahkan informasi atau detail tambahan "
"tentang rapat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminders`: Select notification options to send to attendees. "
"Choose a default notification, or configure new reminders."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Reminders`: Pilih opsi notifikasi untuk dikirim ke peserta. Pilih "
"notifikasi default, atau konfigurasikan pengingat baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recurrent`: Tick the checkbox to create a recurring meeting. Once "
"selected, this opens new fields:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Recurrent`: Centang kotak centang untuk membuat pertemuan "
"berulang. Setelah dipilih, ini membuka kolom baru:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Repeat`: Select the recurring period of this meeting. Depending "
"on what type of recurrence has been selected, a subsequent field appears, in "
"which users can indicate when the meeting should recur. For example, "
"if :guilabel:`Monthly` is selected as the :guilabel:`Repeat` option, a new "
"field appears, in which the user decides on what :guilabel:`Day of Month` "
"the meeting should recur."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Repeat`: Pilih periode berulang pertemuan ini. Tergantung pada "
"jenis pengulangan yang dipilih, kolom berikutnya muncul, di mana user dapat "
"menunjukkan kapan pertemuan harus berulang. Misalnya, "
"jika :guilabel:`Monthly` dipilih sebagai opsi :guilabel:`Repeat`, kolom baru "
"muncul, di mana user memutuskan pada :guilabel:`Day of Month` berapa "
"pertemuan harus berulang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Until`: Select the limited :guilabel:`Number of repetitions` this "
"meeting should recur, the :guilabel:`End date` of when the recurrences "
"should stop, or if the meetings should recur :guilabel:`Forever`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Until`: Pilih :guilabel:`Number of repetitions` terbatas "
"pertemuan ini harus berulang, :guilabel:`End date` kapan pengulangan harus "
"berhenti, atau jika pertemuan harus berulang :guilabel:`Forever`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Timezone`: Select the timezone for which this meeting time is "
"specified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Timezone`: Pilih zona waktu untuk waktu pertemuan ini ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:123
msgid "Coordinate with teams' availability"
msgstr "Koordinasikan dengan ketersediaan tim"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:125
msgid ""
"When scheduling an event for multiple users, on the **Calendar** app "
"dashboard, tick the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Attendees` to view team "
"members' availability. Tick (or untick) the checkbox next to listed users to "
"show (or hide) individual calendars."
msgstr ""
"Saat menjadwalkan acara untuk beberapa user, pada Dashboard aplikasi "
"**Kalender**, centang kotak centang di sebelah :guilabel:`Attendees` untuk "
"melihat ketersediaan anggota tim. Centang (atau hapus centang) kotak centang "
"di sebelah user yang terdaftar untuk menampilkan (atau menyembunyikan) "
"kalender individual."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "View of Attendees section on Calendar app."
msgstr "Tampilan bagian Peserta di aplikasi Kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:135
msgid "Share Availabilities"
msgstr "Bagikan Ketersediaan Anda"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:137
msgid ""
"On the **Calendar** app main dashboard, click the :guilabel:`Share` button "
"at the top of the page, then select :guilabel:`Specific Slots` from the drop-"
"down. Next, click and drag to select the available times and dates on the "
"calendar to add them as options in the invitation."
msgstr ""
"Di dashboard utama aplikasi **Kalender**, klik tombol :guilabel:`Share` di "
"bagian atas halaman, lalu pilih :guilabel:`Specific Slots` dari drop-down. "
"Selanjutnya, klik dan seret untuk memilih waktu dan tanggal yang tersedia di "
"kalender untuk menambahkannya sebagai opsi dalam undangan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Selecting availabilites on the Calendar dashboard."
msgstr "Memilih ketersediaan di dashboard Kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:145
msgid ""
"To remove a selected time range, hover over the availability to click "
"the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus rentang waktu yang dipilih, arahkan kursor ke ketersediaan "
"untuk mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:148
msgid ""
"Once availability has been selected, click :icon:`fa-"
"clipboard` :guilabel:`Copy Link` to copy a sharable link to the clipboard. "
"Or, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Configure` icon button to navigate to "
"the associated appointment."
msgstr ""
"Setelah ketersediaan dipilih, klik :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`Copy "
"Link` untuk menyalin link yang dapat dibagikan ke clipboard. Atau, klik "
"tombol ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Configure` untuk menavigasi ke "
"appointment yang terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Share availability window on Calendar app."
msgstr "Jendela berbagi ketersediaan di aplikasi Kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:155
msgid ""
"On the **Share Availabilities** form, enter an :guilabel:`Appointment "
"Title`. Confirm the correct user is selected in the :guilabel:`Users` field. "
"To add a meeting room to the appointment, click the :guilabel:`Location` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Di formulir **Share Availabilities**, masukkan :guilabel:`Appointment "
"Title`. Konfirmasi user yang benar dipilih di field :guilabel:`Users`. Untuk "
"menambahkan ruang rapat ke appointment, klik field :guilabel:`Location`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:160
msgid ""
"If nothing is selected in the :guilabel:`Location` field, the appointment "
"defaults to an *Online Meeting*."
msgstr ""
"Jika tidak ada yang dipilih di field :guilabel:`Location`, appointment "
"default ke *Online Meeting*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Video Link` field, select the type of video call link that "
"will be used for the generated appointments. If this field is left blank, no "
"meeting URLs will be created."
msgstr ""
"Di field :guilabel:`Video Link`, pilih jenis link panggilan video yang akan "
"digunakan untuk appointment yang dibuat. Jika field ini dibiarkan kosong, "
"tidak ada URL rapat yang akan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:166
msgid ""
"To allow attendees to invite others to the event, tick the :guilabel:`Allow "
"invitations` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memungkinkan peserta mengundang orang lain ke acara, centang "
"kotak :guilabel:`Allow invitations`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:168
msgid ""
"Add a message in the :guilabel:`Introduction Message` field. This is used as "
"a description for the event. Add a message to the :guilabel:`Extra Message "
"on Confirmation` field to be displayed after the appointment is booked."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan pesan di field :guilabel:`Introduction Message`. Ini digunakan "
"sebagai deskripsi untuk acara. Tambahkan pesan ke field :guilabel:`Extra "
"Message on Confirmation` untuk ditampilkan setelah appointment dipesan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:172
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`Save & Copy Link`. To futher customize "
"the appointment, click the :icon:`fa-expand` :guilabel:`(expand)` icon at "
"the top of the pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Klik :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`Save & Copy Link`. Untuk menyesuaikan "
"appointment lebih lanjut, klik ikon :icon:`fa-expand` :guilabel:`(expand)` "
"di bagian atas jendela pop-up."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:175
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Preview` button to see how the appointment link looks "
"for attendees."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :guilabel:`Preview` untuk melihat tampilan tautan appointment "
"bagi peserta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:177
msgid "Optionally, configure the following tabs:"
msgstr "Secara opsional, konfigurasikan tab berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:179
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-schedule`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-schedule`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:180
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-questions`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-questions`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:181
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-messages`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-messages`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:182
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-options`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-options`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:184
msgid ""
"Once the configurations are finished, click the :guilabel:`Share` button to "
"generate a link to send directly, or click :guilabel:`Publish` to publish "
"the appointment selection on the connected Odoo website."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi selesai, klik tombol :guilabel:`Share` untuk membuat "
"tautan yang dapat dikirim langsung, atau klik :guilabel:`Publish` untuk "
"mempublikasikan pilihan appointment di Website Odoo yang terhubung."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:191
msgid "Availabilites tab"
msgstr "Tab Ketersediaan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:193
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Availabilites` tab of the appointment form, time slots can "
"be managed. The target date and time populate as the first time slots."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Availabilites` pada formulir appointment, slot waktu dapat "
"dikelola. Tanggal dan waktu target terisi sebagai slot waktu pertama."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:196
msgid ""
"To add a new time slot, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. Click into the new "
"blank space under the :guilabel:`From` field, then select and enter the new "
"target start date and time, respectively. Repeat under the new blank space "
"under :guilabel:`To` to select and enter the new target end date and time."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan slot waktu baru, klik :guilabel:`Add a line`. Klik ke "
"dalam ruang kosong baru di bawah kolom :guilabel:`From`, kemudian pilih dan "
"masukkan tanggal dan waktu mulai target yang baru. Ulangi di bawah ruang "
"kosong baru di bawah :guilabel:`To` untuk memilih dan memasukkan tanggal dan "
"waktu selesai target yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:206
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Questions` tab, add questions for the attendee to answer "
"when confirming their meeting. Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to configure "
"a :guilabel:`Question`. Then select a :guilabel:`Question Type`, optionally "
"add a :guilabel:`Placeholder` answer, and choose whether it is meeting. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to configure a :guilabel:`Question`. Then "
"select an :guilabel:`Answer Type`, optionally add a "
"placeholder :guilabel:`Answer`, and choose whether it "
"is :guilabel:`Mandatory`."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Questions`, tambahkan pertanyaan untuk dijawab peserta "
"saat mengonfirmasi pertemuan mereka. Klik :guilabel:`Add a line` untuk "
"mengonfigurasi :guilabel:`Question`. Kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Question "
"Type`, opsional tambahkan jawaban :guilabel:`Placeholder`, dan pilih apakah "
"wajib diisi. Klik :guilabel:`Add a line` untuk "
"mengonfigurasi :guilabel:`Question`. Kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Answer Type`, "
"opsional tambahkan :guilabel:`Answer` placeholder, dan pilih "
"apakah :guilabel:`Mandatory`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:213
msgid ""
"To learn how to create more comprehensive questionnaires, head to the "
"**Survey** app documentation on :doc:`creating and configuring data-"
"capturing questions <../marketing/surveys/questions>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mempelajari cara membuat kuesioner yang lebih komprehensif, kunjungi "
"dokumentasi aplikasi **Survey** tentang :doc:`membuat dan mengonfigurasi "
"pertanyaan pengumpulan data <../marketing/surveys/questions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:219
msgid "Communication tab"
msgstr "Tab Komunikasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:221
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Introduction Page` field of the :guilabel:`Communication` "
"tab, add additional meeting information to appear on the invitation."
msgstr ""
"Di kolom :guilabel:`Introduction Page` pada tab :guilabel:`Communication`, "
"tambahkan informasi pertemuan tambahan untuk ditampilkan pada undangan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:224
msgid ""
"Information added to the :guilabel:`Confirmation Page` field appears once "
"the meeting is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Informasi yang ditambahkan ke kolom :guilabel:`Confirmation Page` muncul "
"setelah pertemuan dikonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:226
msgid ""
"Under the *Emails & SMS* heading, click the :guilabel:`Reminders` field to "
"add one or more methods of reminding attendees about the appointment. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Booking Email` field, and :guilabel:`Cancellation Email` "
"field, select an email template to be sent to attendees when booking or "
"cancelling meetings."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah judul *Emails & SMS*, klik kolom :guilabel:`Reminders` untuk "
"menambahkan satu atau lebih metode mengingatkan peserta tentang appointment. "
"Di bawah kolom :guilabel:`Booking Email`, dan kolom :guilabel:`Cancellation "
"Email`, pilih template email yang akan dikirim ke peserta saat memesan atau "
"membatalkan pertemuan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:236
msgid "The :guilabel:`Options` tab provides additional configurations:"
msgstr "Tab :guilabel:`Options` menyediakan konfigurasi tambahan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:238
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow invitations`: Tick the checkbox to allow attendees to "
"invite guests."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Allow invitations`: Centang kotak untuk mengizinkan peserta "
"mengundang tamu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Auto Confirm`: Only shown if :guilabel:`Resources` has been "
"selected in the :guilabel:`Availability On` field. Tick the checkbox and "
"enter a maximum percentage of the selected resource(s)' total capacity to "
"create a manual confirmation requirement to finalize the meeting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Auto Confirm`: Hanya ditampilkan jika :guilabel:`Resources` telah "
"dipilih di kolom :guilabel:`Availability On`. Centang kotak dan masukkan "
"persentase maksimum dari total kapasitas sumber daya yang dipilih untuk "
"membuat persyaratan konfirmasi manual guna menyelesaikan pertemuan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:243
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Display pictures`: Tick the checkbox to display user or resource "
"images across the entire booking flow."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Display pictures`: Centang kotak untuk menampilkan gambar user "
"atau sumber daya di seluruh alur pemesanan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:245
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create Opportunity`: When this is selected, each scheduled "
"appointment creates a new **CRM** opportunity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Create Opportunity`: Ketika ini dipilih, setiap appointment yang "
"dijadwalkan membuat peluang **CRM** baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Up-front Payment`: Tick the checkbox to require users to pay "
"before confirming their booking. Once this is ticked, a link appears "
"to :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Payment Providers`, which "
"enables online payments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Up-front Payment`: Centang kotak untuk mewajibkan user membayar "
"sebelum mengonfirmasi booking mereka. Setelah dicentang, sebuah tautan "
"muncul ke :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Payment Providers`, "
"yang memungkinkan pembayaran online."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:250
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Website`: Specify which website this meeting invitation will be "
"published on."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Website`: Tentukan website mana undangan meeting ini akan "
"dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:251
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: Select :guilabel:`Weekly` or :guilabel:`Flexible` "
"scheduling."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: Pilih penjadwalan :guilabel:`Weekly` "
"atau :guilabel:`Flexible`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:252
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Bookings`: set a minimum hour window to ensure appointments "
"are confirmed a specified amount of time in advance. For example, set "
"`01:00` to require attendees to confirm at least one hour before their "
"appointment time."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Allow Bookings`: tetapkan jendela jam minimum untuk memastikan "
"appointment dikonfirmasi dalam jumlah waktu tertentu sebelumnya. Misalnya, "
"tetapkan `01:00` untuk mewajibkan peserta mengonfirmasi setidaknya satu jam "
"sebelum waktu appointment mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:255
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cancellation`: set a maximum hour window before the appointment "
"that attendees are able to cancel."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cancellation`: tetapkan jendela jam maksimum sebelum appointment "
"yang memungkinkan peserta untuk membatalkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:257
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Timezone`: This defaults to the company's timezone selected in "
"the **Settings** app. To change the timezone, select the desired option from "
"the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Timezone`: Secara default menggunakan timezone perusahaan yang "
"dipilih di aplikasi **Settings**. Untuk mengubah timezone, pilih opsi yang "
"diinginkan dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:3
msgid "Google Calendar synchronization"
msgstr "Sinkronisasi Kalender Google"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:5
msgid ""
"Synchronize Google Calendar with Odoo to see and manage meetings from both "
"platforms (updates go in both directions). This integration helps organize "
"schedules, so a meeting is never missed."
msgstr ""
"Sinkronisasikan Kalender Google dengan Odoo untuk melihat dan mengelola "
"meeting dari kedua platform (pembaruan berjalan dua arah). Integrasi ini "
"membantu mengatur jadwal, sehingga tidak ada meeting yang terlewat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`/applications/general/users/google`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/general/users/google`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:13
msgid "Setup in Google"
msgstr "Pengaturan di Google"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:16
msgid "Select (or create) a project"
msgstr "Pilih (atau buat) sebuah project"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:18
msgid ""
"Create a new Google API project and enable the Google Calendar API. First, "
"go to the `Google API Console <https://console.developers.google.com>`_ and "
"log into the Google account."
msgstr ""
"Buat project Google API baru dan aktifkan Google Calendar API. Pertama, "
"kunjungi `Google API Console <https://console.developers.google.com>`_ dan "
"login ke akun Google."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:22
msgid ""
"If this is the first time visiting this page, Google will prompt the user to "
"enter a country and agree to the Terms of Service. Select a country from the "
"drop-down list and agree to the :abbr:`ToS (Terms of Service)`."
msgstr ""
"Jika ini adalah kunjungan pertama ke halaman ini, Google akan meminta user "
"untuk memasukkan negara dan menyetujui Terms of Service. Pilih negara dari "
"daftar drop-down dan setujui :abbr:`ToS (Terms of Service)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:26
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Select a project` and select (or create) an API "
"project to configure OAuth in, and store credentials. Click :guilabel:`New "
"Project`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Select a project` dan pilih (atau buat) project "
"API untuk mengonfigurasi OAuth di dalamnya, dan menyimpan kredensial. "
"Klik :guilabel:`New Project`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Create a new API project to store credentials."
msgstr "Buat project API baru untuk menyimpan kredensial."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:32
msgid ""
"Give the API project a clear name, like `Odoo Sync`, so it can be "
"identified. Then click the :guilabel:`Create` button."
msgstr ""
"Berikan nama yang jelas pada project API, seperti `Odoo Sync`, agar dapat "
"diidentifikasi. Kemudian klik tombol :guilabel:`Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:36
msgid "Enable Google calendar API"
msgstr "Aktifkan Google calendar API"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:38
msgid ""
"Now, click on :guilabel:`Enabled APIs and Services` in the left menu. "
"Select :guilabel:`Enabled APIs and Services` again if the :guilabel:`Search "
"bar` does not appear."
msgstr ""
"Sekarang, klik :guilabel:`Enabled APIs and Services` di menu sebelah kiri. "
"Pilih :guilabel:`Enabled APIs and Services` lagi jika :guilabel:`Search bar` "
"tidak muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Enable APIs and Services on the API Project."
msgstr "Aktifkan APIs and Services pada Project API."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:44
msgid ""
"After that, search for `Google Calendar API` using the search bar and "
"select :guilabel:`Google Calendar API` from the search results. "
"Click :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah itu, cari `Google Calendar API` menggunakan search bar dan "
"pilih :guilabel:`Google Calendar API` dari hasil pencarian. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Enable`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Enable the Google Calendar API."
msgstr "Aktifkan Google Calendar API."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:51
msgid "OAuth consent screen"
msgstr "Layar persetujuan OAuth"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:53
msgid ""
"Now that the API project has been created, OAuth should be configured. To do "
"that, click on :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen` in the left menu, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Get started` button."
msgstr ""
"Setelah project API dibuat, OAuth harus dikonfigurasi. Untuk melakukannya, "
"klik :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen` di menu sebelah kiri, lalu klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Get started`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:57
msgid ""
"*Personal* Gmail Accounts are only allowed to be **External** User Type, "
"which means Google may require an approval, or for *Scopes* to be added on. "
"However, using a *Google WorkSpace* account allows for **Internal** User "
"Type to be used."
msgstr ""
"Akun Gmail *Personal* hanya diizinkan untuk jenis User **External**, yang "
"berarti Google mungkin memerlukan persetujuan, atau untuk menambahkan "
"*Scopes*. Namun, menggunakan akun *Google WorkSpace* memungkinkan jenis User "
"**Internal** untuk digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:61
msgid ""
"Note, as well, that while the API connection is in the *External* testing "
"mode, then no approval is necessary from Google. User limits in this testing "
"mode is set to 100 users."
msgstr ""
"Perhatikan juga, bahwa selama koneksi API dalam mode pengujian *External*, "
"maka tidak diperlukan persetujuan dari Google. Batas user dalam mode "
"pengujian ini ditetapkan menjadi 100 user."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:64
msgid "Follow the proceeding steps, in order:"
msgstr "Ikuti langkah-langkah berikut, secara berurutan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:66
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`App Information`, type `Odoo` in the :guilabel:`App name` "
"field, then enter the email address for the :guilabel:`User support email` "
"field and click the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"Di :guilabel:`App Information`, ketik `Odoo` di kolom :guilabel:`App name`, "
"lalu masukkan alamat email untuk kolom :guilabel:`User support email` dan "
"klik tombol :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:68
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Audience`, select :guilabel:`External`, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"Di :guilabel:`Audience`, pilih :guilabel:`External`, lalu klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:69
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Contact Information`, enter the email again, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"Di :guilabel:`Contact Information`, masukkan email lagi, lalu klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:71
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Finish`, tick the checkbox to agree to :guilabel:`Google API "
"Services: User Policy.` For the last step, click the :guilabel:`Create` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Di :guilabel:`Finish`, centang kotak untuk menyetujui :guilabel:`Google API "
"Services: User Policy.` Untuk langkah terakhir, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:75
msgid "Authorized domain setup"
msgstr "Pengaturan domain yang diotorisasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:77
msgid ""
"Next, any domains set to appear on the consent screen or in an OAuth "
"client's configuration must be pre-registered. To do so, navigate "
"to :guilabel:`Branding` in the left menu. In the :guilabel:`Authorized "
"domains` section, click the :guilabel:`Add domain` button to create a field "
"to enter an authorized domain. Enter a domain, such as `odoo.com`, then "
"click the :guilabel:`Save` button at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, semua domain yang diatur untuk muncul di layar persetujuan atau "
"dalam konfigurasi klien OAuth harus didaftarkan terlebih dahulu. Untuk "
"melakukannya, navigasikan ke :guilabel:`Branding` di menu sebelah kiri. Di "
"bagian :guilabel:`Authorized domains`, klik tombol :guilabel:`Add domain` "
"untuk membuat kolom untuk memasukkan domain yang diotorisasi. Masukkan "
"domain, seperti `odoo.com`, lalu klik tombol :guilabel:`Save` di bagian "
"bawah halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:84
msgid "Test users"
msgstr "User uji coba"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:86
msgid ""
"To give users the ability to sync with personal Gmail accounts, they must be "
"set as a test user. Setup test users by going to :guilabel:`Audience` in the "
"left-side menu and clicking the :guilabel:`Add users` button in "
"the :guilabel:`Test users` section. Enter any desired user emails, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Save` button."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memberikan user kemampuan sinkronisasi dengan akun Gmail pribadi, "
"mereka harus diatur sebagai test user. Atur test user dengan "
"membuka :guilabel:`Audience` di menu sisi kiri dan klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Add users` di bagian :guilabel:`Test users`. Masukkan "
"email user yang diinginkan, lalu klik tombol :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:92
msgid "Create credentials"
msgstr "Buat kredensial"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:94
msgid ""
"The *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* are both needed to connect Google "
"Calendar to Odoo. This is the last step in the Google console. Begin by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Clients` in the left menu. Then, click :guilabel:`Create "
"Credentials`, and select :guilabel:`OAuth client ID`, Google will open a "
"guide to create credentials."
msgstr ""
"*Client ID* dan *Client Secret* keduanya diperlukan untuk menghubungkan "
"Google Calendar ke Odoo. Ini adalah langkah terakhir di konsol Google. Mulai "
"dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Clients` di menu kiri. Kemudian, "
"klik :guilabel:`Create Credentials`, dan pilih :guilabel:`OAuth client ID`, "
"Google akan membuka panduan untuk membuat kredensial."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:99
msgid ""
"Under :menuselection:`Create OAuth Client ID`, select :guilabel:`Website "
"application` for the :guilabel:`Application Type` field, and type `My Odoo "
"Database` for the :guilabel:`Name`."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah :menuselection:`Create OAuth Client ID`, pilih :guilabel:`Website "
"application` untuk kolom :guilabel:`Application Type`, dan ketik `My Odoo "
"Database` untuk :guilabel:`Name`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:102
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Authorized JavaScript Origins` section, "
"click :guilabel:`+ Add URI` and type the company's Odoo full :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)` address."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Authorized JavaScript Origins`, klik :guilabel:`+ "
"Add URI` dan ketik alamat :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` Odoo "
"lengkap perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:106
msgid ""
"When entering the *Authorized JavaScript Origins*, the exact URL of the Odoo "
"database must be used."
msgstr ""
"Saat memasukkan *Authorized JavaScript Origins*, URL yang tepat dari "
"database Odoo harus digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:109
msgid ""
"If the database is accessible through both an `.odoo.com` subdomain and a "
"custom domain, the custom domain configured as the primary domain should be "
"used. The `.odoo.com` subdomain may not work correctly in all cases and can "
"result in authentication errors."
msgstr ""
"Jika database dapat diakses melalui subdomain `.odoo.com` dan domain khusus, "
"domain khusus yang dikonfigurasi sebagai domain utama harus digunakan. "
"Subdomain `.odoo.com` mungkin tidak berfungsi dengan benar dalam semua kasus "
"dan dapat menghasilkan kesalahan autentikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:113
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs` section, click :guilabel:`+ "
"Add URI` and type the company's Odoo :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` "
"address followed by `/google_account/authentication`. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs`, klik :guilabel:`+ Add "
"URI` dan ketik alamat :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` Odoo perusahaan "
"diikuti dengan `/google_account/authentication`. Terakhir, "
"klik :guilabel:`Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Add the authorized JavaScript origins and the authorized redirect URIs."
msgstr "Tambahkan authorized JavaScript origins dan authorized redirect URIs."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:120
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Client ID` and :guilabel:`Client Secret` will appear, save "
"these somewhere safe."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Client ID` dan :guilabel:`Client Secret` akan muncul, simpan di "
"tempat yang aman."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:123
msgid "Setup in Odoo"
msgstr "Pengaturan di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:125
msgid ""
"Once the *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* are located, open the Odoo "
"database and go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Calendar` to find "
"the :guilabel:`Google Calendar` feature. Tick the checkbox "
"labeled :guilabel:`Google Calendar`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah *Client ID* dan *Client Secret* ditemukan, buka database Odoo dan "
"buka :menuselection:`Settings --> Calendar` untuk menemukan "
"fitur :guilabel:`Google Calendar`. Centang kotak berlabel :guilabel:`Google "
"Calendar`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "The Google Calendar checkbox in General Settings."
msgstr "Kotak centang Google Calendar di General Settings."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:132
msgid ""
"Next, copy and paste the *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* from the Google "
"Calendar API credentials page into their respective fields below "
"the :guilabel:`Google Calendar` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, salin dan tempel *Client ID* dan *Client Secret* dari halaman "
"kredensial Google Calendar API ke kolom masing-masing di bawah kotak "
"centang :guilabel:`Google Calendar`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:137
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Pause Synchronization` checkbox to temporarily pause "
"events from being updated. This allows for testing and troubleshooting "
"without removing credentials or uninstalling the synchronization. To resume "
"the sync, clear the checkbox and save."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak :guilabel:`Pause Synchronization` untuk menghentikan sementara "
"pembaruan acara. Ini memungkinkan pengujian dan troubleshooting tanpa "
"menghapus kredensial atau uninstall sinkronisasi. Untuk melanjutkan "
"sinkronisasi, hapus centang dan simpan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:142
msgid "Sync calendar in Odoo"
msgstr "Sinkronkan kalender di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:144
msgid ""
"Finally, open the :menuselection:`Calendar` app in Odoo and click "
"the :guilabel:`Google` sync button to sync Google Calendar with Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, buka aplikasi :menuselection:`Kalender` di Odoo dan klik tombol "
"sinkronisasi :guilabel:`Google` untuk menyinkronkan Google Kalender dengan "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid ""
"Click the Google sync button in Odoo Calendar to sync Google Calendar with "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol sinkronisasi Google di Odoo Calendar untuk menyinkronkan Google "
"Calendar dengan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:151
msgid ""
"When syncing Google Calendar with Odoo for the first time, the page will "
"redirect to the Google Account. From there, select the :guilabel:`Email "
"Account` that should have access, then select :guilabel:`Continue` (should "
"the app be unverified), and finally select :guilabel:`Continue` (to give "
"permission for the transfer of data)."
msgstr ""
"Saat menyinkronkan Google Calendar dengan Odoo untuk pertama kalinya, "
"halaman akan dialihkan ke Google Account. Dari sana, pilih :guilabel:`Email "
"Account` yang harus memiliki akses, kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Continue` "
"(jika aplikasi tidak terverifikasi), dan terakhir pilih :guilabel:`Continue` "
"(untuk memberikan izin transfer data)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Give Odoo permission to access Google Calendar."
msgstr "Berikan izin Odoo untuk mengakses Google Calendar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:159
msgid "Now, Odoo Calendar is successfully synced with Google Calendar!"
msgstr "Sekarang, Odoo Calendar berhasil disinkronkan dengan Google Calendar!"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:162
msgid ""
"Odoo highly recommends testing the Google calendar synchronization on a test "
"database and a test email address (that is not used for any other purpose) "
"before attempting to sync the desired Google Calendar with the user's "
"production database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo sangat merekomendasikan untuk menguji sinkronisasi Google calendar di "
"database test dan alamat email test (yang tidak digunakan untuk tujuan lain) "
"sebelum mencoba menyinkronkan Google Calendar yang diinginkan dengan "
"database produksi user."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:166
msgid "Once a user synchronizes their Google calendar with the Odoo calendar:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah user menyinkronkan Google calendar mereka dengan Odoo calendar:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:168
msgid ""
"Creating an event in Odoo causes Google to send an invitation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Membuat acara di Odoo menyebabkan Google mengirimkan undangan ke semua "
"peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:169
msgid ""
"Deleting an event in Odoo causes Google to send a cancellation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus acara di Odoo menyebabkan Google mengirimkan pembatalan ke semua "
"peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:170
msgid ""
"Adding a contact to an event causes Google to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan kontak ke acara menyebabkan Google mengirimkan undangan ke semua "
"peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:171
msgid ""
"Removing a contact from an event causes Google to send a cancellation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus kontak dari acara menyebabkan Google mengirimkan pembatalan ke "
"semua peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:173
msgid ""
"Events can be created in *Google Calendar* without sending a notification by "
"selecting :guilabel:`Don't Send` when prompted to send invitation emails."
msgstr ""
"Acara dapat dibuat di *Google Calendar* tanpa mengirim notifikasi dengan "
"memilih :guilabel:`Don't Send` saat diminta untuk mengirim email undangan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:177
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:210
msgid "Troubleshoot sync"
msgstr "Memecahkan masalah sinkronisasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:179
msgid ""
"There may be times when the *Google Calendar* account does not sync "
"correctly with Odoo. Sync issues can be seen in the database logs."
msgstr ""
"Mungkin ada saat ketika akun *Google Calendar* tidak sinkron dengan benar "
"dengan Odoo. Masalah sinkronisasi dapat dilihat di log database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:182
msgid ""
"In these cases, the account needs troubleshooting. A reset can be performed "
"using the :guilabel:`Reset Account` button, which can be accessed by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage Users`. Then, select "
"the user to modify the calendar, and click the :guilabel:`Calendar` tab."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kasus ini, akun perlu dipecahkan masalahnya. Reset dapat dilakukan "
"menggunakan tombol :guilabel:`Reset Account`, yang dapat diakses dengan "
"menavigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Settings --> Manage Users`. Kemudian, "
"pilih user untuk memodifikasi kalender, dan klik tab :guilabel:`Calendar`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Reset buttons highlighted on the calendar tab of the user."
msgstr "Tombol reset disorot pada tab kalender user."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:190
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:224
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Reset Account` under the correct calendar."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Reset Account` di bawah kalender yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:193
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:227
msgid "Reset options"
msgstr "Opsi reset"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:195
msgid ""
"The following reset options are available for troubleshooting Google "
"calendar sync with Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Opsi reset berikut tersedia untuk memecahkan masalah sinkronisasi kalender "
"Google dengan Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Google calendar reset options in Odoo."
msgstr "Opsi reset kalender Google di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:236
msgid ":guilabel:`User's Existing Events`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`User's Existing Events`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:202
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:238
msgid ":guilabel:`Leave them untouched`: no changes to the events."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Leave them untouched`: tidak ada perubahan pada acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:203
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from the current Google Calendar account`: delete the "
"events from *Google Calendar*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delete from the current Google Calendar account`: hapus acara "
"dari *Google Calendar*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:205
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:241
msgid ":guilabel:`Delete from Odoo`: delete the events from the Odoo calendar."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Delete from Odoo`: hapus acara dari kalender Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from both`: delete the events from both *Google Calendar* "
"and Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delete from both`: hapus acara dari *Google Calendar* dan "
"kalender Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:208
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:245
msgid ":guilabel:`Next Synchronization`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Next Synchronization`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:210
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize only new events`: sync new events on *Google "
"Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize only new events`: sinkronkan acara baru di *Google "
"Calendar* dan/atau kalender Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:212
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize all existing events`: sync all events on *Google "
"Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sinkronkan semua acara yang ada`: sinkronkan semua acara di "
"*Google Calendar* dan/atau kalender Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:215
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:252
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` after making the selection to modify the user's "
"events and the calendar synchronization."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` setelah membuat pilihan untuk mengubah acara "
"user dan sinkronisasi kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:219
msgid "Google OAuth FAQ"
msgstr "FAQ OAuth Google"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:221
msgid ""
"At times there can be configuration errors that occur, and troubleshooting "
"is needed to resolve the issue. Below are the most common errors that may "
"occur when configuring the *Google Calendar* for use with Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Terkadang dapat terjadi kesalahan konfigurasi dan diperlukan pemecahan "
"masalah untuk menyelesaikan masalahnya. Berikut adalah kesalahan paling umum "
"yang mungkin terjadi saat mengonfigurasi *Google Calendar* untuk digunakan "
"dengan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:226
msgid "Production vs. testing publishing status"
msgstr "Status publikasi production vs. testing"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:228
msgid ""
"Choosing :guilabel:`Production` as the :guilabel:`Publishing Status` "
"(instead of :guilabel:`Testing`) displays the following warning message:"
msgstr ""
"Memilih :guilabel:`Production` sebagai :guilabel:`Publishing Status` (alih-"
"alih :guilabel:`Testing`) menampilkan pesan peringatan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:231
msgid ""
"`OAuth is limited to 100 sensitive scope logins until the OAuth consent "
"screen is verified. This may require a verification process that can take "
"several days.`"
msgstr ""
"`OAuth dibatasi hingga 100 login cakupan sensitif sampai layar persetujuan "
"OAuth diverifikasi. Ini mungkin memerlukan proses verifikasi yang dapat "
"memakan waktu beberapa hari.`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:234
msgid ""
"To correct this warning, navigate to the `Google API Platform <https://"
"console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials/consent>`_. If "
"the :guilabel:`Publishing Status` is :guilabel:`In Production`, "
"click :guilabel:`Back to Testing` to correct the issue."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbaiki peringatan ini, navigasi ke `Google API Platform <https://"
"console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials/consent>`_. "
"Jika :guilabel:`Publishing Status` adalah :guilabel:`In Production`, "
"klik :guilabel:`Back to Testing` untuk memperbaiki masalahnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:239
msgid "No test users added"
msgstr "Tidak ada user uji yang ditambahkan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:241
msgid ""
"If no test users are added to the :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen`, then "
"an :guilabel:`Error 403: access_denied` populates."
msgstr ""
"Jika tidak ada user uji yang ditambahkan ke :guilabel:`OAuth consent "
"screen`, maka akan muncul :guilabel:`Error 403: access_denied`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "403 Access Denied Error."
msgstr "Error 403 Access Denied."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:247
msgid ""
"To correct this error, return to the :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen`, "
"under :guilabel:`APIs & Services`, and add test users to the app. Add the "
"email to be configured in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbaiki error ini, kembali ke :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen`, di "
"bawah :guilabel:`APIs & Services`, dan tambahkan user uji ke aplikasi. "
"Tambahkan email yang akan dikonfigurasi di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:251
msgid "Application Type"
msgstr "Jenis aplikasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:253
msgid ""
"When creating the credentials (OAuth *Client ID* and *Client Secret*), "
"if :guilabel:`Desktop App` is selected for the :guilabel:`Application Type`, "
"an :guilabel:`Authorization Error` appears (:guilabel:`Error "
"400:redirect_uri_mismatch`)."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat kredensial (OAuth *Client ID* dan *Client Secret*), "
"jika :guilabel:`Desktop App` dipilih untuk :guilabel:`Application Type`, "
"akan muncul :guilabel:`Authorization Error` (:guilabel:`Error "
"400:redirect_uri_mismatch`)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Error 400 Redirect URI Mismatch."
msgstr "Error 400 Redirect URI Mismatch."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:260
msgid ""
"To correct this error, delete the existing credentials, and create new "
"credentials, by selecting :guilabel:`Web Application` for "
"the :guilabel:`Application Type`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbaiki error ini, hapus kredensial yang ada, dan buat kredensial "
"baru, dengan memilih :guilabel:`Web Application` "
"untuk :guilabel:`Application Type`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:263
msgid ""
"Then, under :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs`, click :guilabel:`ADD URI`, "
"and type: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/google_account/authentication` in the "
"field, being sure to replace *yourdbname* in the URL with the **real** Odoo "
"database name."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, di bawah :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs`, klik :guilabel:`ADD "
"URI`, dan ketik: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/google_account/authentication` "
"di kolom tersebut, pastikan untuk mengganti *yourdbname* dalam URL dengan "
"nama database Odoo yang **sebenarnya**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:268
msgid ""
"Ensure that the domain (used in the URI: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/"
"google_account/authentication`) is the exact same domain as configured in "
"the `web.base.url` system parameter."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan bahwa domain (yang digunakan dalam URI: `https://"
"yourdbname.odoo.com/google_account/authentication`) sama persis dengan "
"domain yang dikonfigurasi dalam parameter sistem `web.base.url`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:272
msgid ""
"Access the `web.base.url` by activating :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical header "
"menu --> Parameters section --> System Parameters`."
msgstr ""
"Akses `web.base.url` dengan mengaktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-"
"mode>`, dan navigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Settings --> menu header "
"Technical --> bagian Parameters --> System Parameters`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:3
msgid "Outlook Calendar synchronization"
msgstr "Sinkronisasi Outlook Calendar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:5
msgid ""
"Synchronizing a user's *Outlook Calendar* with Odoo is useful for keeping "
"track of tasks and appointments across all related applications."
msgstr ""
"Sinkronisasi *Kalender Outlook* user dengan Odoo berguna untuk melacak tugas "
"dan appointment di semua aplikasi terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`../../general/users/azure`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/users/azure`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`../../general/email_communication/azure_oauth`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/email_communication/azure_oauth`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:13
msgid "Microsoft Azure setup"
msgstr "Pengaturan Microsoft Azure"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:15
msgid ""
"To sync the *Outlook Calendar* with Odoo's *Calendar*, a Microsoft *Azure* "
"account is required. Creating an account is free for users who have never "
"tried, or paid for, *Azure*. For more information, view the account options "
"on the `Azure website <https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/free/?"
"WT.mc_id=A261C142F>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyinkronkan *Kalender Outlook* dengan *Kalender* Odoo, diperlukan "
"akun Microsoft *Azure*. Membuat akun gratis untuk user yang belum pernah "
"mencoba atau membayar *Azure*. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, lihat opsi akun "
"di `situs web Azure <https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/free/?"
"WT.mc_id=A261C142F>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:20
msgid ""
"Refer to `Microsoft's documentation <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/"
"active-directory/ develop/quickstart-create-new-tenant>`_ on how to set up a "
"Microsoft *Entra ID* (formally called Microsoft *Azure Active Directory "
"(Azure AD)*). This is an API console to manage and register Microsoft "
"applications."
msgstr ""
"Lihat `dokumentasi Microsoft <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-"
"directory/ develop/quickstart-create-new-tenant>`_ tentang cara menyiapkan "
"Microsoft *Entra ID* (sebelumnya disebut Microsoft *Azure Active Directory "
"(Azure AD)*). Ini adalah konsol API untuk mengelola dan mendaftarkan "
"aplikasi Microsoft."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:25
msgid ""
"Existing Microsoft *Entra ID* users should log in at the `Microsoft Azure "
"developer portal <https://portal.azure.com/#home>`_. Next, "
"select :guilabel:`View` under the section labeled :guilabel:`Manage "
"Microsoft Entra ID`."
msgstr ""
"User Microsoft *Entra ID* yang sudah ada harus masuk di `portal pengembang "
"Microsoft Azure <https://portal.azure.com/#home>`_. Selanjutnya, "
"pilih :guilabel:`View` di bagian berlabel :guilabel:`Manage Microsoft Entra "
"ID`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:30
msgid "Register application"
msgstr "Mendaftarkan aplikasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:32
msgid ""
"After logging in with the Microsoft *Entra ID*, `register an application "
"<https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/quickstart-"
"register-app>`_."
msgstr ""
"Setelah masuk dengan Microsoft *Entra ID*, `daftarkan aplikasi <https://"
"docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/quickstart-register-"
"app>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:35
msgid ""
"To create an application, click :guilabel:`+ Add` in the top menu. From the "
"resulting drop-down menu, select :guilabel:`App Registration`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat aplikasi, klik :guilabel:`+ Add` di menu atas. Dari menu drop-"
"down yang muncul, pilih :guilabel:`App Registration`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"Microsoft Azure management page with + Add and App Registration menu "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Halaman manajemen Microsoft Azure dengan + Add dan menu App Registration "
"yang disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:42
msgid "Enter a unique :guilabel:`Name` for the connected application."
msgstr "Masukkan :guilabel:`Name` yang unik untuk aplikasi yang terhubung."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:44
msgid ""
"Choosing the appropriate :guilabel:`Supported account type` is essential, or "
"else the connected application will not work. Users who wish to connect "
"their *Outlook Calendar* to Odoo should select the :guilabel:`Accounts in "
"any organizational directory (Any Microsoft Entra ID directory - "
"Multitenant) and personal Microsoft accounts (e.g. Skype, Xbox)` option "
"for :guilabel:`Supported account types`."
msgstr ""
"Memilih :guilabel:`Supported account type` yang sesuai sangat penting, jika "
"tidak aplikasi yang terhubung tidak akan berfungsi. User yang ingin "
"menghubungkan *Kalender Outlook* mereka ke Odoo harus memilih "
"opsi :guilabel:`Accounts in any organizational directory (Any Microsoft "
"Entra ID directory - Multitenant) and personal Microsoft accounts (e.g. "
"Skype, Xbox)` untuk :guilabel:`Supported account types`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:50
msgid ""
"When configuring the :guilabel:`Redirect URI`, choose the :guilabel:`Web` "
"option from the first drop-down menu. Then, enter the Odoo database URI "
"(URL) followed by `/microsoft_account/authentication`."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengonfigurasi :guilabel:`Redirect URI`, pilih opsi :guilabel:`Web` "
"dari menu drop-down pertama. Kemudian, masukkan URI (URL) database Odoo "
"diikuti dengan `/microsoft_account/authentication`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:55
msgid ""
"Enter `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/microsoft_account/authentication` for "
"the :guilabel:`Redirect URI`. Replace `yourdbname.odoo.com` with "
"the :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)`."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/microsoft_account/authentication` "
"untuk :guilabel:`Redirect URI`. Ganti `yourdbname.odoo.com` "
"dengan :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:59
msgid ""
"Ensure the database's :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` (domain) used "
"in the URI is the exact same domain as the one configured on the "
"`web.base.url` system parameter."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` (domain) database yang "
"digunakan dalam URI sama persis dengan domain yang dikonfigurasi pada "
"parameter sistem `web.base.url`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:62
msgid ""
"Access the `web.base.url` by activating :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical header "
"menu --> Parameters section --> System Parameters`. Then, select it from "
"the :guilabel:`Key` list on the :guilabel:`System Parameters` page."
msgstr ""
"Akses `web.base.url` dengan mengaktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-"
"mode>`, dan navigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Settings --> menu header "
"Technical --> bagian Parameters --> System Parameters`. Kemudian, pilih dari "
"daftar :guilabel:`Key` pada halaman :guilabel:`System Parameters`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"The \"Supported account type\" and \"Redirect URI\" settings in the "
"Microsoft Entra ID portal."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan \"Supported account type\" dan \"Redirect URI\" di portal "
"Microsoft Entra ID."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:71
msgid ""
"For more information on the restrictions and limitations of URIs, check "
"Microsoft's `Redirect URI (reply URL) restrictions and limitations <https://"
"docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/reply-url>`_ page."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang pembatasan dan batasan URI, periksa "
"halaman Microsoft `Redirect URI (reply URL) restrictions and limitations "
"<https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/reply-"
"url>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:75
msgid ""
"Finally, on the application registration page, click :guilabel:`Register` "
"button to complete the application registration. The :guilabel:`Application "
"(client) ID` is produced. Copy this value, as it is needed later, in "
"the :ref:`outlook_calendar/odoo_setup`."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, pada halaman pendaftaran aplikasi, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Register` untuk menyelesaikan pendaftaran "
"aplikasi. :guilabel:`Application (client) ID` akan dihasilkan. Salin nilai "
"ini karena akan diperlukan nanti di :ref:`outlook_calendar/odoo_setup`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"Application client ID highlighted in the essentials section of the newly "
"created\n"
"application."
msgstr ""
"ID klien aplikasi yang disorot di bagian essentials aplikasi yang baru "
"dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:85
msgid "Create client secret"
msgstr "Buat client secret"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:87
msgid ""
"The second credential needed to complete the synchronization of the "
"Microsoft *Outlook Calendar* is the *Client Secret*. The user **must** add a "
"client secret, as this allows Odoo to authenticate itself, requiring no "
"interaction from the user's side. *Certificates* are optional."
msgstr ""
"Kredensial kedua yang diperlukan untuk menyelesaikan sinkronisasi Microsoft "
"*Outlook Calendar* adalah *Client Secret*. User **harus** menambahkan client "
"secret, karena hal ini memungkinkan Odoo untuk melakukan autentikasi, tanpa "
"memerlukan interaksi dari sisi user. *Sertifikat* bersifat opsional."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:91
msgid ""
"To add a client secret, click :menuselection:`Certificates & secrets` in the "
"left menu. Then click :guilabel:`+ New client secret` to create the client "
"secret."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan client secret, klik :menuselection:`Certificates & "
"secrets` di menu sebelah kiri. Kemudian klik :guilabel:`+ New client secret` "
"untuk membuat client secret."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"New client secret page with certificates and secrets menu and new client "
"secret option\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Halaman client secret baru dengan menu certificates and secrets dan opsi new "
"client secret yang disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:99
msgid ""
"Next, type a :guilabel:`Description`, and select when the client "
"secret :guilabel:`Expires`. Available options include: :guilabel:`90 days (3 "
"months)`, :guilabel:`365 days (12 months)`, :guilabel:`545 days (18 "
"months)`, :guilabel:`730 days (24 months)` or :guilabel:`Custom`. "
"The :guilabel:`Custom` option allows the administrator to set "
"a :guilabel:`Start` and :guilabel:`End` date."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, ketik :guilabel:`Description`, dan pilih kapan client "
"secret :guilabel:`Expires`. Opsi yang tersedia meliputi: :guilabel:`90 days "
"(3 months)`, :guilabel:`365 days (12 months)`, :guilabel:`545 days (18 "
"months)`, :guilabel:`730 days (24 months)` atau :guilabel:`Custom`. "
"Opsi :guilabel:`Custom` memungkinkan administrator untuk mengatur "
"tanggal :guilabel:`Start` dan :guilabel:`End`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:105
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Add` to :guilabel:`Add a client secret`."
msgstr "Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Add` untuk :guilabel:`Add a client secret`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:108
msgid ""
"Since resetting the synchronization can be tricky, Odoo recommends setting "
"the maximum allowed expiration date for the client secret (24 months or "
"custom), so there is no need to re-synchronize soon."
msgstr ""
"Karena mengatur ulang sinkronisasi bisa rumit, Odoo merekomendasikan untuk "
"mengatur tanggal kedaluwarsa maksimum yang diizinkan untuk client secret (24 "
"bulan atau custom), sehingga tidak perlu melakukan sinkronisasi ulang dalam "
"waktu dekat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:112
msgid "Copy the :guilabel:`Value` for use in the next section."
msgstr "Salin :guilabel:`Value` untuk digunakan di bagian selanjutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:115
msgid ""
"Client secret values cannot be viewed, except immediately after creation. Be "
"sure to save the secret when created *before* leaving the page."
msgstr ""
"Nilai client secret tidak dapat dilihat, kecuali segera setelah pembuatan. "
"Pastikan untuk menyimpan secret saat dibuat *sebelum* meninggalkan halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:121
msgid "Configuration in Odoo"
msgstr "Konfigurasi di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:123
msgid ""
"In the Odoo database, go to :menuselection:`Calendar app --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`, and tick the checkbox beside the :guilabel:`Outlook Calendar` "
"setting. Remember to click :guilabel:`Save` to implement the changes."
msgstr ""
"Di database Odoo, buka :menuselection:`Calendar app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, dan centang kotak di samping pengaturan :guilabel:`Outlook "
"Calendar`. Ingat untuk mengklik :guilabel:`Save` untuk menerapkan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Outlook Calendar\" setting activated in Odoo."
msgstr "Pengaturan \"Outlook Calendar\" diaktifkan di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:130
msgid ""
"From the Microsoft *Azure* portal, under the :guilabel:`Overview` section of "
"the application, copy the :guilabel:`Application (Client) ID`, if it has not "
"already been copied, and paste it into the :guilabel:`Client ID` field in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Dari portal Microsoft *Azure*, di bagian :guilabel:`Overview` aplikasi, "
"salin :guilabel:`Application (Client) ID`, jika belum disalin, dan tempelkan "
"ke field :guilabel:`Client ID` di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Client ID\" in the Microsoft Azure portal."
msgstr "\"Client ID\" di portal Microsoft Azure."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:138
msgid ""
"Copy the previously-acquired :guilabel:`Value` (Client Secret Value), and "
"paste it into the :guilabel:`Client Secret` field in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Salin :guilabel:`Value` (Client Secret Value) yang telah diperoleh "
"sebelumnya, dan tempelkan ke field :guilabel:`Client Secret` di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Client Secret\" token to be copied from Microsoft to Odoo."
msgstr "Token \"Client Secret\" yang akan disalin dari Microsoft ke Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:145
msgid ""
"Finally, on the Odoo :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` page, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, pada halaman :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` Odoo, "
"klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:150
msgid "Sync with Outlook"
msgstr "Sinkronisasi dengan Outlook"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:154
msgid ""
"Odoo highly recommends testing the Outlook calendar synchronization on a "
"test database and a test email address (that is not used for any other "
"purpose) before attempting to sync the desired Outlook Calendar with the "
"user's production database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo sangat merekomendasikan untuk menguji sinkronisasi kalender Outlook di "
"database uji dan alamat email uji (yang tidak digunakan untuk tujuan lain) "
"sebelum mencoba menyinkronkan Outlook Calendar yang diinginkan dengan "
"database produksi user."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:158
msgid ""
"If the user has any past, present, or future events on their Odoo calendar "
"before syncing their Outlook calendar, Outlook will treat the events pulled "
"from Odoo's calendar during the sync as new events, causing an email "
"notification to be sent from Outlook to all the event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Jika user memiliki acara masa lalu, sekarang, atau masa depan di kalender "
"Odoo mereka sebelum menyinkronkan kalender Outlook mereka, Outlook akan "
"memperlakukan acara yang diambil dari kalender Odoo selama sinkronisasi "
"sebagai acara baru, menyebabkan notifikasi email dikirim dari Outlook ke "
"semua peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:162
msgid ""
"To avoid unwanted emails being sent to all past, present, and future event "
"attendees, the user must add the events from the Odoo calendar to the "
"Outlook calendar before the first ever sync, delete the events from Odoo, "
"and then start the sync."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghindari email yang tidak diinginkan dikirim ke semua peserta acara "
"masa lalu, sekarang, dan masa depan, user harus menambahkan acara dari "
"kalender Odoo ke kalender Outlook sebelum sinkronisasi pertama kali, "
"menghapus acara dari Odoo, dan kemudian memulai sinkronisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:166
msgid ""
"Even after synchronizing the Odoo Calendar with the Outlook calendar, "
"Outlook will still send a notification to all event participants every time "
"an event is edited (created, deleted, unarchived, or event date/time "
"changed), with no exceptions. This is a limitation that cannot be fixed from "
"Odoo's side."
msgstr ""
"Bahkan setelah menyinkronkan Kalender Odoo dengan kalender Outlook, Outlook "
"akan tetap mengirim notifikasi ke semua peserta acara setiap kali acara "
"diedit (dibuat, dihapus, dibatalkan arsip, atau tanggal/waktu acara diubah), "
"tanpa pengecualian. Ini adalah keterbatasan yang tidak dapat diperbaiki dari "
"sisi Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:171
msgid ""
"In summary, once a user synchronizes their Outlook calendar with the Odoo "
"calendar:"
msgstr ""
"Singkatnya, setelah user menyinkronkan kalender Outlook mereka dengan "
"kalender Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:173
msgid ""
"Creating an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send an invitation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Membuat acara di Odoo menyebabkan Outlook mengirim undangan ke semua peserta "
"acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:174
msgid ""
"Deleting an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send a cancellation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus acara di Odoo menyebabkan Outlook mengirim pembatalan ke semua "
"peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:175
msgid ""
"Unarchiving an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Membatalkan arsip acara di Odoo menyebabkan Outlook mengirim undangan ke "
"semua peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:176
msgid ""
"Archiving an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send a cancellation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Mengarsipkan acara di Odoo menyebabkan Outlook mengirim pembatalan ke semua "
"peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:177
msgid ""
"Adding a contact to an event causes Outlook to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan kontak ke acara menyebabkan Outlook mengirim undangan ke semua "
"peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:178
msgid ""
"Removing a contact from an event causes Outlook to send a cancellation to "
"all event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus kontak dari acara menyebabkan Outlook mengirim pembatalan ke semua "
"peserta acara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:181
msgid "Sync Odoo Calendar and Outlook"
msgstr "Sinkronkan Kalender Odoo dan Outlook"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:183
msgid ""
"In the Odoo database, open to the *Calendar* module, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Outlook` sync button on the right-side of the page, beneath "
"the monthly calendar."
msgstr ""
"Di database Odoo, buka modul *Kalender*, dan klik tombol "
"sinkronisasi :guilabel:`Outlook` di sisi kanan halaman, di bawah kalender "
"bulanan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Outlook\" sync button in Odoo Calendar."
msgstr "Tombol sinkronisasi \"Outlook\" di Kalender Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:190
msgid ""
"The synchronization is a two-way process, meaning that events are reconciled "
"in both accounts (*Outlook* and Odoo). The page redirects to a Microsoft "
"login page, and the user is asked to log in to their account, if they are "
"not already. Finally, grant the required permissions by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Accept`."
msgstr ""
"Sinkronisasi adalah proses dua arah, artinya acara direkonsiliasi di kedua "
"akun (*Outlook* dan Odoo). Halaman dialihkan ke halaman login Microsoft, dan "
"user diminta untuk masuk ke akun mereka, jika mereka belum masuk. Terakhir, "
"berikan izin yang diperlukan dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Accept`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Authentication process on Microsoft Outlook OAuth page."
msgstr "Proses autentikasi di halaman OAuth Microsoft Outlook."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:200
msgid ""
"All users that want to use the synchronization simply need to :ref:`sync "
"their calendar with Outlook <outlook/sync>`. The configuration of "
"Microsoft's *Azure* account is only done once, as Microsoft *Entra ID* "
"tenants' client IDs and client secrets are unique, and help the user manage "
"a specific instance of Microsoft cloud services for internal and external "
"users."
msgstr ""
"Semua user yang ingin menggunakan sinkronisasi cukup "
"perlu :ref:`menyinkronkan kalender mereka dengan Outlook <outlook/sync>`. "
"Konfigurasi akun *Azure* Microsoft hanya dilakukan sekali, karena ID klien "
"dan rahasia klien tenant Microsoft *Entra ID* adalah unik, dan membantu user "
"mengelola instans tertentu dari layanan cloud Microsoft untuk user internal "
"dan eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:206
msgid ":doc:`../../general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:207
msgid ":doc:`google`"
msgstr ":doc:`google`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:212
msgid ""
"There may be times when the *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* account does not "
"sync correctly with Odoo. Sync issues can be seen in the database logs."
msgstr ""
"Ada kalanya akun *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* tidak tersinkronisasi dengan "
"benar dengan Odoo. Masalah sinkronisasi dapat dilihat di log database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:215
msgid ""
"In these cases, the account needs troubleshooting. A reset can be performed "
"using the :guilabel:`Reset Account` button, which can be accessed by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage Users`. Then, select "
"the user to modify the calendar, and click on the :guilabel:`Calendar` tab."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kasus ini, akun perlu dipecahkan masalahnya. Reset dapat dilakukan "
"menggunakan tombol :guilabel:`Reset Account`, yang dapat diakses dengan "
"menavigasi ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Settings --> Manage Users`. Kemudian, "
"pilih user untuk memodifikasi kalender, dan klik tab :guilabel:`Calendar`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:229
msgid ""
"The following reset options are available for troubleshooting *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* sync with Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Opsi reset berikut tersedia untuk pemecahan masalah sinkronisasi *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* dengan Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Outlook calendar reset options in Odoo."
msgstr "Opsi reset kalender Outlook di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from the current Microsoft Calendar account`: delete the "
"events from *Microsoft Outlook Calendar*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hapus dari akun Microsoft Calendar saat ini`: hapus acara dari "
"*Microsoft Outlook Calendar*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:242
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from both`: delete the events from both *Microsoft Outlook "
"Calendar* and Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hapus dari keduanya`: hapus acara dari *Microsoft Outlook "
"Calendar* dan kalender Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize only new events`: sync new events on *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sinkronkan hanya acara baru`: sinkronkan acara baru di *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* dan/atau kalender Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:249
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize all existing events`: sync all events on *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sinkronkan semua acara yang ada`: sinkronkan semua acara di "
"*Microsoft Outlook Calendar* dan/atau kalender Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:5
msgid "Dashboards"
msgstr "Dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:13
msgid ""
"**Odoo Dashboards** allows you to consult, interact with, customize, and "
"build interactive dashboards that display real-time data from your Odoo "
"database in an easy-to-understand way. By centralizing data from various "
"Odoo sources in a single location, dashboards provide an overview of key "
"business metrics that can help you monitor business performance and make "
"informed decisions."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Dashboards** memungkinkan Anda untuk melihat, berinteraksi dengan, "
"menyesuaikan, dan membangun dashboard interaktif yang menampilkan data real-"
"time dari database Odoo Anda dengan cara yang mudah dipahami. Dengan "
"memusatkan data dari berbagai sumber Odoo di satu lokasi, dashboard "
"memberikan gambaran umum tentang metrik bisnis kunci yang dapat membantu "
"Anda memantau kinerja bisnis dan membuat keputusan yang tepat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:18
msgid ""
":doc:`Odoo spreadsheets <../../applications/productivity/spreadsheet>` serve "
"as the foundation for dashboards, with tables and charts used to structure "
"and visualize dynamic Odoo data. :ref:`Data sources <spreadsheet/insert/data-"
"sources>` connect a dashboard's underlying spreadsheet to your database, "
"ensuring the most recent data is retrieved every time the dashboard is "
"opened or refreshed."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Spreadsheet Odoo <../../applications/productivity/spreadsheet>` "
"berfungsi sebagai fondasi untuk dashboard, dengan tabel dan grafik yang "
"digunakan untuk menyusun dan memvisualisasikan data Odoo yang "
"dinamis. :ref:`Sumber data <spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` menghubungkan "
"spreadsheet yang mendasari dashboard ke database Anda, memastikan data "
"terbaru diambil setiap kali dashboard dibuka atau disegarkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:24
msgid ""
"With Odoo Dashboards, users can, depending on their :ref:`access rights "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>`:"
msgstr ""
"Dengan Dashboard Odoo, user dapat, tergantung pada :ref:`hak akses "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>` mereka:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:27
msgid ""
":ref:`consult and interact with dashboards <dashboards/use-dashboards>`, "
"including :ref:`standard, pre-configured dashboards <dashboards/standard>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`melihat dan berinteraksi dengan dashboard <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards>`, termasuk :ref:`dashboard standar yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya <dashboards/standard>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:29
msgid ""
"use :ref:`global filters <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` to "
"filter all the data shown on a dashboard"
msgstr ""
"menggunakan :ref:`global filter <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` "
"untuk memfilter semua data yang ditampilkan pada dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:31
msgid ""
":ref:`share a snapshot of a dashboard <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` with "
"internal users who do not have the appropriate access rights or with "
"external users"
msgstr ""
":ref:`membagikan snapshot dashboard <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` dengan "
"user internal yang tidak memiliki hak akses yang sesuai atau dengan user "
"eksternal"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:33
msgid ""
":doc:`build custom dashboards <../../applications/productivity/dashboards/"
"build_and_customize_dashboards>` using Odoo Spreadsheet"
msgstr ""
":doc:`membangun dashboard kustom <../../applications/productivity/dashboards/"
"build_and_customize_dashboards>` menggunakan Spreadsheet Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:36
msgid ""
":ref:`customize dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` to "
"modify what data is shown, the layout, or the filters available"
msgstr ""
":ref:`menyesuaikan dashboard <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` "
"untuk mengubah data yang ditampilkan, tata letak, atau filter yang tersedia"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:38
msgid ""
":ref:`manage access rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` to dashboards"
msgstr ""
":ref:`mengelola hak akses <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` ke dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:39
msgid ""
"centralize frequently consulted Odoo views in a personal :doc:`../../"
"applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard`"
msgstr ""
"memusatkan tampilan Odoo yang sering dilihat dalam :doc:`../../applications/"
"productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard` pribadi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:43
msgid ""
"Once a spreadsheet has been converted into a dashboard, it can only be "
"accessed via the Dashboards app."
msgstr ""
"Setelah spreadsheet dikonversi menjadi dashboard, spreadsheet tersebut hanya "
"dapat diakses melalui aplikasi Dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:45
msgid ""
"Unlike other Odoo dashboards, :guilabel:`My Dashboard` is not based on Odoo "
"Spreadsheet, but rather on :doc:`Odoo views <../studio/views>`."
msgstr ""
"Tidak seperti dashboard Odoo lainnya, :guilabel:`Dashboard Saya` tidak "
"didasarkan pada Spreadsheet Odoo, melainkan pada :doc:`tampilan Odoo <../"
"studio/views>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:51
msgid "Use dashboards"
msgstr "Menggunakan dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:53
msgid ""
"When the Dashboards app is opened, the left panel lists all :ref:`standard, "
"pre-configured dashboards <dashboards/standard>` and :doc:`custom-built "
"dashboards <dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards>` to which a user has "
"been :ref:`granted access <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`, grouped by "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Ketika aplikasi Dashboards dibuka, panel kiri mencantumkan "
"semua :ref:`dashboard standar yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya "
"<dashboards/standard>` dan :doc:`dashboard yang dibuat khusus <dashboards/"
"build_and_customize_dashboards>` yang :ref:`diberikan akses <dashboards/"
"access-and-sharing>` kepada user, dikelompokkan berdasarkan bagian."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:58
msgid "Clicking on a dashboard name opens that dashboard in the main view."
msgstr ""
"Mengklik nama dashboard akan membuka dashboard tersebut di tampilan utama."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Overview of Leads dashboard"
msgstr "Gambaran umum dashboard Leads"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:64
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-angle-double-left` :guilabel:`(double chevron)` icon at "
"the top of the left panel to collapse the left panel, maximizing the space "
"available for dashboards."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-angle-double-left` :guilabel:`(double chevron)` di "
"bagian atas panel kiri untuk menutup panel kiri, memaksimalkan ruang yang "
"tersedia untuk dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:66
msgid ""
"Mark a dashboard as a favorite by clicking the :icon:`fa-"
"star` :guilabel:`(Toggle favorite)` icon in the upper-right corner. "
"Favorited dashboards are grouped in a :guilabel:`Favorites` section at the "
"top of the left panel for easy access."
msgstr ""
"Tandai dashboard sebagai favorit dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"star` :guilabel:`(Toggle favorite)` di sudut kanan atas. Dashboard yang "
"difavoritkan dikelompokkan dalam bagian :guilabel:`Favorites` di bagian atas "
"panel kiri untuk akses yang mudah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:73
msgid "Filter and sort data"
msgstr "Filter dan urutkan data"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:75
msgid ""
"Filtering and sorting allow you to manage what data is displayed and how it "
"is displayed. This can help tailor the view to answer specific business "
"questions."
msgstr ""
"Filtering dan sorting memungkinkan Anda mengelola data apa yang ditampilkan "
"dan bagaimana data tersebut ditampilkan. Ini dapat membantu menyesuaikan "
"tampilan untuk menjawab pertanyaan bisnis tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:78
msgid ""
":ref:`Filtering <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` limits the data "
"presented in charts and tables, allowing you to focus only on records that "
"meet specific criteria,  e.g., viewing sales data only for a specific sales "
"team."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Filtering <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` membatasi data "
"yang disajikan dalam grafik dan tabel, memungkinkan Anda fokus hanya pada "
"catatan yang memenuhi kriteria tertentu, misalnya, melihat data penjualan "
"hanya untuk tim penjualan tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:81
msgid ""
":ref:`Sorting <dashboards/use-dashboards/sort>` reorders the data presented "
"in table columns, allowing you to see the data from different perspectives, "
"e.g., viewing products by sales revenue from highest to lowest."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Sorting <dashboards/use-dashboards/sort>` mengurutkan ulang data yang "
"disajikan dalam kolom tabel, memungkinkan Anda melihat data dari perspektif "
"berbeda, misalnya, melihat produk berdasarkan pendapatan penjualan dari "
"tertinggi ke terendah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:387
msgid "Apply global filters"
msgstr "Terapkan filter global"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:90
msgid ""
"If :doc:`global filters <spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters>` have "
"been configured for a dashboard, a search bar is available above the "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Jika :doc:`filter global <spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters>` telah "
"dikonfigurasi untuk dashboard, bilah pencarian tersedia di atas dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Global filters on the Project dashboard"
msgstr "Filter global pada dashboard Project"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:98
msgid ""
"Global filters are available for all :ref:`standard dashboards <dashboards/"
"standard>`. Additional :doc:`global filters can be added <spreadsheet/"
"work_with_data/global_filters>` by a user with the appropriate :ref:`access "
"rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing/customize-configure-build>`."
msgstr ""
"Filter global tersedia untuk semua :ref:`dashboard standar <dashboards/"
"standard>`. :doc:`Filter global tambahan dapat ditambahkan <spreadsheet/"
"work_with_data/global_filters>` oleh user dengan :ref:`hak akses <dashboards/"
"access-and-sharing/customize-configure-build>` yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:102
msgid ""
"It is also possible to :ref:`search for values <search/values>` by typing "
"directly in the search bar; the search categories shown reflect the "
"available global filters."
msgstr ""
"Juga dimungkinkan untuk :ref:`mencari nilai <search/values>` dengan mengetik "
"langsung di bilah pencarian; kategori pencarian yang ditampilkan "
"mencerminkan filter global yang tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:105
msgid "To apply global filters:"
msgstr "Untuk menerapkan filter global:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:107
msgid ""
"Click within the search bar or click on the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon to access all filters available for that "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Klik di dalam bilah pencarian atau klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` untuk mengakses semua filter yang tersedia "
"untuk dashboard tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:109
msgid ""
"For the relevant filter, select a conditional operator from the first "
"dropdown, e.g., :guilabel:`is in`, then, as relevant, enter or select the "
"appropriate value."
msgstr ""
"Untuk filter yang relevan, pilih operator kondisional dari dropdown pertama, "
"misalnya :guilabel:`is in`, kemudian, sesuai kebutuhan, masukkan atau pilih "
"nilai yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:401
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Filter`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Filter`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:113
msgid ""
"For dashboards with a date filter, this filter can be set via the search bar "
"or via the button with the :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Untuk dashboard dengan filter tanggal, filter ini dapat diatur melalui bilah "
"pencarian atau melalui tombol dengan ikon :icon:`fa-"
"calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Filtering a dashboard by date period"
msgstr "Memfilter dashboard berdasarkan periode tanggal"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:119
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Custom Range` at the bottom of the period selector shows "
"either a manually entered custom range, if relevant, or the start and end "
"date of the selected period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Custom Range` di bagian bawah pemilih periode menampilkan rentang "
"kustom yang dimasukkan secara manual jika relevan, atau tanggal mulai dan "
"akhir dari periode yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:122
msgid ""
"To remove a value from a filter, click the :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon beside the name of the value; to empty a "
"filter, click the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon at the far "
"right of the filter."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus nilai dari filter, klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(remove)` di samping nama nilai; untuk mengosongkan "
"filter, klik ikon :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(remove)` di bagian paling "
"kanan filter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:129
msgid "Sort data"
msgstr "Urutkan data"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:131
msgid ""
"Depending on the dashboard and the table in question, it may be possible to "
"sort the data by column, by clicking the column heading. A :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(caret down)` or :icon:`fa-caret-up` :guilabel:`(caret up)` "
"icon beside a column heading indicates that the column has been sorted in "
"descending or ascending order, respectively. If, when hovering over other "
"column headings, a :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(sort)` icon appears, the "
"column can be sorted."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada dashboard dan tabel yang dimaksud, mungkin dapat mengurutkan "
"data berdasarkan kolom dengan mengklik judul kolom. Ikon :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(caret down)` atau :icon:`fa-caret-up` :guilabel:`(caret "
"up)` di samping judul kolom menunjukkan bahwa kolom telah diurutkan dalam "
"urutan menurun atau menaik. Jika, saat mengarahkan kursor ke judul kolom "
"lain, ikon :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(sort)` muncul, kolom tersebut dapat "
"diurutkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:138
msgid ""
"If conditional formatting has been applied to a table, the original "
"formatting is maintained when the table is resorted by a different column."
msgstr ""
"Jika pemformatan bersyarat telah diterapkan pada tabel, pemformatan asli "
"dipertahankan saat tabel diurutkan ulang berdasarkan kolom yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:142
msgid ""
"In this example, the table was originally sorted by revenue per CRM tag, in "
"decreasing order. Conditional formatting was defined to visualize the "
"proportional revenue using data bars. When the table is resorted by number "
"of leads in descending order, the data bars still reflect the revenue per "
"tag in decreasing order."
msgstr ""
"Dalam contoh ini, tabel awalnya diurutkan berdasarkan pendapatan per tag "
"CRM, dalam urutan menurun. Pemformatan bersyarat didefinisikan untuk "
"memvisualisasikan pendapatan proporsional menggunakan bilah data. Ketika "
"tabel diurutkan ulang berdasarkan jumlah lead dalam urutan menurun, bilah "
"data masih mencerminkan pendapatan per tag dalam urutan menurun."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:0
msgid "Sorting a table with conditional formatting using data bars"
msgstr "Mengurutkan tabel dengan pemformatan bersyarat menggunakan bilah data"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:154
msgid "Access underlying records"
msgstr "Akses catatan yang mendasari"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:156
msgid ""
"While dashboards provide a user-friendly summary of key data, drilling down "
"to the underlying data allows a more detailed analysis. This can be useful "
"for investigating anomalies or providing the full context needed for "
"decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Sementara dashboard menyediakan ringkasan data kunci yang ramah pengguna, "
"menelusuri ke data yang mendasarinya memungkinkan analisis yang lebih rinci. "
"Ini dapat berguna untuk menyelidiki anomali atau memberikan konteks lengkap "
"yang diperlukan untuk pengambilan keputusan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:160
msgid ""
"**Open underlying database records**: To access database records referenced "
"by a dashboard, click on the relevant value in a table or on a data point on "
"a chart. Doing so opens either the individual record, or, in the case of "
"charts or tables displaying consolidated data, a list of the referenced "
"records."
msgstr ""
"**Membuka record database yang mendasari**: Untuk mengakses record database "
"yang direferensikan oleh dashboard, klik nilai yang relevan dalam tabel atau "
"pada titik data pada grafik. Melakukan hal ini akan membuka record "
"individual, atau, dalam kasus grafik atau tabel yang menampilkan data "
"konsolidasi, daftar record yang direferensikan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:165
msgid ""
"**Open underlying database views**: To access the view from which the data "
"for a specific chart or table is retrieved, click on the title of the chart "
"or table. Doing so opens the corresponding list view, pivot view or graph "
"view."
msgstr ""
"**Membuka tampilan database yang mendasari**: Untuk mengakses tampilan dari "
"mana data untuk grafik atau tabel tertentu diambil, klik judul grafik atau "
"tabel. Melakukan hal ini akan membuka tampilan daftar, tampilan pivot, atau "
"tampilan grafik yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:170
msgid ""
"To return to a dashboard after drilling down to underlying records or views, "
"click the :guilabel:`Dashboards` breadcrumb in the upper-left corner."
msgstr ""
"Untuk kembali ke dashboard setelah menelusuri ke catatan atau tampilan yang "
"mendasarinya, klik breadcrumb :guilabel:`Dashboard` di pojok kiri atas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:176
msgid "Expand, copy or download charts"
msgstr "Perluas, salin, atau unduh grafik"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:178
msgid ""
"To see charts in full screen, hover over a chart and click the :icon:`fa-"
"expand` icon."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat grafik dalam layar penuh, arahkan kursor ke grafik dan klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-expand`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:180
msgid ""
"It is also possible to copy or download a chart by hovering over the chart "
"and clicking the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (vertical ellipsis) icon, then "
"clicking :icon:`os-copy-as-image` :guilabel:`Copy as image` or :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download` as relevant."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menyalin atau mengunduh grafik dengan mengarahkan kursor ke "
"grafik dan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (elipsis vertikal), lalu "
"klik :icon:`os-copy-as-image` :guilabel:`Salin sebagai gambar` "
"atau :icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`Unduh` sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:185
msgid ""
":ref:`Expanding a time-series chart to full screen <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` allows a more detailed analysis."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Memperluas grafik deret waktu ke layar penuh <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` memungkinkan analisis yang lebih "
"mendetail."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:191
msgid "Analyze time-series charts"
msgstr "Analisis grafik deret waktu"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:193
msgid ""
"Time-series charts, i.e., charts showing data over time, can be analyzed "
"more closely by:"
msgstr ""
"Grafik deret waktu, yaitu grafik yang menampilkan data dari waktu ke waktu, "
"dapat dianalisis lebih mendalam dengan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:195
msgid ""
":ref:`adjusting the granularity <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-"
"charts-granularity>`;"
msgstr ""
":ref:`menyesuaikan granularitas <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-"
"charts-granularity>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:196
msgid ""
":ref:`zooming in <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` "
"on a chosen time span."
msgstr ""
":ref:`memperbesar <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-"
"scroll>` rentang waktu yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:202
msgid "Adjust granularity"
msgstr "Sesuaikan granularitas"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:204
msgid ""
"For many time-series charts it is possible to adjust the granularity of the "
"unit of time on the x-axis."
msgstr ""
"Untuk banyak grafik deret waktu, dimungkinkan untuk menyesuaikan "
"granularitas satuan waktu pada sumbu-x."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:207
msgid ""
"To do so, hover over the chart, click the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon, then select the desired granularity."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, arahkan kursor ke grafik, klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)`, lalu pilih granularitas yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Changing time granularity on a chart's y-axis"
msgstr "Mengubah granularitas waktu pada sumbu-y grafik"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:217
msgid "Zoom in on a time span and scroll"
msgstr "Perbesar rentang waktu dan gulir"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:219
msgid ""
"When a time-series chart is :ref:`expanded to full screen <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards/charts>`, a slider below the chart allows you to:"
msgstr ""
"Ketika grafik deret waktu :ref:`diperluas ke layar penuh <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards/charts>`, slider di bawah grafik memungkinkan Anda untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:222
msgid ""
"zoom in on a specific time span by dragging the ends of the slider to select "
"the desired time span;"
msgstr ""
"memperbesar rentang waktu tertentu dengan menyeret ujung slider untuk "
"memilih rentang waktu yang diinginkan;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:224
msgid ""
"when you have zoomed in, to scroll through the chart while maintaining the "
"level of zoom by dragging the slider to the left or right."
msgstr ""
"ketika Anda telah memperbesar, untuk menggulir grafik sambil mempertahankan "
"tingkat zoom dengan menyeret slider ke kiri atau kanan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:227
msgid "Resize the slider to return to the initial view."
msgstr "Ubah ukuran slider untuk kembali ke tampilan awal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:230
msgid ""
"In this example from the :guilabel:`Warehouse Daily Operations` dashboard, "
"the chart shows transfers yet to be assigned to a responsible user, by day. "
"The zoom of the chart has been adjusted to show data for five days, and the "
"current position of the slider allows data from the last five days to be "
"shown."
msgstr ""
"Dalam contoh ini dari dashboard :guilabel:`Warehouse Daily Operations`, "
"grafik menampilkan transfer yang belum ditugaskan ke user yang bertanggung "
"jawab, per hari. Zoom grafik telah disesuaikan untuk menampilkan data selama "
"lima hari, dan posisi slider saat ini memungkinkan data dari lima hari "
"terakhir untuk ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:0
msgid "Zoomed-in chart with slider"
msgstr "Grafik yang diperbesar dengan slider"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:241
msgid "Standard dashboards"
msgstr "Dashboard standar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:243
msgid ""
"Depending on which apps are installed, a series of standard dashboards is "
"available by default."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada aplikasi mana yang terpasang, serangkaian dashboard standar "
"tersedia secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:245
msgid ""
"These pre-configured dashboards have been designed to provide the most "
"relevant insights for the topic in question, and users with the "
"appropriate :ref:`access rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` "
"can :ref:`consult and interact <dashboards/use-dashboards>` with them. "
"Dashboard-specific :ref:`filters <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-"
"filters>`, available via the search bar, allow the entire dashboard to be "
"filtered for selected values."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya ini dirancang untuk memberikan "
"wawasan paling relevan untuk topik yang dimaksud, dan user dengan :ref:`hak "
"akses <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` yang sesuai dapat :ref:`berkonsultasi "
"dan berinteraksi <dashboards/use-dashboards>` dengan dashboard "
"tersebut. :ref:`Filter <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` khusus "
"dashboard, yang tersedia melalui bilah pencarian, memungkinkan seluruh "
"dashboard difilter untuk nilai yang dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:251
msgid ""
"Standard dashboards can be :ref:`customized <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"customize>` by a user with the appropriate :ref:`access rights <dashboards/"
"access-and-sharing/customize-configure-build>`. For example, dashboard "
"elements like tables and charts, or global filters can be added, edited, or "
"removed."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard standar dapat :ref:`disesuaikan <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"customize>` oleh user dengan :ref:`hak akses <dashboards/access-and-sharing/"
"customize-configure-build>` yang sesuai. Misalnya, elemen dashboard seperti "
"tabel dan grafik, atau filter global dapat ditambahkan, diedit, atau dihapus."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:257
msgid ""
"When customizing a standard dashboard, it is highly recommended "
"to :ref:`duplicate the dashboard <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/"
"duplicate-dashboard>` and make any changes on the duplicated version. "
"Standard dashboards are reinstalled at each Odoo version upgrade, meaning "
"any customizations on the original version are lost."
msgstr ""
"Saat menyesuaikan dashboard standar, sangat disarankan "
"untuk :ref:`menduplikasi dashboard <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/"
"duplicate-dashboard>` dan membuat perubahan apa pun pada versi duplikat. "
"Dashboard standar dipasang ulang pada setiap peningkatan versi Odoo, yang "
"berarti setiap penyesuaian pada versi asli akan hilang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:265
msgid "Configuration settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan konfigurasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:268
msgid ""
"Only a user with the appropriate :ref:`access rights <access-rights/groups>` "
"can configure or modify settings for dashboards and dashboard sections."
msgstr ""
"Hanya user dengan :ref:`hak akses <access-rights/groups>` yang sesuai yang "
"dapat mengonfigurasi atau mengubah pengaturan untuk dashboard dan bagian "
"dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:271
msgid ""
"To manage dashboards and dashboard sections, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Dashboards`. The following actions are "
"possible at the level of dashboard sections:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola dashboard dan bagian dashboard, "
"buka :menuselection:`Konfigurasi --> Dashboard`. Tindakan berikut dapat "
"dilakukan pada tingkat bagian dashboard:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:274
msgid ""
"**Change the order of dashboard sections** by using the :icon:`oi-"
"draggable` :guilabel:`(drag handle)` icon to move a section to a new "
"position."
msgstr ""
"**Mengubah urutan bagian dashboard** dengan menggunakan ikon :icon:`oi-"
"draggable` :guilabel:`(pegangan seret)` untuk memindahkan bagian ke posisi "
"baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:277
msgid ""
"**Duplicate a dashboard section** by selecting the relevant section name, "
"clicking the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button, and then :icon:`fa-"
"clone` :guilabel:`Duplicate`. The dashboards within the section are not "
"duplicated."
msgstr ""
"**Menduplikasi bagian dashboard** dengan memilih nama bagian yang relevan, "
"mengklik tombol :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Tindakan`, kemudian :icon:`fa-"
"clone` :guilabel:`Duplikasi`. Dashboard dalam bagian tersebut tidak "
"diduplikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:281
msgid ""
"**Delete a dashboard section** by selecting the relevant section name, "
"clicking the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button then :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`Delete`."
msgstr ""
"**Menghapus bagian dashboard** dengan memilih nama bagian yang relevan, "
"mengklik tombol :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Tindakan`, kemudian :icon:`fa-"
"trash-o` :guilabel:`Hapus`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:285
msgid ""
"Standard, pre-installed dashboard sections cannot be deleted; custom "
"dashboard sections, on the other hand, can be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Bagian dashboard standar yang sudah terpasang sebelumnya tidak dapat "
"dihapus; bagian dashboard kustom, sebaliknya, dapat dihapus."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:288
msgid ""
"**Create a new dashboard section** by clicking :guilabel:`New`, then "
"entering the section name. When creating a new section, it is possible to "
"add a dashboard to the new section directly by clicking :guilabel:`Add a "
"spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"**Buat bagian dashboard baru** dengan mengklik :guilabel:`New`, lalu "
"masukkan nama bagian. Saat membuat bagian baru, dimungkinkan untuk "
"menambahkan dashboard ke bagian baru secara langsung dengan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Add a spreadsheet`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:292
msgid ""
"Clicking on an individual dashboard section lists all dashboards within that "
"section. The following actions are possible:"
msgstr ""
"Mengklik bagian dashboard individual akan menampilkan semua dashboard dalam "
"bagian tersebut. Tindakan berikut dimungkinkan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:295
msgid ""
"**Change the order of a dashboard within its section** by using "
"the :icon:`oi-draggable` :guilabel:`(drag handle)` icon to move the "
"dashboard to a new position."
msgstr ""
"**Ubah urutan dashboard dalam bagiannya** dengan menggunakan ikon :icon:`oi-"
"draggable` :guilabel:`(drag handle)` untuk memindahkan dashboard ke posisi "
"baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:298
msgid ""
"**Edit the name of a dashboard section or dashboard** by clicking the name "
"and modifying it."
msgstr ""
"**Edit nama bagian dashboard atau dashboard** dengan mengklik nama dan "
"memodifikasinya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:300
msgid ""
"**Add or remove user groups** to :ref:`control access to the dashboard "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>`."
msgstr ""
"**Tambahkan atau hapus grup user** untuk :ref:`mengontrol akses ke dashboard "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:303
msgid ""
"**Select one or more companies** if, in a :doc:`multi-company <../../"
"applications/general/companies/multi_company>` database, the dashboard "
"should only be visible to users of a specific company or companies. If this "
"field is left blank, the dashboard is visible to all users with the "
"appropriate access rights, regardless of which company is currently selected "
"in the database."
msgstr ""
"**Pilih satu atau lebih perusahaan** jika, dalam database :doc:`multi-"
"perusahaan <../../applications/general/companies/multi_company>`, dashboard "
"hanya boleh terlihat oleh user dari perusahaan atau perusahaan tertentu. "
"Jika kolom ini dibiarkan kosong, dashboard terlihat oleh semua user dengan "
"hak akses yang sesuai, terlepas dari perusahaan mana yang saat ini dipilih "
"dalam database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:309
msgid ""
"**Unpublish a dashboard** by disabling the :guilabel:`Is Published` toggle."
msgstr ""
"**Batalkan publikasi dashboard** dengan menonaktifkan toggle :guilabel:`Is "
"Published`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:311
msgid ""
"**Edit the underlying spreadsheet** of a dashboard by clicking :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`Edit` on the line of the relevant dashboard."
msgstr ""
"**Edit spreadsheet yang mendasari** dashboard dengan mengklik :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`Edit` pada baris dashboard yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:315
msgid ""
"When customizing a standard dashboard, it is highly recommended "
"to :ref:`duplicate the dashboard <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/"
"duplicate-dashboard>` and make any changes on the underlying spreadsheet of "
"the duplicated version. Standard dashboards are reinstalled at each Odoo "
"version upgrade, meaning any customizations on the original version are lost."
msgstr ""
"Saat menyesuaikan dashboard standar, sangat disarankan "
"untuk :ref:`menduplikasi dashboard <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/"
"duplicate-dashboard>` dan membuat perubahan apa pun pada spreadsheet yang "
"mendasari versi yang diduplikasi. Dashboard standar diinstal ulang pada "
"setiap peningkatan versi Odoo, yang berarti setiap kustomisasi pada versi "
"asli akan hilang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:320
msgid ""
"**Delete a dashboard** by clicking the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` "
"icon."
msgstr ""
"**Hapus dashboard** dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"trash` :guilabel:`(trash)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:323
msgid ""
"A standard dashboard that is deleted is reinstalled at the next Odoo version "
"upgrade."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard standar yang dihapus akan diinstal ulang pada peningkatan versi "
"Odoo berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:325
msgid ""
"**Add a new dashboard to the section** by clicking :guilabel:`Add a "
"spreadsheet`. Two options exist:"
msgstr ""
"**Tambahkan dashboard baru ke bagian** dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Add a "
"spreadsheet`. Dua opsi tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:328
msgid ""
"To convert an existing spreadsheet into a dashboard and add it to the new "
"section, select the relevant spreadsheet, then click :guilabel:`Confirm`. "
"Back in the section overview, update the :guilabel:`Group` "
"and :guilabel:`Company` fields if needed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonversi spreadsheet yang ada menjadi dashboard dan menambahkannya "
"ke bagian baru, pilih spreadsheet yang relevan, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Confirm`. Kembali ke tampilan bagian, perbarui "
"bidang :guilabel:`Group` dan :guilabel:`Company` jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:332
msgid ""
"To start creating a dashboard from scratch, select :guilabel:`Blank "
"spreadsheet`. To return to the section overview, click the name of the "
"section in the top-left corner, above the menu bar. Update "
"the :guilabel:`Group` and :guilabel:`Company` fields if needed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mulai membuat dashboard dari awal, pilih :guilabel:`Blank "
"spreadsheet`. Untuk kembali ke ringkasan bagian, klik nama bagian di pojok "
"kiri atas, di atas bilah menu. Perbarui kolom :guilabel:`Group` "
"dan :guilabel:`Company` jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:337
msgid ""
"After a spreadsheet has been converted into a dashboard, it can only "
"be :ref:`accessed and edited via the Dashboards app "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah spreadsheet dikonversi menjadi dashboard, spreadsheet hanya "
"dapat :ref:`diakses dan diedit melalui aplikasi Dashboard "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:341
msgid ""
"A newly created dashboard is by default accessible to users belonging to the "
"default internal :ref:`user group <access-rights/groups>`. Edit this if "
"needed via the :guilabel:`Configuration` settings of the relevant dashboard "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard yang baru dibuat secara default dapat diakses oleh user yang "
"termasuk dalam :ref:`grup user <access-rights/groups>` internal default. "
"Edit ini jika diperlukan melalui pengaturan :guilabel:`Configuration` dari "
"bagian dashboard yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:344
msgid ""
"It is also possible to :ref:`convert a spreadsheet into a dashboard "
"<spreadsheet/get-started/convert-to-dashboard>` and add it to a dashboard "
"section starting from the spreadsheet in the Documents app."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan juga untuk :ref:`mengonversi spreadsheet menjadi dashboard "
"<spreadsheet/get-started/convert-to-dashboard>` dan menambahkannya ke bagian "
"dashboard mulai dari spreadsheet di aplikasi Dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:351
msgid "Access rights and sharing"
msgstr "Hak akses dan pembagian"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:356
msgid "Using dashboards"
msgstr "Menggunakan dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:358
msgid ""
"The *right to view and interact with a dashboard* is based on :ref:`user "
"groups <access-rights/groups>`, and is managed in the :ref:`Configuration "
"settings <dashboards/access-and-sharing/manage-view-access>` of the "
"Dashboards app. Only users who are part of a group that has been granted "
"access to a specific dashboard see that dashboard in the left-hand panel "
"when the Dashboards app is opened. Users with `Dashboard / Admin` access "
"rights can view all dashboards."
msgstr ""
"*Hak untuk melihat dan berinteraksi dengan dashboard* didasarkan "
"pada :ref:`grup user <access-rights/groups>`, dan dikelola "
"dalam :ref:`pengaturan Configuration <dashboards/access-and-sharing/manage-"
"view-access>` dari aplikasi Dashboard. Hanya user yang merupakan bagian dari "
"grup yang telah diberikan akses ke dashboard tertentu yang melihat dashboard "
"tersebut di panel sebelah kiri saat aplikasi Dashboard dibuka. User dengan "
"hak akses `Dashboard / Admin` dapat melihat semua dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:365
msgid ""
"However, the *visibility of dynamic Odoo data within a dashboard* is handled "
"separately. This is based on a user's :ref:`access rights <access-rights/"
"user-permissions>` to the model from which the data has been retrieved, and "
"takes into account any record rules that may restrict access."
msgstr ""
"Namun, *visibilitas data Odoo dinamis dalam dashboard* ditangani secara "
"terpisah. Ini didasarkan pada :ref:`hak akses <access-rights/user-"
"permissions>` user ke model tempat data diambil, dan memperhitungkan aturan "
"record apa pun yang dapat membatasi akses."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:370
msgid ""
"User permissions are taken into account when a user opens a dashboard, with "
"the dashboard only being populated with data the user is authorized to see. "
"This means that a user could in theory be able to view a dashboard but, due "
"to a lack of appropriate permissions, not be able to see the Odoo data the "
"dashboard's creator intended to be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Izin user diperhitungkan ketika user membuka dashboard, dengan dashboard "
"hanya diisi dengan data yang user berwenang untuk melihat. Ini berarti user "
"secara teori dapat melihat dashboard tetapi, karena kurangnya izin yang "
"sesuai, tidak dapat melihat data Odoo yang dimaksudkan oleh pembuat "
"dashboard untuk ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:375
msgid ""
"Therefore, it is crucial to take user permissions into consideration when "
"granting dashboard access to groups."
msgstr ""
"Oleh karena itu, sangat penting untuk mempertimbangkan izin user saat "
"memberikan akses dashboard ke grup."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:379
msgid ""
"Granting the user group `Sales / User: Own Documents Only` access to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` dashboard would serve little purpose. While users "
"belonging to that group would be able to view and interact with the "
"dashboard, they would only see data related to their own sales, rendering "
"the overall dashboard misleading."
msgstr ""
"Memberikan akses grup user `Sales / User: Own Documents Only` ke "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Sales` tidak akan banyak berguna. Meskipun user yang "
"termasuk dalam grup tersebut dapat melihat dan berinteraksi dengan "
"dashboard, mereka hanya akan melihat data yang terkait dengan penjualan "
"mereka sendiri, membuat dashboard secara keseluruhan menyesatkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:387
msgid "Manage access rights to view dashboards"
msgstr "Mengelola hak akses untuk melihat dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:389
msgid "To manage users' rights to view and interact with a dashboard:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola hak user untuk melihat dan berinteraksi dengan dashboard:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:391
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:121
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the Dashboards app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Dashboards`."
msgstr ""
"Di aplikasi Dashboard, buka :menuselection:`Konfigurasi --> Dashboard`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:392
msgid "From the list of dashboard sections, open the relevant section."
msgstr "Dari daftar bagian dashboard, buka bagian yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:393
msgid "On the line of the relevant dashboard, in the :guilabel:`Group` column:"
msgstr "Pada baris dashboard yang relevan, di kolom :guilabel:`Grup`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:395
msgid ""
"add a user group by clicking the field until a dropdown with user groups "
"appears, then selecting the appropriate user group. In the dropdown, "
"click :guilabel:`Search More` to access the full list of user groups;"
msgstr ""
"tambahkan grup user dengan mengklik field hingga dropdown dengan grup user "
"muncul, lalu pilih grup user yang sesuai. Dalam dropdown, "
"klik :guilabel:`Cari Lebih Banyak` untuk mengakses daftar lengkap grup user;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:398
msgid ""
"remove a user group by clicking the relevant group name, then "
"clicking :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(Delete)`."
msgstr ""
"hapus grup user dengan mengklik nama grup yang relevan, lalu klik :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(Hapus)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:404
msgid "Building, customizing and configuring dashboards"
msgstr "Membangun, menyesuaikan, dan mengonfigurasi dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:406
msgid ""
"Only users with `Dashboards / Admin` access rights can :ref:`customize "
"dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` or :ref:`configure "
"dashboard settings <dashboards/configuration>`. To :ref:`build a dashboard "
"from scratch <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>`, a user must have both "
"`Dashboards / Admin` and, at minimum for the Documents app, `Documents / "
"User` access rights."
msgstr ""
"Hanya user dengan hak akses `Dashboard / Admin` yang "
"dapat :ref:`menyesuaikan dashboard <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"customize>` atau :ref:`mengonfigurasi pengaturan dashboard <dashboards/"
"configuration>`. Untuk :ref:`membangun dashboard dari awal "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/build>`, user harus memiliki hak akses "
"`Dashboard / Admin` dan, minimal untuk aplikasi Dokumen, hak akses "
"`Dokumen / User`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:415
msgid "Sharing a dashboard snapshot"
msgstr "Membagikan snapshot dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:417
msgid ""
"To share a frozen version of a dashboard with an internal user who does not "
"have the appropriate access or with an external party, click :icon:`fa-share-"
"alt` :guilabel:`Share` at the top-right of the page then click the :icon:`fa-"
"clone` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon to copy a shareable link to your clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membagikan versi frozen dari dashboard dengan user internal yang tidak "
"memiliki akses yang sesuai atau dengan pihak eksternal, klik :icon:`fa-share-"
"alt` :guilabel:`Bagikan` di bagian kanan atas halaman, lalu klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-clone` :guilabel:`(salin)` untuk menyalin link yang dapat "
"dibagikan ke clipboard Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:3
msgid "Build and customize dashboards"
msgstr "Membangun dan menyesuaikan dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:5
msgid ""
"In addition to consulting :ref:`standard dashboards <dashboards/standard>`, "
"users with the appropriate :ref:`access rights <dashboards/access-and-"
"sharing/customize-configure-build>` can :ref:`build custom dashboards from "
"scratch <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>` or :ref:`customize existing "
"dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` to respond to "
"specific business needs."
msgstr ""
"Selain berkonsultasi dengan :ref:`dashboard standar <dashboards/standard>`, "
"user dengan :ref:`hak akses <dashboards/access-and-sharing/customize-"
"configure-build>` yang sesuai dapat :ref:`membangun dashboard kustom dari "
"awal <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>` atau :ref:`menyesuaikan "
"dashboard yang ada <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` untuk "
"merespons kebutuhan bisnis tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:14
msgid "Build a dashboard"
msgstr "Membangun dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:16
msgid ""
"In its most simple terms, building a dashboard involves :doc:`inserting Odoo "
"data into a spreadsheet <../spreadsheet/insert>` then :ref:`converting that "
"spreadsheet into a dashboard <spreadsheet/get-started/convert-to-dashboard>`."
msgstr ""
"Dalam istilah yang paling sederhana, membangun dashboard "
"melibatkan :doc:`memasukkan data Odoo ke dalam spreadsheet <../spreadsheet/"
"insert>` kemudian :ref:`mengonversi spreadsheet tersebut menjadi dashboard "
"<spreadsheet/get-started/convert-to-dashboard>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:20
msgid ""
"However, to build a dashboard that delivers relevant and valuable insights, "
"it is important to consider the process in terms of three key "
"stages: :ref:`preparation <build_and_customize_dashboards/build-"
"preparation>`, :ref:`data insertion and manipulation "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/build-insertion-manipulation>`, "
"and :ref:`data visualization <build_and_customize_dashboards/build-"
"visualization>`."
msgstr ""
"Namun, untuk membangun dashboard yang memberikan insight relevan dan "
"berharga, penting untuk mempertimbangkan prosesnya dalam tiga tahap "
"kunci: :ref:`persiapan <build_and_customize_dashboards/build-"
"preparation>`, :ref:`penyisipan dan manipulasi data "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/build-insertion-manipulation>`, "
"dan :ref:`visualisasi data <build_and_customize_dashboards/build-"
"visualization>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:29
msgid "Preparation"
msgstr "Persiapan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:48
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:64
msgid "This stage involves:"
msgstr "Tahap ini melibatkan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:33
msgid ""
"defining the purpose of the dashboard, in other words, the business "
"questions it needs to answer, and deciding what data would answer those "
"questions;"
msgstr ""
"mendefinisikan tujuan dashboard, dengan kata lain, pertanyaan bisnis yang "
"perlu dijawab, dan memutuskan data apa yang akan menjawab pertanyaan "
"tersebut;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:35
msgid ""
"determining where to find the relevant Odoo data and deciding "
"which :doc:`type of view <../../studio/views>` (i.e., list, pivot table, or "
"chart) is most suited for the data analysis needed;"
msgstr ""
"menentukan di mana menemukan data Odoo yang relevan dan "
"memutuskan :doc:`tipe tampilan <../../studio/views>` mana (yaitu, list, "
"tabel pivot, atau grafik) yang paling cocok untuk analisis data yang "
"diperlukan;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:38
msgid ""
"preparing the Odoo data by refining the views to focus on the most relevant "
"information, e.g., by using :doc:`search filters <../../essentials/search>`, "
"by making only certain list fields visible, or by deciding which dimensions "
"and measures a pivot table should use;"
msgstr ""
"menyiapkan data Odoo dengan memperbaiki tampilan untuk fokus pada informasi "
"yang paling relevan, misalnya, dengan menggunakan :doc:`filter pencarian "
"<../../essentials/search>`, dengan membuat hanya kolom list tertentu yang "
"terlihat, atau dengan memutuskan dimensi dan ukuran mana yang harus "
"digunakan tabel pivot;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:41
msgid "sourcing any other information needed to support the dashboard."
msgstr "mencari informasi lain yang diperlukan untuk mendukung dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:46
msgid "Data insertion and manipulation"
msgstr "Penyisipan dan manipulasi data"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:50
msgid ""
"inserting the prepared :doc:`lists <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_list>`, :doc:`pivot tables <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_pivot_table>` or :doc:`charts <../spreadsheet/insert/insert_chart>` "
"into the spreadsheet you will use to build your dashboard;"
msgstr ""
"memasukkan :doc:`daftar <../spreadsheet/insert/insert_list>`, :doc:`tabel "
"pivot <../spreadsheet/insert/insert_pivot_table>`, atau :doc:`grafik <../"
"spreadsheet/insert/insert_chart>` yang telah disiapkan ke dalam spreadsheet "
"yang akan Anda gunakan untuk membuat dashboard;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:53
msgid ""
"manipulating the data, if needed, to be able to draw the necessary insights. "
"This may involve performing calculations or creating custom metrics "
"using :doc:`standard or Odoo-specific functions and formulas <../spreadsheet/"
"work_with_data/functions>`, referencing data from various sources within the "
"spreadsheet, or :ref:`converting static pivot tables to dynamic pivot tables "
"<spreadsheet/insert-pivot-table/static-convert>`."
msgstr ""
"memanipulasi data, jika diperlukan, untuk dapat menarik insight yang "
"diperlukan. Ini mungkin melibatkan melakukan kalkulasi atau membuat metrik "
"khusus menggunakan :doc:`fungsi dan formula standar atau khusus Odoo <../"
"spreadsheet/work_with_data/functions>`, mereferensikan data dari berbagai "
"sumber dalam spreadsheet, atau :ref:`mengonversi tabel pivot statis menjadi "
"tabel pivot dinamis <spreadsheet/insert-pivot-table/static-convert>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:62
msgid "Data visualization"
msgstr "Visualisasi data"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:66
msgid ""
"presenting the data on at least the first sheet of your spreadsheet (i.e., "
"the sheet that will serve as the front end of your dashboard) in a clear, "
"visual, and meaningful way so it is easy to interpret. Concretely, this "
"means deciding on the layout and order of elements such as tables and "
"charts, as well as using tools and techniques to guide the user, such as "
"clear and descriptive headings, text formatting and colors, carefully chosen "
"chart types, and conditional formatting to highlight specific data visually;"
msgstr ""
"menyajikan data setidaknya pada sheet pertama spreadsheet Anda (yaitu, sheet "
"yang akan berfungsi sebagai front end dashboard Anda) dengan cara yang "
"jelas, visual, dan bermakna sehingga mudah diinterpretasikan. Secara "
"konkret, ini berarti memutuskan tata letak dan urutan elemen seperti tabel "
"dan grafik, serta menggunakan alat dan teknik untuk memandu user, seperti "
"judul yang jelas dan deskriptif, pemformatan teks dan warna, jenis grafik "
"yang dipilih dengan cermat, dan pemformatan bersyarat untuk menyoroti data "
"tertentu secara visual;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:72
msgid ""
":doc:`inserting clickable links <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_clickable_links>`, if relevant, to provide access to Odoo menu items, "
"URLs, or other sheets within the same spreadsheet if these should also be "
"accessible from the front end of your dashboard;"
msgstr ""
":doc:`memasukkan tautan yang dapat diklik <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_clickable_links>`, jika relevan, untuk memberikan akses ke item menu "
"Odoo, URL, atau sheet lain dalam spreadsheet yang sama jika ini juga harus "
"dapat diakses dari front end dashboard Anda;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:75
msgid ""
":doc:`creating global filters <../spreadsheet/work_with_data/"
"global_filters>` to allow users to tailor the view to their needs;"
msgstr ""
":doc:`membuat filter global <../spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters>` "
"untuk memungkinkan user menyesuaikan tampilan sesuai kebutuhan mereka;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:77
msgid ""
":ref:`converting the spreadsheet into a dashboard <spreadsheet/get-started/"
"convert-to-dashboard>`, determining whether to add the dashboard to an "
"existing or new dashboard section, and :ref:`managing access rights to the "
"dashboard <dashboards/access-and-sharing/manage-view-access>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mengonversi spreadsheet menjadi dashboard <spreadsheet/get-started/"
"convert-to-dashboard>`, menentukan apakah akan menambahkan dashboard ke "
"bagian dashboard yang ada atau baru, dan :ref:`mengelola hak akses ke "
"dashboard <dashboards/access-and-sharing/manage-view-access>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:83
msgid ""
"Use standard dashboards as inspiration for how to best present and visualize "
"data. For example, for charts, :ref:`open the underlying spreadsheet "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/open-spreadsheet>` of a standard "
"dashboard, hover over a chart and click the :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(menu)` icon, then :icon:`fa-pencil-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Edit` to see the chart properties on the right side of the "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan dashboard standar sebagai inspirasi untuk cara terbaik menyajikan "
"dan memvisualisasikan data. Misalnya, untuk grafik, :ref:`buka spreadsheet "
"yang mendasari <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/open-spreadsheet>` "
"dashboard standar, arahkan kursor ke grafik dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(menu)`, lalu :icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Edit` "
"untuk melihat properti grafik di sisi kanan layar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:89
msgid ""
"The possibility to link to other sheets within the same spreadsheet allows "
"the creation of a multi-page dashboard, with users able to navigate between "
"pages thanks to clickable links. Global filters apply across all pages of a "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Kemungkinan untuk menautkan ke sheet lain dalam spreadsheet yang sama "
"memungkinkan pembuatan dashboard multi-halaman, dengan user dapat menavigasi "
"antar halaman berkat link yang dapat diklik. Filter global berlaku di semua "
"halaman dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:94
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorial: Dashboard from scratch <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"dashboard-from-scratch-8957>`_"
msgstr ""
"Tutorial Odoo: Dashboard dari awal <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"dashboard-from-scratch-8957>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:100
msgid "Customize a dashboard"
msgstr "Kustomisasi dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:102
msgid ""
"A dashboard can be customized by :ref:`opening its underlying spreadsheet "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/open-spreadsheet>`, i.e., the Odoo "
"spreadsheet from which the dashboard has been created, and :ref:`making any "
"desired changes <dashboards/customize-dashboard/edit-spreadsheet>`."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard dapat disesuaikan dengan :ref:`membuka spreadsheet dasarnya "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/open-spreadsheet>`, yaitu, "
"spreadsheet Odoo dari mana dashboard telah dibuat, dan :ref:`membuat "
"perubahan yang diinginkan <dashboards/customize-dashboard/edit-spreadsheet>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:110
msgid "Open the underlying spreadsheet"
msgstr "Buka spreadsheet yang mendasari"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:113
msgid ""
"When customizing a :ref:`standard dashboard <dashboards/standard>`, it is "
"highly recommended to :ref:`duplicate the dashboard "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/duplicate-dashboard>` and make any "
"changes on the underlying spreadsheet of the duplicated version. Standard "
"dashboards are reinstalled at each Odoo version upgrade, meaning any "
"customizations on the original version are lost."
msgstr ""
"Saat menyesuaikan :ref:`dashboard standar <dashboards/standard>`, sangat "
"disarankan untuk :ref:`menduplikasi dashboard "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/duplicate-dashboard>` dan membuat "
"perubahan apa pun pada spreadsheet dasar dari versi yang diduplikasi. "
"Dashboard standar diinstal ulang pada setiap peningkatan versi Odoo, yang "
"berarti setiap penyesuaian pada versi asli akan hilang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:119
msgid "To open a dashboard's underlying spreadsheet:"
msgstr "Untuk membuka spreadsheet yang mendasari dashboard:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:122
msgid ""
"Open the relevant dashboard section, then, on the line of the relevant "
"dashboard, click :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Buka bagian dashboard yang relevan, kemudian pada baris dashboard yang "
"relevan, klik :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:126
msgid ""
"To temporarily unpublish a dashboard while you make changes, "
"disable :guilabel:`Is Published` *before* editing the dashboard, making note "
"to republish it when the customization has been finalized."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyembunyikan sementara dashboard saat Anda melakukan perubahan, "
"nonaktifkan :guilabel:`Is Published` *sebelum* mengedit dashboard, dan catat "
"untuk menerbitkannya kembali setelah kustomisasi selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:129
msgid ""
"Users who do not have the appropriate :ref:`access rights <dashboards/access-"
"and-sharing/customize-configure-build>` to customize a dashboard can still "
"access a read-only version of the dashboard's underlying spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna yang tidak memiliki :ref:`hak akses <dashboards/access-and-sharing/"
"customize-configure-build>` yang sesuai untuk mengkustomisasi dashboard "
"masih dapat mengakses versi read-only dari spreadsheet yang mendasari "
"dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:132
msgid ""
"With :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` activated, click on "
"the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)` icon beside the name of a dashboard "
"in the left panel to open its underlying spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Dengan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>` diaktifkan, klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)` di samping nama dashboard di panel "
"kiri untuk membuka spreadsheet yang mendasarinya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:136
msgid "The spreadsheet that opens typically consists of at least two sheets:"
msgstr "Spreadsheet yang terbuka biasanya terdiri dari setidaknya dua sheet:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:138
msgid ""
"**The first sheet** always serves as the front end of your dashboard, and "
"contains the tables and charts used to structure and visualize the data."
msgstr ""
"**Sheet pertama** selalu berfungsi sebagai front end dashboard Anda, dan "
"berisi tabel dan grafik yang digunakan untuk menyusun dan memvisualisasikan "
"data."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:141
msgid ""
"**The second and any subsequent sheets** typically contain data used for the "
"calculation of key metrics shown on the first sheet."
msgstr ""
"**Sheet kedua dan berikutnya** biasanya berisi data yang digunakan untuk "
"penghitungan metrik utama yang ditampilkan pada sheet pertama."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:145
msgid ""
"The :ref:`data sources <spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` that maintain the "
"connection between the spreadsheet and the relevant models in your database "
"can be viewed by clicking :menuselection:`Data` on the spreadsheet's menu "
"bar. These data sources are identified by their respective :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(pivot table)`, :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(list)` "
"or :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`(chart)` icon, followed by their ID and "
"name, e.g., :icon:`oi-view-pivot` *(#1) Sales Analysis by Product*."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Sumber data <spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` yang mempertahankan "
"koneksi antara spreadsheet dan model yang relevan dalam database Anda dapat "
"dilihat dengan mengklik :menuselection:`Data` pada bilah menu spreadsheet. "
"Sumber data ini diidentifikasi dengan ikon :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(pivot table)`, :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(list)`, "
"atau :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`(chart)` masing-masing, diikuti dengan "
"ID dan namanya, misalnya :icon:`oi-view-pivot` *(#1) Sales Analysis by "
"Product*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:152
msgid ""
"For :ref:`standard dashboards <dashboards/standard>`, while the data sources "
"are still active and visible in the :menuselection:`Data` menu, the "
"corresponding lists and pivot tables have been removed from the spreadsheet "
"for better performance and a neater appearance."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :ref:`dashboard standar <dashboards/standard>`, meskipun sumber data "
"masih aktif dan terlihat di menu :menuselection:`Data`, list dan tabel pivot "
"yang sesuai telah dihapus dari spreadsheet untuk kinerja yang lebih baik dan "
"tampilan yang lebih rapi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:159
msgid "Duplicate a dashboard"
msgstr "Duplikasi dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:161
msgid "To duplicate a dashboard:"
msgstr "Untuk menduplikasi dashboard:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:164
msgid ""
"Open the relevant dashboard section, then, on the line of the dashboard you "
"want to duplicate, click :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Buka bagian dashboard yang relevan, kemudian pada baris dashboard yang ingin "
"Anda duplikasi, klik :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:166
msgid ""
"In the spreadsheet that opens, click :menuselection:`File -->` :icon:`os-"
"copy-file` :menuselection:`Make a copy`."
msgstr ""
"Dalam spreadsheet yang terbuka, klik :menuselection:`File -->` :icon:`os-"
"copy-file` :menuselection:`Make a copy`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:168
msgid ""
"Rename the duplicated dashboard by clicking the name of the spreadsheet at "
"the top left of the screen and editing as needed."
msgstr ""
"Ganti nama dashboard yang diduplikasi dengan mengklik nama spreadsheet di "
"pojok kiri atas layar dan edit sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:172
msgid ""
"To return to the overview of the dashboard section, click the name of the "
"original dashboard at the top left of the page, then the name of the "
"dashboard section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk kembali ke ringkasan bagian dashboard, klik nama dashboard asli di "
"pojok kiri atas halaman, kemudian nama bagian dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:174
msgid ""
"After duplicating a dashboard, delete the original dashboard by clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon or rename it by clicking on "
"the name then editing it."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menduplikasi dashboard, hapus dashboard asli dengan mengklik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` atau ganti namanya dengan mengklik "
"nama kemudian mengeditnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:180
msgid "Add, edit, or remove dashboard elements"
msgstr "Tambah, edit, atau hapus elemen dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:182
msgid "Dashboards can be customized in various ways, such as by:"
msgstr "Dashboard dapat dikustomisasi dengan berbagai cara, seperti dengan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:184
msgid ""
"adding new tables and charts based on previously inserted or :ref:`newly "
"inserted Odoo data <dashboards/customize-dashboard/edit-spreadsheet-new-odoo-"
"data>`. This requires a similar approach to :ref:`building a dashboard from "
"scratch <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>`;"
msgstr ""
"menambahkan tabel dan grafik baru berdasarkan data Odoo yang telah "
"disisipkan sebelumnya atau :ref:`data Odoo yang baru disisipkan <dashboards/"
"customize-dashboard/edit-spreadsheet-new-odoo-data>`. Ini memerlukan "
"pendekatan yang mirip dengan :ref:`membuat dashboard dari awal "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/build>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:187
msgid ""
":doc:`adding new global filters <../spreadsheet/work_with_data/"
"global_filters>` or editing or deleting existing ones;"
msgstr ""
":doc:`menambahkan filter global baru <../spreadsheet/work_with_data/"
"global_filters>` atau mengedit atau menghapus yang sudah ada;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:189
msgid ""
":doc:`adding or editing clickable links <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_clickable_links>` to Odoo menus, URLs, or to other sheets within the "
"same spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
":doc:`menambahkan atau mengedit tautan yang dapat diklik <../spreadsheet/"
"insert/insert_clickable_links>` ke menu Odoo, URL, atau ke sheet lain dalam "
"spreadsheet yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:193
msgid ""
"The first tab of the spreadsheet serves as the front end of the dashboard. "
"Any tables or charts that should be visible on the final dashboard need to "
"be added to this sheet."
msgstr ""
"Tab pertama dari spreadsheet berfungsi sebagai front end dari dashboard. "
"Tabel atau grafik apa pun yang harus terlihat pada dashboard akhir perlu "
"ditambahkan ke sheet ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:195
msgid ""
"Dashboard elements that are no longer needed can be deleted from the "
"spreadsheet. If, after deleting a dashboard element, a :ref:`data source "
"<spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` is no longer being used in the "
"spreadsheet, this is indicated by a :icon:`fa-exclamation-"
"triangle` :guilabel:`(warning)` icon in the :guilabel:`Data` menu."
msgstr ""
"Elemen dashboard yang tidak lagi diperlukan dapat dihapus dari spreadsheet. "
"Jika, setelah menghapus elemen dashboard, sebuah :ref:`sumber data "
"<spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` tidak lagi digunakan dalam spreadsheet, "
"hal ini ditandai dengan ikon :icon:`fa-exclamation-"
"triangle` :guilabel:`(peringatan)` di menu :guilabel:`Data`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:0
msgid "Warning to indicate data source no longer used in spreadsheet"
msgstr ""
"Peringatan untuk menunjukkan sumber data tidak lagi digunakan dalam "
"spreadsheet"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:206
msgid "Insert new Odoo data"
msgstr "Sisipkan data Odoo baru"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:208
msgid ""
"New Odoo data, such as lists, pivot tables, or charts, can be inserted into "
"a dashboard, starting from the relevant list view, pivot view, or graph "
"view. Concretely, a list or pivot table is inserted into a new sheet in the "
"dashboard's underlying spreadsheet; a chart is inserted on the first sheet "
"of the spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Data Odoo baru, seperti daftar, tabel pivot, atau grafik, dapat disisipkan "
"ke dalam dashboard, dimulai dari tampilan daftar, tampilan pivot, atau "
"tampilan grafik yang relevan. Secara konkret, daftar atau tabel pivot "
"disisipkan ke dalam sheet baru di spreadsheet yang mendasari dashboard; "
"grafik disisipkan pada sheet pertama dari spreadsheet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:213
msgid "To insert new data:"
msgstr "Untuk menyisipkan data baru:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:215
msgid ""
"With the relevant list view, pivot view or graph view open in your database, "
"proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Dengan tampilan daftar, tampilan pivot, atau tampilan grafik yang relevan "
"terbuka di database Anda, lanjutkan sebagai berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:217
msgid ""
"For a list view, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon beside "
"the name of the view, then :guilabel:`Spreadsheet -->` :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :menuselection:`Insert list in spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk tampilan daftar, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Tindakan)` di "
"samping nama tampilan, kemudian :guilabel:`Spreadsheet -->` :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :menuselection:`Sisipkan daftar di spreadsheet`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:220
msgid ""
"For a pivot or graph view, click :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet` at the "
"top left of the view."
msgstr ""
"Untuk tampilan pivot atau grafik, klik :guilabel:`Sisipkan dalam "
"Spreadsheet` di kiri atas tampilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:222
msgid ""
"In the window that opens, edit the name if needed. For a list, edit the "
"number of records, i.e., rows to be inserted, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela yang terbuka, edit nama jika diperlukan. Untuk daftar, edit "
"jumlah catatan, yaitu baris yang akan disisipkan, jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:224
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Dashboards` tab then select in which dashboard the "
"list, pivot table, or chart should be inserted."
msgstr ""
"Klik tab :guilabel:`Dashboard` kemudian pilih di dashboard mana daftar, "
"tabel pivot, atau grafik harus disisipkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:227
msgid ""
"The dashboard's underlying spreadsheet opens, with the new data inserted "
"either on a new sheet (list or pivot table) or on the first sheet (chart)."
msgstr ""
"Spreadsheet yang mendasari dashboard terbuka, dengan data baru yang "
"disisipkan baik pada sheet baru (daftar atau tabel pivot) atau pada sheet "
"pertama (grafik)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:231
msgid ":doc:`Inserting Odoo data into a spreadsheet <../spreadsheet/insert>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Menyisipkan data Odoo ke dalam spreadsheet <../spreadsheet/insert>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:3
msgid "My Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard Saya"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:6
msgid ""
"To have access to **My Dashboard**, make sure the :guilabel:`Dashboards` "
"(`board`) module is :ref:`installed <general/install>` in addition to "
"the :guilabel:`Spreadsheet dashboard` (`spreadsheet_dashboard)` module."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memiliki akses ke **My Dashboard**, pastikan "
"modul :guilabel:`Dashboard` (`board`) telah :ref:`diinstal <general/"
"install>` selain modul :guilabel:`Spreadsheet dashboard` "
"(`spreadsheet_dashboard)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:10
msgid ""
"**My Dashboard** allows you to centralize the :doc:`Odoo views <../../studio/"
"views>` you consult most regularly, making it possible to see critical tasks "
"at a glance without having to first navigate through multiple apps."
msgstr ""
"**Dashboard Saya** memungkinkan Anda memusatkan :doc:`tampilan Odoo <../../"
"studio/views>` yang paling sering Anda konsultasikan, sehingga memungkinkan "
"untuk melihat tugas-tugas penting sekilas tanpa harus terlebih dahulu "
"menavigasi melalui beberapa aplikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:14
msgid "My Dashboard is empty until at least one view has been added."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard Saya kosong hingga setidaknya satu tampilan telah ditambahkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:0
msgid "Example of views added to My Dashboard"
msgstr "Contoh tampilan yang ditambahkan ke Dashboard Saya"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:19
msgid ""
"Views inserted in My Dashboard are fully dynamic and retain many features of "
"the source view, e.g., sorting of lists, changing the measures used for a "
"pivot table or cohort view, changing the chart type, or clicking on a value "
"or data point to view the underlying record(s)."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan yang disisipkan di Dashboard Saya sepenuhnya dinamis dan "
"mempertahankan banyak fitur dari tampilan sumber, misalnya penyortiran "
"daftar, mengubah ukuran yang digunakan untuk tabel pivot atau tampilan "
"kohort, mengubah jenis grafik, atau mengklik nilai atau titik data untuk "
"melihat catatan yang mendasarinya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:24
msgid ""
"It is not possible to change the domain, i.e., the :doc:`filtering or "
"grouping <../../essentials/search>`, of a view that has been added to My "
"Dashboard. To change the domain, make the necessary changes in the original "
"view, then re-insert the view in My Dashboard and delete the originally "
"inserted view."
msgstr ""
"Tidak mungkin mengubah domain, yaitu :doc:`pemfilteran atau pengelompokan "
"<../../essentials/search>`, dari tampilan yang telah ditambahkan ke "
"Dashboard Saya. Untuk mengubah domain, lakukan perubahan yang diperlukan "
"pada tampilan asli, lalu sisipkan kembali tampilan tersebut di Dashboard "
"Saya dan hapus tampilan yang awalnya disisipkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:28
msgid ""
"Unlike other Odoo dashboards, My Dashboard is not based on **Odoo "
"Spreadsheet**."
msgstr ""
"Tidak seperti dashboard Odoo lainnya, Dashboard Saya tidak didasarkan pada "
"**Odoo Spreadsheet**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:33
msgid "Add views"
msgstr "Tambahkan tampilan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:35
msgid "Most Odoo views can be added to My Dashboard, including:"
msgstr ""
"Sebagian besar tampilan Odoo dapat ditambahkan ke Dashboard Saya, termasuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:37
msgid ""
":ref:`multiple record views <studio/views/multiple-records>` like list, "
"kanban, and map"
msgstr ""
":ref:`tampilan catatan ganda <studio/views/multiple-records>` seperti "
"daftar, kanban, dan peta"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:38
msgid ""
":ref:`timeline views <studio/views/timeline>` like calendar, cohort, and "
"gantt"
msgstr ""
":ref:`tampilan timeline <studio/views/timeline>` seperti kalender, kohort, "
"dan gantt"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:39
msgid ":ref:`reporting views <studio/views/reporting>` like pivot and graph"
msgstr ""
":ref:`tampilan pelaporan <studio/views/reporting>` seperti pivot dan grafik"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:41
msgid "To add a view to My Dashboard:"
msgstr "Untuk menambahkan tampilan ke Dashboard Saya:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:43
msgid ""
"With the relevant view open in your database, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon beside the name of the view, "
"then :menuselection:`Dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"Dengan tampilan yang relevan terbuka di database Anda, klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Tindakan)` di samping nama tampilan, "
"kemudian :menuselection:`Dashboard`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:45
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Add to my Dashboard`, rename the view if desired, then "
"click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah :guilabel:`Tambahkan ke Dashboard Saya`, ganti nama tampilan jika "
"diinginkan, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:0
msgid "Adding a view to My Dashboard"
msgstr "Menambahkan tampilan ke Dashboard Saya"

