msgid "Refresh the page."
msgstr "Segarkan halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:53
msgid ""
"The added view is now visible as a widget in My Dashboard in the Dashboards "
"app."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan yang ditambahkan sekarang terlihat sebagai widget di Dashboard Saya "
"dalam aplikasi Dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:56
msgid ""
"If added views are not showing in My Dashboard, refresh the browser page."
msgstr ""
"Jika tampilan yang ditambahkan tidak muncul di Dashboard Saya, segarkan "
"halaman browser."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:61
msgid "Customize layout"
msgstr "Sesuaikan tata letak"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:63
msgid ""
"When at least one view has been added to My Dashboard, the page can be "
"customized as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Ketika setidaknya satu tampilan telah ditambahkan ke Dashboard Saya, halaman "
"dapat disesuaikan sebagai berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:65
msgid ""
"**Change the layout of the page**: Click :guilabel:`Change Layout` in the "
"top-right corner and select the desired layout."
msgstr ""
"**Ubah tata letak halaman**: Klik :guilabel:`Ubah Tata Letak` di pojok kanan "
"atas dan pilih tata letak yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:69
msgid ""
"For multi-column layouts, the column limits are identified by :icon:`fa-"
"caret-left` :guilabel:`(left caret)` and :icon:`fa-caret-"
"right` :guilabel:`(right caret)` icons at the bottom of the page. If needed, "
"scroll to the bottom of the page to see the column limits."
msgstr ""
"Untuk tata letak multi-kolom, batas kolom ditandai dengan ikon :icon:`fa-"
"caret-left` :guilabel:`(tanda sisipan kiri)` dan :icon:`fa-caret-"
"right` :guilabel:`(tanda sisipan kanan)` di bagian bawah halaman. Jika "
"perlu, gulir ke bagian bawah halaman untuk melihat batas kolom."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:0
msgid "Column limits visible at bottom of page"
msgstr "Batas kolom terlihat di bagian bawah halaman"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:76
msgid ""
"**Collapse and expand widgets**: By default, an inserted widget is shown "
"fully expanded. To collapse, or minimize, a widget, and show only the title, "
"click the :icon:`fa-window-minimize` :guilabel:`(minimize)` icon at the top "
"right of the widget. To expand a widget, click the :icon:`fa-window-"
"maximize` :guilabel:`(maximize)` icon."
msgstr ""
"**Ciutkan dan perluas widget**: Secara default, widget yang disisipkan "
"ditampilkan secara penuh. Untuk menciutkan, atau meminimalkan, widget dan "
"hanya menampilkan judulnya, klik ikon :icon:`fa-window-"
"minimize` :guilabel:`(minimalkan)` di kanan atas widget. Untuk memperluas "
"widget, klik ikon :icon:`fa-window-maximize` :guilabel:`(maksimalkan)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:80
msgid ""
"**Move widgets**: Drag and drop widgets to the desired location in the same "
"column or a different column."
msgstr ""
"**Pindahkan widget**: Seret dan lepas widget ke lokasi yang diinginkan di "
"kolom yang sama atau kolom yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:82
msgid ""
"**Remove widgets**: To remove a widget from the page, click the :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon."
msgstr ""
"**Hapus widget**: Untuk menghapus widget dari halaman, klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(hapus)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:3
msgid "Data Cleaning"
msgstr "Pembersihan Data"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Data Cleaning** app maintains data integrity and consistency with "
"the following features:"
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Data Cleaning** Odoo menjaga integritas dan konsistensi data "
"dengan fitur-fitur berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:7
msgid ""
":ref:`Deduplicates <data_cleaning/deduplication>`: merges or removes "
"duplicate entries to ensure data is unique."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Deduplikasi <data_cleaning/deduplication>`: menggabungkan atau "
"menghapus entri duplikat untuk memastikan data bersifat unik."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:9
msgid ""
":ref:`Recycles <data_cleaning/recycle>`: identifies outdated records to "
"either archive or delete them."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Daur ulang <data_cleaning/recycle>`: mengidentifikasi catatan yang "
"sudah usang untuk diarsipkan atau dihapus."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:11
msgid ""
":ref:`Formats <data_cleaning/field-cleaning>`: standardizes text data by "
"finding and replacing it according to specified needs."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pemformatan <data_cleaning/field-cleaning>`: menstandardisasi data "
"teks dengan menemukan dan menggantinya sesuai kebutuhan yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:14
msgid ""
"Customizable rules ensure text data stays up-to-date, streamlined, "
"consistently formatted, and aligned with company-specific formatting "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Aturan yang dapat disesuaikan memastikan data teks tetap terkini, efisien, "
"diformat secara konsisten, dan selaras dengan persyaratan pemformatan khusus "
"perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:20
msgid "Install modules"
msgstr "Instal modul"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:22
msgid ""
"The **Data Cleaning** application consists of several modules. :ref:`Install "
"<general/install>` the following to access all available features:"
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Data Cleaning** terdiri dari beberapa modul. :ref:`Instal "
"<general/install>` yang berikut untuk mengakses semua fitur yang tersedia:"

