#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:3
msgid "Canned responses"
msgstr "Tanggapan Otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Canned responses* are customizable inputs where a typed shortcut populates "
"a longer response. A user enters a keyword shortcut, which is then "
"automatically replaced by the expanded substitution response. Canned "
"responses save time by allowing users to use shorthand phrases to populate "
"longer messages. This also limits the possibility of errors when typing out "
"longer messages because these are pre-set messages. This maintains "
"consistency throughout customer interactions."
msgstr ""
"*Canned responses* adalah input yang dapat disesuaikan di mana pintasan yang "
"diketik mengisi respons yang lebih panjang. User memasukkan pintasan kata "
"kunci, yang kemudian secara otomatis diganti dengan respons substitusi yang "
"diperluas. Canned responses menghemat waktu dengan memungkinkan user "
"menggunakan frasa singkat untuk mengisi pesan yang lebih panjang. Ini juga "
"membatasi kemungkinan kesalahan saat mengetik pesan yang lebih panjang "
"karena ini adalah pesan yang telah ditetapkan sebelumnya. Ini menjaga "
"konsistensi di seluruh interaksi pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:11
msgid ""
"Canned responses consist of two main components: the *shortcut* and the "
"*substitution*. The shortcut is the keyword or key phrase that is to be "
"replaced. The substitution is the longer message that replaces the shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Canned responses terdiri dari dua komponen utama: *pintasan* dan "
"*substitusi*. Pintasan adalah kata kunci atau frasa kunci yang akan diganti. "
"Substitusi adalah pesan yang lebih panjang yang menggantikan pintasan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:None
msgid "A live chat conversation using a canned response."
msgstr "Percakapan live chat yang menggunakan canned response."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:18
msgid ""
"Canned responses are available :ref:`to use <discuss/use-cases>` in **Live "
"Chat** conversations, the **Discuss** app, and the *Chatter*. Canned "
"responses are also available in direct message conversations, channel "
"conversations, and *WhatsApp* messages."
msgstr ""
"Canned responses tersedia :ref:`untuk digunakan <discuss/use-cases>` dalam "
"percakapan **Live Chat**, aplikasi **Diskusi**, dan *Chatter*. Canned "
"responses juga tersedia dalam percakapan pesan langsung, percakapan channel, "
"dan pesan *WhatsApp*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:25
msgid "Creating canned responses"
msgstr "Membuat canned responses"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:27
msgid ""
"Canned responses are managed through the **Discuss** application. To create "
"a new canned response, or manage the list of existing responses, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Discuss app --> Configuration --> Canned Responses`."
msgstr ""
"Canned responses dikelola melalui aplikasi **Diskusi**. Untuk membuat canned "
"response baru, atau mengelola daftar respons yang ada, "
"buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Diskusi --> Konfigurasi --> Canned Responses`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:31
msgid ""
"Then, to create a new canned response, click :guilabel:`New` at the top-left "
"of the list. Doing so reveals a new blank line in the list."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, untuk membuat canned response baru, klik :guilabel:`Baru` di kiri "
"atas daftar. Melakukan ini akan menampilkan baris kosong baru dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:34
msgid ""
"Canned responses consist of two main components, a *shortcut* the user "
"enters, and the *substitution* that replaces the shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Canned responses terdiri dari dua komponen utama, *pintasan* yang dimasukkan "
"user, dan *substitusi* yang menggantikan pintasan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:None
msgid ""
"A list of canned responses emphasizing the shortcut and substitution fields."
msgstr "Daftar respons cepat yang menekankan field shortcut dan substitution."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:40
msgid ""
"Type a shortcut command in the :guilabel:`Shortcut` field. Next, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Substitution` field, and type the message that will replace "
"the shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Ketik perintah shortcut di field :guilabel:`Shortcut`. Selanjutnya, klik "
"field :guilabel:`Substitution`, dan ketik pesan yang akan menggantikan "
"shortcut tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:44
msgid ""
"Try to connect the shortcut to the topic of the substitution. Not only does "
"this make it easier to use the responses, it prevents the list of responses "
"from becoming disorganized and overwhelming."
msgstr ""
"Cobalah menghubungkan shortcut dengan topik substitution. Hal ini tidak "
"hanya memudahkan penggunaan respons, tetapi juga mencegah daftar respons "
"menjadi tidak teratur dan membingungkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:48
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Created by` field automatically populates with the name of "
"the user that creates a new response. This field cannot be edited."
msgstr ""
"Field :guilabel:`Created by` secara otomatis terisi dengan nama user yang "
"membuat respons baru. Field ini tidak dapat diedit."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:51
msgid ""
"To :ref:`share <discuss/sharing-responses>` this response with other users, "
"select one or more groups in the :guilabel:`Authorized Group` field that "
"should have access."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :ref:`membagikan <discuss/sharing-responses>` respons ini kepada user "
"lain, pilih satu atau beberapa grup di field :guilabel:`Authorized Group` "
"yang harus memiliki akses."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:55
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Authorized Group` field is left blank, the response can "
"**only** be used by the user that created it."
msgstr ""
"Jika field :guilabel:`Authorized Group` dibiarkan kosong, respons **hanya** "
"dapat digunakan oleh user yang membuatnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:58
msgid ""
"Canned responses created by the database are automatically credited as "
"created by *OdooBot*. They must be assigned to an *authorized group* before "
"they can be used by **any** users. To view the responses created by "
"*OdooBot*, navigate to :menuselection:`Discuss app --> Configuration --> "
"Canned Responses`."
msgstr ""
"Respons cepat yang dibuat oleh database secara otomatis dikreditkan sebagai "
"dibuat oleh *OdooBot*. Respons tersebut harus ditetapkan ke *authorized "
"group* sebelum dapat digunakan oleh user **mana pun**. Untuk melihat respons "
"yang dibuat oleh *OdooBot*, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Diskusi "
"--> Configuration --> Canned Responses`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:63
msgid ""
"Lastly, the :guilabel:`Last Used` field keeps track of the date and time "
"each response was most recently used. This field cannot be edited."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, field :guilabel:`Last Used` melacak tanggal dan waktu setiap "
"respons terakhir kali digunakan. Field ini tidak dapat diedit."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:69
msgid "Share responses"
msgstr "Bagikan respons"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:71
msgid ""
"Canned responses, by default, are made available **only** to the user who "
"creates them. To make a canned response available for others to use, they "
"need to be shared."
msgstr ""
"Respons cepat, secara default, hanya tersedia untuk user yang membuatnya. "
"Untuk membuat respons cepat tersedia bagi orang lain, respons tersebut perlu "
"dibagikan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:75
msgid ""
"Users with *Administrator* access rights can view and edit canned responses "
"created by other users through the **Discuss** app. However, they are "
"**only** able to use them if they are included in an authorized group that "
"has been designated on that canned responses item line, located on "
"the :guilabel:`Canned Responses` page."
msgstr ""
"User dengan hak akses *Administrator* dapat melihat dan mengedit respons "
"cepat yang dibuat oleh user lain melalui aplikasi **Diskusi**. Namun, mereka "
"**hanya** dapat menggunakannya jika mereka termasuk dalam grup yang "
"berwenang yang telah ditentukan pada baris item respons cepat tersebut, yang "
"terletak di halaman :guilabel:`Canned Responses`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:80
msgid ""
"Access to shared responses is granted on the :ref:`groups <access-rights/"
"groups>` level."
msgstr ""
"Akses ke respons bersama diberikan pada level :ref:`grup <access-rights/"
"groups>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:82
msgid ""
"To view the *Groups* a user is a member of, first enable :ref:`Developer "
"mode <developer-mode>`, then navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> "
"Users & Companies --> Users`. Select a user from the list, and click to open "
"their :guilabel:`User Record`. Then, click the :guilabel:`Groups` smart "
"button at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat *Groups* yang menjadi anggota user, pertama "
"aktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>`, kemudian navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Settings --> Users & Companies --> Users`. Pilih "
"user dari daftar, dan klik untuk membuka :guilabel:`User Record` mereka. "
"Kemudian, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Groups` di bagian atas halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:88
msgid ""
"To view a list of users in a specific group, first enable :doc:`Developer "
"mode <../../general/developer_mode/>`. Next, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users & Companies --> Groups`. Select a "
"group from the list, then click to open the :guilabel:`Group Record`. A list "
"of users is included on the :guilabel:`Users` tab."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat daftar user dalam grup tertentu, pertama aktifkan :doc:`mode "
"pengembang <../../general/developer_mode/>`. Selanjutnya, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Settings --> Users & Companies --> Groups`. "
"Pilih grup dari daftar, kemudian klik untuk membuka :guilabel:`Group "
"Record`. Daftar user disertakan pada tab :guilabel:`Users`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:93
msgid ""
"After determining what groups should have access to a response, they "
"**must** :ref:`be added <discuss/created-canned-response>` to "
"the :guilabel:`Authorized Groups` field for each canned response."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menentukan grup mana yang harus memiliki akses ke respons, mereka "
"**harus** :ref:`ditambahkan <discuss/created-canned-response>` ke "
"field :guilabel:`Authorized Groups` untuk setiap respons cepat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:98
msgid ""
"The user who created the response can use it, even if they are not a member "
"of one of the *Authorized Groups*."
msgstr ""
"User yang membuat respons dapat menggunakannya, meskipun mereka bukan "
"anggota salah satu *Authorized Groups*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:104
msgid "Use a canned response"
msgstr "Gunakan respons cepat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:106
msgid ""
"To use a canned response in a conversation, click the :icon:`fa-plus-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon in the message window. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Insert a Canned Response`. This opens a list of available "
"canned responses. Either select a response from the list, or type the "
"appropriate shortcut, then click the :icon:`fa-paper-"
"plane` :guilabel:`(send)` icon or hit :kbd:`Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan respons cepat dalam percakapan, klik ikon :icon:`fa-plus-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` di jendela pesan. Kemudian, "
"klik :guilabel:`Insert a Canned Response`. Ini membuka daftar respons cepat "
"yang tersedia. Pilih respons dari daftar, atau ketik shortcut yang sesuai, "
"kemudian klik ikon :icon:`fa-paper-plane` :guilabel:`(send)` atau "
"tekan :kbd:`Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:112
msgid ""
"Typing `::` in the *Chatter* composer, or chat window, on its own generates "
"a drop-down list of available canned responses. A response can be selected "
"from the list, in addition to the use of shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Mengetik `::` di composer *Chatter*, atau jendela chat, secara mandiri "
"menghasilkan daftar drop-down respons cepat yang tersedia. Respons dapat "
"dipilih dari daftar, selain menggunakan shortcut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:116
msgid ""
"To search through the list of available responses, type `::`, followed by "
"the first few letters of the shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencari melalui daftar respons yang tersedia, ketik `::`, diikuti oleh "
"beberapa huruf pertama dari shortcut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:0
msgid "A live chat window with a list of all available canned responses."
msgstr "Jendela live chat dengan daftar semua respons cepat yang tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:123
msgid ":doc:`Chatter <chatter>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Chatter <chatter>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:124
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:430
msgid ":doc:`Discuss <../discuss>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Diskusi <../discuss>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/canned_responses.rst:125
msgid ":ref:`Commands and Canned Responses <live-chat/canned-responses>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Perintah dan Respons Cepat <live-chat/canned-responses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:3
msgid "Chatter"
msgstr "Obrolan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:9
msgid ""
"The *Chatter* feature is integrated throughout Odoo to streamline "
"communication, maintain traceability, and provide accountability among team "
"members. Chatter windows, known as *composers*, are located on almost every "
"record within the database, and allow users to communicate with both "
"internal users and external contacts."
msgstr ""
"Fitur *Chatter* terintegrasi di seluruh Odoo untuk menyederhanakan "
"komunikasi, menjaga ketertelusuran, dan memberikan akuntabilitas di antara "
"anggota tim. Jendela Chatter, yang dikenal sebagai *composer*, terletak di "
"hampir setiap record dalam database, dan memungkinkan user untuk "
"berkomunikasi dengan user internal maupun kontak eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:14
msgid ""
"Chatter composers also enable users to log notes, upload files, and schedule "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"Composer Chatter juga memungkinkan user untuk mencatat catatan, mengunggah "
"file, dan menjadwalkan aktivitas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:17
msgid "Chatter thread"
msgstr "Thread Chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:19
msgid ""
"A *chatter thread* can be found on most pages in the database, and serves as "
"a record of the updates and edits made to a record. A note is logged in the "
"chatter thread when a change is made to the record. The note includes "
"details of the change, and a time stamp."
msgstr ""
"*Thread chatter* dapat ditemukan di sebagian besar halaman dalam database, "
"dan berfungsi sebagai catatan pembaruan dan pengeditan yang dilakukan pada "
"record. Catatan dicatat dalam thread chatter ketika perubahan dilakukan pada "
"record. Catatan tersebut mencakup detail perubahan dan stempel waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:24
msgid ""
"A user, Mitchell Admin, needs to update the email address of a contact. "
"After they save the changes to the contact record, a note is logged in the "
"chatter of the contact record with the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Seorang user, Mitchell Admin, perlu memperbarui alamat email dari sebuah "
"kontak. Setelah mereka menyimpan perubahan pada record kontak, catatan "
"dicatat dalam chatter dari record kontak dengan informasi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:28
msgid "The date when the change occurred."
msgstr "Tanggal ketika perubahan terjadi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:29
msgid "The email address as it was previously listed."
msgstr "Alamat email sebagaimana tercantum sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:30
msgid "The updated email address."
msgstr "Alamat email yang diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:0
msgid "A close up of a chatter thread with an update to a contact record."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan dekat dari thread chatter dengan pembaruan pada record kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:35
msgid ""
"If a record was created, or edited, via an imported file, or was otherwise "
"updated through an intervention by the system, the chatter thread creates a "
"log note, and credits the change to OdooBot."
msgstr ""
"Jika sebuah record dibuat, atau diedit, melalui file yang diimpor, atau "
"diperbarui melalui intervensi sistem, thread chatter membuat catatan log, "
"dan mengaitkan perubahan tersebut kepada OdooBot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "A close up of a chatter thread of an OdooBot created contact record."
msgstr "Tampilan dekat dari thread chatter record kontak yang dibuat OdooBot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:45
msgid "Add followers"
msgstr "Tambahkan follower"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:47
msgid ""
"A *follower* is a user or contact that is added to a record and is notified "
"when the record is updated, based on specific :ref:`follower subscription "
"settings <discuss/edit-subscription>`. Followers can add themselves, or can "
"be added by another user."
msgstr ""
"*Follower* adalah user atau kontak yang ditambahkan ke record dan diberi "
"notifikasi ketika record diperbarui, berdasarkan :ref:`pengaturan langganan "
"follower <discuss/edit-subscription>` tertentu. Follower dapat menambahkan "
"diri mereka sendiri, atau dapat ditambahkan oleh user lain."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:52
msgid ""
"If a user creates, or is assigned to a record, they are automatically added "
"as a follower."
msgstr ""
"Jika seorang user membuat, atau ditugaskan ke sebuah record, mereka secara "
"otomatis ditambahkan sebagai follower."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:54
msgid ""
"To follow a record, navigate to any record with a chatter thread. For "
"example, to open a *Helpdesk* ticket, navigate to :menuselection:`Helpdesk "
"app --> Tickets --> All Tickets`, and select a ticket from the list to open "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengikuti record, navigasikan ke record mana pun yang memiliki thread "
"chatter. Misalnya, untuk membuka tiket *Pusat Bantuan*, navigasikan "
"ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Pusat Bantuan --> Tiket --> Semua Tiket`, dan "
"pilih tiket dari daftar untuk membukanya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:58
msgid ""
"At the top-right, above the chatter composer, click :guilabel:`Follow`. "
"Doing this changes the button to read :guilabel:`Following`. Click it again "
"to :guilabel:`Unfollow`."
msgstr ""
"Di pojok kanan atas, di atas composer chatter, klik :guilabel:`Ikuti`. "
"Melakukan ini mengubah tombol menjadi :guilabel:`Mengikuti`. Klik lagi "
"untuk :guilabel:`Berhenti Mengikuti`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:62
msgid "Manage followers"
msgstr "Kelola follower"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:64
msgid ""
"To add another user, or contact, as a follower, click the |user|. This opens "
"a drop-down list of the current followers. Click :guilabel:`Add Followers` "
"to open an :guilabel:`Invite Follower` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan user atau kontak lain sebagai follower, klik |user|. Ini "
"akan membuka daftar drop-down follower saat ini. Klik :guilabel:`Add "
"Followers` untuk membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Invite Follower`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:68
msgid ""
"Select one or more contacts from the :guilabel:`Recipients` drop-down list. "
"To notify the contacts, tick the :guilabel:`Send Notification` checkbox. "
"Edit the message template as desired, then click :guilabel:`Add Followers`."
msgstr ""
"Pilih satu atau beberapa kontak dari daftar drop-"
"down :guilabel:`Recipients`. Untuk memberi notifikasi kepada kontak, centang "
"kotak :guilabel:`Send Notification`. Edit template pesan sesuai kebutuhan, "
"lalu klik :guilabel:`Add Followers`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:72
msgid ""
"To remove followers, click the |user| to open the current followers list. "
"Find the name of the follower to be removed, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"remove` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghapus follower, klik |user| untuk membuka daftar follower saat "
"ini. Temukan nama follower yang akan dihapus, dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"remove` :guilabel:`(remove)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:78
msgid "Edit follower subscription"
msgstr "Edit langganan follower"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:80
msgid ""
"The updates a follower receives can vary based on their subscription "
"settings. To see the type of updates a follower is subscribed to, and to "
"edit the list, click the |user|. Find the appropriate follower in the list, "
"then click the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon. This opens "
"the :guilabel:`Edit Subscription` pop-up window for the follower."
msgstr ""
"Update yang diterima follower dapat bervariasi berdasarkan pengaturan "
"langganan mereka. Untuk melihat jenis update yang dilanggan follower, dan "
"untuk mengedit daftar, klik |user|. Temukan follower yang sesuai dalam "
"daftar, lalu klik ikon :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)`. Ini akan "
"membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Edit Subscription` untuk follower tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:85
msgid ""
"The list of available subscription settings varies depending on the record "
"type. For example, a follower of a *Helpdesk* ticket may be informed when "
"the ticket is rated. This option would not be available for the followers of "
"a *CRM* opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Daftar pengaturan langganan yang tersedia bervariasi tergantung pada jenis "
"record. Misalnya, follower dari tiket *Pusat Bantuan* dapat diberitahu "
"ketika tiket dinilai. Opsi ini tidak akan tersedia untuk follower dari "
"peluang *CRM*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:89
msgid ""
"Tick the checkbox for any updates the follower should receive, and clear the "
"checkbox for any updates they should **not** receive. "
"Click :guilabel:`Apply` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak untuk setiap update yang harus diterima follower, dan hapus "
"centang untuk update yang **tidak** boleh mereka terima. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Apply` setelah selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:95
msgid "The Edit Subscription window on a Helpdesk ticket."
msgstr "Jendela Edit Subscription pada tiket Pusat Bantuan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:95
msgid ""
"The Edit Subscription options vary depending on the record type. These are "
"the options for a Helpdesk ticket."
msgstr ""
"Opsi Edit Subscription bervariasi tergantung pada jenis record. Ini adalah "
"opsi untuk tiket Pusat Bantuan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:101
msgid "Log notes"
msgstr "Catat catatan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:103
msgid ""
"The chatter function includes the ability to log internal notes on "
"individual records. These notes are only accessible to internal users, and "
"are available on any records that feature a chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Fungsi chatter mencakup kemampuan untuk mencatat catatan internal pada "
"record individual. Catatan ini hanya dapat diakses oleh user internal, dan "
"tersedia pada semua record yang menampilkan thread chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:107
msgid ""
"To log an internal note, first navigate to a record. For example, to open a "
"*CRM* opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> My "
"Pipeline`, and click on the Kanban card of an opportunity to open it. Then, "
"at the top-right, above the chatter composer, click :guilabel:`Log note`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencatat catatan internal, pertama navigasi ke record. Misalnya, untuk "
"membuka peluang *CRM*, navigasi ke :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> My "
"Pipeline`, dan klik pada kartu Kanban peluang untuk membukanya. Kemudian, di "
"kanan atas, di atas chatter composer, klik :guilabel:`Log note`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:112
msgid ""
"Enter the note in the chatter composer. To tag an internal user, type `@`, "
"and begin typing the name of the person to tag. Then, select a name from the "
"drop-down menu. Depending on their notification settings, the user is "
"notified by email, or through Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan catatan di chatter composer. Untuk menandai user internal, ketik "
"`@`, dan mulai mengetik nama orang yang akan ditandai. Kemudian, pilih nama "
"dari menu drop-down. Tergantung pada pengaturan notifikasi mereka, user akan "
"diberitahu melalui email, atau melalui Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:117
msgid ""
"Outside contacts can also be tagged in an internal log note. The contact "
"then receives an email with the contents of the note they were tagged in, "
"including any attachments added directly to the note. If they respond to the "
"email, their response is logged in the chatter, and they are added to the "
"record as a follower."
msgstr ""
"Kontak eksternal juga dapat ditandai dalam catatan log internal. Kontak "
"kemudian menerima email dengan isi catatan yang mereka tandai, termasuk "
"lampiran yang ditambahkan langsung ke catatan. Jika mereka merespons email, "
"respons mereka dicatat dalam chatter, dan mereka ditambahkan ke record "
"sebagai follower."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:122
msgid ""
"Outside contacts are **not** able to log in to view the entire chatter "
"thread, and are only notified of specific updates, based on "
"their :ref:`follower subscription settings <discuss/edit-subscription>`, or "
"when they are tagged directly."
msgstr ""
"Kontak eksternal **tidak** dapat login untuk melihat seluruh thread chatter, "
"dan hanya diberitahu tentang update tertentu, berdasarkan :ref:`pengaturan "
"langganan follower <discuss/edit-subscription>` mereka, atau ketika mereka "
"ditandai secara langsung."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:129
msgid "Send messages"
msgstr "Kirim pesan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:131
msgid ""
"Chatter composers can send messages to outside contacts, without having to "
"leave the database, or open a different application. This makes it easy to "
"communicate with potential customers in the *Sales* and *CRM* applications, "
"or vendors in the *Purchase* app."
msgstr ""
"Chatter composer dapat mengirim pesan ke kontak eksternal, tanpa harus "
"meninggalkan database, atau membuka aplikasi yang berbeda. Ini memudahkan "
"untuk berkomunikasi dengan calon pelanggan di aplikasi *Penjualan* dan "
"*CRM*, atau vendor di aplikasi *Pembelian*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:135
msgid ""
"To send a message, first navigate to a record. For example, to send a "
"message from a *CRM* opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> "
"Sales --> My Pipeline`, and click on the Kanban card of an opportunity to "
"open it. Then, at the top-right, above the chatter composer, "
"click :guilabel:`Send message`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim pesan, pertama navigasi ke record. Misalnya, untuk mengirim "
"pesan dari peluang *CRM*, navigasi ke :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> "
"My Pipeline`, dan klik pada kartu Kanban peluang untuk membukanya. Kemudian, "
"di kanan atas, di atas chatter composer, klik :guilabel:`Send message`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:141
msgid ""
"Press :command:`Ctrl + Enter` to send a message, instead of using "
"the :guilabel:`Send` button."
msgstr ""
"Tekan :command:`Ctrl + Enter` untuk mengirim pesan, daripada menggunakan "
"tombol :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:143
msgid ""
"If any :ref:`followers <discuss/add-followers>` have been added to the "
"record, they are added as recipients of the message."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada :ref:`follower <discuss/add-followers>` yang telah ditambahkan ke "
"record, mereka ditambahkan sebagai penerima pesan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:147
msgid ""
":ref:`Followers <discuss/add-followers>` of a record are added as recipients "
"of a message automatically. If a follower should **not** receive a message, "
"they must be removed as a follower before the message is sent, or a note is "
"logged."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pengikut <discuss/add-followers>` dari sebuah rekaman ditambahkan "
"sebagai penerima pesan secara otomatis. Jika seorang pengikut **tidak** "
"boleh menerima pesan, mereka harus dihapus sebagai pengikut sebelum pesan "
"dikirim, atau sebuah catatan dicatat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid ""
"A chatter composer preparing to send a message to the followers of a CRM "
"opportunity and\n"
"the customer listed on the opportunity record."
msgstr ""
"Penyusun chatter yang bersiap mengirim pesan kepada pengikut peluang CRM dan "
"pelanggan yang tercantum pada rekaman peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:156
msgid "Expand full composer"
msgstr "Perluas penyusun penuh"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:158
msgid ""
"The chatter composer can be expanded to a larger pop-up window, allowing for "
"additional customizations."
msgstr ""
"Penyusun chatter dapat diperluas menjadi jendela pop-up yang lebih besar, "
"memungkinkan kustomisasi tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:161
msgid ""
"To open the full composer, click the :icon:`fa-expand` :guilabel:`(expand)` "
"icon in the bottom-right corner of the composer window."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuka penyusun penuh, klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"expand` :guilabel:`(perluas)` di sudut kanan bawah jendela penyusun."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:167
msgid "A chatter composer with emphasis on the expand icon."
msgstr "Penyusun chatter dengan penekanan pada ikon perluas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:167
msgid "The expand icon in a chatter composer."
msgstr "Ikon perluas di penyusun chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:169
msgid ""
"Doing this opens a :guilabel:`Compose Email` pop-up window. Confirm or edit "
"the intended :guilabel:`Recipients` of the message, or add additional "
"recipients. The :guilabel:`Subject` field auto-populates based on the title "
"of the record, though it can be edited, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan ini membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Tulis Email`. Konfirmasi "
"atau edit :guilabel:`Penerima` yang dituju dari pesan, atau tambahkan "
"penerima tambahan. Bidang :guilabel:`Subjek` terisi otomatis berdasarkan "
"judul rekaman, meskipun dapat diedit jika diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:173
msgid ""
"To use an :doc:`email template <../../general/companies/email_template/>` "
"for the message, click the |ve| icon, then select a template from the list. "
"Existing templates can also be overwritten or deleted from this menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan :doc:`templat email <../../general/companies/"
"email_template/>` untuk pesan, klik ikon |ve|, lalu pilih templat dari "
"daftar. Templat yang ada juga dapat ditimpa atau dihapus dari menu ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:178
msgid ""
"The number and type of templates available vary, based on the record the "
"message is created from."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah dan jenis templat yang tersedia bervariasi, berdasarkan rekaman "
"tempat pesan dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:180
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(paperclip)` icon to add any files to "
"the message, then click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(klip kertas)` untuk menambahkan "
"file ke pesan, lalu klik :guilabel:`Kirim`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "The expanded full chatter composer in the CRM application."
msgstr "Penyusun chatter penuh yang diperluas di aplikasi CRM."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:187
msgid "Generate text with AI"
msgstr "Hasilkan teks dengan AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:189
msgid ""
"To generate message text using AI, click the AI icon from the expanded "
"chatter composer. This opens a :guilabel:`Generate Text with AI` pop-up."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghasilkan teks pesan menggunakan AI, klik ikon AI dari penyusun "
"chatter yang diperluas. Ini membuka pop-up :guilabel:`Hasilkan Teks dengan "
"AI`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:192
msgid ""
"Enter a prompt in the :guilabel:`Send a message` field to instruct the AI on "
"the type of content needed, then press enter, or click the :icon:`fa-paper-"
"plane` :guilabel:`(paper plane)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan prompt di bidang :guilabel:`Kirim pesan` untuk menginstruksikan AI "
"tentang jenis konten yang diperlukan, lalu tekan enter, atau klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-paper-plane` :guilabel:`(pesawat kertas)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "The generate text with AI popup."
msgstr "Pop-up hasilkan teks dengan AI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:198
msgid ""
"After the text is generated, click :guilabel:`Insert` to insert the text "
"into the message composer."
msgstr ""
"Setelah teks dihasilkan, klik :guilabel:`Sisipkan` untuk menyisipkan teks ke "
"dalam penyusun pesan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:201
msgid ""
"Before sending the final message, be sure to edit any commentary from the "
"AI, or any text in brackets."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum mengirim pesan akhir, pastikan untuk mengedit komentar apa pun dari "
"AI, atau teks apa pun dalam tanda kurung."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:0
msgid "A draft of an email with text generated by AI."
msgstr "Draf email dengan teks yang dihasilkan oleh AI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:208
msgid "Edit sent messages"
msgstr "Edit pesan yang dikirim"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:210
msgid ""
"Messages can be edited after they are sent, to fix typos, correct mistakes, "
"or add missing information."
msgstr ""
"Pesan dapat diedit setelah dikirim, untuk memperbaiki kesalahan ketik, "
"mengoreksi kesalahan, atau menambahkan informasi yang hilang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:214
msgid ""
"When messages are edited after they have been sent, an updated message is "
"**not** sent to the recipient."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pesan diedit setelah dikirim, pesan yang diperbarui **tidak** "
"dikirimkan kepada penerima."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:217
msgid ""
"To edit a sent message, click the |ve| menu to the right of the message. "
"Then, select :guilabel:`Edit`. Make any necessary adjustments to the message."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit pesan yang telah dikirim, klik menu |ve| di sebelah kanan "
"pesan. Kemudian, pilih :guilabel:`Edit`. Lakukan penyesuaian yang diperlukan "
"pada pesan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "The edit message option in a chatter thread."
msgstr "Opsi edit pesan dalam thread chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:223
msgid ""
"To save the changes, press :command:`Ctrl + Enter`. To discard the changes, "
"press :command:`Escape`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyimpan perubahan, tekan :command:`Ctrl + Enter`. Untuk membatalkan "
"perubahan, tekan :command:`Escape`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:226
msgid ""
"Users with Admin-level access rights can edit any sent messages. Users "
"without Admin rights can **only** edit messages they created."
msgstr ""
"User dengan hak akses tingkat Admin dapat mengedit pesan apa pun yang telah "
"dikirim. User tanpa hak Admin **hanya** dapat mengedit pesan yang mereka "
"buat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:232
msgid "Search messages"
msgstr "Cari pesan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:234
msgid ""
"Chatter threads can become long after a while, because of all the "
"information they contain. To make it easier to find a specific entry, users "
"can search the text of messages and notes for specific keywords."
msgstr ""
"Thread chatter dapat menjadi panjang seiring waktu, karena semua informasi "
"yang terkandung di dalamnya. Untuk memudahkan pencarian entri tertentu, "
"pengguna dapat mencari teks pesan dan catatan untuk kata kunci tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:238
msgid ""
"First, select a record with a chatter thread. For example, to search a *CRM* "
"opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> My Pipeline`, "
"and click on the Kanban card of an opportunity to open it. Then, at the top-"
"right, above the chatter composer, click the :icon:`oi-"
"search` :guilabel:`(search)` icon to open the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pilih rekaman dengan thread chatter. Misalnya, untuk mencari "
"peluang *CRM*, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`aplikasi CRM --> Penjualan --> "
"Pipeline Saya`, dan klik pada kartu Kanban peluang untuk membukanya. "
"Kemudian, di pojok kanan atas, di atas composer chatter, klik ikon :icon:`oi-"
"search` :guilabel:`(cari)` untuk membuka bilah pencarian."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:243
msgid ""
"Enter a keyword or phrase into the search bar, then hit :command:`Enter`, or "
"click the :icon:`oi-search` :guilabel:`(search)` icon to the right of the "
"search bar. Any messages or notes containing the keyword or phrase entered "
"are listed below the search bar, with the keyword highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan kata kunci atau frasa ke dalam bilah pencarian, kemudian "
"tekan :command:`Enter`, atau klik ikon :icon:`oi-search` :guilabel:`(cari)` "
"di sebelah kanan bilah pencarian. Pesan atau catatan apa pun yang berisi "
"kata kunci atau frasa yang dimasukkan akan ditampilkan di bawah bilah "
"pencarian, dengan kata kunci disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:248
msgid ""
"To be taken directly to a particular message in the chatter thread, hover "
"over the upper-right corner of the result to reveal a :guilabel:`Jump` "
"button. Click this button to be directed to that message's location in the "
"thread."
msgstr ""
"Untuk langsung menuju pesan tertentu dalam thread chatter, arahkan kursor ke "
"pojok kanan atas hasil untuk menampilkan tombol :guilabel:`Lompat`. Klik "
"tombol ini untuk diarahkan ke lokasi pesan tersebut dalam thread."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:255
msgid ""
"Search results in a chatter thread emphasising the search icon and the jump "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Hasil pencarian dalam thread chatter yang menekankan ikon pencarian dan "
"tombol lompat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:255
msgid ""
"Search results in a chatter thread. Hover over the upper-right corner of a "
"result to see the **Jump** option. Click it to be taken directly to that "
"message in the chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Hasil pencarian dalam thread chatter. Arahkan kursor ke pojok kanan atas "
"hasil untuk melihat opsi **Lompat**. Klik untuk langsung menuju pesan "
"tersebut dalam thread chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:261
msgid "Schedule activities"
msgstr "Jadwalkan kegiatan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:263
msgid ""
"*Activities* are follow-up tasks tied to a record in an Odoo database. "
"Activities can be scheduled on any database page that contains a chatter "
"thread, Kanban view, list view, or activities view of an application."
msgstr ""
"*Aktivitas* adalah tugas tindak lanjut yang terkait dengan rekaman dalam "
"database Odoo. Aktivitas dapat dijadwalkan di halaman database mana pun yang "
"berisi thread chatter, tampilan Kanban, tampilan daftar, atau tampilan "
"aktivitas dari sebuah aplikasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:267
msgid ""
"To schedule an activity through a chatter thread, click "
"the :guilabel:`Activities` button, located at the top of the chatter on any "
"record. On the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up window that appears, "
"select an :guilabel:`Activity Type` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menjadwalkan aktivitas melalui thread chatter, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Aktivitas`, yang terletak di bagian atas chatter pada "
"rekaman apa pun. Pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Jadwalkan Aktivitas` yang "
"muncul, pilih :guilabel:`Jenis Aktivitas` dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:272
msgid ""
"Individual applications have a list of *Activity Types* dedicated to that "
"application. For example, to view and edit the activities available for the "
"*CRM* application, go to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> "
"Activity Types`."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi individu memiliki list *Tipe-Tipe Kegiatan* dedicated to that "
"application. Contohnya, untuk melihat dan mengedit kegiatan yang tersedia "
"untuk aplikasi *CRM*, pergi ke :menuselection:`app CRM --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Tipe-Tipe Kegiatan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:276
msgid ""
"Enter a title for the activity in the :guilabel:`Summary` field, located in "
"the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan judul untuk kegiatan di field :guilabel:`Ringkasan`, berlokasi di "
"jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Jadwalkan Kegiatan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:279
msgid ""
"Select a name from the :guilabel:`Assigned to` drop-down menu to assign the "
"activity to a different user. Otherwise, the user creating the activity is "
"automatically assigned."
msgstr ""
"Pilih nama dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`Ditetapkan kepada` untuk "
"menetapkan aktivitas kepada user yang berbeda. Jika tidak, user yang membuat "
"aktivitas secara otomatis ditetapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:282
msgid ""
"Add any additional information in the optional :guilabel:`Log a note...` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan informasi tambahan di kolom opsional :guilabel:`Catat sebuah "
"catatan...`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:285
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Due Date` field on the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up "
"window auto-populates based on the configuration settings for the "
"selected :guilabel:`Activity Type`. However, this date can be changed by "
"selecting a day on the calendar in the :guilabel:`Due Date` field."
msgstr ""
"Field :guilabel:`Tenggat Waktu` pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Jadwalkan "
"Kegiatan` diisi berdasarkan pengaturan konfigurasi untuk :guilabel:`Tipe "
"Kegiatan` terpilih. Namun, tanggal ini dapat diganti dengan memilih hari "
"pada kalender di field :guilabel:`Tenggat Waktu`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:289
msgid "Lastly, click one of the following buttons:"
msgstr "Terakhir, pilih salah satu dari tombol berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:291
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: adds the activity to the chatter "
"under :guilabel:`Planned activities`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jadwal`: tambahkan kegiatan ke chatter di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Kegiatan yang direncanakan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:292
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule & Mark as Done`: adds the details of the activity to the "
"chatter under :guilabel:`Today`. The activity is added to :guilabel:`Today`, "
"and is automatically marked as done."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jadwalkan & Tandai Selesai`: menambahkan detail aktivitas ke "
"chatter di bawah :guilabel:`Hari Ini`. Aktivitas ditambahkan "
"ke :guilabel:`Hari Ini`, dan secara otomatis ditandai sebagai selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:295
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Done \\& Schedule Next`: adds the task under :guilabel:`Today` "
"marked as done, and opens a new activity window."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Selesai \\& Jadwalkan Berikutnya`: menambahkan task di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Hari Ini` ditandai sebagai selesai, dan buka jendela "
"kegiatan baru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:297
msgid ":guilabel:`Cancel`: discards any changes made on the pop-up window."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Batal`: membatalkan perubahan apa pun yang dibuat pada jendela "
"pop-up."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:299
msgid ""
"Scheduled activities are added to the chatter for the record "
"under :guilabel:`Planned activities`, and are color-coded based on their due "
"date."
msgstr ""
"Aktivitas yang dijadwalkan ditambahkan ke chatter untuk rekaman di "
"bawah :guilabel:`Aktivitas yang direncanakan`, dan diberi kode warna "
"berdasarkan tanggal jatuh tempo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:302
msgid "**Red** icons indicate an overdue activity."
msgstr "Ikon **Merah** menunjukkan aktivitas yang terlambat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:303
msgid ""
"**Yellow** icons indicate an activity with a due date scheduled for the "
"current date."
msgstr ""
"Ikon **Kuning** menunjukkan aktivitas dengan tanggal jatuh tempo yang "
"dijadwalkan untuk tanggal saat ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:304
msgid ""
"**Green** icons indicate an activity with a due date scheduled in the future."
msgstr ""
"Ikon **hijau** menunjukkan aktivitas dengan tanggal jatuh tempo yang "
"dijadwalkan di masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "A chatter thread with planned activities with varying due dates."
msgstr ""
"Thread chatter dengan aktivitas yang direncanakan dengan berbagai tanggal "
"jatuh tempo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:310
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(info)` icon next to a planned "
"activity to see additional details."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(info)` di samping aktivitas "
"yang direncanakan untuk melihat detail tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:0
msgid "A detailed view of a planned activity."
msgstr "Tampilan detail dari aktivitas yang direncanakan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:316
msgid ""
"After completing an activity, click :guilabel:`Mark Done` under the activity "
"entry in the chatter. This opens a :guilabel:`Mark Done` pop-up window, "
"where additional notes about the activity can be entered. After adding any "
"comments to the pop-up window, click: :guilabel:`Done \\& Schedule "
"Next`, :guilabel:`Done`, or :guilabel:`Discard`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menyelesaikan aktivitas, klik :guilabel:`Mark Done` di bawah entri "
"aktivitas dalam chatter. Ini membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Mark Done`, "
"tempat catatan tambahan tentang aktivitas dapat dimasukkan. Setelah "
"menambahkan komentar apa pun ke jendela pop-up, klik: :guilabel:`Done \\& "
"Schedule Next`, :guilabel:`Done`, atau :guilabel:`Discard`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:321
msgid ""
"After the activity is marked complete, an entry with the activity type, "
"title, and any other details that were included in the pop-up window are "
"listed in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Setelah aktivitas ditandai selesai, entri dengan jenis aktivitas, judul, dan "
"detail lain yang disertakan dalam jendela pop-up akan tercantum dalam "
"chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid ""
"A chatter thread with a completed activity, included additional details."
msgstr ""
"Thread chatter dengan aktivitas yang telah selesai, termasuk detail tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:330
msgid "Attach files"
msgstr "Lampirkan file"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:332
msgid ""
"Files can be added as attachments in the chatter, either to send with "
"messages, or to include with a record."
msgstr ""
"File dapat ditambahkan sebagai lampiran dalam chatter, baik untuk dikirim "
"dengan pesan, maupun untuk disertakan dengan record."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:336
msgid ""
"After a file has been added to a chatter thread, it can be downloaded by any "
"user with access to the thread. Click the |paperclip| to make the files "
"header visible, if necessary. Then, click the :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`(download)` icon the file to download it."
msgstr ""
"Setelah file ditambahkan ke thread chatter, file tersebut dapat diunduh oleh "
"user mana pun yang memiliki akses ke thread. Klik |paperclip| untuk membuat "
"header file terlihat, jika perlu. Kemudian, klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`(download)` untuk mengunduh file."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:340
msgid ""
"To attach a file, click the |paperclip| located at the top of the chatter "
"composer of any record that contains a chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melampirkan file, klik |paperclip| yang terletak di bagian atas "
"composer chatter dari record mana pun yang berisi thread chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:343
msgid ""
"This opens a file explorer pop-up window. Navigate to the desired file, "
"select it, then click :guilabel:`Open` to add it to the record. "
"Alternatively, files can be dragged and dropped directly onto a chatter "
"thread."
msgstr ""
"Ini membuka jendela pop-up file explorer. Navigasikan ke file yang "
"diinginkan, pilih file tersebut, lalu klik :guilabel:`Open` untuk "
"menambahkannya ke record. Alternatifnya, file dapat diseret dan dijatuhkan "
"langsung ke thread chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:347
msgid ""
"After files have been added, they are listed in the chatter thread, under "
"a :guilabel:`Files` heading."
msgstr ""
"Setelah file ditambahkan, file tersebut tercantum dalam thread chatter, di "
"bawah judul :guilabel:`Files`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:351
msgid ""
"After at least one file has been added to a chatter record, a new button "
"labeled :guilabel:`Attach files` appears below the :guilabel:`Files` "
"heading. To attach any additional files, this is the button that **must** be "
"used, instead of the |paperclip| at the top of the chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Setelah setidaknya satu file ditambahkan ke record chatter, tombol baru "
"berlabel :guilabel:`Attach files` muncul di bawah judul :guilabel:`Files`. "
"Untuk melampirkan file tambahan, tombol inilah yang **harus** digunakan, "
"bukan |paperclip| di bagian atas thread chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:356
msgid ""
"After the :guilabel:`Files` section heading appears in the thread, clicking "
"the |paperclip| no longer opens a file explorer pop-up window. Instead, "
"clicking the |paperclip| toggles the :guilabel:`Files` section from visible "
"to invisible in the chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Setelah judul bagian :guilabel:`Files` muncul dalam thread, mengklik |"
"paperclip| tidak lagi membuka jendela pop-up file explorer. Sebaliknya, "
"mengklik |paperclip| mengalihkan bagian :guilabel:`Files` dari terlihat ke "
"tidak terlihat dalam thread chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:0
msgid ""
"A chatter thread with a file attached and the Attach files button added."
msgstr ""
"Thread chatter dengan file yang dilampirkan dan tombol Attach files yang "
"ditambahkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:366
msgid "Integrations"
msgstr "Integrasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:368
msgid ""
"Beyond the standard features, additional integrations can be enabled to work "
"with the chatter feature, specifically *WhatsApp* and *Google Translate*."
msgstr ""
"Selain fitur standar, integrasi tambahan dapat diaktifkan untuk bekerja "
"dengan fitur chatter, khususnya *WhatsApp* dan *Google Translate*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:372
msgid ""
"Before the *WhatsApp* and *Google Translate* integrations can be used with "
"the chatter, they **must** be configured. Step-by-step instructions on how "
"to set-up each of these features can be found in the documentation below:"
msgstr ""
"Sebelum integrasi *WhatsApp* dan *Google Translate* dapat digunakan dengan "
"chatter, keduanya **harus** dikonfigurasi. Petunjuk langkah demi langkah "
"tentang cara menyiapkan masing-masing fitur ini dapat ditemukan dalam "
"dokumentasi di bawah ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:376
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:433
msgid ":doc:`WhatsApp <../whatsapp>`"
msgstr ":doc:`WhatsApp <../whatsapp>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:377
msgid ":doc:`Google Translate <../../general/integrations/google_translate>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Google Translate <../../general/integrations/google_translate>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:380
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:3
msgid "WhatsApp"
msgstr "WhatsApp"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:382
msgid ""
"*WhatsApp* is an instant messaging and voice-over-IP app that allows users "
"to send and receive messages, as well as share content."
msgstr ""
"*WhatsApp* adalah aplikasi perpesanan instan dan voice-over-IP yang "
"memungkinkan user untuk mengirim dan menerima pesan, serta berbagi konten."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:386
msgid ""
"*WhatsApp* is an Odoo Enterprise-only application that does **not** work in "
"the Odoo Community edition. To sign up for an Odoo Enterprise edition, click "
"here: `Odoo Free Trial <https://www.odoo.com/trial>`_."
msgstr ""
"*WhatsApp* adalah aplikasi khusus Odoo Enterprise yang **tidak** berfungsi "
"di edisi Odoo Community. Untuk mendaftar edisi Odoo Enterprise, klik di "
"sini: `Uji Coba Gratis Odoo <https://www.odoo.com/trial>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:390
msgid ""
"After *WhatsApp* has been configured and enabled within a database, "
"a :guilabel:`WhatsApp` button is added above the chatter composer on any "
"applicable record. If one or more approved *WhatsApp* templates are found "
"for that model, clicking this button opens a :guilabel:`Send WhatsApp "
"Message` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Setelah *WhatsApp* dikonfigurasi dan diaktifkan dalam database, "
"tombol :guilabel:`WhatsApp` ditambahkan di atas komposer chatter pada setiap "
"record yang berlaku. Jika satu atau lebih template *WhatsApp* yang disetujui "
"ditemukan untuk model tersebut, mengklik tombol ini akan membuka jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Kirim Pesan WhatsApp`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:396
msgid ""
"*WhatsApp* templates **must** be approved before they can be used. "
"See :ref:`WhatsApp templates <productivity/whatsapp/templates>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Template *WhatsApp* **harus** disetujui sebelum dapat digunakan. "
"Lihat :ref:`Template WhatsApp <productivity/whatsapp/templates>` untuk "
"informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "A send WhatsApp message pop-up window."
msgstr "Jendela pop-up kirim pesan WhatsApp."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:403
msgid "Google Translate"
msgstr "Google Translate"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:405
msgid ""
"*Google Translate* can be used to translate user-generated text in the Odoo "
"chatter."
msgstr ""
"*Google Translate* dapat digunakan untuk menerjemahkan teks yang dibuat user "
"di chatter Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:407
msgid ""
"To enable *Google Translate* on a database, an *API key* must first :doc:`be "
"created <../../general/integrations/google_translate>` through the `Google "
"API Console <https://console.developers.google.com/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan *Google Translate* pada database, *kunci API* harus "
"terlebih dahulu :doc:`dibuat <../../general/integrations/google_translate>` "
"melalui `Konsol API Google <https://console.developers.google.com/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:411
msgid ""
"After creating the API key, navigate to the :menuselection:`Settings app --> "
"Discuss section` and paste the key in the :guilabel:`Message Translation` "
"field. Click :guilabel:`Save` to save the changes."
msgstr ""
"Setelah membuat kunci API, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Settings "
"--> bagian Discuss` dan tempelkan kunci tersebut di "
"field :guilabel:`Terjemahan Pesan`. Klik :guilabel:`Simpan` untuk menyimpan "
"perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:416
msgid "Translate a chatter message"
msgstr "Menerjemahkan pesan chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:418
msgid ""
"To translate a user's text from another language, click the |ve| menu to the "
"right of the chatter. Then, select :guilabel:`Translate`. The content "
"translates to the language set in the :doc:`user's preferences <../../"
"general/users/language/>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menerjemahkan teks user dari bahasa lain, klik menu |ve| di sebelah "
"kanan chatter. Kemudian, pilih :guilabel:`Terjemahkan`. Konten akan "
"diterjemahkan ke bahasa yang ditetapkan di :doc:`preferensi user <../../"
"general/users/language/>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "alt text"
msgstr "teks alternatif"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:426
msgid ""
"Using the *Google Translate* API **requires** a current billing account with "
"`Google <https://myaccount.google.com/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan API *Google Translate* **memerlukan** akun penagihan aktif "
"dengan `Google <https://myaccount.google.com/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:431
msgid ":doc:`Discuss Channels <../discuss/team_communication/>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Channel Diskusi <../discuss/team_communication/>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:432
msgid ":doc:`Activities <../../essentials/activities>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Aktivitas <../../essentials/activities>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:3
msgid "Configure ICE servers with Twilio"
msgstr "Konfigurasi server ICE dengan Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo Discuss uses WebRTC API and peer-to-peer connections for voice and "
"video calls. If one of the call attendees is behind a symmetric NAT, you "
"need to configure an ICE server to establish a connection to the call "
"attendee. To set up an ICE server, first, create a Twilio account for video "
"calls, and then, connect that Twilio account to Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Discuss menggunakan WebRTC API dan koneksi peer-to-peer untuk panggilan "
"suara dan video. Jika salah satu peserta panggilan berada di belakang NAT "
"simetris, Anda perlu mengonfigurasi server ICE untuk membuat koneksi ke "
"peserta panggilan tersebut. Untuk menyiapkan server ICE, pertama, buat akun "
"Twilio untuk panggilan video, lalu hubungkan akun Twilio tersebut ke Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:11
msgid "Create a Twilio account"
msgstr "Buat akun Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:13
msgid ""
"First, go to `Twilio <https://www.twilio.com>`_ and click :guilabel:`Sign "
"up` to create a new Twilio account. Next, enter your name and email address, "
"create a password, and accept Twilio's terms of service. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Start your free trial`. Verify your email address with "
"Twilio, as per their instructions."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, buka `Twilio <https://www.twilio.com>`_ dan klik :guilabel:`Sign "
"up` untuk membuat akun Twilio baru. Selanjutnya, masukkan nama dan alamat "
"email Anda, buat password, dan terima persyaratan layanan Twilio. Kemudian, "
"klik :guilabel:`Start your free trial`. Verifikasi alamat email Anda dengan "
"Twilio, sesuai instruksi mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:18
msgid ""
"Next, enter your phone number into Twilio. Then, Twilio will send you an SMS "
"text message containing a verification code. Enter the verification code "
"into Twilio to verify your phone number."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, masukkan nomor telepon Anda ke Twilio. Kemudian, Twilio akan "
"mengirimi Anda pesan teks SMS yang berisi kode verifikasi. Masukkan kode "
"verifikasi tersebut ke Twilio untuk memverifikasi nomor telepon Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:22
msgid ""
"After that, Twilio redirects to a welcome page. Use the following list to "
"answer Twilio's questions:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah itu, Twilio mengarahkan ke halaman selamat datang. Gunakan daftar "
"berikut untuk menjawab pertanyaan Twilio:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:25
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Which Twilio product are you here to use?`, "
"select :guilabel:`Video`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`Which Twilio product are you here to use?`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Video`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:26
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`What do you plan to build with Twilio?`, "
"select :guilabel:`Other`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`What do you plan to build with Twilio?`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Other`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:27
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`How do you want to build with Twilio?`, "
"select :guilabel:`With no code at all`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`How do you want to build with Twilio?`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`With no code at all`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:28
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`What is your goal today?`, select :guilabel:`3rd party "
"integrations`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`What is your goal today?`, pilih :guilabel:`3rd party "
"integrations`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:None
msgid "The Twilio welcome page."
msgstr "Halaman selamat datang Twilio."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:34
msgid ""
"If necessary, change the billing country. Finally, click :guilabel:`Get "
"Started with Twilio`."
msgstr ""
"Jika perlu, ubah negara penagihan. Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Get Started "
"with Twilio`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:37
msgid "Locate the Twilio Account SID and Auth Token"
msgstr "Menemukan Twilio Account SID dan Auth Token"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:39
msgid ""
"To locate the Account SID and Auth Token, go to the Twilio account "
"dashboard. Then, click :guilabel:`Develop` on the sidebar. In "
"the :guilabel:`Account Info` section, locate the :guilabel:`Account SID` and "
"the :guilabel:`Auth Token`. Both of these are needed to connect Twilio to "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menemukan Account SID dan Auth Token, buka dashboard akun Twilio. "
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Develop` di sidebar. Di bagian :guilabel:`Account "
"Info`, temukan :guilabel:`Account SID` dan :guilabel:`Auth Token`. Keduanya "
"diperlukan untuk menghubungkan Twilio ke Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Twilio Account SID and Auth Token can be found uner the Account Info "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Twilio Account SID dan Auth Token dapat ditemukan di bagian Account Info."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:49
msgid "Connect Twilio to Odoo"
msgstr "Menghubungkan Twilio ke Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:51
msgid ""
"Open the Odoo database and go to :menuselection:`Settings --> General "
"Settings --> Discuss`. Check the box next to :guilabel:`Use Twilio ICE "
"servers` and enter the Twilio account's :guilabel:`Account SID` "
"and :guilabel:`Auth Token`. Finally, click :guilabel:`Save` to apply these "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Buka database Odoo dan buka :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --"
"> Discuss`. Centang kotak di sebelah :guilabel:`Use Twilio ICE servers` dan "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Account SID` dan :guilabel:`Auth Token` akun Twilio. "
"Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Save` untuk menerapkan perubahan ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:None
msgid "Enable the \"Use Twilio ICE servers\" option in Odoo General Settings."
msgstr "Aktifkan opsi \"Use Twilio ICE servers\" di Pengaturan Umum Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:61
msgid "Define a list of custom ICE servers"
msgstr "Menentukan daftar server ICE kustom"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:63
msgid ""
"This step is not required for the Twilio configuration. However, if Twilio "
"is not configured or is not working at any given moment, Odoo will fall back "
"on the custom ICE servers list. The user must define the list of custom ICE "
"servers."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini tidak diperlukan untuk konfigurasi Twilio. Namun, jika Twilio "
"tidak dikonfigurasi atau tidak berfungsi pada waktu tertentu, Odoo akan "
"kembali ke daftar server ICE kustom. User harus menentukan daftar server ICE "
"kustom."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:67
msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --> Discuss`, click "
"the :guilabel:`ICE Servers` button under :guilabel:`Custom ICE server list`."
msgstr ""
"Di :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --> Discuss`, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`ICE Servers` di bawah :guilabel:`Custom ICE server list`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:None
msgid "The \"ICE Servers\" button in Odoo General Settings."
msgstr "Tombol \"ICE Servers\" di Pengaturan Umum Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:74
msgid ""
"Odoo will redirect to the :guilabel:`ICE servers` page. Here you can define "
"your own list of ICE servers."
msgstr ""
"Odoo akan mengarahkan ke halaman :guilabel:`ICE servers`. Di sini Anda dapat "
"menentukan daftar server ICE Anda sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:None
msgid "The \"ICE servers\" page in Odoo."
msgstr "Halaman \"ICE servers\" di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/ice_servers.rst:82
msgid ""
"For on-premise instances of Odoo, the package `python3-gevent` is necessary "
"for the Discuss module to run calls/video calls on Ubuntu (Linux) servers."
msgstr ""
"Untuk instance Odoo on-premise, paket `python3-gevent` diperlukan agar modul "
"Diskusi dapat menjalankan panggilan/panggilan video di server Ubuntu (Linux)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:3
msgid "Use channels for team communication"
msgstr "Gunakan channel untuk komunikasi tim"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:5
msgid ""
"Use channels in the Odoo **Discuss** app to organize discussions between "
"individual teams, departments, projects, or any other group that requires "
"regular communication. With channels, employees can communicate inside "
"dedicated spaces within the Odoo database around specific topics, updates, "
"and latest developments having to do with the organization."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan saluran di aplikasi **Diskusi** Odoo untuk mengatur diskusi antara "
"tim, departemen, proyek, atau grup lain yang memerlukan komunikasi rutin. "
"Dengan saluran, karyawan dapat berkomunikasi dalam ruang khusus di dalam "
"database Odoo seputar topik, pembaruan, dan perkembangan terbaru yang "
"berkaitan dengan organisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:11
msgid "Create a new channel"
msgstr "Membuat saluran baru"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:13
msgid ""
"To create a new channel, navigate to the :menuselection:`Discuss` app, and "
"then click on the :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`Channels` heading in the left-side menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat saluran baru, buka aplikasi :menuselection:`Diskusi`, lalu "
"klik ikon :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` di samping "
"judul :guilabel:`Channels` di menu sisi kiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:None
msgid "View of discuss's sidebar and a channel being created in Odoo Discuss."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan sidebar Diskusi dan saluran yang sedang dibuat di Odoo Diskusi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:20
msgid ""
"The channel's :guilabel:`Group Name`, :guilabel:`Description`, "
"and :guilabel:`Privacy` settings can be modified by clicking on the "
"channel's settings, represented by a :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon "
"in the left sidebar menu, next to the channel's name."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nama Grup`, :guilabel:`Deskripsi`, dan "
"pengaturan :guilabel:`Privasi` saluran dapat diubah dengan mengklik "
"pengaturan saluran, yang ditunjukkan oleh ikon :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` di menu sidebar kiri, di samping nama saluran."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:25
msgid "Privacy tab"
msgstr "Tab Privasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:27
msgid ""
"To control which users can join a channel, open the channel's setting page "
"and navigate to the :guilabel:`Privacy` tab."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengontrol user mana yang dapat bergabung ke saluran, buka halaman "
"pengaturan saluran dan buka tab :guilabel:`Privasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:None
msgid "View of a channel's settings form in Odoo Discuss."
msgstr "Tampilan formulir pengaturan saluran di Odoo Diskusi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:33
msgid ""
"To limit access of the channel to a specific group, select an option from "
"the :guilabel:`Authorized Group` drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatasi akses saluran ke grup tertentu, pilih opsi dari menu drop-"
"down :guilabel:`Grup yang Diizinkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:36
msgid ""
"To automatically add members of a group as followers of the channel, click "
"the :guilabel:`Auto Subscribe Groups` field, and select one or more groups "
"from the list."
msgstr ""
"Untuk secara otomatis menambahkan anggota grup sebagai pengikut saluran, "
"klik bidang :guilabel:`Grup Langganan Otomatis`, dan pilih satu atau lebih "
"grup dari daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:40
msgid ""
"Users who are automatically added as followers can manually edit their "
"subscription to the channel, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"User yang secara otomatis ditambahkan sebagai pengikut dapat mengedit "
"langganan mereka ke saluran secara manual, jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:43
msgid ""
"The option to :guilabel:`Auto Subscribe Groups` automatically adds users of "
"that particular user group as followers. In other words, "
"while :guilabel:`Authorized Groups` limits which users can access the "
"channel, :guilabel:`Auto Subscribe Groups` automatically adds users as "
"members as long as they are part of a specific user group. The same is true "
"for :guilabel:`Auto Subscribe Departments`."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`Grup Langganan Otomatis` secara otomatis menambahkan user "
"dari grup user tertentu sebagai pengikut. Dengan kata lain, "
"sementara :guilabel:`Grup yang Diizinkan` membatasi user mana yang dapat "
"mengakses saluran, :guilabel:`Grup Langganan Otomatis` secara otomatis "
"menambahkan user sebagai anggota selama mereka adalah bagian dari grup user "
"tertentu. Hal yang sama berlaku untuk :guilabel:`Departemen Langganan "
"Otomatis`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:49
msgid "Invite members to a channel"
msgstr "Mengundang anggota ke saluran"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:51
msgid ""
"To invite members to a channel, click on the :guilabel:`Members` tab. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line`, then select either a :guilabel:`Partner` "
"or :guilabel:`Guest` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengundang anggota ke saluran, klik tab :guilabel:`Anggota`. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris`, lalu pilih :guilabel:`Partner` "
"atau :guilabel:`Tamu` dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:54
msgid ""
"Inviting members can also be done from the **Discuss** app's main dashboard, "
"by selecting the channel, clicking the :icon:`fa-user-plus` :guilabel:`(add "
"user)` icon in the top-right corner of the dashboard, and finally "
"clicking :guilabel:`Invite to Channel` once all the users have been added."
msgstr ""
"Mengundang anggota juga dapat dilakukan dari Dashboard utama aplikasi "
"**Diskusi**, dengan memilih saluran, mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-user-"
"plus` :guilabel:`(tambahkan user)` di sudut kanan atas dashboard, dan "
"terakhir mengklik :guilabel:`Undang ke Saluran` setelah semua user telah "
"ditambahkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:None
msgid "View of Discuss' option to invite members in Odoo Discuss."
msgstr "Tampilan opsi mengundang anggota di Odoo Diskusi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:63
msgid "Quick search bar"
msgstr "Bilah pencarian cepat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:65
msgid ""
"Once at least 20 channels, direct messages, or live chat conversations are "
"pinned in the sidebar, a :guilabel:`Quick search…` bar is displayed. This "
"feature is a convenient way to filter conversations and find relevant "
"communications."
msgstr ""
"Setelah setidaknya 20 saluran, pesan langsung, atau percakapan Live Chat "
"disematkan di sidebar, bilah :guilabel:`Pencarian cepat…` ditampilkan. Fitur "
"ini adalah cara yang nyaman untuk memfilter percakapan dan menemukan "
"komunikasi yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the Discuss' sidebar emphasizing the quick search bar in Odoo "
"Discuss."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan sidebar Diskusi yang menekankan bilah pencarian cepat di Odoo "
"Diskusi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:73
msgid "Finding channels"
msgstr "Menemukan saluran"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:75
msgid ""
"To view all available channels, click on the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon to the right of the :guilabel:`CHANNELS` menu. "
"Users can join or leave channels on this screen by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Join` or :guilabel:`Leave` buttons that appear in the channel "
"boxes."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat semua kanal yang tersedia, klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`gear` di sebelah kanan menu :guilabel:`CHANNELS`. User dapat "
"bergabung atau keluar dari kanal di layar ini dengan mengklik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Join` atau :guilabel:`Leave` yang muncul di kotak kanal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:79
msgid ""
"There is also the ability to apply filtering criteria and save them for "
"later use. The :guilabel:`Search...` function accepts wildcards by using the "
"underscore character [ `_` ], and specific searches can be saved by using "
"the :menuselection:`Favorites --> Save Current Search` drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Ada juga kemampuan untuk menerapkan kriteria filter dan menyimpannya untuk "
"digunakan nanti. Fungsi :guilabel:`Search...` menerima wildcard dengan "
"menggunakan karakter garis bawah [ `_` ], dan pencarian spesifik dapat "
"disimpan dengan menggunakan menu drop-down :menuselection:`Favorites --> "
"Save Current Search`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:85
msgid "Linking channel in chatter"
msgstr "Menghubungkan kanal di chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:87
msgid ""
"Channels can be linked in the *chatter* of a record to share relvant "
"discussions. To do so, type: `#` and the channel name. Click or press enter "
"on the *Channel* name. Upon logging the note a link to the channel appears. "
"After clicking on the link a chat window with the channel conversation pops "
"up in the lower right corner of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Kanal dapat dihubungkan di *chatter* suatu record untuk berbagi diskusi yang "
"relevan. Untuk melakukannya, ketik: `#` dan nama kanal. Klik atau tekan "
"enter pada nama *Channel*. Setelah mencatat catatan, tautan ke kanal akan "
"muncul. Setelah mengklik tautan, jendela chat dengan percakapan kanal akan "
"muncul di sudut kanan bawah layar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:92
msgid ""
"Users are able to contribute to this group channel by typing messages in "
"window and pressing *enter*."
msgstr ""
"User dapat berkontribusi ke kanal grup ini dengan mengetik pesan di jendela "
"dan menekan *enter*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:None
msgid "Channel linked in chatter."
msgstr "Kanal dihubungkan di chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication.rst:99
msgid ":doc:`../discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:3
msgid "Documents"
msgstr "Dokumen"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Odoo Documents** allows you to store, view, and manage files within Odoo."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Dokumen** memungkinkan Anda menyimpan, melihat, dan mengelola file "
"dalam Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:7
msgid ""
"Folders and documents are organized into sections accessible from the tree "
"on the left. The following sections are available:"
msgstr ""
"Folder dan dokumen diatur dalam bagian yang dapat diakses dari pohon di "
"sebelah kiri. Bagian berikut tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:16
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`Shared with me`: includes files that have been "
"shared with the user but are not part of any parent folder they have access "
"to."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`Shared with me`: mencakup file yang telah "
"dibagikan dengan user tetapi bukan bagian dari folder induk mana pun yang "
"dapat mereka akses."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:18
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`Recent`: shows recently modified files the "
"user has permission to view or edit."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`Recent`: menampilkan file yang baru "
"dimodifikasi yang memiliki izin untuk dilihat atau diedit oleh user."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:20
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Trash`: stores :ref:`deleted files and folders "
"<documents/deletion-delay>`."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Trash`: menyimpan :ref:`file dan folder yang "
"dihapus <documents/deletion-delay>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:22
msgid ""
"Click a section in the tree to view its contents. Select a folder to open "
"it, :ref:`manage it <documents/folders>`, and access its files."
msgstr ""
"Klik bagian di pohon untuk melihat isinya. Pilih folder untuk "
"membukanya, :ref:`mengelolanya <documents/folders>`, dan mengakses filenya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click a file to open it and :ref:`take available actions <documents/"
"documents>`. To close the file, press **Esc** or click the :icon:`fa-remove` "
"(:guilabel:`close`) icon. You can also drag and drop a file or folder to "
"move it to another folder or section."
msgstr ""
"Klik file untuk membukanya dan :ref:`mengambil tindakan yang tersedia "
"<documents/documents>`. Untuk menutup file, tekan **Esc** atau klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-remove` (:guilabel:`close`). Anda juga dapat menyeret dan "
"menjatuhkan file atau folder untuk memindahkannya ke folder atau bagian lain."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:30
msgid ""
"Use the :ref:`search bar <search/values>` to quickly find specific items."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan :ref:`bilah pencarian <search/values>` untuk menemukan item tertentu "
"dengan cepat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:31
msgid ""
"The :doc:`chatter <discuss/chatter>` tracks changes to folders and files and "
"allows communication with internal users and external contacts. Open "
"the :ref:`Details panel <documents/details-panel>` to access it."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Chatter <discuss/chatter>` melacak perubahan pada folder dan file "
"serta memungkinkan komunikasi dengan pengguna internal dan kontak eksternal. "
"Buka :ref:`panel Detail <documents/details-panel>` untuk mengaksesnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:36
msgid ":doc:`Sign documentation <sign>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Dokumentasi Sign <sign>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:44
msgid "Deletion delay"
msgstr "Jeda penghapusan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:46
msgid ""
"By default, items moved to the trash remain there for 30 days before being "
"permanently deleted. To adjust this delay, go to :menuselection:`Documents --"
"> Configuration --> Settings` and edit the :guilabel:`Deletion delay (days)` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, item yang dipindahkan ke tempat sampah tetap berada di sana "
"selama 30 hari sebelum dihapus secara permanen. Untuk menyesuaikan penundaan "
"ini, buka :menuselection:`Documents --> Configuration --> Settings` dan edit "
"bidang :guilabel:`Deletion delay (days)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:53
msgid "File centralization"
msgstr "Sentralisasi file"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:55
msgid ""
"File centralization allows for automatically organizing all files associated "
"with a specific app into dedicated folders. It is enabled by default for "
"each app upon installation. To disable file centralization, modify the "
"default folder, or configure the tags to be added to the app-specific files, "
"go to :menuselection:`Documents --> Configuration --> Settings`, and edit "
"the relevant setting under the :guilabel:`File Centralization` section."
msgstr ""
"Sentralisasi file memungkinkan untuk secara otomatis mengatur semua file "
"yang terkait dengan aplikasi tertentu ke dalam folder khusus. Ini diaktifkan "
"secara default untuk setiap aplikasi saat instalasi. Untuk menonaktifkan "
"sentralisasi file, memodifikasi folder default, atau mengonfigurasi tag yang "
"akan ditambahkan ke file khusus aplikasi, buka :menuselection:`Dokumen --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, dan edit pengaturan yang relevan di bawah "
"bagian :guilabel:`Sentralisasi File`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:62
msgid ""
"File centralization cannot be disabled for :guilabel:`Accounting` documents. "
"A sub-folder is automatically created for each journal type (e.g., Sales, "
"Purchase, Bank, etc.), and the journal name is added as a tag on each "
"document. Click :guilabel:`Journals` to edit the list of journals to "
"synchronize and define their corresponding folders and tags."
msgstr ""
"Sentralisasi file tidak dapat dinonaktifkan untuk "
"dokumen :guilabel:`Akuntansi`. Sub-folder secara otomatis dibuat untuk "
"setiap jenis jurnal (misalnya, Penjualan, Pembelian, Bank, dll.), dan nama "
"jurnal ditambahkan sebagai tag pada setiap dokumen. Klik :guilabel:`Jurnal` "
"untuk mengedit daftar jurnal yang akan disinkronkan dan menentukan folder "
"serta tag yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:66
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Human Resources` files, a sub-folder is automatically created "
"for each employee, and specific tags are added to the files based on the "
"document type (e.g., :guilabel:`Contracts`, :guilabel:`Payslips`, etc.). You "
"can also create additional :guilabel:`Employee Subfolders` automatically by "
"entering the desired folder names, separated by commas."
msgstr ""
"Untuk file :guilabel:`Human Resources`, sub-folder secara otomatis dibuat "
"untuk setiap karyawan, dan tag khusus ditambahkan ke file berdasarkan jenis "
"dokumen (misalnya, :guilabel:`Kontrak`, :guilabel:`Slip Gaji`, dll.). Anda "
"juga dapat membuat :guilabel:`Subfolder Karyawan` tambahan secara otomatis "
"dengan memasukkan nama folder yang diinginkan, dipisahkan dengan koma."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:73
msgid ""
"Changing the folder or tags only affects new files; existing files remain "
"unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Mengubah folder atau tag hanya memengaruhi file baru; file yang sudah ada "
"tetap tidak berubah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:74
msgid ""
"When file centralization is enabled for an app, deleting a record in that "
"app moves its attachments to the trash in the Documents app."
msgstr ""
"Ketika sentralisasi file diaktifkan untuk sebuah aplikasi, menghapus record "
"di aplikasi tersebut akan memindahkan lampirannya ke tempat sampah di "
"aplikasi Dokumen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:80
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Folder-folder"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:82
msgid ""
"You can organize files in folders available in the :icon:`fa-"
"building` :guilabel:`Company` or :icon:`fa-hdd-o` :guilabel:`My Drive` "
"sections."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengatur file dalam folder yang tersedia di bagian :icon:`fa-"
"building` :guilabel:`Company` atau :icon:`fa-hdd-o` :guilabel:`My Drive`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:85
msgid ""
"To create a folder, select the desired section in the tree, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, and select :guilabel:`Folder`. In the pop-up, enter "
"the folder's :guilabel:`Name` and click :guilabel:`Save`. To create a sub-"
"folder, select the parent folder first, then follow the same steps."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat folder, pilih bagian yang diinginkan di pohon, "
"klik :guilabel:`New`, dan pilih :guilabel:`Folder`. Pada jendela pop-up, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Name` folder dan klik :guilabel:`Save`. Untuk membuat "
"sub-folder, pilih folder induk terlebih dahulu, lalu ikuti langkah yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:90
msgid ""
"Some folders and sub-folders are created automatically based on "
"the :ref:`file centralization settings <documents/file-centralization>`."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa folder dan sub-folder dibuat secara otomatis "
"berdasarkan :ref:`pengaturan sentralisasi file <documents/file-"
"centralization>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:93
msgid ""
"To manage a folder or sub-folder, select it and click the :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`Actions`) icon above the tree. The following options are "
"available in the menu:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola folder atau sub-folder, pilih folder tersebut dan klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Actions`) di atas pohon. Opsi berikut "
"tersedia di menu:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:96
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`Download`: Download the folder as a .zip "
"file, including its files and sub-folders."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`Download`: Unduh folder sebagai file .zip, "
"termasuk file dan sub-foldernya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:98
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Rename`: Modify the folder's name."
msgstr ":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Rename`: Ubah nama folder."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:99
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-share-alt` :guilabel:`Share`: :ref:`Share the folder and manage "
"its access rights <documents/access-rights>`."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-share-alt` :guilabel:`Bagikan`: :ref:`Bagikan folder dan kelola "
"hak aksesnya <documents/access-rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:101
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-star-o` :guilabel:`Add star`: Mark a folder as a favorite for "
"quicker access. This setting is user-specific and does not affect other "
"users' workspaces. You can then use the :ref:`Starred filter <search/"
"favorites>` to navigate to your favorite folders quickly."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-star-o` :guilabel:`Add star`: Tandai folder sebagai favorit untuk "
"akses lebih cepat. Pengaturan ini khusus untuk user dan tidak memengaruhi "
"workspace user lain. Anda kemudian dapat menggunakan :ref:`filter Starred "
"<search/favorites>` untuk menavigasi ke folder favorit Anda dengan cepat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:104
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`Info & Tags`: View the "
"folder's :ref:`details <documents/details-panel>` and chatter."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`Info & Tags`: Lihat :ref:`detail "
"<documents/details-panel>` dan chatter folder."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:106
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Move to trash`: Move the folder and its content "
"to the :ref:`trash <documents/deletion-delay>`."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Move to trash`: Pindahkan folder dan isinya "
"ke :ref:`tempat sampah <documents/deletion-delay>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:108
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions on Select`: Define the server actions that "
"are available (as buttons) for the files in the folder. Click an action to "
"add or remove it. Click :guilabel:`Add Custom Action` to :ref:`create a new "
"one <reference/actions/server>`."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions on Select`: Tentukan server action yang "
"tersedia (sebagai tombol) untuk file dalam folder. Klik action untuk "
"menambah atau menghapusnya. Klik :guilabel:`Add Custom Action` "
"untuk :ref:`membuat yang baru <reference/actions/server>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:111
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Automations`: Create :doc:`automation rules </"
"applications/studio/automated_actions>`."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Automations`: Buat :doc:`aturan automasi </"
"applications/studio/automated_actions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:115
msgid ""
"Setting up automation rules requires activating :doc:`/applications/studio`, "
"which may impact your `pricing plan <https://www.odoo.com/pricing>`_."
msgstr ""
"Menyiapkan aturan automasi memerlukan pengaktifan :doc:`/applications/"
"studio`, yang mungkin memengaruhi `paket harga <https://www.odoo.com/"
"pricing>`_ Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`AI Auto-sort`: Use Odoo AI to automatically organize the files in "
"the folder and trigger actions based on the provided AI prompt. Add the "
"corresponding actions for your prompt in the lower section of the popup. "
"This option requires the **Odoo AI** app to be installed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penyortiran Otomatis AI`: Gunakan Odoo AI untuk secara otomatis "
"mengatur file di folder dan memicu tindakan berdasarkan prompt AI yang "
"diberikan. Tambahkan tindakan yang sesuai untuk prompt Anda di bagian bawah "
"popup. Opsi ini memerlukan aplikasi **Odoo AI** untuk diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:123
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:197
msgid "Switch to the list view to:"
msgstr "Beralih ke tampilan daftar untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:125
msgid "manage multiple folders at once."
msgstr "kelola beberapa folder sekaligus."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:126
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Export` or :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`Insert in spreadsheet` one or multiple folders."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Export` atau :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`Insert in spreadsheet` satu atau beberapa folder."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:128
msgid ""
"quickly execute actions such "
"as :guilabel:`Share`, :guilabel:`Download`, :guilabel:`Rename`, etc. Hover "
"over a folder line and click the corresponding icon at the end of the line "
"to perform the desired action."
msgstr ""
"lakukan tindakan dengan cepat "
"seperti :guilabel:`Share`, :guilabel:`Download`, :guilabel:`Rename`, dll. "
"Arahkan kursor ke baris folder dan klik ikon yang sesuai di akhir baris "
"untuk melakukan tindakan yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:135
msgid "Files"
msgstr "File"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/documents.rst:137
msgid ""
"To upload a file, select the desired folder in the tree, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, and select :guilabel:`Upload`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengunggah file, pilih folder yang diinginkan di pohon, "
