#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:67
msgid ""
"Once the call queue is set up and the changes are applied, a manager can log "
"into the `Axivox management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_ and "
"connect dynamic agents to the queue manually."
msgstr ""
"Setelah antrian panggilan diatur dan perubahan diterapkan, manajer dapat "
"masuk ke `konsol manajemen Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_ dan "
"menghubungkan agen dinamis ke antrian secara manual."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:70
msgid ""
"To connect an agent, click :guilabel:`Queues`, located in the left-hand "
"menu. Doing so opens the :guilabel:`Queues` dashboard, with a few different "
"columns listed:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghubungkan agen, klik :guilabel:`Queues`, yang terletak di menu "
"sebelah kiri. Tindakan ini membuka dashboard :guilabel:`Queues`, dengan "
"beberapa kolom yang tercantum:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:73
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: name of the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Name`: nama antrian."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extension`: number of the extension to be dialed to reach the "
"queue."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Extension`: nomor ekstensi yang harus dipanggil untuk mencapai "
"antrian."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:75
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Agent Connection`: number to dial for dynamic agents to log into "
"the queue."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Koneksi Agen`: nomor yang ditekan agen dinamis untuk masuk ke "
"antrean."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Agent disconnection`: number to dial for dynamic agents to log "
