msgid ":guilabel:`Connected Agents`: name of agents connected to the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Agen Terhubung`: nama agen yang terhubung ke antrean."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:79
msgid ""
"The following buttons are also available on the :guilabel:`Queues` dashboard:"
msgstr ""
"Tombol-tombol berikut juga tersedia pada dashboard :guilabel:`Antrean`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:81
msgid ":guilabel:`Connect an agent`: manually connect an agent to the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Hubungkan agen`: hubungkan agen ke antrean secara manual."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Report`: run a report on the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Laporan`: jalankan laporan pada antrean."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:83
msgid ":guilabel:`Delete`: delete the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Hapus`: hapus antrean."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:84
msgid ":guilabel:`Edit`: make changes to the queue's settings."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Edit`: ubah pengaturan antrean."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:86
msgid ""
"When agents are connected to the queue, or are live with a customer, they "
"are displayed under the :guilabel:`Connected Agents` column."
msgstr ""
"Ketika agen terhubung ke antrean atau sedang berbicara dengan pelanggan, "
"mereka ditampilkan di bawah kolom :guilabel:`Agen Terhubung`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:89
msgid "If they are static agents, they **always** show up as connected."
msgstr ""
"Jika mereka adalah agen statis, mereka **selalu** muncul sebagai terhubung."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:91
msgid ""
"Connect an agent by clicking the orange button labeled :guilabel:`Connect an "
"agent`. Then, select the desired agent's name from the drop-down menu, and "
"click :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Hubungkan agen dengan mengklik tombol oranye berlabel :guilabel:`Hubungkan "
"agen`. Kemudian, pilih nama agen yang diinginkan dari menu tarik-turun, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Hubungkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:94
msgid ""
"To manually log a dynamic agent out of a call queue, navigate to the `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, and "
"click :guilabel:`Queues` from the left-hand menu. Then, click the "
"green :guilabel:`Refresh` button at the top of the :guilabel:`Connected "
"agents` column. From here, click the red :guilabel:`Disconnect` button, and "
"they are immediately disconnected. This can be helpful in situations where "
"agents forget to log out at the end of the day."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengeluarkan agen dinamis dari antrean panggilan secara manual, "
"navigasi ke <https://manage.axivox.com>, dan klik :guilabel:`Antrean` dari "
"menu sebelah kiri. Kemudian, klik tombol hijau :guilabel:`Segarkan` di "
"bagian atas kolom :guilabel:`Agen terhubung`. Dari sini, klik tombol "
"merah :guilabel:`Putuskan`, dan mereka akan langsung terputus. Ini dapat "
"membantu dalam situasi di mana agen lupa untuk keluar di akhir hari."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:None
msgid ""
"Call queue with connected agents column highlighted and connect an agent and "
"report buttons\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Antrean panggilan dengan kolom agen terhubung disorot dan tombol hubungkan "
"agen serta laporan\n"
"disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:105
msgid "Report"
msgstr "Laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:107
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Report` to open a :guilabel:`Queue report` page that shows "
"queue activity. This report includes who connected and when when, as well as "
"what phone calls were handled by the queue.f This information is showcased "
"on a separate :guilabel:`Queue report` page."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Laporan` untuk membuka halaman :guilabel:`Laporan Antrean` "
"yang menampilkan aktivitas antrean. Laporan ini mencakup siapa yang "
"terhubung dan kapan, serta panggilan telepon apa yang ditangani oleh "
"antrean. Informasi ini ditampilkan pada halaman :guilabel:`Laporan Antrean` "
"terpisah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:111
msgid ""
"Set the report's date in the :guilabel:`Period` field. To pick a specific "
"date range, use the :guilabel:`From` and :guilabel:`to` fields. The "
"information can be organized by :guilabel:`Event type` (covered below), "
"and :guilabel:`Call ID`."
msgstr ""
"Atur tanggal laporan di bidang :guilabel:`Periode`. Untuk memilih rentang "
"tanggal tertentu, gunakan bidang :guilabel:`Dari` dan :guilabel:`ke`. "
"Informasi dapat diatur berdasarkan :guilabel:`Jenis peristiwa` (dijelaskan "
"di bawah), dan :guilabel:`ID Panggilan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:115
msgid "Generate the report by clicking :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr "Buat laporan dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Terapkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:117
msgid ""
"Each report can be exported to a :abbr:`CSV (comma separated value)` file "
"for further use and analysis, via the :guilabel:`Export to CSV` button."
msgstr ""
"Setiap laporan dapat diekspor ke file :abbr:`CSV (comma separated value)` "
"untuk penggunaan dan analisis lebih lanjut, melalui tombol :guilabel:`Ekspor "
"ke CSV`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:120
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Event type` field is clicked, a drop-down menu appears "
"with the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Ketika bidang :guilabel:`Jenis peristiwa` diklik, menu tarik-turun muncul "
"dengan opsi-opsi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:123
msgid ":guilabel:`The caller quit`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Penelepon keluar`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:124
msgid ":guilabel:`An agent is connecting`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Agen sedang menghubungkan`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:125
msgid ":guilabel:`An agent is disconnecting`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Agen sedang memutuskan sambungan`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:126
msgid ":guilabel:`The call was terminated (agent hangs up)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Panggilan diakhiri (agen menutup telepon)`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:127
msgid ":guilabel:`The call was terminated (caller hangs up)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Panggilan diakhiri (penelepon menutup telepon)`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:128
msgid ":guilabel:`The caller is connected to an agent.`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Penelepon terhubung ke agen.`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:129
msgid ":guilabel:`Someone is entering the queue`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Seseorang sedang memasuki antrean`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:130
msgid ":guilabel:`The caller exits the queue (no agent is connected)`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penelepon keluar dari antrean (tidak ada agen yang terhubung)`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:131
msgid ":guilabel:`The caller exits the queue (timeout)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Penelepon keluar dari antrean (waktu habis)`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:132
msgid ":guilabel:`No one is answering`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tidak ada yang menjawab`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:133
msgid ":guilabel:`No one is answering, the caller hangs up`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tidak ada yang menjawab, penelepon menutup telepon`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Transfer`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Transfer`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:135
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Blind Transfer` (when the caller is transferred without "
"interacting with an agent)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Blind Transfer` (ketika penelepon ditransfer tanpa berinteraksi "
"dengan agen)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:137
msgid ""
"Any or all of the thirteen options can be selected from the :guilabel:`Event "
"type` drop-down menu. Clicking :guilabel:`Check all` selects all the "
"available options from the drop-down menu, and clicking :guilabel:`Uncheck "
"all` removes all selections from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Salah satu atau semua dari tiga belas pilihan dapat dipilih dari menu drop-"
"down :guilabel:`Jenis peristiwa`. Mengklik :guilabel:`Centang semua` memilih "
"semua opsi yang tersedia dari menu drop-down, dan mengklik :guilabel:`Hapus "
"centang semua` menghapus semua pilihan dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:141
msgid ""
"To select an individual :guilabel:`Event type`, click on the desired option "
"in the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih :guilabel:`Jenis peristiwa` individual, klik pada opsi yang "
"diinginkan di menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:None
msgid "Axivox queue report with result, event type, and period highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Laporan antrean Axivox dengan hasil, jenis peristiwa, dan periode yang "
"disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:147
msgid "Connect to queue on Odoo"
msgstr "Sambungkan ke antrean di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:149
msgid ""
"Dynamic agents can connect manually to the Axivox call queue from the Odoo "
"**VoIP** widget once the **VoIP** app is configured for the individual user "
"in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Agen dinamis dapat terhubung secara manual ke antrean panggilan Axivox dari "
"widget **VoIP** Odoo setelah aplikasi **VoIP** dikonfigurasi untuk user "
"individual di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:152
msgid ""
"To access the Odoo **VoIP** widget, click the :icon:`oi-"
"voip` :guilabel:`(VoIP)`  icon in the upper-right corner of the screen "
"anywhere in an Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses widget **VoIP** Odoo, klik ikon :icon:`oi-"
"voip` :guilabel:`(VoIP)` di sudut kanan atas layar di mana saja dalam "
"database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:156
msgid ":doc:`axivox_config`"
msgstr ":doc:`axivox_config`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:157
msgid ":doc:`../phone_widget`"
msgstr ":doc:`../phone_widget`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:159
msgid ""
"For an agent to connect to the call queue, dial the :guilabel:`Agent "
"connection` number, and then press the green call button :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon in the **VoIP** widget. Then, the agent "
"hears a short, two-second message indicating the agent is logged in. The "
"call automatically ends."
msgstr ""
"Agar agen dapat terhubung ke antrean panggilan, hubungi "
"nomor :guilabel:`Koneksi agen`, lalu tekan tombol panggilan hijau :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)` di widget **VoIP**. Kemudian, agen mendengar "
"pesan singkat berdurasi dua detik yang menunjukkan agen telah masuk. "
"Panggilan otomatis berakhir."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:164
msgid ""
"To view the connected agents in a call queue, navigate to the `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, and "
"click :guilabel:`Queues` from the left-hand menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat agen yang terhubung dalam antrean panggilan, navigasi ke "
"`konsol manajemen Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Antrean` dari menu sebelah kiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:167
msgid ""
"Then, click the green :guilabel:`Refresh` button at the top of "
"the :guilabel:`Connected agents` column. Any agent, static or dynamic, that "
"is connected to the queue currently appears in the column next to the queue "
"they are logged into."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, klik tombol hijau :guilabel:`Refresh` di bagian atas "
"kolom :guilabel:`Connected agents`. Agen apa pun, baik statis maupun "
"dinamis, yang saat ini terhubung ke antrean akan muncul di kolom di sebelah "
"antrean tempat mereka masuk."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/call_queues.rst:171
msgid ""
"To log out of the queue, open the Odoo **VoIP** widget, dial "
"the :guilabel:`Agent disconnection` number, and then press the green call "
"button :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon. The agent is disconnected "
"from the queue after a short, two-second message."
msgstr ""
"Untuk keluar dari antrean, buka widget **VoIP** Odoo, tekan "
"nomor :guilabel:`Agent disconnection`, lalu tekan tombol panggil "
"hijau :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)`. Agen akan terputus dari antrean "
"setelah pesan singkat selama dua detik."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:3
msgid "Conference calls"
msgstr "Panggilan konferensi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:5
msgid ""
"Conference calls help employees connect quickly and efficiently, so matters "
"can be discussed in an open forum of sorts. Attendees can be limited, via a "
"sign-in code. That way, confidential matters stay private."
msgstr ""
"Panggilan konferensi membantu karyawan terhubung dengan cepat dan efisien, "
"sehingga berbagai hal dapat didiskusikan dalam semacam forum terbuka. "
"Peserta dapat dibatasi melalui kode sign-in. Dengan cara itu, hal-hal yang "
"bersifat rahasia tetap bersifat pribadi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:9
msgid ""
"This document covers the configuration of conference calls in Axivox for use "
"in Odoo *VoIP*."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen ini mencakup konfigurasi panggilan konferensi di Axivox untuk "
"digunakan dalam *VoIP* Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:12
msgid "Add a virtual conference"
msgstr "Tambahkan konferensi virtual"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:14
msgid ""
"To add a virtual conference room, navigate to the `Axivox management console "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. After logging in, click "
"on :guilabel:`Conferences` in the menu on the left."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan ruang konferensi virtual, buka `konsol manajemen Axivox "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Setelah masuk, klik :guilabel:`Conferences` "
"di menu sebelah kiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:18
msgid ""
"Next, click the green button labeled, :guilabel:`Add a conference`, and "
"a :guilabel:`New conference` form appears."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik tombol hijau berlabel :guilabel:`Add a conference`, dan "
"formulir :guilabel:`New conference` akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:None
msgid "New conference form on Axivox."
msgstr "Formulir konferensi baru di Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:25
msgid ""
"From here, fill in the :guilabel:`Name` field, and set "
"an :guilabel:`Internal extension`."
msgstr ""
"Dari sini, isi kolom :guilabel:`Name`, dan atur :guilabel:`Internal "
"extension`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:27
msgid ""
"The internal extension is what everyone in the network uses to quickly dial "
"into the conference call, instead of typing in the whole phone number."
msgstr ""
"Internal extension adalah yang digunakan semua orang di jaringan untuk cepat "
"menghubungi panggilan konferensi, daripada mengetik seluruh nomor telepon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:31
msgid ""
"Pick a number between three and five digits long, making it easy to remember "
"and dial."
msgstr ""
"Pilih nomor antara tiga hingga lima digit, sehingga mudah diingat dan "
"dihubungi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:33
msgid ""
"Next, set the :guilabel:`Access code`, if the conference room requires "
"security. This is a password to get into the conference, once the extension "
"for the conference is dialed. Immediately after dialing the extension, a "
"digital receptionist prompts for the :guilabel:`Access code`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, atur :guilabel:`Access code`, jika ruang konferensi memerlukan "
"keamanan. Ini adalah kata sandi untuk masuk ke konferensi, setelah ekstensi "
"untuk konferensi dihubungi. Segera setelah menghubungi ekstensi, resepsionis "
"digital akan meminta :guilabel:`Access code`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:37
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Administrator extension` field, click the drop-down menu, "
"and select the user's extension that manages the call."
msgstr ""
"Di kolom :guilabel:`Administrator extension`, klik menu drop-down, dan pilih "
"ekstensi user yang mengelola panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:40
msgid ""
"Finally, in the :guilabel:`Wait for the administrator to start the "
"conference` field, click the drop-down menu, and select :guilabel:`Yes` "
"or :guilabel:`No`."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, di kolom :guilabel:`Wait for the administrator to start the "
"conference`, klik menu drop-down, dan pilih :guilabel:`Yes` "
"atau :guilabel:`No`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:43
msgid ""
"Should the selection be :guilabel:`Yes`, then nobody is allowed to utilize "
"the virtual conference room until the administrator is present, and logged "
"into the conference call."
msgstr ""
"Jika pilihan yang dipilih adalah :guilabel:`Yes`, maka tidak ada yang "
"diizinkan untuk menggunakan ruang konferensi virtual sampai administrator "
"hadir, dan masuk ke panggilan konferensi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:46
msgid ""
"When all fields are filled in, be sure to :guilabel:`Save` the "
"configuration. Then, click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right "
"corner to implement the change in production."
msgstr ""
"Ketika semua kolom telah diisi, pastikan untuk :guilabel:`Save` konfigurasi. "
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Apply changes` di sudut kanan atas untuk "
"menerapkan perubahan dalam produksi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:49
msgid ""
"Upon doing so, the conference is added, and the Axivox administrator has the "
"option to :guilabel:`Delete` or :guilabel:`Edit` the conference from the "
"Axivox :guilabel:`Conference` main dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Setelah melakukannya, konferensi ditambahkan, dan administrator Axivox "
"memiliki opsi untuk :guilabel:`Delete` atau :guilabel:`Edit` konferensi dari "
"dashboard utama :guilabel:`Conference` Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:53
msgid ""
"To invite an Axivox user to a specific conference call, "
"click :guilabel:`Invite` to the right of the desired conference, and proceed "
"to enter the extension or phone number of the invitee in the pop-up window "
"that appears."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengundang user Axivox ke panggilan konferensi tertentu, "
"klik :guilabel:`Invite` di sebelah kanan konferensi yang diinginkan, dan "
"lanjutkan dengan memasukkan ekstensi atau nomor telepon orang yang diundang "
"di jendela pop-up yang muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:57
msgid ""
"Once the extension or number is added into the :guilabel:`Please enter the "
"phone number of the person you want to invite` field, click the "
"green :guilabel:`Invite` button, and the recipient immediately receives a "
"phone call, automatically linking them to the conference."
msgstr ""
"Setelah ekstensi atau nomor ditambahkan ke dalam kolom :guilabel:`Please "
"enter the phone number of the person you want to invite`, klik tombol "
"hijau :guilabel:`Invite`, dan penerima segera menerima panggilan telepon, "
"yang secara otomatis menghubungkan mereka ke konferensi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:66
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:32
msgid "Incoming numbers"
msgstr "Nomor masuk"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:68
msgid ""
"To open a conference to a wider audience, an Axivox conference can be linked "
"to *Incoming numbers*."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuka konferensi kepada audiens yang lebih luas, konferensi Axivox "
"dapat dihubungkan ke *Nomor masuk*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:70
msgid ""
"To do that, log into the `Axivox management console <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_, and click :guilabel:`Incoming numbers` in the menu on "
"the left."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, masuk ke `konsol manajemen Axivox <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_, lalu klik :guilabel:`Incoming numbers` di menu sebelah "
"kiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:73
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Incoming numbers` dashboard, click :guilabel:`Edit` to the "
"far-right of the :guilabel:`Number` to which the conference should be "
"attached."
msgstr ""
"Pada dashboard :guilabel:`Incoming numbers`, klik :guilabel:`Edit` di "
"sebelah kanan :guilabel:`Number` yang akan dilampirkan konferensi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:76
msgid ""
"Then, under the first field, labeled, :guilabel:`Destination type for voice "
"call`, click the drop-down menu, and select :guilabel:`Conference`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, di bawah bidang pertama, berlabel :guilabel:`Destination type for "
"voice call`, klik menu drop-down, lalu pilih :guilabel:`Conference`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:79
msgid ""
"Next, in the :guilabel:`Conference` field, click the drop-down menu, and "
"select the specific conference that should be attached to this incoming "
"number."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, di bidang :guilabel:`Conference`, klik menu drop-down, lalu "
"pilih konferensi spesifik yang harus dilampirkan ke nomor masuk ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:82
msgid ""
"Now, whenever this incoming number is dialed, the caller is let into the "
"conference, if there is not an :guilabel:`Access code` required. If there "
"*is* an :guilabel:`Access code` required, the caller is then prompted to "
"enter the :guilabel:`Access code` to enter the conference."
msgstr ""
"Sekarang, setiap kali nomor masuk ini dihubungi, penelepon akan dimasukkan "
"ke dalam konferensi, jika tidak ada :guilabel:`Access code` yang diperlukan. "
"Jika *ada* :guilabel:`Access code` yang diperlukan, penelepon kemudian akan "
"diminta untuk memasukkan :guilabel:`Access code` untuk memasuki konferensi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:87
msgid "Start call in Odoo"
msgstr "Memulai panggilan di Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:89
msgid ""
"Anywhere in the Odoo database, open the *VoIP* widget, by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`☎️ (phone)` icon, located in the upper-right corner. Then, "
"dial the specific extension number for the conference, and click "
"the :guilabel:`📞 (phone)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Di mana saja dalam database Odoo, buka widget *VoIP*, dengan mengklik "
"ikon :guilabel:`☎️ (phone)`, yang terletak di pojok kanan atas. Kemudian, "
"tekan nomor ekstensi spesifik untuk konferensi, lalu klik ikon :guilabel:`📞 "
"(phone)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:None
msgid "Connecting to a conference extension using the Odoo VoIP widget."
msgstr "Menghubungkan ke ekstensi konferensi menggunakan widget VoIP Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/conference_calls.rst:97
msgid ""
"Once the digital receptionist answers, enter the :guilabel:`Access code` (if "
"needed), and press the :guilabel:`# (pound)` icon/key."
msgstr ""
"Setelah resepsionis digital menjawab, masukkan :guilabel:`Access code` (jika "
"diperlukan), lalu tekan ikon/tombol :guilabel:`# (pound)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:3
msgid "Advanced dial plans"
msgstr "Dial plan lanjutan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:5
msgid ""
"Typically, companies have a lot of incoming calls every day, but many do not "
"want their teams to answer calls 24 hours a day, 7 days a week."
msgstr ""
"Biasanya, perusahaan menerima banyak panggilan masuk setiap hari, tetapi "
"banyak yang tidak ingin tim mereka menjawab panggilan 24 jam sehari, 7 hari "
"seminggu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:8
msgid ""
"By using Axivox advanced dial plan features, the process can be automated, "
"and routing can be set up for all scenarios. This way, customers are never "
"left waiting, or frustrated, because they cannot get in touch with anyone."
msgstr ""
"Dengan menggunakan fitur dial plan lanjutan Axivox, proses dapat "
"diotomatisasi, dan perutean dapat diatur untuk semua skenario. Dengan cara "
"ini, pelanggan tidak akan pernah menunggu atau frustrasi, karena mereka "
"tidak dapat menghubungi siapa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:12
msgid ""
"By utilizing the advanced elements in dial plans, companies can automate "
"call routing for certain days or times, like company holidays. Companies can "
"also allow callers to enter extensions themselves, and get transferred "
"automatically using a digital receptionist. This way, an administrative team "
"does **not** have to be available around the clock."
msgstr ""
"Dengan memanfaatkan elemen lanjutan dalam dial plan, perusahaan dapat "
"mengotomatisasi perutean panggilan untuk hari atau waktu tertentu, seperti "
"hari libur perusahaan. Perusahaan juga dapat mengizinkan penelepon untuk "
"memasukkan ekstensi sendiri, dan ditransfer secara otomatis menggunakan "
"resepsionis digital. Dengan cara ini, tim administratif **tidak** harus "
"tersedia sepanjang waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:17
msgid ""
"There is even the option to route callers, depending on where they are "
"calling from in the world, thus maximizing efficiency."
msgstr ""
"Bahkan ada opsi untuk merutekan penelepon, tergantung dari mana mereka "
"menelepon di dunia, sehingga memaksimalkan efisiensi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:21
msgid ""
"For more information on basic dial plans, and how to add elements, "
"visit :doc:`dial_plan_basics`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang dial plan dasar, dan cara menambahkan "
"elemen, kunjungi :doc:`dial_plan_basics`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:24
msgid ""
"Using a browser add-on for spelling may hinder the use of the visual editor "
"in dial plans. Do **not** use a translator with the Axivox management "
"console."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan add-on browser untuk ejaan dapat menghambat penggunaan editor "
"visual dalam dial plan. **Jangan** gunakan penerjemah dengan konsol "
"manajemen Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:28
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:160
msgid "Advanced elements"
msgstr "Elemen lanjutan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:30
msgid ""
"In Axivox dial plans (as described in :doc:`dial_plan_basics`), there are "
"two advanced elements that can be used."
msgstr ""
"Dalam dial plan Axivox (seperti dijelaskan di :doc:`dial_plan_basics`), "
"terdapat dua elemen lanjutan yang dapat digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:33
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:164
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Record`: recording feature is enabled (requires plan change, "
"enabled in Axivox settings)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Record`: fitur perekaman diaktifkan (memerlukan perubahan paket, "
"diaktifkan di pengaturan Axivox)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:166
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Caller ID`: replace the caller ID by the called number or free "
"text."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID Penelepon`: mengganti ID penelepon dengan nomor yang dipanggil "
"atau teks bebas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:37
msgid ""
"To add one of these elements, navigate to the :guilabel:`Dial plans` page, "
"located in the menu on the left side of the `Axivox management console "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan salah satu elemen ini, buka halaman :guilabel:`Rencana "
"Panggilan`, yang terletak di menu di sisi kiri `konsol manajemen Axivox "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:40
msgid ""
"Next, click on the :guilabel:`Visual Editor` button to the right of the "
"desired dial plan to edit it. Finally, open the :guilabel:`New element` drop-"
"down menu, select the element, and click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik tombol :guilabel:`Editor Visual` di sebelah kanan rencana "
"panggilan yang diinginkan untuk mengeditnya. Terakhir, buka menu drop-"
"down :guilabel:`Elemen Baru`, pilih elemen tersebut, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Tambah`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:None
msgid ""
"Visual editor for a dial plan in Axivox, with Add and the dispatcher element "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Editor visual untuk rencana panggilan di Axivox, dengan Tambah dan elemen "
"dispatcher yang disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:48
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:99
msgid "For more information, visit :ref:`voip/axivox/dial_plans`."
msgstr "Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, kunjungi :ref:`voip/axivox/dial_plans`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:51
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Record` element records calls that are routed through this "
"element, and requires an additional plan change in Axivox."
msgstr ""
"Elemen :guilabel:`Rekam` merekam panggilan yang diarahkan melalui elemen "
"ini, dan memerlukan perubahan rencana tambahan di Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:54
msgid ""
"To enable recording on Axivox, navigate to :guilabel:`Settings` in the "
"`Axivox management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Then, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Recording` drop-down menu, near the bottom of the page. From "
"there, select :guilabel:`Enabled` from the drop-down menu to enable "
"recording using the :guilabel:`Record` element in a dial plan."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan perekaman di Axivox, buka :guilabel:`Pengaturan` di "
"`konsol manajemen Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Kemudian, buka menu "
"drop-down :guilabel:`Perekaman`, di dekat bagian bawah halaman. Dari sana, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Aktif` dari menu drop-down untuk mengaktifkan perekaman "
"menggunakan elemen :guilabel:`Rekam` dalam rencana panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:60
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Recording` drop-down menu is unavailable and unable to "
"change, then consult Axivox to enable the feature."
msgstr ""
"Jika menu drop-down :guilabel:`Perekaman` tidak tersedia dan tidak dapat "
"diubah, konsultasikan dengan Axivox untuk mengaktifkan fitur tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:63
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Caller ID` element allows for the replacement of the caller "
"ID downstream, after routing."
msgstr ""
"Elemen :guilabel:`ID Penelepon` memungkinkan penggantian ID penelepon di "
"hilir, setelah perutean."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:66
msgid ""
"Upon adding the :guilabel:`Caller ID` element to the dial plan, and double-"
"clicking it to configure it, two options appear."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menambahkan elemen :guilabel:`ID Penelepon` ke rencana panggilan, "
"dan mengklik dua kali untuk mengkonfigurasinya, dua opsi muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:69
msgid ""
"The first is a :guilabel:`Free text` field, where any text can be input to "
"replace the caller ID. The second option is :guilabel:`Replace the caller ID "
"by the called number`. This option replaces the caller's ID with "
"the :guilabel:`Incoming number`."
msgstr ""
"Yang pertama adalah bidang :guilabel:`Teks bebas`, di mana teks apa pun "
"dapat diinput untuk mengganti ID penelepon. Opsi kedua "
"adalah :guilabel:`Ganti ID penelepon dengan nomor yang dipanggil`. Opsi ini "
"mengganti ID penelepon dengan :guilabel:`Nomor masuk`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:74
msgid ""
"A company may want to use the :guilabel:`Caller ID` element to replace "
"the :guilabel:`Incoming number`, so employees, or outside transfers, cannot "
"see the number, and information is kept private."
msgstr ""
"Perusahaan mungkin ingin menggunakan elemen :guilabel:`ID Penelepon` untuk "
"mengganti :guilabel:`Nomor masuk`, sehingga karyawan atau transfer eksternal "
"tidak dapat melihat nomornya, dan informasi tetap pribadi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:79
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:135
msgid "Basic routing elements"
msgstr "Elemen perutean dasar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:81
msgid ""
"Basic routing elements in Axivox dial plans provide extension-based routing. "
"This can be done by adding either a *Menu* to numerically link the dial-by-"
"numbers to an action, or by using a *Digital Receptionist* to automatically "
"route or listen for an extension, based on a key input from the caller."
msgstr ""
"Elemen perutean dasar dalam rencana panggilan Axivox menyediakan perutean "
"berbasis ekstensi. Hal ini dapat dilakukan dengan menambahkan *Menu* untuk "
"menghubungkan nomor panggilan secara numerik ke tindakan, atau dengan "
"menggunakan *Resepsionis Digital* untuk secara otomatis merutekan atau "
"mendengarkan ekstensi, berdasarkan input tombol dari penelepon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:86
msgid ""
"The main difference between the two elements is that the *Digital "
"Receptionist* does **not** need to be pre-configured numerically with "
"actions. Instead, it acts as a virtual receptionist."
msgstr ""
"Perbedaan utama antara kedua elemen tersebut adalah *Resepsionis Digital* "
"**tidak** perlu dikonfigurasi secara numerik dengan tindakan terlebih "
"dahulu. Sebaliknya, ia bertindak sebagai resepsionis virtual."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Menu`: add a dial-by-number directory and configured downstream "
"actions (not terminal). For example, a dial-by-numbers function could "
"feature an element, wherein clicking '2' takes the caller to the element "
"linked to '2' on the Menu element in the dial plan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Menu`: tambahkan direktori nomor panggilan dan tindakan hilir "
"yang dikonfigurasi (bukan terminal). Misalnya, fungsi nomor panggilan dapat "
"menampilkan elemen, di mana mengklik '2' membawa penelepon ke elemen yang "
"ditautkan ke '2' pada elemen Menu dalam rencana panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:92
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Digital Receptionist`: attach a virtual dispatcher to listen for "
"extensions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Resepsionis Digital`: melampirkan petugas operator virtual untuk "
"mendengarkan ekstensi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:94
msgid ""
"To add one of these elements, navigate to the :guilabel:`Dial plans` page, "
"located in the menu on the left side of the `Axivox management console "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Next, click on the :guilabel:`Visual Editor` "
"button to the right of the dial plan, to edit the dial plan. Then, open "
"the :guilabel:`New element` drop-down menu, select the element, and "
"click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan salah satu elemen ini, buka halaman :guilabel:`Rencana "
"Panggilan`, yang terletak di menu di sisi kiri `konsol manajemen Axivox "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Selanjutnya, klik tombol :guilabel:`Editor "
"Visual` di sebelah kanan rencana panggilan, untuk mengedit rencana "
"panggilan. Kemudian, buka menu drop-down :guilabel:`Elemen Baru`, pilih "
"elemen tersebut, dan klik :guilabel:`Tambah`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:102
msgid "Digital receptionist scenario"
msgstr "Skenario resepsionis digital"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:104
msgid ""
"The *Digital Receptionist* element is a listen-feature that accurately "
"routes callers through a dial plan, based on the extension they enter, via "
"the key pad."
msgstr ""
"Elemen *Resepsionis Digital* adalah fitur pendengar yang secara akurat "
"merutekan penelepon melalui rencana panggilan, berdasarkan ekstensi yang "
"mereka masukkan, melalui tombol angka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:107
msgid ""
"Set a *Digital Receptionist* to eliminate the need of a team, or live "
"receptionist, to be on-call all the time. With that element in place, calls "
"now reach their destination, without a real person interjecting."
msgstr ""
"Atur *Resepsionis Digital* untuk menghilangkan kebutuhan tim, atau "
"resepsionis langsung, untuk siaga setiap saat. Dengan elemen tersebut, "
"panggilan kini mencapai tujuannya, tanpa campur tangan orang sungguhan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:111
msgid ""
"After adding the :guilabel:`Digital Receptionist` element to a dial plan, "
"connect the appropriate endpoints, and double-click on the element to set "
"the :guilabel:`Timeout` on the :guilabel:`receptionist` pop-up window that "
"appears."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menambahkan elemen :guilabel:`Resepsionis Digital` ke rencana "
"panggil, hubungkan titik akhir yang sesuai, dan klik dua kali pada elemen "
"tersebut untuk mengatur :guilabel:`Batas Waktu` pada jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`resepsionis` yang muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:115
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Timeout` can be set in `5` second increments, from `5` "
"seconds to `60` seconds."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Batas Waktu` dapat diatur dalam kelipatan `5` detik, dari `5` "
"detik hingga `60` detik."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:118
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Digital Receptionist` element **requires** a :guilabel:`Play "
"a file` element on either side of it, to explain what action to take, and "
"when a wrong extension is entered."
msgstr ""
"Elemen :guilabel:`Resepsionis Digital` **memerlukan** "
"elemen :guilabel:`Mainkan file` di kedua sisinya, untuk menjelaskan tindakan "
"apa yang harus diambil, dan ketika ekstensi yang salah dimasukkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:122
msgid ""
"While customizing a dial plan in a :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` pop-up "
"window, add a :guilabel:`Menu` element, with a :guilabel:`Greeting message` "
"that might read, `Press star to dial an extension`."
msgstr ""
"Saat menyesuaikan rencana panggil di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Editor "
"Dialplan`, tambahkan elemen :guilabel:`Menu`, dengan :guilabel:`Pesan "
"sambutan` yang mungkin berbunyi, `Tekan bintang untuk memutar ekstensi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:126
msgid ""
"Then, on the :guilabel:`Menu` element, for the :guilabel:`* (star)` option, "
"link a :guilabel:`Play a file` element, that plays an :guilabel:`Audio "
"message` saying, 'Enter the extension of the person you are trying to reach'."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, pada elemen :guilabel:`Menu`, untuk opsi :guilabel:`* (bintang)`, "
"tautkan elemen :guilabel:`Mainkan file`, yang memutar :guilabel:`Pesan "
"audio` yang mengatakan, 'Masukkan ekstensi orang yang ingin Anda hubungi'."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:130
msgid ""
"Following the first :guilabel:`Play a file` element, add "
"the :guilabel:`Digital Receptionist` element, followed by "
"another :guilabel:`Play a file` element, which states, 'That is not a valid "
"extension'."
msgstr ""
"Setelah elemen :guilabel:`Mainkan file` pertama, tambahkan "
"elemen :guilabel:`Resepsionis Digital`, diikuti oleh "
"elemen :guilabel:`Mainkan file` lainnya, yang menyatakan, 'Itu bukan "
"ekstensi yang valid'."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:134
msgid ""
"This last element is in place to close the loop, should the caller not enter "
"a correct extension."
msgstr ""
"Elemen terakhir ini ada untuk menutup siklus, jika penelepon tidak "
"memasukkan ekstensi yang benar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:136
msgid ""
"Finally, this last :guilabel:`Play a file` element is looped back into "
"the :guilabel:`Menu` element."
msgstr ""
"Akhirnya, elemen :guilabel:`Mainkan file` terakhir ini diulang kembali ke "
"elemen :guilabel:`Menu`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:0
msgid "A digital receptionist element highlighted in an example dial plan."
msgstr "Elemen resepsionis digital yang disorot dalam contoh rencana panggil."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:144
msgid ""
"Dial plan elements can be configured by double-clicking them, and selecting "
"different features of the Axivox console to them."
msgstr ""
"Elemen rencana panggil dapat dikonfigurasi dengan mengklik dua kali, dan "
"memilih fitur konsol Axivox yang berbeda untuk elemen tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:147
msgid ""
"For example, an :guilabel:`Audio message` needs to be made, and then "
"selected in a :guilabel:`Play a file` or :guilabel:`Menu` element."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, :guilabel:`Pesan audio` perlu dibuat, kemudian dipilih dalam "
"elemen :guilabel:`Mainkan file` atau :guilabel:`Menu`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:150
msgid ""
"For more information, see this documentation :ref:`voip/axivox/"
"audio_messages`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, lihat dokumentasi :ref:`voip/axivox/"
"audio_messages`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:153
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:147
msgid "Advanced routing elements"
msgstr "Elemen perutean lanjutan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:155
msgid ""
"Advanced routing elements route calls automatically as they are received "
"into the incoming number(s). This can be configured using geo-location, "
"whitelisting, or time-based variables. Calls pass through a filter prior to "
"their final destination, and are routed, based on the set variable(s)."
msgstr ""
"Elemen perutean lanjutan merutekan panggilan secara otomatis saat diterima "
"ke nomor masuk. Ini dapat dikonfigurasi menggunakan geo-lokasi, daftar "
"putih, atau variabel berbasis waktu. Panggilan melewati filter sebelum "
"tujuan akhir mereka, dan dirutekan, berdasarkan variabel yang ditetapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:160
msgid "The following are advanced routing elements:"
msgstr "Berikut adalah elemen perutean lanjutan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:162
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dispatcher`: create a call filter to route traffic, based on the "
"geo-location of the caller ID."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dispatcher`: buat filter panggilan untuk merutekan lalu lintas, "
"berdasarkan geo-lokasi ID penelepon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:164
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Access List`: create a tailored access list, with VIP customer "
"preference."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Daftar Akses`: buat daftar akses yang disesuaikan, dengan "
"preferensi pelanggan VIP."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:165
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:154
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time Condition`: create time conditions to route incoming traffic "
"around holidays, or other sensitive time-frames."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kondisi Waktu`: buat kondisi waktu untuk merutekan lalu lintas "
"masuk seputar hari libur, atau kerangka waktu sensitif lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:169
msgid ""
"Whitelisting is a technical term used to create a list of allowed numbers. "
"Conversely, blacklisting is used to create a list of denied numbers."
msgstr ""
"Whitelisting adalah istilah teknis yang digunakan untuk membuat daftar nomor "
"yang diizinkan. Sebaliknya, blacklisting digunakan untuk membuat daftar "
"nomor yang ditolak."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:172
msgid ""
"To add one of these elements, navigate to the :guilabel:`Dial plans` page, "
"located in the menu on the left side of the `Axivox management console "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Next, click on the :guilabel:`Visual Editor` "
"button to the right of the dial plan, to edit the dial plan. Then, open "
"the :guilabel:`New element` drop-down menu, select the element, and "
"click :guilabel:`Add`. For more information, visit :ref:`voip/axivox/"
"dial_plans`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan salah satu elemen ini, navigasikan ke "
"halaman :guilabel:`Dial plans`, yang terletak di menu di sisi kiri `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Selanjutnya, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Visual Editor` di sebelah kanan dial plan untuk mengedit "
"dial plan. Kemudian, buka menu drop-down :guilabel:`New element`, pilih "
"elemen, dan klik :guilabel:`Add`. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, "
"kunjungi :ref:`voip/axivox/dial_plans`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:179
msgid "Dispatcher scenario"
msgstr "Skenario dispatcher"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:181
msgid ""
"A *Dispatcher* element is a dial plan feature that directs calls, based on "
"region or geo-location. In most cases, the :guilabel:`Dispatcher` element in "
"a dial plan is linked to the :guilabel:`Start` element, in order to filter "
"or screen calls as they come into an incoming number."
msgstr ""
"Elemen *Dispatcher* adalah fitur dial plan yang mengarahkan panggilan "
"berdasarkan wilayah atau lokasi geografis. Dalam sebagian besar kasus, "
"elemen :guilabel:`Dispatcher` dalam dial plan dihubungkan ke "
"elemen :guilabel:`Start`, untuk menyaring atau memfilter panggilan saat "
"masuk ke nomor incoming."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:185
msgid ""
"Double-click the :guilabel:`Dispatcher` element in the :guilabel:`Dialplan "
"Editor` pop-up window to configure it."
msgstr ""
"Klik dua kali elemen :guilabel:`Dispatcher` di jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` untuk mengonfigurasinya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:188
msgid ""
"This element checks numbers (routed through this element), according to "
"regular expressions. To add a regular expression, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` on the bottom of the :guilabel:`Dispatcher` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Elemen ini memeriksa nomor (yang dialihkan melalui elemen ini) sesuai dengan "
"ekspresi reguler. Untuk menambahkan ekspresi reguler, klik :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` di bagian bawah jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Dispatcher`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:192
msgid ""
"Then, under :guilabel:`Name`, enter a recognizable name to identify this "
"expression. This is the name that appears in the :guilabel:`Dispatcher` "
"element on the dial plan showcased in the :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` pop-up "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, di bawah :guilabel:`Name`, masukkan nama yang dapat dikenali untuk "
"mengidentifikasi ekspresi ini. Ini adalah nama yang muncul di "
"elemen :guilabel:`Dispatcher` pada dial plan yang ditampilkan di jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:196
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Regular expression` field, enter the country code, or area "
"code, which Axivox should route for incoming calls. This is especially "
"helpful when a company would like to filter their customers to certain "
"queues, or users based on the customer's geo-location."
msgstr ""
"Di bidang :guilabel:`Regular expression`, masukkan kode negara atau kode "
"area yang harus dialihkan oleh Axivox untuk panggilan masuk. Ini sangat "
"membantu ketika perusahaan ingin menyaring pelanggan mereka ke antrian "
"tertentu, atau pengguna berdasarkan lokasi geografis pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:200
msgid ""
"To specify all numbers behind a certain country code, or area code, include "
"`\\d+` after the country code, or country code + area code."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menentukan semua nomor di belakang kode negara atau kode area "
"tertentu, sertakan `\\d+` setelah kode negara, atau kode negara + kode area."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:None
msgid ""
"Dispatcher configuration panel, with name, regular expression and add a line "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Panel konfigurasi dispatcher, dengan name, regular expression, dan add a "
"line disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:208
msgid "`02\\\\d+`: validates the numbers starting with `02`"
msgstr "`02\\\\d+`: memvalidasi nomor yang dimulai dengan `02`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:209
msgid "`00\\\\d+`: validates all numbers beginning with `00`"
msgstr "`00\\\\d+`: memvalidasi semua nomor yang dimulai dengan `00`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:210
msgid ""
"`0052\\\\d+` validates all numbers beginning with `0052` (Mexico country "
"code)"
msgstr ""
"`0052\\\\d+` memvalidasi semua nomor yang dimulai dengan `0052` (kode negara "
"Meksiko)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:211
msgid ""
"`001716\\\\d+`: validates all numbers beginning with `001716` (USA country "
"code + Western New York area code)"
msgstr ""
"`001716\\\\d+`: memvalidasi semua nomor yang dimulai dengan `001716` (kode "
"negara AS + kode area Western New York)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:215
msgid ""
"A regular expression (shortened to \"regex\" or \"regexp\"), sometimes "
"referred to as a \"rational expression,\" is a sequence of characters that "
"specifies a match pattern in text. In other words, a match is made within "
"the given range of numbers."
msgstr ""
"Ekspresi reguler (disingkat \"regex\" atau \"regexp\"), kadang-kadang "
"disebut sebagai \"rational expression\", adalah urutan karakter yang "
"menentukan pola pencocokan dalam teks. Dengan kata lain, pencocokan dibuat "
"dalam rentang nomor yang diberikan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:219
msgid ""
"When the desired configurations are complete on the :guilabel:`Dispatcher` "
"pop-up window, be sure to click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Ketika konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai pada jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Dispatcher`, pastikan untuk mengklik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:222
msgid ""
"Upon doing so, the :guilabel:`Dispatcher` element appears with different "
"routes available to configure, based on the :guilabel:`Regular Expressions` "
"that were set."
msgstr ""
"Setelah melakukannya, elemen :guilabel:`Dispatcher` muncul dengan rute yang "
"berbeda yang tersedia untuk dikonfigurasi, berdasarkan :guilabel:`Regular "
"Expressions` yang telah ditetapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:225
msgid ""
"Attach these routes to any :guilabel:`New element` in "
"the :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Lampirkan rute ini ke :guilabel:`New element` mana pun di jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:227
msgid ""
"By default, there is an :guilabel:`Unknown` path that appears on "
"the :guilabel:`Dispatcher` element after setting at least "
"one :guilabel:`Regular Expression`."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, ada jalur :guilabel:`Unknown` yang muncul pada "
"elemen :guilabel:`Dispatcher` setelah menetapkan setidaknya "
"satu :guilabel:`Regular Expression`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:230
msgid ""
"Calls follow this route/path when their number does not match "
"any :guilabel:`Regular Expression` set on the :guilabel:`Dispatcher` element."
msgstr ""
"Panggilan mengikuti rute/jalur ini ketika nomor mereka tidak cocok "
"dengan :guilabel:`Regular Expression` mana pun yang ditetapkan pada "
"elemen :guilabel:`Dispatcher`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:None
msgid "Dial plan with dispatcher element highlighted."
msgstr "Dial plan dengan elemen dispatcher disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:238
msgid "Time condition scenario"
msgstr "Skenario kondisi waktu"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:240
msgid ""
"When a :guilabel:`Time Condition` element is added to a dial plan, it has a "
"simple :guilabel:`True` and :guilabel:`False` routing."
msgstr ""
"Ketika elemen :guilabel:`Kondisi Waktu` ditambahkan ke dial plan, elemen ini "
"memiliki perutean :guilabel:`Benar` dan :guilabel:`Salah` yang sederhana."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:243
msgid ""
"After adding the :guilabel:`Time Condition` element to a dial plan, double-"
"click it to configure the variables. :guilabel:`Hour/"
"Minute`, :guilabel:`Days of the week`, :guilabel:`Day of the month`, "
"and :guilabel:`Month` can all be configured."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menambahkan elemen :guilabel:`Kondisi Waktu` ke dial plan, klik "
"ganda untuk mengonfigurasi variabel. :guilabel:`Jam/Menit`, :guilabel:`Hari "
"dalam seminggu`, :guilabel:`Tanggal dalam bulan`, dan :guilabel:`Bulan` "
"semuanya dapat dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:247
msgid ""
"If the time which the caller contacts the incoming number matches the set "
"time conditions, then the :guilabel:`True` path is followed, otherwise "
"the :guilabel:`False` path is followed."
msgstr ""
"Jika waktu saat penelepon menghubungi nomor masuk cocok dengan kondisi waktu "
"yang ditetapkan, maka jalur :guilabel:`Benar` akan diikuti, jika tidak maka "
"jalur :guilabel:`Salah` akan diikuti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:251
msgid ""
"For a company that is closed yearly for the American Independence Day "
"holiday (July 4th) the following time conditions should be set:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk perusahaan yang tutup setiap tahun pada hari libur Hari Kemerdekaan "
"Amerika (4 Juli), kondisi waktu berikut harus ditetapkan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:254
msgid ":guilabel:`Hour/Minute` - `0:0 to 23:59`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jam/Menit` - `0:0 to 23:59`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:255
msgid ":guilabel:`Day of the week` - `All to All`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Hari dalam seminggu` - `All to All`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:256
msgid ":guilabel:`Day of the month` - `From 4 to 4`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tanggal dalam bulan` - `From 4 to 4`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:257
msgid ":guilabel:`Month` - `July`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Bulan` - `July`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:259
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Time Condition` element is especially useful for holidays, "
"weekends, and to set working hours. When a caller reaches a destination "
"where they can be helped, either with a real person or voicemail, this "
"reduces wasted time and hangups."
msgstr ""
"Elemen :guilabel:`Kondisi Waktu` sangat berguna untuk hari libur, akhir "
"pekan, dan untuk mengatur jam kerja. Ketika penelepon mencapai tujuan di "
"mana mereka dapat dibantu, baik dengan orang sungguhan atau pesan suara, ini "
"mengurangi waktu terbuang dan pemutusan telepon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:None
msgid ""
"Time condition element set in a dial plan on Axivox. Time condition is "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Elemen kondisi waktu yang ditetapkan dalam dial plan di Axivox. Kondisi "
"waktu disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:268
msgid ""
"To set the :guilabel:`Timezone` that the :guilabel:`Time Condition` operates "
"under, navigate to `Axivox management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, "
"and click :guilabel:`Settings` in the menu on the left. Then, set "
"the :guilabel:`Timezone` using the second field from the bottom, by clicking "
"the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur :guilabel:`Zona Waktu` yang digunakan oleh :guilabel:`Kondisi "
"Waktu`, navigasikan ke `konsol manajemen Axivox <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_, dan klik :guilabel:`Pengaturan` di menu sebelah kiri. "
"Kemudian, atur :guilabel:`Zona Waktu` menggunakan bidang kedua dari bawah, "
"dengan mengklik menu tarik-turun."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:274
msgid "Access list scenario"
msgstr "Skenario daftar akses"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:276
msgid ""
"An *Access List* element in a dial plan allows for the routing of certain "
"numbers, and disallows (denies) other numbers."
msgstr ""
"Elemen *Daftar Akses* dalam dial plan memungkinkan perutean nomor tertentu, "
"dan melarang (menolak) nomor lain."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:279
msgid ""
"After adding an :guilabel:`Access List` element to a dial plan, it can be "
"configured by double-clicking on the element directly in "
"the :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menambahkan elemen :guilabel:`Daftar Akses` ke dial plan, elemen "
"tersebut dapat dikonfigurasi dengan mengklik ganda pada elemen tersebut "
"langsung di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Editor Dialplan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:282
msgid ""
"Two fields appear where regular expressions can based in "
"the :guilabel:`Allow` and :guilabel:`Deny` fields of the :guilabel:`Access "
"List` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Dua bidang muncul di mana ekspresi reguler dapat dimasukkan dalam "
"bidang :guilabel:`Izinkan` dan :guilabel:`Tolak` pada jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Daftar Akses`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:286
msgid ""
"For a very important customer, their number can be set in "
"the :guilabel:`Allow` field, and these callers can be sent directly to "
"management."
msgstr ""
"Untuk pelanggan yang sangat penting, nomor mereka dapat ditetapkan di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Izinkan`, dan penelepon ini dapat dikirim langsung ke "
"manajemen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:290
msgid ""
"A regular expression (shortened to \"regex\" or \"regexp\"), sometimes also "
"referred to as a \"rational expression,\" is a sequence of characters that "
"specifies a match pattern in text."
msgstr ""
"Ekspresi reguler (disingkat \"regex\" atau \"regexp\"), kadang-kadang juga "
"disebut sebagai \"ekspresi rasional,\" adalah urutan karakter yang "
"menentukan pola pencocokan dalam teks."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:None
msgid ""
"Access list element configuration with the allow/deny fields highlighted."
msgstr "Konfigurasi elemen daftar akses dengan bidang izinkan/tolak disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:298
msgid "`2\\\\d\\\\d`: validates numbers from `200 to 299`"
msgstr "`2\\\\d\\\\d`: memvalidasi nomor dari `200 to 299`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:299
msgid "`02\\\\d*`: validates all numbers beginning with `02`"
msgstr "`02\\\\d*`: memvalidasi semua angka yang dimulai dengan `02`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:300
msgid "`0017165551212`: validates the number (`0017165551212`)"
msgstr "`0017165551212`: memvalidasi nomor (`0017165551212`)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:302
msgid ""
"After setting the :guilabel:`Allow` and :guilabel:`Deny` fields with regular "
"expressions or numbers, click :guilabel:`Save` on the :guilabel:`Access "
"List` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengatur kolom :guilabel:`Allow` dan :guilabel:`Deny` dengan "
"ekspresi reguler atau angka, klik :guilabel:`Save` pada jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Access List`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:305
msgid ""
"Then, on the :guilabel:`Access list` element in the dial plan, three paths "
"(or routes) are available to link to further actions."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, pada elemen :guilabel:`Access list` di dial plan, terdapat tiga "
"jalur (atau rute) yang tersedia untuk dihubungkan ke tindakan selanjutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:308
msgid ""
"Unknown calls can be routed through the regular menu flow by adding "
"a :guilabel:`Menu` element, and connecting it to the :guilabel:`Unknown` "
"path. :guilabel:`Refused` calls can be routed to the :guilabel:`Hang up` "
"element. Lastly, :guilabel:`Authorized` callers can be sent to a specific "
"extension or queue."
msgstr ""
"Panggilan tidak dikenal dapat dialihkan melalui alur menu reguler dengan "
"menambahkan elemen :guilabel:`Menu`, dan menghubungkannya ke "
"jalur :guilabel:`Unknown`. Panggilan :guilabel:`Refused` dapat dialihkan ke "
"elemen :guilabel:`Hang up`. Terakhir, penelepon :guilabel:`Authorized` dapat "
"dikirim ke ekstensi atau antrian tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:None
msgid "Access list element highlighted in an example dial plan."
msgstr "Elemen access list yang disorot dalam contoh dial plan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:318
msgid "Switches"
msgstr "Switch"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:320
msgid ""
"A *Switch* element in Axivox is a simple activated/deactivated route action."
msgstr ""
"Elemen *Switch* di Axivox adalah tindakan rute yang sederhana yang dapat "
"diaktifkan/dinonaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:322
msgid ""
"These can be activated or chosen quickly, allowing for quick routing "
"changes, without altering the dial plan."
msgstr ""
"Ini dapat diaktifkan atau dipilih dengan cepat, memungkinkan perubahan rute "
"yang cepat, tanpa mengubah dial plan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:325
msgid ""
"Alternate routes can be configured, so that in a moments notice, they can be "
"switched to. This could be for new availability, or to adjust traffic flow "
"for any number of reasons."
msgstr ""
"Rute alternatif dapat dikonfigurasi, sehingga dalam waktu singkat, dapat "
"dialihkan. Ini bisa untuk ketersediaan baru, atau untuk menyesuaikan aliran "
"lalu lintas untuk berbagai alasan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:328
msgid ""
"Axivox allows for a simple on/off switch, and a multi-switch, which can have "
"several paths to choose from."
msgstr ""
"Axivox memungkinkan switch on/off sederhana, dan multi-switch, yang dapat "
"memiliki beberapa jalur untuk dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:331
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Switch`: a manual on/off control that can divert traffic, based "
"on whether it is opened (on) or closed (off)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Switch`: kontrol manual on/off yang dapat mengalihkan lalu "
"lintas, berdasarkan apakah dibuka (on) atau ditutup (off)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:333
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:156
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Multi-Switch`: a mechanism to create paths, and turn them on and "
"off, to divert incoming calls."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Multi-Switch`: mekanisme untuk membuat jalur, dan mengaktifkan "
"atau menonaktifkannya, untuk mengalihkan panggilan masuk."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:337
msgid "Basic switch"
msgstr "Switch dasar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:339
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Switch` can be set in the `Axivox management console <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_ by navigating to :guilabel:`Switches` in the left menu. "
"To create a new switch click :guilabel:`Add a switch` from "
"the :guilabel:`Switches` dashboard, configure a :guilabel:`Name` for it, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Switch` dapat diatur di `konsol manajemen Axivox <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_ dengan menavigasi ke :guilabel:`Switches` di menu kiri. "
"Untuk membuat switch baru klik :guilabel:`Add a switch` dari "
"Dashboard :guilabel:`Switches`, konfigurasikan :guilabel:`Name` untuk switch "
"tersebut, dan klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:344
msgid ""
"Then, toggle the desired switch to either :guilabel:`On` or :guilabel:`Off`, "
"from the :guilabel:`State` column on the :guilabel:`Switches` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, toggle switch yang diinginkan ke :guilabel:`On` "
"atau :guilabel:`Off`, dari kolom :guilabel:`State` pada "
"Dashboard :guilabel:`Switches`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:347
msgid ""
"This :guilabel:`On` / :guilabel:`Off` state automatically routes traffic in "
"a dial plan, in which this switch is set."
msgstr ""
"Status :guilabel:`On` / :guilabel:`Off` ini secara otomatis mengalihkan lalu "
"lintas di dial plan, di mana switch ini diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:350
msgid ""
"The traffic travels to the :guilabel:`Active` route when :guilabel:`On` is "
"toggled in the switch. The call traffic travels to the :guilabel:`Inactive` "
"route when :guilabel:`Off` is toggled in the switch."
msgstr ""
"Lalu lintas berjalan ke rute :guilabel:`Active` ketika :guilabel:`On` "
"diaktifkan di switch. Lalu lintas panggilan berjalan ke "
"rute :guilabel:`Inactive` ketika :guilabel:`Off` diaktifkan di switch."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:354
msgid ""
"Changes can be made on the fly, just be sure to click :guilabel:`Apply "
"changes` to implement the them."
msgstr ""
"Perubahan dapat dilakukan secara langsung, pastikan untuk "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Apply changes` untuk menerapkannya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:358
msgid "Add a switch to dial plan"
msgstr "Tambahkan switch ke dial plan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:360
msgid ""
"To add a :guilabel:`Switch` to a dial plan, navigate to `Axivox management "
"console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, and click on :guilabel:`Dial plans` "
"in the left menu. Then, click :guilabel:`Visual Editor` next to the desired "
"dial plan to open the :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Switch` ke dial plan, navigasikan ke `konsol "
"manajemen Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, dan klik :guilabel:`Dial "
"plans` di menu kiri. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Visual Editor` di sebelah "
"dial plan yang diinginkan untuk membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Dialplan "
"Editor`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:365
msgid ""
"Then, from the :guilabel:`New element` drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Switch`, and then click :guilabel:`Add`. Double-click on "
"the element to further configure the :guilabel:`Switch` element."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`New element`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Switch`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Add`. Klik dua kali pada "
"elemen untuk mengonfigurasi lebih lanjut elemen :guilabel:`Switch`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:None
msgid ""
"Switch configuration in a dial plan, with inactive and active routes "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi switch di dial plan, dengan rute tidak aktif dan aktif yang "
"disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:373
msgid "Multi-switch"
msgstr "Multi-switch"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:375
msgid ""
"A *Multi-Switch* element in Axivox is a switch where multiple paths can be "
"configured, and switched between."
msgstr ""
"Elemen *Multi-Switch* di Axivox adalah switch di mana beberapa jalur dapat "
"dikonfigurasi dan dialihkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:378
msgid ""
"To configure and set a :guilabel:`Multi-Switch` element, navigate to `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Then, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Switches` menu item in the left menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi dan mengatur elemen :guilabel:`Multi-Switch`, "
"navigasikan ke `konsol manajemen Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. "
"Kemudian, klik item menu :guilabel:`Switches` di menu kiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:381
msgid ""
"Toggle to the :guilabel:`Multi-switch` tab to create, or set, a pre-"
"configured :guilabel:`Multi-Switch` element."
msgstr ""
"Beralih ke tab :guilabel:`Multi-switch` untuk membuat atau mengatur "
"elemen :guilabel:`Multi-Switch` yang telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:384
msgid ""
"To create a new :guilabel:`Multi-Switch`, click :guilabel:`Create new`. "
"Then, enter a :guilabel:`Name` for the element, and then enter "
"the :guilabel:`Available choice`. Enter one :guilabel:`Available choice` per "
"line. Do **not** duplicate any entries."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat :guilabel:`Multi-Switch` baru, klik :guilabel:`Create new`. "
"Kemudian, masukkan :guilabel:`Name` untuk elemen tersebut, lalu "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Available choice`. Masukkan satu :guilabel:`Available "
"choice` per baris. **Jangan** menduplikasi entri apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:388
msgid "Remember to click :guilabel:`Save` when done."
msgstr "Jangan lupa untuk klik :guilabel:`Save` setelah selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:390
msgid ""
"To select the :guilabel:`State` of the :guilabel:`Multi-Switch`, click the "
"drop-down menu next to the :guilabel:`Multi-Switch` name, under "
"the :guilabel:`Multi-switch` tab on the :guilabel:`Switches` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memilih :guilabel:`State` dari :guilabel:`Multi-Switch`, klik menu "
"drop-down di sebelah nama :guilabel:`Multi-Switch`, di bawah "
"tab :guilabel:`Multi-switch` pada Dashboard :guilabel:`Switches`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:394
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`State` chosen is the route that is followed in the dial plan. "
"The :guilabel:`State` can be edited on the fly, just be sure to "
"click :guilabel:`Apply changes`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`State` yang dipilih adalah rute yang diikuti di dial "
"plan. :guilabel:`State` dapat diedit secara langsung, pastikan untuk "
"klik :guilabel:`Apply changes`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:398
msgid "Add a multi-switch to dial plan"
msgstr "Tambahkan multi-switch ke dial plan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:400
msgid ""
"To add a :guilabel:`Multi-Switch` element to a dial plan, navigate to "
"`Axivox management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, and "
"click :guilabel:`Dial plans` in the left menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan elemen :guilabel:`Multi-Switch` ke dial plan, navigasikan "
"ke `konsol manajemen Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, dan "
"klik :guilabel:`Dial plans` di menu kiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:403
msgid ""
"Then, select or create a dial plan. Next, click :guilabel:`Visual Editor` on "
"the desired dial plan."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, pilih atau buat dial plan. Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Visual "
"Editor` pada dial plan yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:405
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` pop-up window that appears, click on "
"the :guilabel:`New element` drop-down menu, and select :guilabel:`Multi-"
"Switch`. Then, click :guilabel:`Add`. Double-click on the element to further "
"configure the :guilabel:`Switch` element."
msgstr ""
"Pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` yang muncul, klik menu drop-"
"down :guilabel:`New element`, dan pilih :guilabel:`Multi-Switch`. Kemudian, "
"klik :guilabel:`Add`. Klik dua kali pada elemen untuk mengonfigurasi lebih "
"lanjut elemen :guilabel:`Switch`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_advanced.rst:None
msgid ""
"Multi-switch configuration in a dial plan, with chosen route highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi multi-switch di dial plan, dengan rute yang dipilih disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:3
msgid "Dial plan basics"
msgstr "Dasar-dasar dial plan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:5
msgid ""
"When someone calls a business, they might need to get in contact with "
"customer support, a sales team, or even a person's direct line. The caller "
"might also be in search of some information about the business, such as "
"store hours. Or, they might want to leave a voicemail, so someone from the "
"company can call them back. With dial plans in Axivox, a company can manage "
"how incoming calls like this are handled."
msgstr ""
"Ketika seseorang menelepon bisnis, mereka mungkin perlu menghubungi dukungan "
"pelanggan, tim penjualan, atau bahkan saluran langsung seseorang. Penelepon "
"mungkin juga mencari informasi tentang bisnis, seperti jam operasional toko. "
"Atau, mereka mungkin ingin meninggalkan pesan suara, sehingga seseorang dari "
"perusahaan dapat menelepon mereka kembali. Dengan dial plan di Axivox, "
"perusahaan dapat mengelola bagaimana panggilan masuk seperti ini ditangani."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:11
msgid ""
"Using proper call architecture through a dial plan, callers get directed to "
"the right people, or to the right information, in a quick, efficient manner."
msgstr ""
"Dengan menggunakan arsitektur panggilan yang tepat melalui dial plan, "
"penelepon diarahkan ke orang yang tepat, atau ke informasi yang tepat, "
"dengan cara yang cepat dan efisien."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:14
msgid "This document covers the basic configuration of dial plans in Axivox."
msgstr "Dokumen ini mencakup konfigurasi dasar dial plan di Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:17
msgid ""
"For more information on advanced dial plans, visit :doc:`dial_plan_advanced`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang dial plan lanjutan, "
"kunjungi :doc:`dial_plan_advanced`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:20
msgid ""
"Using a browser add-on for spelling may hinder the use of the visual editor "
"in dial plans. Do not use a translator with the Axivox management console."
msgstr ""
"Penggunaan add-on browser untuk ejaan dapat menghambat penggunaan editor "
"visual dalam dial plan. Jangan gunakan penerjemah dengan konsol manajemen "
"Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:26
msgid "Dial plans"
msgstr "Dial plan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:28
msgid ""
"Access dial plans by navigating to `Axivox management console <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_, and clicking on :guilabel:`Dial plans` from the menu "
"on the left."
msgstr ""
"Akses dial plan dengan menavigasi ke `konsol manajemen Axivox <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_, dan klik :guilabel:`Dial plans` dari menu di sebelah "
"kiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:31
msgid ""
"To add a new dial plan from the :guilabel:`Dial plan` page, click the green "
"button labeled, :guilabel:`Add a new dial plan`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan dial plan baru dari halaman :guilabel:`Dial plan`, klik "
"tombol hijau berlabel :guilabel:`Add a new dial plan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:35
msgid ""
"Axivox has no limit to the number of dial plans that can be created. These "
"can be added, and improved upon, at any time. This allows for sandboxes to "
"be created with many different configurations."
msgstr ""
"Axivox tidak memiliki batasan jumlah dial plan yang dapat dibuat. Ini dapat "
"ditambahkan dan ditingkatkan kapan saja. Hal ini memungkinkan pembuatan "
"sandbox dengan berbagai konfigurasi yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:None
msgid ""
"Dial plan dashboard with the edit features and Add a dial plan button "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard dial plan dengan fitur edit dan tombol Add a dial plan disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:43
msgid ""
"To edit an existing dial plan, choose one of the following options to the "
"right of the saved dial plan:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit dial plan yang ada, pilih salah satu opsi berikut di sebelah "
"kanan dial plan yang tersimpan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`Delete`: this action deletes the attached dial plan."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Delete`: tindakan ini menghapus dial plan yang terlampir."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:47
msgid ":guilabel:`Edit`: this action allows the user to edit the dial plan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Edit`: tindakan ini memungkinkan user untuk mengedit dial plan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visual Editor`: this action opens a visual editor window, where "
"the dial plan architecture can be viewed and edited."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Visual Editor`: tindakan ini membuka jendela editor visual, di "
"mana arsitektur dial plan dapat dilihat dan diedit."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duplicate`: this action duplicates the dial plan, and puts it at "
"the bottom of the list, with an extension of one number (+1) larger than the "
"original extension."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Duplicate`: tindakan ini menduplikasi dial plan dan "
"menempatkannya di bagian bawah daftar, dengan ekstensi satu nomor (+1) lebih "
"besar dari ekstensi asli."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:54
msgid "Dialplan editor (visual editor)"
msgstr "Editor dialplan (editor visual)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:56
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Visual Editor` button is clicked for a dial plan on "
"the :guilabel:`Dial plan` page, a pop-up :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` window "
"appears."
msgstr ""
"Ketika tombol :guilabel:`Visual Editor` diklik untuk dial plan di "
"halaman :guilabel:`Dial plan`, jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` "
"akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:59
msgid ""
"This pop-up window is the primary place where the architecture, or "
"structure, of the dial plan is configured. In this window, a :abbr:`GUI "
"(graphical user interface)` appears, where various dial plan elements can be "
"configured and linked together."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up ini adalah tempat utama di mana arsitektur, atau struktur, "
"dial plan dikonfigurasi. Di jendela ini, muncul :abbr:`GUI (graphical user "
"interface)`, di mana berbagai elemen dial plan dapat dikonfigurasi dan "
"dihubungkan bersama."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:None
msgid ""
"Visual editor for an example dial plan, with the new element, Add, and Save "
"buttons\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Editor visual untuk contoh dial plan, dengan elemen baru, tombol Add, dan "
"Save yang disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:69
msgid ""
"New dial plans come blank with :guilabel:`New element` options for the user "
"to :guilabel:`Add` and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Dial plan baru datang dalam keadaan kosong dengan opsi :guilabel:`New "
"element` bagi user untuk :guilabel:`Add` dan :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:72
msgid ""
"The method for saving in the :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` is different from "
"saving any other edits in the Axivox management console because "
"the :guilabel:`Save` button **must** be pressed before closing "
"the :menuselection:`Visual editor`."
msgstr ""
"Metode penyimpanan di :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` berbeda dari penyimpanan "
"edit lainnya di konsol manajemen Axivox karena tombol :guilabel:`Save` "
"**harus** ditekan sebelum menutup :menuselection:`Visual editor`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:76
msgid ""
"Then, before these changes can take place on the Axivox platform, the user "
"**must** click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right corner of "
"the :guilabel:`Dial plan` page."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, sebelum perubahan ini dapat berlaku di platform Axivox, user "
"**harus** klik :guilabel:`Apply changes` di pojok kanan atas "
"halaman :guilabel:`Dial plan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:79
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` pop-up window, users can add a new "
"element to the dial plan. To do that, open the :guilabel:`New element` drop-"
"down menu, and select the desired element. Then, click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Dari jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor`, user dapat menambahkan "
"elemen baru ke dial plan. Untuk melakukannya, buka menu drop-"
"down :guilabel:`New element`, dan pilih elemen yang diinginkan. Kemudian, "
"klik :guilabel:`Add`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:83
msgid ""
"Doing so adds that element to the visual editor display of the dial plan "
"being modified. This element can be moved where desired amongst the other "
"elements present in the dial plan."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan ini menambahkan elemen tersebut ke tampilan editor visual dari "
"dial plan yang sedang dimodifikasi. Elemen ini dapat dipindahkan ke posisi "
"yang diinginkan di antara elemen-elemen lain yang ada di dial plan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:86
msgid ""
"Connect elements in the dial plan by clicking and dragging outward from "
"the :guilabel:`(open circle)` icon on the right side of the element. Doing "
"so reveals an :guilabel:`(arrow)` icon. Proceed to drag "
"this :guilabel:`(arrow)` icon to the desired element in the dial plan that "
"it is meant to connect with."
msgstr ""
"Hubungkan elemen-elemen dalam dial plan dengan mengklik dan menyeret keluar "
"dari ikon :guilabel:`(lingkaran terbuka)` di sisi kanan elemen. Melakukan "
"ini akan memunculkan ikon :guilabel:`(panah)`. Lanjutkan dengan menyeret "
"ikon :guilabel:`(panah)` ini ke elemen yang diinginkan dalam dial plan yang "
"akan dihubungkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:91
msgid ""
"Connect the :guilabel:`(arrow)` icon to the circle on the left side of the "
"desired element."
msgstr ""
"Hubungkan ikon :guilabel:`(panah)` ke lingkaran di sisi kiri elemen yang "
"diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:93
msgid ""
"Calls displayed in the dial plan flow from left-to-right in the element."
msgstr ""
"Panggilan yang ditampilkan dalam dial plan mengalir dari kiri ke kanan dalam "
"elemen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:95
msgid ""
"In order to further configure a :guilabel:`New element`, double-click on the "
"element inside the dial plan, to reveal a subsequent pop-up window, wherein "
"additional customizations can be entered."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi :guilabel:`Elemen baru` lebih lanjut, klik dua kali "
"pada elemen di dalam dial plan untuk memunculkan jendela pop-up selanjutnya, "
"di mana kustomisasi tambahan dapat dimasukkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:98
msgid ""
"Each element has a different configuration pop-up window that appears when "
"double-clicked."
msgstr ""
"Setiap elemen memiliki jendela pop-up konfigurasi yang berbeda yang muncul "
"saat diklik dua kali."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:101
msgid ""
"All elements **must** have a final destination in the dial plan in order to "
"close a loop. This can be accomplished by implementing the :guilabel:`Hang "
"up` element, or looping the element back to a :guilabel:`Menu` element "
"or :guilabel:`Digital Receptionist` element elsewhere in the dial plan."
msgstr ""
"Semua elemen **harus** memiliki tujuan akhir dalam dial plan untuk menutup "
"loop. Ini dapat dicapai dengan menerapkan elemen :guilabel:`Tutup`, atau "
"mengulang elemen kembali ke elemen :guilabel:`Menu` atau "
"elemen :guilabel:`Resepsionis Digital` di tempat lain dalam dial plan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:0
msgid ""
"Dial plan, shown with highlight looping open end back to the beginning of "
"the menu\n"
"element."
msgstr ""
"Dial plan, ditampilkan dengan sorotan yang mengulang ujung terbuka kembali "
"ke awal elemen menu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:111
msgid ""
"Once all desired dial plan elements and configurations are complete, "
"remember to click :guilabel:`Save` before exiting the :guilabel:`Dialplan "
"Editor` pop-up window. Then, click :guilabel:`Apply changes` on "
"the :guilabel:`Dial plans` page to ensure they are implemented into Axivox "
"production."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua elemen dan konfigurasi dial plan yang diinginkan selesai, "
"ingat untuk mengklik :guilabel:`Simpan` sebelum keluar dari jendela pop-"
"up :guilabel:`Editor Dialplan`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Terapkan "
"perubahan` pada halaman :guilabel:`Dial plans` untuk memastikan perubahan "
"diterapkan ke produksi Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:117
msgid "Dial plan elements"
msgstr "Elemen dial plan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:119
msgid ""
"The following elements are available in the :guilabel:`New element` drop-"
"down menu, while designing a dial plan in the :guilabel:`Dialplan Editor` "
"pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Elemen-elemen berikut tersedia dalam menu drop-down :guilabel:`Elemen baru`, "
"saat merancang dial plan di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Editor Dialplan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:123
msgid "Basic elements"
msgstr "Elemen dasar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:125
msgid ""
"These are the basic elements that are used in simple dial plans in Axivox:"
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah elemen dasar yang digunakan dalam dial plan sederhana di Axivox:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:127
msgid ":guilabel:`Call`: call an extension or queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Panggil`: panggil ekstensi atau antrian."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:128
msgid ":guilabel:`Play a file`: play an audio file or voice greeting."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Putar file`: putar file audio atau salam suara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:129
msgid ":guilabel:`Voicemail`: forward to a voicemail (terminal)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pesan suara`: teruskan ke pesan suara (terminal)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:130
msgid ":guilabel:`Hang up`: hang up the call (terminal)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tutup`: tutup panggilan (terminal)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Queue`: attach a call queue with a group of users to answer a "
"call."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Antrian`: lampirkan antrian panggilan dengan grup pengguna untuk "
"menjawab panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Conference`: add a conference room for a caller to connect to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Konferensi`: tambahkan ruang konferensi untuk penelepon terhubung."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:137
msgid ""
"Routing elements change or route the path of a caller, these are some basic "
"routing elements used in Axivox:"
msgstr ""
"Elemen perutean mengubah atau merutekan jalur penelepon, berikut adalah "
"beberapa elemen perutean dasar yang digunakan di Axivox:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Menu`: add a dial-by-number directory and configure downstream "
"actions (not terminal)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Menu`: tambahkan direktori dial-by-number dan konfigurasikan "
"tindakan downstream (bukan terminal)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:141
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Switch`: attach a manual on/off control that can divert traffic "
"based on whether it is opened (On) or closed (Off)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Switch`: pasang kontrol manual on/off yang dapat mengalihkan lalu "
"lintas berdasarkan apakah terbuka (On) atau tertutup (Off)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Digital Receptionist`: attach a virtual dispatcher to listen for "
"extensions to connect to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Digital Receptionist`: pasang dispatcher virtual untuk "
"mendengarkan ekstensi yang akan dihubungkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:149
msgid "These are the more advanced elements that route calls in Axivox:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut adalah elemen yang lebih canggih yang merutekan panggilan di Axivox:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:151
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dispatcher`: create a call filter to route traffic based on the "
"geo-location of the caller ID."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dispatcher`: buat filter panggilan untuk merutekan lalu lintas "
"berdasarkan geo-lokasi ID penelepon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Access List`: create a tailored access list with VIP customer "
"preference."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Access List`: buat daftar akses yang disesuaikan dengan "
"preferensi pelanggan VIP."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:162
msgid "The following are more advanced elements (not routing) in Axivox:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut ini adalah elemen yang lebih canggih (bukan routing) di Axivox:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:169
msgid ""
"Dial plan elements can be configured by double-clicking them, and linking "
"different aspects of the Axivox console to them."
msgstr ""
"Elemen dial plan dapat dikonfigurasi dengan mengklik dua kali pada elemen "
"tersebut, dan menghubungkan berbagai aspek konsol Axivox ke elemen tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:173
msgid "Attach to incoming number"
msgstr "Pasang ke nomor masuk"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:175
msgid ""
"To attach an existing dial plan to an incoming number, go to `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_ , and click "
"on :guilabel:`Incoming numbers`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memasang dial plan yang ada ke nomor masuk, buka `konsol manajemen "
"Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, dan klik :guilabel:`Incoming numbers`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:178
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Edit` next to the number to which the dial plan "
"should be attached."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Edit` di sebelah nomor yang akan dipasangi dial "
"plan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:180
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a separate page wherein that number's dial plan can be "
"modified. To do that, select :guilabel:`Dial plan` from "
"the :guilabel:`Destination type for voice call` field drop-down menu. Then, "
"choose the desired dial plan from the :guilabel:`Dial plan` field that "
"appears."
msgstr ""
"Dengan melakukan ini akan menampilkan halaman terpisah di mana dial plan "
"nomor tersebut dapat dimodifikasi. Untuk melakukannya, pilih :guilabel:`Dial "
"plan` dari menu drop-down bidang :guilabel:`Destination type for voice "
"call`. Kemudian, pilih dial plan yang diinginkan dari bidang :guilabel:`Dial "
"plan` yang muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:184
msgid ""
"With that in place, that means when that specific number calls in, the "
"configured dial plan is activated, and runs through the prompts to properly "
"route the caller."
msgstr ""
"Dengan pengaturan tersebut, berarti ketika nomor tertentu tersebut melakukan "
"panggilan masuk, dial plan yang dikonfigurasi akan diaktifkan dan "
"menjalankan prompt untuk merutekan penelepon dengan benar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:187
msgid ""
"Finally, :guilabel:`Save` the changes, and click :guilabel:`Apply changes` "
"in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, :guilabel:`Save` perubahan tersebut, dan klik :guilabel:`Apply "
"changes` di sudut kanan atas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:191
msgid "Basic dial plan scenario"
msgstr "Skenario dial plan dasar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:193
msgid ""
"The following showcases a basic dial plan scenario for call routing, where "
"additional elements can be added to expand the setup. This basic dial plan "
"scenario includes the following linked elements :menuselection:`Start --> "
"Play a file --> Menu --> (Hang-up, Calls, Queues, Conferences) --> "
"(Voicemail, Hang-up)`."
msgstr ""
"Berikut ini menampilkan skenario dial plan dasar untuk routing panggilan, di "
"mana elemen tambahan dapat ditambahkan untuk memperluas pengaturan. Skenario "
"dial plan dasar ini mencakup elemen yang terhubung "
"berikut :menuselection:`Start --> Play a file --> Menu --> (Hang-up, Calls, "
"Queues, Conferences) --> (Voicemail, Hang-up)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:None
msgid "Basic dial plan configuration."
msgstr "Konfigurasi dial plan dasar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dial_plan_basics.rst:203
msgid ""
"This setup does **not** include any basic or advanced call routing. For more "
"information on call routing, reference this "
"documentation: :doc:`dial_plan_advanced`."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan ini **tidak** menyertakan routing panggilan dasar atau lanjutan. "
"Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang routing panggilan, rujuk dokumentasi "
"ini: :doc:`dial_plan_advanced`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:3
msgid "Dynamic caller ID"
msgstr "ID penelepon dinamis"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Caller ID* identifies the caller when they make a phone call. It allows the "
"recipient of the call to see what number the caller is calling from. Caller "
"ID shows users and clients who is calling, so they can choose to pick up or "
"decline the call."
msgstr ""
"*Caller ID* mengidentifikasi penelepon saat mereka melakukan panggilan "
"telepon. Ini memungkinkan penerima panggilan untuk melihat nomor mana yang "
"digunakan penelepon untuk menelepon. Caller ID menunjukkan kepada pengguna "
"dan klien siapa yang menelepon, sehingga mereka dapat memilih untuk menjawab "
"atau menolak panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:9
msgid ""
"Axivox offers a dynamic caller ID option to choose which number is displayed "
"on outgoing calls."
msgstr ""
"Axivox menawarkan opsi caller ID dinamis untuk memilih nomor mana yang "
"ditampilkan pada panggilan keluar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:11
msgid ""
"International numbers can be purchased to do business transactions "
"internationally, via a phone call, from a number that has an area code or "
"country code of the destination being called. By displaying a local number, "
"this can increase customer engagement."
msgstr ""
"Nomor internasional dapat dibeli untuk melakukan transaksi bisnis secara "
"internasional, melalui panggilan telepon, dari nomor yang memiliki kode area "
"atau kode negara dari tujuan yang dipanggil. Dengan menampilkan nomor lokal, "
"hal ini dapat meningkatkan keterlibatan pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:15
msgid ""
"Some companies have many employees making calls from a call center. These "
"employees are not always available to receive a return phone call from a "
"prospective customer. In this case, :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet "
"Protocol)` can be configured in such a way that dynamic caller ID shows the "
"main company phone number, so any number of employees in the group can "
"answer the call. This way, a call is never missed."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa perusahaan memiliki banyak karyawan yang melakukan panggilan dari "
"call center. Karyawan ini tidak selalu tersedia untuk menerima panggilan "
"balik dari calon pelanggan. Dalam kasus ini, :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over "
"Internet Protocol)` dapat dikonfigurasi sedemikian rupa sehingga caller ID "
"dinamis menampilkan nomor telepon utama perusahaan, sehingga sejumlah "
"karyawan dalam grup dapat menjawab panggilan. Dengan cara ini, panggilan "
"tidak akan pernah terlewat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:24
msgid "Default outgoing number"
msgstr "Nomor keluar default"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:26
msgid ""
"In Axivox a *default number* can be set. This is a company's main number. "
"This means, when anyone from the company (user/employee) calls a number "
"outside the company, the default outgoing number shows up automatically on "
"the caller ID."
msgstr ""
"Di Axivox, *nomor default* dapat diatur. Ini adalah nomor utama perusahaan. "
"Artinya, ketika siapa pun dari perusahaan (user/karyawan) menelepon nomor di "
"luar perusahaan, nomor keluar default muncul secara otomatis pada caller ID."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:30
msgid ""
"If someone from outside the company tries to call back a user/employee, they "
"are then funneled back through the main line (default number). If there is a "
"dial plan set up, they are prompted to make selections. This is especially "
"helpful in cases where employees change positions frequently, or if they "
"leave the company."
msgstr ""
"Jika seseorang dari luar perusahaan mencoba menelepon balik user/karyawan, "
"mereka kemudian disalurkan kembali melalui saluran utama (nomor default). "
"Jika ada dial plan yang diatur, mereka diminta untuk membuat pilihan. Ini "
"sangat membantu dalam kasus di mana karyawan sering berganti posisi, atau "
"jika mereka meninggalkan perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:39
msgid ""
"To access the default number, go to the `Axivox management console <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_, and log in. Then, click into :guilabel:`Settings` in "
"the left menu, and navigate to :guilabel:`Default outgoing number`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses nomor default, buka `konsol manajemen Axivox <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_, dan masuk. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Settings` di menu "
"sebelah kiri, dan navigasikan ke :guilabel:`Default outgoing number`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:43
msgid ""
"From here, change the :guilabel:`Default outgoing number` by clicking the "
"drop-down menu, and making a selection from the incoming phone numbers "
"available on Axivox."
msgstr ""
"Dari sini, ubah :guilabel:`Default outgoing number` dengan mengklik menu "
"drop-down, dan membuat pilihan dari nomor telepon masuk yang tersedia di "
"Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:46
msgid ""
"Be sure to :guilabel:`Save` the changes, then click :guilabel:`Apply "
"changes` in the upper-right corner of the :guilabel:`General Settings` page "
"to implement the change."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan untuk :guilabel:`Save` perubahan tersebut, kemudian "
"klik :guilabel:`Apply changes` di sudut kanan atas "
"halaman :guilabel:`General Settings` untuk menerapkan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:49
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Default outgoing number` is what shows up by default in the "
"Axivox management portal. However, the outgoing number can also be "
"configured differently at the user level."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Default outgoing number` adalah yang muncul secara default di "
"portal manajemen Axivox. Namun, nomor keluar juga dapat dikonfigurasi secara "
"berbeda di tingkat user."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:53
msgid "Users"
msgstr "Pengguna"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:55
msgid ""
"To configure the outgoing number at the user level, log in to the `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Next, "
"click :guilabel:`Users` from the menu on the left, and then "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` to the right of the user that is to be configured."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi nomor keluar di tingkat user, masuk ke `konsol "
"manajemen Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Selanjutnya, "
"klik :guilabel:`Users` dari menu di sebelah kiri, kemudian "
"klik :guilabel:`Edit` di sebelah kanan user yang akan dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:59
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Outgoing number`, click the drop-down menu to select either "
"the :guilabel:`Default outgoing number` (as specified here: :ref:`voip/"
"axivox/dynamic-caller-id-default`), or any of the incoming numbers on the "
"Axivox account."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah :guilabel:`Outgoing number`, klik menu drop-down untuk "
"memilih :guilabel:`Default outgoing number` (seperti yang ditentukan di "
"sini: :ref:`voip/axivox/dynamic-caller-id-default`), atau salah satu dari "
"nomor masuk di akun Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:63
msgid ""
"Choosing the :guilabel:`Default` selection in the :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"number` drop-down menu ensures this user has the :guilabel:`Default outgoing "
"number` shown on their caller ID when making calls."
msgstr ""
"Memilih pilihan :guilabel:`Default` di menu drop-down :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"number` memastikan user ini memiliki :guilabel:`Default outgoing number` "
"yang ditampilkan pada caller ID mereka saat melakukan panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:66
msgid ""
"If a specific number is chosen, and that number is assigned to this user "
"under :guilabel:`Incoming numbers` (in the Axivox console's menu on the "
"left), that means this user has a direct line for customers to reach them."
msgstr ""
"Jika nomor tertentu dipilih, dan nomor tersebut ditetapkan kepada user ini "
"di bawah :guilabel:`Incoming numbers` (di menu konsol Axivox di sebelah "
"kiri), itu berarti user ini memiliki saluran langsung bagi pelanggan untuk "
"menghubungi mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:70
msgid ""
"Once the desired changes are complete, be sure to click :guilabel:`Save`, "
"then click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right corner to implement "
"the change."
msgstr ""
"Setelah perubahan yang diinginkan selesai, pastikan untuk "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Save`, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Apply changes` di sudut "
"kanan atas untuk menerapkan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:74
msgid ""
"By default, when creating a new user in Axivox, the :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"number` is automatically set to :guilabel:`Default`."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, saat membuat user baru di Axivox, :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"number` secara otomatis diatur ke :guilabel:`Default`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:78
msgid "Advanced options"
msgstr "Opsi-opsi tingkat lanjut"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:80
msgid ""
"To access the :guilabel:`Advanced options`, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` option in the menu on the left of the `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Advanced options` to the right of :guilabel:`Default "
"outgoing number`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses :guilabel:`Advanced options`, navigasikan ke "
"opsi :guilabel:`Settings` di menu sebelah kiri `konsol manajemen Axivox "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Advanced options` "
"di sebelah kanan :guilabel:`Default outgoing number`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:84
msgid ""
"By default, there are not any advanced rules set. To create one, click the "
"green :guilabel:`+ (plus)` icon. Doing so reveals a line with two blank "
"fields. From here, different caller IDs can be set up, depending on what "
"location the user/employee is calling from."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, tidak ada aturan lanjutan yang diatur. Untuk membuatnya, "
"klik ikon hijau :guilabel:`+ (plus)`. Melakukan hal ini akan menampilkan "
"baris dengan dua kolom kosong. Dari sini, caller ID yang berbeda dapat "
"diatur, tergantung pada lokasi mana user/karyawan melakukan panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:88
msgid ""
"To create a rule, first set the :guilabel:`Destination prefix` in the first "
"empty field. This is the country code, complete with zero(s) in front of it. "
"Then, in the second empty field, select the phone number that should be used "
"for calling out from that country code."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat aturan, pertama atur :guilabel:`Destination prefix` di kolom "
"kosong pertama. Ini adalah kode negara, lengkap dengan nol di depannya. "
"Kemudian, di kolom kosong kedua, pilih nomor telepon yang harus digunakan "
"untuk panggilan keluar dari kode negara tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:93
msgid ""
"Check the box for :guilabel:`Apply advanced rules even for users with a "
"default outgoing number configured` to allow these rules to take precedent "
"over all other outgoing configurations."
msgstr ""
"Centang kotak untuk :guilabel:`Apply advanced rules even for users with a "
"default outgoing number configured` agar aturan ini lebih diutamakan "
"daripada semua konfigurasi keluar lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:97
msgid ""
"The order of the rules can be modified by dragging-and-dropping them into "
"another order. The first matching rule is applied."
msgstr ""
"Urutan aturan dapat diubah dengan cara menarik dan melepaskannya ke urutan "
"lain. Aturan pertama yang cocok akan diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:101
msgid ""
"For example, a company wants all users/employees to utilize the configured "
"number for Great Britain when calling from the `0044` country code (Great "
"Britain)."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, sebuah perusahaan ingin semua user/karyawan menggunakan nomor yang "
"dikonfigurasi untuk Britania Raya saat menelepon dari kode negara `0044` "
"(Britania Raya)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:104
msgid ""
"To accomplish that, simply type in `0044` into the :guilabel:`Destination "
"prefix` field, and select the number starting with the `+44` country code. "
"Order the rules as necessary, and select the checkbox to supersede all other "
"rules, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melakukannya, cukup ketik `0044` ke dalam field :guilabel:`Awalan "
"Tujuan`, dan pilih nomor yang dimulai dengan kode negara `+44`. Atur urutan "
"aturan sesuai kebutuhan, dan centang kotak untuk menggantikan semua aturan "
"lain, jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:0
msgid "Advanced options for the default outgoing number."
msgstr "Opsi lanjutan untuk nomor keluar default."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/dynamic_caller_id.rst:112
msgid ""
"Once the desired configurations are complete, be sure to "
"click :guilabel:`Save`, then click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-"
"right corner to implement the change."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, pastikan untuk "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Simpan`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Terapkan perubahan` di "
"pojok kanan atas untuk menerapkan perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:3
msgid "Manage users in Axivox"
msgstr "Mengelola user di Axivox"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:5
msgid ""
"Managing Axivox :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` users is an "
"important part of setting up :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` in "
"an Odoo database. Each Axivox user has a unique name, phone number and/or "
"extension, and a voicemail. This way, they can be reached in a variety of "
"convenient ways."
msgstr ""
"Mengelola user :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` Axivox adalah "
"bagian penting dari pengaturan :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` "
"di database Odoo. Setiap user Axivox memiliki nama unik, nomor telepon dan/"
"atau ekstensi, dan voicemail. Dengan cara ini, mereka dapat dihubungi dengan "
"berbagai cara yang mudah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:10
msgid ""
"Axivox users are organized in a simple, straightforward way in the Axivox "
"console, so an administrator can manage users quickly and easily."
msgstr ""
"User Axivox diatur dengan cara yang sederhana dan mudah di konsol Axivox, "
"sehingga administrator dapat mengelola user dengan cepat dan mudah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:14
msgid ""
"This documentation covers how to configure everything through a provider "
"called, Axivox. Depending on the chosen VoIP provider, the processes to "
"manage users may be different."
msgstr ""
"Dokumentasi ini mencakup cara mengonfigurasi semuanya melalui penyedia yang "
"disebut Axivox. Tergantung pada penyedia VoIP yang dipilih, proses untuk "
"mengelola user mungkin berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:18
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:20
msgid ""
"Begin at the Axivox management console by navigating to `https://"
"manage.axivox.com <https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Log in with the appropriate "
"administrator credentials."
msgstr ""
"Mulai dari konsol manajemen Axivox dengan membuka `https://manage.axivox.com "
"<https://manage.axivox.com>`_. Masuk dengan kredensial administrator yang "
"sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:24
msgid ""
"Actions in the Axivox management console **must** be double-saved, in order "
"for the changes to take effect. To save any changes, click :guilabel:`Save` "
"in the individualized changes screen. Then, to implement those changes, "
"click the :guilabel:`Apply Changes` button in the upper-right corner of the "
"console."
msgstr ""
"Tindakan di konsol manajemen Axivox **harus** disimpan dua kali, agar "
"perubahan dapat diterapkan. Untuk menyimpan perubahan apa pun, "
"klik :guilabel:`Simpan` di layar perubahan individual. Kemudian, untuk "
"menerapkan perubahan tersebut, klik tombol :guilabel:`Terapkan Perubahan` di "
"pojok kanan atas konsol."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:34
msgid ""
"Incoming numbers are all the numbers a company is paying to use to receive "
"calls."
msgstr ""
"Nomor masuk adalah semua nomor yang dibayar oleh perusahaan untuk digunakan "
"menerima panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:36
msgid ""
"Click on :menuselection:`Incoming numbers` from the menu on the left of the "
"Axivox management console. Doing so reveals the :guilabel:`Incoming numbers` "
"page, where all the incoming numbers are listed, along with "
"their :guilabel:`Destination` and SMS information."
msgstr ""
"Klik :menuselection:`Nomor masuk` dari menu di sebelah kiri konsol manajemen "
"Axivox. Tindakan ini akan menampilkan halaman :guilabel:`Nomor masuk`, di "
"mana semua nomor masuk terdaftar, beserta informasi :guilabel:`Tujuan` dan "
"SMS-nya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:40
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Destination` determines the action that is taken, or the path "
"the caller follows when dialing said numbers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tujuan` menentukan tindakan yang diambil, atau jalur yang diikuti "
"penelepon saat memanggil nomor tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:43
msgid ""
"To edit the :guilabel:`Destination`, click the :guilabel:`Edit` button to "
"the far-right of the incoming number line to be modified. Then, on "
"the :guilabel:`Edit number` page that appears, the :guilabel:`Destination "
"type for voice call` can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit :guilabel:`Tujuan`, klik tombol :guilabel:`Edit` di sisi "
"paling kanan dari baris nomor masuk yang akan diubah. Kemudian, pada "
"halaman :guilabel:`Edit nomor` yang muncul, :guilabel:`Jenis tujuan untuk "
"panggilan suara` dapat diubah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:47
msgid ""
"The options available in the :guilabel:`Destination type for voice call` "
"drop-down menu are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Opsi yang tersedia di menu drop-down :guilabel:`Jenis tujuan untuk panggilan "
"suara` adalah sebagai berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Not configured`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tidak dikonfigurasi`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:51
msgid ":guilabel:`Extension`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ekstensi`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:52
msgid ":guilabel:`Dial plan`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Rencana panggilan`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:53
msgid ":guilabel:`Voicemail`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Voicemail`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:54
msgid ":guilabel:`Hang up`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tutup`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:55
msgid ":guilabel:`Conference`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Konferensi`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:57
msgid ""
"Depending on the selection made in the :guilabel:`Destination type for voice "
"call` drop-down menu, a second, selection-specific drop-down menu is "
"populated with further configuration options. Additionally, more fields are "
"revealed, based on the selection made in the :guilabel:`Destination type for "
"voice call` drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada pilihan yang dibuat dalam menu drop-down :guilabel:`Jenis "
"tujuan untuk panggilan suara`, menu drop-down kedua yang spesifik untuk "
"pilihan tersebut akan diisi dengan opsi konfigurasi lebih lanjut. Selain "
"itu, lebih banyak field akan ditampilkan berdasarkan pilihan yang dibuat "
"dalam menu drop-down :guilabel:`Jenis tujuan untuk panggilan suara`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:62
msgid ""
"Once the desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right corner to implement them."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`, "
"kemudian klik :guilabel:`Terapkan perubahan` di sudut kanan atas untuk "
"menerapkannya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:66
msgid "New users"
msgstr "User baru"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:68
msgid ""
"Every employee using :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` at the "
"company needs an Axivox user account associated with them."
msgstr ""
"Setiap karyawan yang menggunakan :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` "
"di perusahaan memerlukan akun user Axivox yang terkait dengan mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:71
msgid ""
"To view existing users in the Axivox management console, "
"click :guilabel:`Users` from the menu on the left of the console. Every user "
"has a :guilabel:`Number`, :guilabel:`Name`, option for "
"a :guilabel:`Voicemail`, and an :guilabel:`Outgoing number` specified."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat user yang ada di konsol manajemen Axivox, "
"klik :guilabel:`User` dari menu di sisi kiri konsol. Setiap user "
"memiliki :guilabel:`Nomor`, :guilabel:`Nama`, opsi untuk :guilabel:`Pesan "
"suara`, dan :guilabel:`Nomor keluar` yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:75
msgid ""
"To create a new user in the Axivox console, click :guilabel:`Add a user` to "
"reveal a :guilabel:`New user` form. The following tabs are available for "
"configuring the new user:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat user baru di konsol Axivox, klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan user` "
"untuk menampilkan formulir :guilabel:`User baru`. Tab berikut tersedia untuk "
"mengkonfigurasi user baru:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`General`: basic information, including the extension of the user, "
"can be set."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Umum`: informasi dasar, termasuk ekstensi user, dapat diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Forwardings`: internal forwards on 'no answer' or busy signals."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penerusan`: penerusan internal saat 'tidak dijawab' atau sinyal "
"sibuk."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:80
msgid ":guilabel:`Follow Me`: external forward configuration."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ikuti Saya`: konfigurasi penerusan eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:81
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Keys`: set hot-keys within the :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet "
"Protocol)` system."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tombol`: atur tombol pintas dalam sistem :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over "
"Internet Protocol)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`SIP Identifiers`: :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)` "
"username and password for external configuration."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pengenal SIP`: nama user dan kata sandi :abbr:`SIP (Session "
"Initiation Protocol)` untuk konfigurasi eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Permissions`: set access rights for users in the Axivox "
"management console."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izin`: atur hak akses untuk user di konsol manajemen Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:87
msgid "General tab"
msgstr "Tab umum"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:89
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`General` tab of the :guilabel:`New user` form, in "
"the :guilabel:`Extension` field, input an extension that is unique to the "
"user. This is the number internal users dial to reach a specific employee."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Umum` dari formulir :guilabel:`User baru`, dalam "
"field :guilabel:`Ekstensi`, masukkan ekstensi yang unik untuk user. Ini "
"adalah nomor yang dihubungi user internal untuk menghubungi karyawan "
"tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:93
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Name` field, input the employee name."
msgstr "Dalam field :guilabel:`Nama`, masukkan nama karyawan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:95
msgid ""
"Next, fill out the :guilabel:`Email address of the user` field. A valid "
"email address for the employee should be added here, where the user receives "
"business emails."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, isi field :guilabel:`Alamat email user`. Alamat email yang "
"valid untuk karyawan harus ditambahkan di sini, di mana user menerima email "
"bisnis."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:98
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`GSM number` field, enter an alternative number at which "
"the user can be reached. Be sure to include the country code."
msgstr ""
"Dalam field :guilabel:`Nomor GSM`, masukkan nomor alternatif di mana user "
"dapat dihubungi. Pastikan untuk menyertakan kode negara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:102
msgid ""
"A country code is a locator code that allows access to the desired country's "
"phone system. The country code is dialed first, prior to the target number. "
"Each country in the world has its own specific country code."
msgstr ""
"Kode negara adalah kode lokasi yang memungkinkan akses ke sistem telepon "
"negara yang diinginkan. Kode negara dihubungi terlebih dahulu, sebelum nomor "
"tujuan. Setiap negara di dunia memiliki kode negara spesifiknya sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:106
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/onsip.rst:113
msgid ""
"For a list of comprehensive country codes, visit: `https://countrycode.org "
"<https://countrycode.org>`_."
msgstr ""
"Untuk daftar lengkap kode negara, kunjungi: `https://countrycode.org "
"<https://countrycode.org>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:None
msgid "General tab layout in the Axivox management console."
msgstr "Tata letak tab General di konsol manajemen Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:113
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Voicemail` field, select either :guilabel:`Yes` "
"or :guilabel:`No` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Pada field :guilabel:`Voicemail`, pilih :guilabel:`Yes` atau :guilabel:`No` "
"dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:116
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Directory` field, the administrator has the option to "
"leave it blank, by making no changes, or selecting :guilabel:`Default` from "
"the drop-down menu. The :guilabel:`Directory` is used in the *Digital "
"Receptionist* feature element of a dial-plan."
msgstr ""
"Pada field :guilabel:`Directory`, administrator memiliki opsi untuk "
"membiarkannya kosong, dengan tidak membuat perubahan, atau "
"memilih :guilabel:`Default` dari menu drop-down. :guilabel:`Directory` "
"digunakan dalam elemen fitur *Digital Receptionist* dari dial-plan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:120
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the :guilabel:`General` tab, there are two separate options "
"with selection boxes."
msgstr ""
"Di bagian bawah tab :guilabel:`General`, terdapat dua opsi terpisah dengan "
"kotak pilihan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:122
msgid ""
"The first option is :guilabel:`This user can receive multiple calls at the "
"same time`. By selecting this option, users are able to receive calls when "
"on another call."
msgstr ""
"Opsi pertama adalah :guilabel:`This user can receive multiple calls at the "
"same time`. Dengan memilih opsi ini, user dapat menerima panggilan saat "
"sedang dalam panggilan lain."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:125
msgid ""
"The second option, :guilabel:`This user must log-in to call`, provides the "
"option to make it mandatory for the user to log in."
msgstr ""
"Opsi kedua, :guilabel:`This user must log-in to call`, menyediakan opsi "
"untuk mewajibkan user untuk login."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:129
msgid ""
"If a company uses physical VoIP phones on desks, and wants their employees "
"to be able to log in from *any* phone or desk in the office, they would make "
"the selection for :guilabel:`This user must log-in to call`."
msgstr ""
"Jika sebuah perusahaan menggunakan telepon VoIP fisik di meja, dan ingin "
"karyawan mereka dapat login dari *sembarang* telepon atau meja di kantor, "
"mereka akan membuat pilihan untuk :guilabel:`This user must log-in to call`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:133
msgid ""
"Once the desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, klik :guilabel:`Save`, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Apply changes` di pojok kanan atas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:139
msgid "Forwardings tab"
msgstr "Tab Forwardings"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:141
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Forwardings` tab of the :guilabel:`New user` form, a "
"company can decide what happens if someone calls a user, and the call is not "
"answered."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Forwardings` dari formulir :guilabel:`New user`, "
"perusahaan dapat memutuskan apa yang terjadi jika seseorang menelepon user, "
"dan panggilan tidak dijawab."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:145
msgid ""
"Forwardings are disabled when the :guilabel:`Follow Me` option is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Forwardings dinonaktifkan ketika opsi :guilabel:`Follow Me` diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:147
msgid ""
"For example, under the :guilabel:`Forwarding on no answer` field, when the "
"button for :guilabel:`Add a destination` is selected, the option to add a "
"specific user or phone number is revealed. After entering "
"the :guilabel:`Destination`, a specific time frame can be selected by "
"sliding the :guilabel:`seconds bar` to the desired ring time."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, di bawah field :guilabel:`Forwarding on no answer`, ketika "
"tombol :guilabel:`Add a destination` dipilih, opsi untuk menambahkan user "
"atau nomor telepon tertentu ditampilkan. Setelah "
"memasukkan :guilabel:`Destination`, kerangka waktu tertentu dapat dipilih "
"dengan menggeser :guilabel:`seconds bar` ke waktu dering yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:152
msgid ""
"Additional :guilabel:`Destinations` can be added on with different ring "
"times."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Destinations` tambahan dapat ditambahkan dengan waktu dering yang "
"berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:155
msgid ""
"Ring times can be staggered, so the call is forwarded to another user after "
"the first user does not pick up the call. The option to :guilabel:`Send to "
"voicemail as a last resort` is available to the administrator, should "
"the :guilabel:`Destinations` not pick up."
msgstr ""
"Waktu dering dapat dibuat berselang-seling, sehingga panggilan diteruskan ke "
"user lain setelah user pertama tidak mengangkat panggilan. Opsi "
"untuk :guilabel:`Send to voicemail as a last resort` tersedia untuk "
"administrator, jika :guilabel:`Destinations` tidak mengangkat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:159
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Forwarding on busy` field, an administrator "
"can :guilabel:`Add a destination`. When clicked, they can then set "
"the :guilabel:`Destination` (user) and time frame. Should the original "
"user's :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` extension, or incoming "
"number, be busy, the call is forwarded to the destination(s)."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah field :guilabel:`Forwarding on busy`, administrator "
"dapat :guilabel:`Add a destination`. Ketika diklik, mereka kemudian dapat "
"mengatur :guilabel:`Destination` (user) dan kerangka waktu. Jika "
"ekstensi :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` user asli, atau nomor "
"masuk, sedang sibuk, panggilan diteruskan ke destinasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:None
msgid ""
"Manage forwarding calls to different users or phone numbers in the "
"Forwardings tab."
msgstr ""
"Kelola penerusan panggilan ke user atau nomor telepon yang berbeda di tab "
"Forwardings."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:168
msgid ""
"When the desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right corner of the page."
msgstr ""
"Setelah konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, klik :guilabel:`Save`, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Apply changes` di pojok kanan atas halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:172
msgid "Follow Me tab"
msgstr "Tab Follow Me"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:174
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Follow Me` option is selected, under "
"the :guilabel:`Follow Me` tab of the :guilabel:`New user` form, "
"no :menuselection:`Forwardings` can be made."
msgstr ""
"Ketika opsi :guilabel:`Follow Me` dipilih, di bawah tab :guilabel:`Follow "
"Me` dari formulir :guilabel:`New user`, tidak "
"ada :menuselection:`Forwardings` yang dapat dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:177
msgid ""
"Also, when the :guilabel:`Follow Me` option is selected, the :guilabel:`Add "
"a destination` button can be selected to add users, or a destination phone "
"number, to the original user's account. That way, these added numbers ring "
"when a call is received."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, ketika opsi :guilabel:`Follow Me` dipilih, tombol :guilabel:`Add "
"a destination` dapat dipilih untuk menambahkan user, atau nomor telepon "
"tujuan, ke akun user asli. Dengan cara ini, nomor-nomor yang ditambahkan "
"akan berdering saat panggilan diterima."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:181
msgid ""
"After entering the :guilabel:`Destination`, a specific time frame can be "
"made by sliding the :guilabel:`seconds bar` to the desired ring time. "
"Additional :guilabel:`Destinations` can be added with different ring times."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memasukkan :guilabel:`Destination`, kerangka waktu tertentu dapat "
"dibuat dengan menggeser :guilabel:`seconds bar` ke waktu dering yang "
"diinginkan. :guilabel:`Destinations` tambahan dapat ditambahkan dengan waktu "
"dering yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:186
msgid ""
"The original user's :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` number does "
"**not** ring with this option selected. Ring times can also be staggered, so "
"the call is forwarded to another user after the first user does not pick up "
"the call."
msgstr ""
"Nomor :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` user asli **tidak** "
"berdering saat opsi ini dipilih. Waktu dering juga dapat diatur bertahap, "
"sehingga panggilan diteruskan ke user lain setelah user pertama tidak "
"mengangkat panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:None
msgid ""
"Ring destinations like different users or phone numbers from the Follow Me "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Tujuan dering seperti user berbeda atau nomor telepon dari tab Follow Me."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:195
msgid ""
"The Odoo mobile app, or another :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)` "
"mobile client, allows for simultaneous ringing of the user's extension or "
"incoming number. For more information, visit the :doc:`VoIP Mobile "
"Integrations <../devices_integrations>` documentation."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi mobile Odoo, atau klien mobile :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation "
"Protocol)` lainnya, memungkinkan dering simultan dari ekstensi user atau "
"nomor masuk. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, kunjungi dokumentasi :doc:`VoIP "
"Mobile Integrations <../devices_integrations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:199
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:345
msgid ""
"Once all desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, klik :guilabel:`Save`, "
"lalu klik :guilabel:`Apply changes` di pojok kanan atas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:203
msgid "Keys tab"
msgstr "Tab Keys"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:205
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Keys` tab of the :guilabel:`New user` form, speed dial "
"actions for the user can be configured. Some more advanced options are "
"available, as well."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Keys` pada formulir :guilabel:`New user`, aksi "
"panggilan cepat untuk user dapat dikonfigurasi. Beberapa opsi lebih lanjut "
"juga tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:208
msgid "The following options are available to set to numerical values `1-20`."
msgstr "Opsi-opsi berikut tersedia untuk diatur ke nilai numerik `1-20`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:210
msgid "These actions can be set on each number:"
msgstr "Aksi-aksi ini dapat diatur pada setiap nomor:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:212
msgid ":guilabel:`Not configured`: the default action, which is nothing."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Not configured`: aksi default, yaitu tidak melakukan apa-apa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:213
msgid ""
":guilabel:`BLF (Busy lamp fields)`: this action shows the status of other "
"users' phones connected to the Axivox phone system. This is primarily used "
"on a desk-phone."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`BLF (Busy lamp fields)`: aksi ini menampilkan status telepon user "
"lain yang terhubung ke sistem telepon Axivox. Ini terutama digunakan pada "
"telepon meja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:215
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quick Call`: this action allows for a speed-dial of an external "
"number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Quick Call`: aksi ini memungkinkan panggilan cepat ke nomor "
"eksternal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:216
msgid ":guilabel:`Line`: this action allows the user to call another user."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Line`: aksi ini memungkinkan user menelepon user lain."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:217
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Switch`: this action allows the user to switch between calls from "
"a desk-phone."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Switch`: aksi ini memungkinkan user beralih antar panggilan dari "
"telepon meja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:218
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pickup`: this action allows the user to pick up an incoming call "
"from a desk-phone."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pickup`: aksi ini memungkinkan user mengangkat panggilan masuk "
"dari telepon meja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:None
msgid ""
"Manage user page with Keys tab highlighted and number 2 key drop-down menu "
"selected (with\n"
"highlight)"
msgstr ""
"Halaman kelola user dengan tab Keys disorot dan menu drop-down kunci nomor 2 "
"dipilih (dengan sorotan)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:225
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:313
msgid ""
"Once all the desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save`, "
"then click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua konfigurasi yang diinginkan selesai, klik :guilabel:`Save`, "
"lalu klik :guilabel:`Apply changes` di pojok kanan atas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:229
msgid ""
"Many of the preceding options have secondary options available, as well, "
"that can be used to link a user, or external phone number. These **must** be "
"filled out in conjunction with the initial action."
msgstr ""
"Banyak dari opsi sebelumnya juga memiliki opsi sekunder yang tersedia, yang "
"dapat digunakan untuk menghubungkan user, atau nomor telepon eksternal. Ini "
"**harus** diisi bersamaan dengan aksi awal."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:234
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Number of keys` field can be changed by entering in the "
"desired numerical value in the :guilabel:`Number of keys` field, located at "
"the top of the :guilabel:`Keys` tab of the :guilabel:`New user` form."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Number of keys` dapat diubah dengan memasukkan nilai "
"numerik yang diinginkan di bidang :guilabel:`Number of keys`, yang terletak "
"di bagian atas tab :guilabel:`Keys` pada formulir :guilabel:`New user`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:239
msgid "SIP Identifiers tab"
msgstr "Tab Pengidentifikasi SIP"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:241
msgid ""
"*SIP*, which stands for Session Initiation Protocol telephony, allows one to "
"make and receive calls through an internet connection. The :guilabel:`SIP "
"Identifiers` tab on the :guilabel:`New user` form, contains credentials "
"needed to configure Axivox users in Odoo and/or a different :abbr:`SIP "
"(Session Initiation Protocol)` mobile client."
msgstr ""
"*SIP*, yang merupakan singkatan dari Session Initiation Protocol telephony, "
"memungkinkan seseorang untuk melakukan dan menerima panggilan melalui "
"koneksi internet. Tab :guilabel:`Pengidentifikasi SIP` pada "
"formulir :guilabel:`User baru`, berisi kredensial yang diperlukan untuk "
"mengonfigurasi user Axivox di Odoo dan/atau klien seluler :abbr:`SIP "
"(Session Initiation Protocol)` yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:247
msgid "See the documentation on configuring Axivox, using the SIP identifiers:"
msgstr ""
"Lihat dokumentasi tentang mengonfigurasi Axivox, menggunakan "
"pengidentifikasi SIP:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:249
msgid ":doc:`Use VoIP services in Odoo with Axivox <axivox_config>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Gunakan layanan VoIP di Odoo dengan Axivox <axivox_config>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:250
msgid ":doc:`Axivox Mobile Integrations <../devices_integrations>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Integrasi Seluler Axivox <../devices_integrations>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:252
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`SIP Identifiers` tab, the :guilabel:`SIP username` "
"field represents the user's information that was entered in "
"the :guilabel:`Extension` field, under the :guilabel:`General` tab."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah tab :guilabel:`Pengidentifikasi SIP`, bidang :guilabel:`Nama "
"pengguna SIP` mewakili informasi user yang dimasukkan di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Ekstensi`, di bawah tab :guilabel:`Umum`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:255
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Domain` field is assigned to the company by the Axivox "
"representative."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Domain` ditetapkan ke perusahaan oleh perwakilan Axivox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:257
msgid ""
"The value in the :guilabel:`SIP Password` field is unique for every Axivox "
"user. This value is used to sign into Axivox on Odoo, and for any "
"mobile :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)` clients."
msgstr ""
"Nilai di bidang :guilabel:`Kata Sandi SIP` adalah unik untuk setiap user "
"Axivox. Nilai ini digunakan untuk sign in ke Axivox di Odoo, dan untuk klien "
"seluler :abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)` apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:None
msgid "Important credentials used for external configurations of Axivox VoIP."
msgstr ""
"Kredensial penting yang digunakan untuk konfigurasi eksternal Axivox VoIP."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:264
msgid ""
"The value listed in the :guilabel:`Address of the proxy server` field is "
"typically: `pabx.axivox.com`, but is subject to change by Axivox, so be sure "
"to check the :guilabel:`SIP Identifiers` tab for the most accurate value."
msgstr ""
"Nilai yang tercantum di bidang :guilabel:`Alamat server proxy` biasanya: "
"`pabx.axivox.com`, tetapi dapat berubah oleh Axivox, jadi pastikan untuk "
"memeriksa tab :guilabel:`Pengidentifikasi SIP` untuk nilai yang paling "
"akurat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:268
msgid ""
"Once all desired configurations have been made, click :guilabel:`Save`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Apply changes` in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua konfigurasi yang diinginkan telah dibuat, "
"klik :guilabel:`Simpan`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Terapkan perubahan` di sudut "
"kanan atas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/manage_users.rst:272
msgid "Permissions tab"
msgstr "Tab Izin"

