msgstr ""
"Masukkan nomor telepon yang akan dipanggil dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"keyboard-o` :guilabel:`(keyboard)`, lalu masukkan nomor telepon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:99
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon to redial the last "
"called contact."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)` untuk memanggil ulang "
"kontak terakhir yang dipanggil."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:100
msgid ""
"Search for a specific contact's name or go to the :guilabel:`Contacts` tab. "
"Then, select the contact and click the :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` "
"icon."
msgstr ""
"Cari nama kontak tertentu atau buka tab :guilabel:`Kontak`. Kemudian, pilih "
"kontak dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:103
msgid ""
"When receiving calls in Odoo, the **Phone** widget rings, and displays a "
"notification. To close the widget, click the :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(close)` icon in the upper-right of the widget screen."
msgstr ""
"Saat menerima panggilan di Odoo, widget **Telepon** berdering dan "
"menampilkan notifikasi. Untuk menutup widget, klik ikon :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(tutup)` di pojok kanan atas layar widget."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:107
msgid ""
"The |VOIP| number is the one provided by Axivox. It can be accessed by "
"navigating to `https://manage.axivox.com/ <https://manage.axivox.com/>`_. "
"After logging into the portal, go to :menuselection:`Users --> Outgoing "
"number` (column)."
msgstr ""
"Nomor |VOIP| adalah nomor yang disediakan oleh Axivox. Nomor ini dapat "
"diakses dengan membuka `https://manage.axivox.com/ <https://"
"manage.axivox.com/>`_. Setelah masuk ke portal, buka :menuselection:`User --"
"> Nomor keluar` (kolom)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:112
msgid "Transfer a phone call"
msgstr "Transfer panggilan telepon"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:114
msgid ""
"Manually transferring a call only happens when on a call. To transfer a call "
"within the *Phone* widget, first, answer the call using the green :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Transfer panggilan secara manual hanya terjadi saat sedang dalam panggilan. "
"Untuk mentransfer panggilan dalam widget *Telepon*, pertama, jawab panggilan "
"menggunakan ikon :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)` hijau."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:117
msgid ""
"Once the incoming call is answered, click the :icon:`fa-arrows-"
"h` :guilabel:`(left-right arrows)` icon. Then, enter the extension of the "
"user the call should be forwarded to. Finally, click :guilabel:`Transfer` to "
"route the call to that phone number."
msgstr ""
"Setelah panggilan masuk dijawab, klik ikon :icon:`fa-arrows-"
"h` :guilabel:`(panah kiri-kanan)`. Kemudian, masukkan ekstensi user yang "
"akan menerima panggilan yang diteruskan. Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Transfer` "
"untuk merutekan panggilan ke nomor telepon tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:122
msgid ""
"To find the extension for a user, consult the **Phone** administrator. If "
"the user has :guilabel:`Administration` access rights set "
"to :guilabel:`Settings`, find extensions by going "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app` and click the :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Manage Users` button. Select the user, and go to "
"the :guilabel:`VoIP` tab. That user's extension is their :guilabel:`VoIP "
"username`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menemukan ekstensi untuk user, konsultasikan dengan administrator "
"**Telepon**. Jika user memiliki hak akses :guilabel:`Administrasi` yang "
"disetel ke :guilabel:`Pengaturan`, temukan ekstensi dengan "
"membuka :menuselection:`aplikasi Pengaturan` dan klik tombol :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Kelola User`. Pilih user, dan buka tab :guilabel:`VoIP`. "
"Ekstensi user tersebut adalah :guilabel:`Nama user VoIP` mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:128
msgid ""
"If the user does not pick up the call or is busy with another call, then "
"calls can be automatically transferred. This gets configured with the |VOIP| "
"service provider."
msgstr ""
"Jika user tidak mengangkat panggilan atau sedang sibuk dengan panggilan "
"lain, maka panggilan dapat diteruskan secara otomatis. Hal ini dikonfigurasi "
"dengan penyedia layanan |VOIP|."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:132
msgid "Forward a phone call"
msgstr "Teruskan panggilan telepon"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:134
msgid ""
"To forward a call within the |VOIP| widget, first, answer the call using the "
"green :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Untuk meneruskan panggilan dalam widget |VOIP|, pertama, jawab panggilan "
"menggunakan ikon :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)` hijau."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:137
msgid ""
"Then, click the :icon:`fa-arrows-h` :guilabel:`(left-right arrows)` icon. "
"Enter the full phone number of the user the call should be forwarded to. "
"Finally, click :guilabel:`Transfer` to route the call to that phone number."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, klik ikon :icon:`fa-arrows-h` :guilabel:`(panah kiri-kanan)`. "
"Masukkan nomor telepon lengkap user yang akan menerima panggilan yang "
"diteruskan. Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Transfer` untuk merutekan panggilan ke "
"nomor telepon tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:142
msgid "Send an email through the Phone widget"
msgstr "Kirim email melalui widget Telepon"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:144
msgid ""
"Emails can also be sent through the **Phone** widget. This is helpful for "
"sending follow-up emails to the call participants, emailing a question to a "
"coworker, or reminding a vendor to send over some components during a check-"
"in call."
msgstr ""
"Email juga dapat dikirim melalui widget **Telepon**. Ini berguna untuk "
"mengirim email tindak lanjut kepada peserta panggilan, mengirim pertanyaan "
"melalui email kepada rekan kerja, atau mengingatkan vendor untuk mengirimkan "
"beberapa komponen selama panggilan check-in."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:148
msgid ""
"To send an email through the **Phone** widget, click the :icon:`oi-"
"voip` :guilabel:`(Show Softphone)` icon, located in the top navigation bar. "
"When this is clicked, the **Phone** widget will appear in the bottom-left "
"corner of the page. Then, search for a contact to email or find them in "
"the :guilabel:`Contacts` tab of the **Phone** widget."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim email melalui widget **Telepon**, klik ikon :icon:`oi-"
"voip` :guilabel:`Tampilkan Softphone`, yang terletak di bilah navigasi atas. "
"Ketika diklik, widget **Telepon** akan muncul di sudut kiri bawah halaman. "
"Kemudian, cari kontak untuk diemail atau temukan mereka di "
"tab :guilabel:`Kontak` pada widget **Telepon**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:153
msgid ""
"Next, click the :icon:`fa-envelope-o` :guilabel:`(envelope)` icon, and then "
"select the email recipients, enter the email's subject line, and write the "
"email. When it is ready to be sent, click :guilabel:`Send`. To schedule an "
"email to send later, click the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` "
"icon next to :guilabel:`Send`, click :guilabel:`Send Later`, pick the "
"scheduled time, and click :guilabel:`Schedule`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik ikon :icon:`fa-envelope-o` :guilabel:`(amplop)`, lalu "
"pilih penerima email, masukkan baris subjek email, dan tulis email. Ketika "
"sudah siap dikirim, klik :guilabel:`Send`. Untuk menjadwalkan pengiriman "
"email nanti, klik ikon :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` di "
"samping :guilabel:`Send`, klik :guilabel:`Send Later`, pilih waktu yang "
"dijadwalkan, dan klik :guilabel:`Schedule`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:164
msgid ""
"Each section below goes through common issues with the **Phone** widget and "
"how to resolve them."
msgstr ""
"Setiap bagian di bawah ini membahas masalah umum dengan widget **Telepon** "
"dan cara mengatasinya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:167
msgid "Missing parameter"
msgstr "Parameter hilang"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:169
msgid ""
"If a *Missing Parameter* error message appears in the **Phone** widget, "
"refresh the window, and try again."
msgstr ""
"Jika pesan error *Parameter Hilang* muncul di widget **Telepon**, muat ulang "
"jendela, dan coba lagi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:175
msgid ""
"If an *Incorrect Number* error message appears in the **Phone** widget, make "
"sure to use the international format, leading with the :icon:`fa-"
"plus` :guilabel:`(plus)`, followed by the international country code (e.g., "
"+16506913277, where `+1` is the international prefix for the United States.)"
msgstr ""
"Jika pesan error *Nomor Salah* muncul di widget **Telepon**, pastikan untuk "
"menggunakan format internasional, diawali dengan :icon:`fa-"
"plus` :guilabel:`(plus)`, diikuti dengan kode negara internasional "
"(misalnya, +16506913277, di mana `+1` adalah awalan internasional untuk "
"Amerika Serikat)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:182
msgid "The websocket connection with the server has been lost"
msgstr "Koneksi websocket dengan server telah terputus"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:184
msgid ""
"If a *The websocket connection with the server has been lost. Please try to "
"refresh the page.* error message appears in the **Phone** widget, then "
"refresh the page close other browser tabs."
msgstr ""
"Jika pesan error *Koneksi websocket dengan server telah terputus. Silakan "
"coba muat ulang halaman.* muncul di widget **Telepon**, muat ulang halaman "
"dan tutup tab browser lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:187
msgid ""
"This error is caused by returning to the database after a period of "
"inactivity, like lunch, or if there are too many browser tabs open."
msgstr ""
"Error ini disebabkan oleh kembali ke database setelah periode tidak aktif, "
"seperti makan siang, atau jika terlalu banyak tab browser yang terbuka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:191
msgid "Failed to start the user agent"
msgstr "Gagal memulai agen user"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:193
msgid ""
"If a *Failed to start the user agent. The URL of the websocket may be wrong. "
"Please have an administrator verify the websocket server URL in the General "
"Settings.* error message appears in the *Phone* widget, then update the "
"browser and computer."
msgstr ""
"Jika pesan error *Gagal memulai user agent. URL websocket mungkin salah. "
"Silakan minta administrator untuk memverifikasi URL server websocket di "
"Pengaturan Umum.* muncul di widget *Telepon*, perbarui browser dan komputer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:197
msgid ""
"This error is caused by the browser or computer not being up-to-date (and "
"can also cause issues with the microphone)."
msgstr ""
"Error ini disebabkan oleh browser atau komputer yang tidak mutakhir (dan "
"juga dapat menyebabkan masalah dengan mikrofon)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:201
msgid "Grayed-out Phone widget"
msgstr "Widget Telepon berwarna abu-abu"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:203
msgid ""
"If the **Phone** widget is completely grayed out and cannot be interacted "
"with, then update the browser and computer, and delete the Google Chrome "
"extension causing the problem."
msgstr ""
"Jika widget **Telepon** sepenuhnya berwarna abu-abu dan tidak dapat "
"berinteraksi, perbarui browser dan komputer, dan hapus ekstensi Google "
"Chrome yang menyebabkan masalah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:207
msgid "Cannot connect to the VoIP phone number"
msgstr "Tidak dapat terhubung ke nomor telepon VoIP"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:209
msgid ""
"If the user cannot connect to their |VOIP| phone number, then their Odoo "
"profile is missing their |VoIP| :guilabel:`Secret`. To add "
"it, :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users & Companies --> Users` select the "
"user, and click the *VoIP* tab. Under the *Credentials* section, enter the "
"user's :guilabel:`Secret`. This is the user's password to their account for "
"their |VOIP| service provider."
msgstr ""
"Jika user tidak dapat terhubung ke nomor telepon |VOIP| mereka, maka profil "
"Odoo mereka tidak memiliki |VoIP| :guilabel:`Secret`. Untuk "
"menambahkannya, :menuselection:`Aplikasi Settings --> Users & Companies --> "
"Users`, pilih user, dan klik tab *VoIP*. Di bawah bagian *Credentials*, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Secret` user. Ini adalah kata sandi user untuk akun "
"mereka pada penyedia layanan |VOIP| mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:5
msgid "Sales calls with Odoo Phone"
msgstr "Panggilan Penjualan dengan Odoo Telepon"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:7
msgid ""
"Using Odoo **Phone** increases call efficiency, reduces costs, and allows a "
"salesperson to access the Odoo database while on a call. Instead of relying "
"on a separate phone for sales calls, a salesperson can make calls directly "
"from the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan Odoo **Telepon** meningkatkan efisiensi panggilan, mengurangi "
"biaya, dan memungkinkan tenaga penjual mengakses database Odoo saat "
"melakukan panggilan. Alih-alih mengandalkan telepon terpisah untuk panggilan "
"Penjualan, tenaga penjual dapat melakukan panggilan langsung dari database "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:11
msgid ""
"This article goes over setting up Odoo **Phone** for a sales team that "
"already has the **Phone** app configured. If it is **not** configured, refer "
"to the :doc:`Phone <../phone>` documentation to get started."
msgstr ""
"Artikel ini membahas pengaturan **Telepon** Odoo untuk tim penjualan yang "
"sudah memiliki aplikasi **Telepon** yang terkonfigurasi. Jika **belum** "
"dikonfigurasi, lihat dokumentasi :doc:`Telepon <../phone>` untuk memulai."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:16
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorial: Sales calls with VoIP <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"sales-calls-with-voip-4562>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Tutorial Odoo: Panggilan penjualan dengan VoIP <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/sales-calls-with-voip-4562>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:20
msgid "Make a sales call"
msgstr "Melakukan panggilan penjualan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:22
msgid ""
"This workflow begins in the **CRM** app. As a salesperson, click into a "
"sales opportunity. If it does not already have a call activity scheduled, "
"click :guilabel:`Activities` in the opportunity's chatter, then set the "
"activity's :guilabel:`Activity Type` to :guilabel:`Call`, and then fill out "
"the rest of the activity form, and finally click :guilabel:`Schedule`."
msgstr ""
"Alur kerja ini dimulai di aplikasi **CRM**. Sebagai tenaga penjualan, klik "
"ke dalam peluang penjualan. Jika belum memiliki aktivitas panggilan yang "
"dijadwalkan, klik :guilabel:`Activities` di chatter peluang, lalu "
"atur :guilabel:`Activity Type` aktivitas menjadi :guilabel:`Call`, kemudian "
"isi sisa formulir aktivitas, dan terakhir klik :guilabel:`Schedule`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:27
msgid ""
"From here, there are three ways to begin a phone call with the customer:"
msgstr ""
"Dari sini, ada tiga cara untuk memulai panggilan telepon dengan pelanggan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:29
msgid ""
"Hover over the :guilabel:`Phone` field in the opportunity form, then "
"click :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`Call`."
msgstr ""
"Arahkan kursor ke kolom :guilabel:`Telepon` di formulir peluang, lalu "
"klik :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`Call`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:31
msgid "In the opportunity's chatter, click the customer's phone number."
msgstr "Di chatter peluang, klik nomor telepon pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:32
msgid ""
"In the upper-right corner, click the :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(VoIP)` icon "
"to open the |VOIP| widget. From the :guilabel:`Next Activities` tab, select "
"the call, and finally click the :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon "
"near the bottom of the widget."
msgstr ""
"Di sudut kanan atas, klik ikon :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(VoIP)` untuk "
"membuka widget |VOIP|. Dari tab :guilabel:`Next Activities`, pilih "
"panggilan, dan terakhir klik ikon :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` di "
"dekat bagian bawah widget."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:66
msgid "Work during a call"
msgstr "Bekerja selama panggilan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:39
msgid ""
"Once the call with the customer begins, the salesperson can still move about "
"the Odoo database. Also, there are shortcut icons in the *Phone* widget that "
"the salesperson can use to access common actions, like sending an email to "
"the customer, or pulling up their profile. Learn more about :doc:`the "
"documents a salesperson can access <phone_widget>` during a call."
msgstr ""
"Setelah panggilan dengan pelanggan dimulai, tenaga penjual masih dapat "
"berpindah di database Odoo. Selain itu, terdapat ikon pintasan di widget "
"*Telepon* yang dapat digunakan tenaga penjual untuk mengakses tindakan umum, "
"seperti mengirim email ke pelanggan atau membuka profil mereka. Pelajari "
"lebih lanjut tentang :doc:`dokumen yang dapat diakses tenaga penjual "
"<phone_widget>` selama panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:44
msgid "The salesperson can also take some actions during the call:"
msgstr ""
"Tenaga penjualan juga dapat melakukan beberapa tindakan selama panggilan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:46
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:75
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-arrows-h` :guilabel:`(transfer)`: Transfer a call to another team "
"member."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-arrows-h` :guilabel:`(transfer)`: Transfer panggilan ke anggota "
"tim lain."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:47
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`(microphone)`: The salesperson can mute "
"themselves during a call."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`(microphone)`: Salesperson dapat membisukan "
"diri mereka sendiri selama panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:48
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:78
msgid ":icon:`fa-pause` :guilabel:`(pause)`: Place the caller on hold."
msgstr ":icon:`fa-pause` :guilabel:`(pause)`: Menahan penelepon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:None
msgid ""
"The *Phone* widget opened to a call, showing the shortcut icons a "
"salesperson has access\n"
"to."
msgstr ""
"Widget *Telepon* terbuka untuk panggilan, menampilkan ikon pintasan yang "
"dapat diakses\n"
"tenaga penjual."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:55
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:81
msgid "Handle call follow-ups"
msgstr "Menangani tindak lanjut panggilan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:57
msgid ""
"The *Phone* widget can handle some common follow-up tasks, but salespeople "
"can still navigate Odoo for tasks not available in the widget."
msgstr ""
"Widget *Telepon* dapat menangani beberapa tugas tindak lanjut umum, tetapi "
"tenaga penjual masih dapat menavigasi Odoo untuk tugas yang tidak tersedia "
"di widget."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:86
msgid ""
"Here are some of the common follow-up tasks that can be managed from the "
"*Phone* widget:"
msgstr ""
"Berikut adalah beberapa tugas tindak lanjut umum yang dapat dikelola dari "
"widget *Telepon*:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:62
msgid ""
"Send a follow-up email sharing new product offerings to the customer using "
"the :icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(envelope)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Kirim email tindak lanjut yang membagikan penawaran produk baru kepada "
"pelanggan menggunakan ikon :icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(envelope)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:64
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:90
msgid ""
"Update the customer's mailing address by clicking on the :icon:`fa-"
"user` :guilabel:`(user)` icon, which opens their profile."
msgstr ""
"Perbarui alamat surat pelanggan dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"user` :guilabel:`(user)`, yang membuka profil mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:66
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:92
msgid ""
"Schedule a second call with the customer by clicking the :icon:`fa-clock-"
"o` :guilabel:`(clock)` icon, setting the :guilabel:`Activity Type` field "
"to :guilabel:`Call`, and then filling out the rest of the form."
msgstr ""
"Jadwalkan panggilan kedua dengan pelanggan dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"clock-o` :guilabel:`(clock)`, mengatur bidang :guilabel:`Activity Type` "
"ke :guilabel:`Call`, lalu mengisi sisa formulir."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:71
msgid "Send a quotation while on a call"
msgstr "Mengirim penawaran harga saat melakukan panggilan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:73
msgid ""
"If the customer is ready to see a sales quotation while on the call, the "
"salesperson can send that quotation without leaving the call."
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan siap melihat penawaran harga penjualan saat melakukan "
"panggilan, salesperson dapat mengirim penawaran harga tersebut tanpa "
"meninggalkan panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:76
msgid ""
"To send a quotation while on a call, the salesperson should be in the sales "
"opportunity they initiated the call from. From here, they will :doc:`send "
"the quotation as they normally would <../../sales/sales/sales_quotations/"
"create_quotations>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengirim penawaran harga saat melakukan panggilan, salesperson harus "
"berada di peluang penjualan tempat mereka memulai panggilan. Dari sini, "
"mereka akan :doc:`mengirim penawaran harga seperti biasa <../../sales/sales/"
"sales_quotations/create_quotations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:80
msgid ""
"An added benefit of being on the call with the customer while the "
"salesperson is sending the quotation is that any specific questions are "
"answered in real-time."
msgstr ""
"Manfaat tambahan dari melakukan panggilan dengan pelanggan saat salesperson "
"mengirim penawaran harga adalah pertanyaan spesifik apa pun dijawab secara "
"real-time."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:84
msgid "End the sales call"
msgstr "Mengakhiri panggilan penjualan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:86
msgid ""
"When it is time to end the call, the salesperson clicks the red :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon in the lower-right corner of the *Phone* "
"widget. When they do, the call is logged in the opportunity's chatter."
msgstr ""
"Ketika saatnya mengakhiri panggilan, tenaga penjual mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)` merah di pojok kanan bawah widget *Telepon*. "
"Ketika mereka melakukannya, panggilan dicatat di chatter peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/sales_calls.rst:90
msgid ""
"If they have not done so already, the salesperson then marks the phone call "
"activity as done. To do so, navigate to the opportunity's chatter and find "
"the :guilabel:`Planned Activities` section, then click :icon:`fa-"
"check` :guilabel:`Mark Done` on the planned call to remove it from "
"the :guilabel:`Next Activities` tab in the *Phone* widget."
msgstr ""
"Jika mereka belum melakukannya, salesperson kemudian menandai aktivitas "
"panggilan telepon sebagai selesai. Untuk melakukannya, navigasi ke chatter "
"dari opportunity dan temukan bagian :guilabel:`Aktivitas Terencana`, lalu "
"klik :icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Tandai Selesai` pada panggilan yang "
"direncanakan untuk menghapusnya dari tab :guilabel:`Aktivitas Berikutnya` di "
"widget *Telepon*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:5
msgid "Support calls with Odoo Phone"
msgstr "Panggilan dukungan dengan Odoo Telepon"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:7
msgid ""
"A useful tool for support teams, Odoo **Phone** is used as a way to get in "
"contact with customers who need some help. Using the **Phone** app can help "
"improve customer satisfaction, reduce support costs, and allows support "
"agents to navigate an Odoo database while on a call."
msgstr ""
"Alat yang berguna untuk tim dukungan, Odoo **Telepon** digunakan sebagai "
"cara untuk menghubungi pelanggan yang membutuhkan bantuan. Menggunakan "
"aplikasi **Telepon** dapat membantu meningkatkan kepuasan pelanggan, "
"mengurangi biaya dukungan, dan memungkinkan agen dukungan untuk menavigasi "
"database Odoo saat sedang melakukan panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:11
msgid ""
"Instead of being tied to their desks, support agents can take calls from "
"anywhere they have access to the Odoo :doc:`Phone <../phone>` app."
msgstr ""
"Alih-alih terikat di meja mereka, agen dukungan dapat menerima panggilan "
"dari mana saja selama mereka memiliki akses ke aplikasi :doc:`Telepon <../"
"phone>` Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:15
msgid ""
"This feature requires at least one :doc:`call queue <axivox/call_queues>` to "
"be configured."
msgstr ""
"Fitur ini memerlukan setidaknya satu :doc:`call queue <axivox/call_queues>` "
"yang dikonfigurasi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:18
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorial: Working as a Support Agent <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/working-as-a-support-agent-odoo-voip-4617>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Tutorial Odoo: Bekerja sebagai Agen Dukungan <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/working-as-a-support-agent-odoo-voip-4617>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:22
msgid "Log into a support queue"
msgstr "Masuk ke antrian dukungan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:24
msgid ""
"If :doc:`call queues <axivox/call_queues>` are set up, begin a support shift "
"by logging into a call queue."
msgstr ""
"Jika :doc:`call queues <axivox/call_queues>` telah diatur, mulai shift "
"dukungan dengan masuk ke call queue."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:27
msgid ""
"Begin by clicking :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Show Softphone)` in the top-"
"right corner of the Odoo database. From there, click :icon:`fa-keyboard-"
"o` :guilabel:`(keyboard)`, then dial the *agent connection* number and "
"click :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)`."
msgstr ""
"Mulai dengan mengklik :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Tampilkan Softphone)` di "
"pojok kanan atas database Odoo. Dari sana, klik :icon:`fa-keyboard-"
"o` :guilabel:`(keyboard)`, lalu hubungi nomor *koneksi agen* dan "
"klik :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:31
msgid ""
"Once the support agent calls their *agent connection code*, they'll hear a "
"short message letting them know they are logged into the queue. From here, "
"the agent receives support calls according to the administrator's :doc:`call "
"queue strategy <axivox/call_queues>`. When a support agent receives a call, "
"the *Phone* widget appears in the bottom-right corner of their screen with "
"the caller's phone number, as well as their name if the number is tied to a "
"customer profile."
msgstr ""
"Setelah agen dukungan memanggil *kode koneksi agen* mereka, mereka akan "
"mendengar pesan singkat yang memberi tahu bahwa mereka masuk ke dalam "
"antrian. Dari sini, agen menerima panggilan dukungan sesuai "
"dengan :doc:`strategi antrian panggilan <axivox/call_queues>` administrator. "
"Ketika agen dukungan menerima panggilan, widget *Telepon* muncul di pojok "
"kanan bawah layar mereka dengan nomor telepon penelepon, serta nama mereka "
"jika nomor tersebut terhubung dengan profil pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:38
msgid ""
"When support staff are added as :doc:`static agents <axivox/call_queues>` to "
"a call queue, they do not need to log into the queue to receive calls from "
"that queue."
msgstr ""
"Ketika staf dukungan ditambahkan sebagai :doc:`static agents <axivox/"
"call_queues>` ke call queue, mereka tidak perlu masuk ke antrian untuk "
"menerima panggilan dari antrian tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:42
msgid "Call a customer from a support ticket"
msgstr "Menghubungi pelanggan dari tiket dukungan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:44
msgid ""
"As part of a support agent's daily tasks, they might be asked to call "
"customers with open support tickets. With Odoo **Phone**, the support agent "
"can stay in the Odoo database throughout the entire workflow."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai bagian dari tugas harian agen dukungan, mereka mungkin diminta untuk "
"menelepon pelanggan dengan tiket dukungan yang terbuka. Dengan Odoo "
"**Telepon**, agen dukungan dapat tetap berada di database Odoo sepanjang "
"keseluruhan alur kerja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:48
msgid ""
"From the database's home page, click the **Helpdesk** app, click into a "
"helpdesk, and then open a ticket. If the ticket does not already have a call "
"activity scheduled, click :guilabel:`Activities` in the ticket's chatter, "
"then set the activity's :guilabel:`Activity Type` to :guilabel:`Call`, and "
"then fill out the rest of the activity form, and finally "
"click :guilabel:`Schedule`."
msgstr ""
"Dari halaman beranda database, klik aplikasi **Pusat Bantuan**, klik ke "
"dalam helpdesk, lalu buka tiket. Jika tiket belum memiliki aktivitas "
"panggilan yang dijadwalkan, klik :guilabel:`Activities` di chatter tiket, "
"lalu atur :guilabel:`Activity Type` aktivitas ke :guilabel:`Call`, lalu isi "
"sisa formulir aktivitas, dan terakhir klik :guilabel:`Schedule`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:None
msgid "Scheduling a call activity for a support ticket."
msgstr "Menjadwalkan aktivitas panggilan untuk tiket dukungan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:56
msgid "From here, the agent has three ways to make a call:"
msgstr "Dari sini, agen memiliki tiga cara untuk melakukan panggilan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:58
msgid ""
"Hover over the :guilabel:`Phone` field in the ticket, then click :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`Call`."
msgstr ""
"Arahkan kursor ke bidang :guilabel:`Telepon` di tiket, lalu klik :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`Panggil`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:60
msgid "In the ticket's chatter, click the customer's phone number."
msgstr "Di chatter tiket, klik nomor telepon pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:61
msgid ""
"In the upper-right corner, click the :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Show "
"Softphone)` icon to open the *Phone* widget. From the :guilabel:`Activities` "
"tab, select the call, and finally click the :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon near the bottom of the widget."
msgstr ""
"Di pojok kanan atas, klik ikon :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Tampilkan "
"Softphone)` untuk membuka widget *Telepon*. Dari tab :guilabel:`Aktivitas`, "
"pilih panggilan, dan terakhir klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)` di dekat bagian bawah widget."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:68
msgid ""
"Once the call with the customer begins, the support agent can still move "
"about the Odoo database. Also, there are shortcut icons in the *Phone* "
"widget that the support agent can use to access common actions, like sending "
"an email to the customer, or pulling up their profile. Learn more "
"about :doc:`the documents a support agent can access <phone_widget>` during "
"a call."
msgstr ""
"Setelah panggilan dengan pelanggan dimulai, agen dukungan masih dapat "
"berpindah di database Odoo. Selain itu, terdapat ikon pintasan di widget "
"*Telepon* yang dapat digunakan agen dukungan untuk mengakses tindakan umum, "
"seperti mengirim email ke pelanggan atau membuka profil mereka. Pelajari "
"lebih lanjut tentang :doc:`dokumen yang dapat diakses agen dukungan "
"<phone_widget>` selama panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:73
msgid "The support agent can also take some actions during the call:"
msgstr "Agen dukungan juga dapat melakukan beberapa tindakan selama panggilan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:76
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`(microphone)`: The support agent can mute "
"themselves during a call."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`(mikrofon)`: Agen dukungan dapat "
"menonaktifkan suara mereka sendiri selama panggilan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:83
msgid ""
"The *Phone* widget can handle some common follow-up tasks, but support "
"agents can still navigate Odoo for tasks not available in the widget."
msgstr ""
"Widget *Telepon* dapat menangani beberapa tugas tindak lanjut umum, tetapi "
"agen dukungan masih dapat menavigasi Odoo untuk tugas yang tidak tersedia di "
"widget."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:88
msgid ""
"Send a follow-up email sharing troubleshooting steps with the customer using "
"the :icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(envelope)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Kirim email tindak lanjut yang membagikan langkah-langkah pemecahan masalah "
"kepada pelanggan menggunakan ikon :icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(amplop)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:97
msgid "End the support call"
msgstr "Akhiri panggilan dukungan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:99
msgid ""
"When it is time to end the call, the support agent clicks the red :icon:`fa-"
"phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon in the lower-right corner of the *Phone* "
"widget. When they do, the call is logged in the ticket's chatter."
msgstr ""
"Ketika tiba waktunya untuk mengakhiri panggilan, agen dukungan mengklik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telepon)` berwarna merah di pojok kanan "
"bawah widget *Telepon*. Ketika mereka melakukannya, panggilan dicatat di "
"chatter tiket."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:103
msgid ""
"If they have not done so already, the support agent then marks the phone "
"call activity as done. To do so, navigate to the ticket's chatter and find "
"the :guilabel:`Planned Activities` section, then click :icon:`fa-"
"check` :guilabel:`Mark Done` on the planned call to remove it from "
"the :guilabel:`Next Activities` tab in the *Phone* widget."
msgstr ""
"Jika mereka belum melakukannya, agen dukungan kemudian menandai aktivitas "
"panggilan telepon sebagai selesai. Untuk melakukannya, navigasi ke chatter "
"tiket dan temukan bagian :guilabel:`Aktivitas Terencana`, lalu "
"klik :icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Tandai Selesai` pada panggilan yang "
"direncanakan untuk menghapusnya dari tab :guilabel:`Aktivitas Berikutnya` di "
"widget *Telepon*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:109
msgid "Log out of a support queue"
msgstr "Keluar dari antrean dukungan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:111
msgid ""
"Once the agent's shift ends, or if they are taking a break, they can log out "
"of the support call queue."
msgstr ""
"Setelah shift agen berakhir, atau jika mereka sedang istirahat, mereka dapat "
"keluar dari antrean panggilan dukungan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:114
msgid ""
"Begin by clicking :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Show Softphone)` in the top-"
"right corner of the Odoo database. From there, click :icon:`fa-keyboard-"
"o` :guilabel:`(keyboard)`, then dial the *agent disconnection* number and "
"click :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`phone`."
msgstr ""
"Mulai dengan mengklik :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Tampilkan Softphone)` di "
"pojok kanan atas database Odoo. Dari sana, klik :icon:`fa-keyboard-"
"o` :guilabel:`(keyboard)`, lalu hubungi nomor *pemutusan koneksi agen* dan "
"klik :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`telepon`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/support_calls.rst:118
msgid ""
"Once the support agent calls their *agent disconnection code*, they'll hear "
"a short message letting them know they are logged out of the queue. From "
"here, the agent will no longer receive support calls until they log back in."
msgstr ""
"Setelah agen dukungan menelepon *kode pemutusan agen* mereka, mereka akan "
"mendengar pesan singkat yang memberi tahu mereka bahwa mereka telah keluar "
"dari antrean. Dari sini, agen tidak akan lagi menerima panggilan dukungan "
"sampai mereka masuk kembali."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:7
msgid "Sign"
msgstr "Sign"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Odoo Sign** allows you to sign, send, and approve documents online using "
"electronic signatures."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Sign** memungkinkan Anda untuk menandatangani, mengirim, dan "
"menyetujui dokumen secara online menggunakan tanda tangan elektronik."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:20
msgid ""
"Just like a handwritten signature, an electronic signature represents a "
"person's agreement to the content of a document. Signatures generated using "
"the Sign app are considered as :doc:`valid electronic signatures <sign/"
"validity>` in the European Union and the United States of America, and meet "
"the requirements for electronic signatures in most countries."
msgstr ""
"Sama seperti tanda tangan tulisan tangan, tanda tangan elektronik "
"merepresentasikan persetujuan seseorang terhadap konten dokumen. Tanda "
"tangan yang dihasilkan menggunakan aplikasi Sign dianggap "
"sebagai :doc:`tanda tangan elektronik yang sah <sign/validity>` di Uni Eropa "
"dan Amerika Serikat, dan memenuhi persyaratan untuk tanda tangan elektronik "
"di sebagian besar negara."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:25
msgid "With Sign, you can:"
msgstr "Dengan Sign, Anda dapat:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:27
msgid ""
":ref:`prepare documents for signing <sign/request-signatures/prepare-"
"document>` by one or more signers using drag-and-drop fields"
msgstr ""
":ref:`persiapkan dokumen untuk ditandatangani <sign/request-signatures/"
"prepare-document>` oleh satu atau beberapa penandatangan menggunakan bidang "
"drag-and-drop"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:29
msgid ""
"send :ref:`one-off documents for signing <sign/request-signatures/one-off>` "
"from the Sign app or from an Odoo record"
msgstr ""
"mengirim :ref:`dokumen satu kali untuk ditandatangani <sign/request-"
"signatures/one-off>` dari aplikasi Sign atau dari record Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:31
msgid ""
"create and use :ref:`templates <sign/request-signatures/templates>` to send "
"frequently used documents for signing from the Sign app or from an Odoo "
"record"
msgstr ""
"membuat dan menggunakan :ref:`templat <sign/request-signatures/templates>` "
"untuk mengirim dokumen yang sering digunakan untuk ditandatangani dari "
"aplikasi Sign atau dari record Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:33
msgid ""
"create :ref:`document envelopes <sign/request-signatures/create-envelope>` "
"to send multiple documents in a single signature request or sign multiple "
"documents at the same time"
msgstr ""
"membuat :ref:`amplop dokumen <sign/request-signatures/create-envelope>` "
"untuk mengirim beberapa dokumen dalam satu permintaan tanda tangan atau "
"menandatangani beberapa dokumen secara bersamaan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:35
msgid ""
":ref:`sign documents that have been prepared using Odoo Sign <sign/sign-"
"document/signature-request>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`menandatangani dokumen yang telah disiapkan menggunakan Odoo Sign "
"<sign/sign-document/signature-request>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:37
msgid ""
":ref:`sign non-prepared documents <sign/sign-document/pdf-document>` from "
"the Sign app, from the chatter of an Odoo record, or from "
"the :doc:`Documents <documents>` app"
msgstr ""
":ref:`menandatangani dokumen yang tidak disiapkan <sign/sign-document/pdf-"
"document>` dari aplikasi Sign, dari chatter record Odoo, atau dari "
"aplikasi :doc:`Dokumen <documents>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:39
msgid ""
"configure :ref:`auto-complete fields <sign/configuration/auto-fill>` that "
"populate with data from your database during signing"
msgstr ""
"mengonfigurasi :ref:`bidang pengisian otomatis <sign/configuration/auto-"
"fill>` yang terisi dengan data dari database Anda selama penandatanganan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:41
msgid ""
"define :ref:`advanced configuration for signers <sign/request-signatures/"
"signer-settings>` to require authentication (via SMS, Aadhaar eSign, or "
"itsme®), allow delegation, or, for templates, assign a fixed signer"
msgstr ""
"menentukan :ref:`konfigurasi lanjutan untuk penandatangan <sign/request-"
"signatures/signer-settings>` untuk memerlukan autentikasi (melalui SMS, "
"Aadhaar eSign, atau itsme®), mengizinkan delegasi, atau, untuk template, "
"menetapkan penandatangan tetap"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:46
msgid "`Odoo Sign: product page <https://www.odoo.com/app/sign>`_"
msgstr "`Odoo Sign: halaman produk <https://www.odoo.com/app/sign>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign.rst:47
msgid "`Odoo Tutorials: Sign [video] <https://www.odoo.com/slides/sign-61>`_"
msgstr "`Tutorial Odoo: Sign [video] <https://www.odoo.com/slides/sign-61>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:8
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:10
msgid ""
"Sign's general settings, available via :menuselection:`Sign --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, allow you to:"
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan umum Sign, tersedia melalui :menuselection:`Sign --> Konfigurasi "
"--> Pengaturan`, memungkinkan Anda untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:13
msgid ""
"add :ref:`Default Terms & Conditions <sign/configuration/settings-t-and-c>` "
"to the signature request email"
msgstr ""
"menambahkan :ref:`Syarat & Ketentuan Default <sign/configuration/settings-t-"
"and-c>` ke email permintaan tanda tangan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:15
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manage template access`; once enabled, it is possible to restrict "
"access to a template to specific user groups when :ref:`creating or editing "
"the template <sign/request-signatures/templates>`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kelola akses templat`; setelah diaktifkan, dimungkinkan untuk "
"membatasi akses ke templat untuk grup user tertentu saat :ref:`membuat atau "
"mengedit templat <sign/request-signatures/templates>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:18
msgid ""
"enable the following additional authentication methods, manage the service, "
"and buy credits:"
msgstr ""
"mengaktifkan metode autentikasi tambahan berikut, mengelola layanan, dan "
"membeli kredit:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:20
msgid ""
":ref:`Aadhaar eSign <sign/security/authentication-aadhaar>` (available in "
"India)"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Aadhaar eSign <sign/security/authentication-aadhaar>` (tersedia di "
"India)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:21
msgid ""
":ref:`itsme® <sign/security/authentication-itsme>` (available in the EU, the "
"UK, Norway, and Iceland)"
msgstr ""
":ref:`itsme® <sign/security/authentication-itsme>` (tersedia di UE, Inggris, "
"Norwegia, dan Islandia)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:24
msgid ""
"manage authentication via SMS and :ref:`buy credits <in_app_purchase/"
"credits>`"
msgstr ""
"mengelola autentikasi melalui SMS dan :ref:`membeli kredit <in_app_purchase/"
"credits>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:25
msgid ""
"upload a `.p12` or `.pfx` file containing a personal digital certificate, "
"allowing you to add a :ref:`cryptographic, or digital, signature <sign/"
"security/cryptographic>` to a document"
msgstr ""
"mengunggah file `.p12` atau `.pfx` yang berisi sertifikat digital pribadi, "
"sehingga Anda dapat menambahkan :ref:`tanda tangan kriptografis, atau "
"digital <sign/security/cryptographic>` ke dokumen"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:31
msgid "Default terms and conditions"
msgstr "Syarat dan ketentuan default"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:33
msgid ""
"Terms and conditions allow a business to standardize the legal relationship "
"with its clients, define obligations and expectations, manage risk, and "
"protect its interests by setting clear rules for aspects such as liability "
"and dispute resolution."
msgstr ""
"Syarat dan ketentuan memungkinkan bisnis untuk menstandarkan hubungan hukum "
"dengan kliennya, mendefinisikan kewajiban dan harapan, mengelola risiko, dan "
"melindungi kepentingannya dengan menetapkan aturan yang jelas untuk aspek-"
"aspek seperti tanggung jawab dan penyelesaian sengketa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:37
msgid "To add default terms and conditions to signature requests:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan syarat dan ketentuan default ke permintaan tanda tangan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:39
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Sign --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"enable :guilabel:`Sign Default Terms & Conditions`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Sign --> Configuration --> Settings` dan "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Sign Default Terms & Conditions`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:42
msgid "Choose the desired option:"
msgstr "Pilih opsi yang diinginkan:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Terms in Email`: This option is selected by default and places "
"the terms and conditions at the bottom of the signature request email. Add "
"your terms and conditions to the text box."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Terms in Email`: Opsi ini dipilih secara default dan menempatkan "
"syarat dan ketentuan di bagian bawah email permintaan tanda tangan. "
"Tambahkan syarat dan ketentuan Anda ke kotak teks."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:47
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Terms as Web Page`: This option displays the terms and conditions "
"on a web page; the link to that page is then added as a link in the "
"signature request email. Click :guilabel:`Save`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Update Terms`. Add your terms and conditions to the text "
"box, then click :guilabel:`Save`. Click :guilabel:`Preview` to see how the "
"terms and conditions will be displayed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Terms as Web Page`: Opsi ini menampilkan syarat dan ketentuan "
"pada halaman web; tautan ke halaman tersebut kemudian ditambahkan sebagai "
"tautan di email permintaan tanda tangan. Klik :guilabel:`Save`, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Update Terms`. Tambahkan syarat dan ketentuan Anda ke kotak "
"teks, lalu klik :guilabel:`Save`. Klik :guilabel:`Preview` untuk melihat "
"bagaimana syarat dan ketentuan akan ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:54
msgid ""
"In the text box, type `/` to open the :ref:`powerbox <essentials/html_editor/"
"commands>`, then use commands to insert headings, bulleted lists, etc."
msgstr ""
"Di kotak teks, ketik `/` untuk membuka :ref:`powerbox <essentials/"
"html_editor/commands>`, lalu gunakan perintah untuk menyisipkan heading, "
"daftar berpoin, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/configuration.rst:57
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/security_authentication.rst:133
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/security_authentication.rst:166
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/security_authentication.rst:190
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/security_authentication.rst:259
