#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:75
msgid ""
"In order to create a Meta business account, the user must have a personal "
"Facebook account that has existed for a minimum of one hour prior to setting "
"up the Facebook Business account. Trying to create the business account "
"prior to this time results in an error."
