#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:761
msgid ""
"For example, in the :guilabel:`Body` tab, if the following is typed, \"Hello "
"{{1}},\", then `{{1}}` must be set in the :guilabel:`Variables` tab. For "
"this specific case, the message should greet the customer by name, so the "
"`{{1}}` should be configured to populate the `{{1}}` :guilabel:`Field` with "
"the :guilabel:`Customer` name."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, di tab :guilabel:`Body`, jika yang diketik adalah \"Hello {{1}},"
"\", maka `{{1}}` harus diatur di tab :guilabel:`Variables`. Untuk kasus "
"khusus ini, pesan harus menyapa pelanggan dengan nama, sehingga `{{1}}` "
"harus dikonfigurasi untuk mengisi :guilabel:`Field` `{{1}}` dengan "
"nama :guilabel:`Customer`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:767
msgid "Customizing WhatsApp templates is out of the scope of Odoo Support."
msgstr "Kustomisasi template WhatsApp berada di luar cakupan Dukungan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:772
msgid "Meta template approval"
msgstr "Persetujuan template Meta"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:774
msgid ""
"After updating the dynamic variables on the template, the template needs to "
"be resubmitted to Meta for approval. Click :guilabel:`Submit for Approval` "
"to start the approval process. An email is sent to the administrator of the "
"Meta account when the template has been approved."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memperbarui variabel dinamis pada template, template perlu "
"dikirimkan ulang ke Meta untuk persetujuan. Klik :guilabel:`Submit for "
"Approval` untuk memulai proses persetujuan. Email dikirim ke administrator "
"akun Meta ketika template telah disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:778
msgid ""
"Following the approval from Meta, sync the templates again in the Odoo "
"database. See this documentation: :ref:`productivity/whatsapp/sync-"
"templates`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah persetujuan dari Meta, sinkronkan template lagi di database Odoo. "
"Lihat dokumentasi ini: :ref:`productivity/whatsapp/sync-templates`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:782
msgid ""
"To see the status, go to `Meta Business Suite <https://business.facebook.com/"
"wa/manage/home>`__ and select :menuselection:`Account tools --> Message "
"templates`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat status, buka `Meta Business Suite <https://"
"business.facebook.com/wa/manage/home>`__ dan pilih :menuselection:`Account "
"tools --> Message templates`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:788
msgid "Syncing templates"
msgstr "Sinkronisasi template"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:790
msgid ""
"Templates must be synced on the Odoo database once they are approved by the "
"Meta team. To do so, begin by navigating to :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> "
"Configuration --> WhatsApp Business Accounts` and select the configuration "
"that should be synced. Under the section marked :menuselection:`Sending "
"messages`, towards the bottom, click :guilabel:`Sync Templates`. Meta "
"updates the templates that are approved so that they can be utilized with "
"various apps in the database."
msgstr ""
"Template harus disinkronkan pada database Odoo setelah disetujui oleh tim "
"Meta. Untuk melakukannya, mulai dengan menavigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> Configuration --> WhatsApp Business "
"Accounts` dan pilih konfigurasi yang harus disinkronkan. Di bawah bagian "
"yang ditandai :menuselection:`Sending messages`, di bagian bawah, "
"klik :guilabel:`Sync Templates`. Meta memperbarui template yang disetujui "
"sehingga dapat digunakan dengan berbagai aplikasi dalam database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid ""
"Syncing Meta WhatsApp templates to the Odoo database, with the 'Sync "
"Templates'\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Sinkronisasi template WhatsApp Meta ke database Odoo, dengan 'Sync "
"Templates' disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:801
msgid ""
"A successful message in green appears in the upper-right corner with the "
"number of templates updated."
msgstr ""
"Pesan sukses berwarna hijau muncul di sudut kanan atas dengan jumlah "
"template yang diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:805
msgid ""
"Templates can also be synced individually from the template itself. Navigate "
"to the :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> Templates` dashboard and select the "
"template to sync. Then, click the :guilabel:`Sync Template` button located "
"in the top menu of the template's form."
msgstr ""
"Template juga dapat disinkronkan secara individual dari template itu "
"sendiri. Navigasi ke dashboard :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> Templates` "
"dan pilih template untuk disinkronkan. Kemudian, klik tombol :guilabel:`Sync "
"Template` yang terletak di menu atas formulir template."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:812
msgid "Create WhatsApp templates in Meta"
msgstr "Membuat template WhatsApp di Meta"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:814
msgid ""
"First, navigate to `Meta Business Suite <https://business.facebook.com/wa/"
"manage/home>`__, and then go to :menuselection:`Account tools --> Message "
"templates`."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, navigasi ke `Meta Business Suite <https://business.facebook.com/wa/"
"manage/home>`__, kemudian buka :menuselection:`Account tools --> Message "
"templates`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid ""
"Account tools highlighted in business manager with the manage templates link "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Alat akun disorot di business manager dengan link kelola template disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:820
msgid ""
"To create a WhatsApp template, click the blue :guilabel:`Create template` "
"button, and then select the :guilabel:`Category` from one of the following:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat template WhatsApp, klik tombol biru :guilabel:`Create "
"template`, kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Category` dari salah satu berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:829
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Name` of the template and then select "
"the :guilabel:`Language` for the template."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan :guilabel:`Name` template, lalu pilih :guilabel:`Language` untuk "
"template tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:833
msgid ""
"Multiple languages can be selected by typing the language names, then "
"selecting the other languages as needed."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa bahasa dapat dipilih dengan mengetik nama bahasa, kemudian memilih "
"bahasa lain sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid ""
"Template configuration options listed, with Marketing, Utility, Name and "
"Language\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Opsi konfigurasi template yang terdaftar, dengan Marketing, Utility, Name, "
"dan Language disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:840
msgid ""
"After making the appropriate selections, click :guilabel:`Continue` in the "
"top-right corner. The browser redirects to the :guilabel:`Edit template` "
"page where the :guilabel:`Header`, :guilabel:`Body`, :guilabel:`Footer`, "
"and :guilabel:`Buttons` are configured. To the right of the template is a "
"preview of what the template looks like in production."
msgstr ""
"Setelah membuat pilihan yang sesuai, klik :guilabel:`Continue` di sudut "
"kanan atas. Browser mengarahkan ulang ke halaman :guilabel:`Edit template` "
"di mana :guilabel:`Header`, :guilabel:`Body`, :guilabel:`Footer`, "
"dan :guilabel:`Buttons` dikonfigurasi. Di sebelah kanan template terdapat "
"pratinjau tentang tampilan template dalam produksi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid "Edit the template using a header, body, footer and buttons."
msgstr "Edit template menggunakan header, body, footer, dan tombol."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:848
msgid ""
"When all necessary changes are made to the template, "
"click :guilabel:`Submit` button in the top-right corner, and a window "
"populates to confirm the language. Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to approve and "
"then another window states that the template has been submitted to Meta for "
"review and approval."
msgstr ""
"Ketika semua perubahan yang diperlukan dibuat pada template, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Submit` di sudut kanan atas, dan jendela muncul untuk "
"mengonfirmasi bahasa. Klik :guilabel:`Confirm` untuk menyetujui dan kemudian "
"jendela lain menyatakan bahwa template telah dikirimkan ke Meta untuk "
"ditinjau dan disetujui."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:853
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Status` of the template remains :guilabel:`In review` until a "
"decision is made by Meta. Once an email confirmation approving the template "
"is received, the templates need to be synced from within the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status` dari template tetap :guilabel:`In review` hingga "
"keputusan dibuat oleh Meta. Setelah email konfirmasi yang menyetujui "
"template diterima, template perlu disinkronkan dari dalam database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:858
msgid ""
"`Meta Business: create message templates for your WhatsApp Business account "
"<https://www.facebook.com/business/help/2055875911147364>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Meta Business: membuat template pesan untuk akun WhatsApp Business Anda "
"<https://www.facebook.com/business/help/2055875911147364>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:860
msgid ""
"`Meta's WhatsApp template documentation <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"docs/whatsapp/business-management-api/message-templates/>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentasi template WhatsApp Meta <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/"
"whatsapp/business-management-api/message-templates/>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:868
msgid ""
"Notifications in WhatsApp are handled similar to a message conversation in "
"Odoo. A pop-up window appears with the received conversation from the "
"customer. By default, notifications are set in the WhatsApp business account "
"configuration in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Notifikasi di WhatsApp ditangani mirip dengan percakapan pesan di Odoo. "
"Jendela pop-up muncul dengan percakapan yang diterima dari pelanggan. Secara "
"default, notifikasi diatur dalam konfigurasi akun bisnis WhatsApp di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:872
msgid ""
"Notification settings can be adjusted by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> Configuration --> WhatsApp Business "
"Accounts`. From there, select the account and scroll down to "
"the :menuselection:`Control` section where notifications are handled. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Notify users` heading, type in the field which users should "
"be notified for this particular WhatsApp channel."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan notifikasi dapat disesuaikan dengan menavigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> Configuration --> WhatsApp Business "
"Accounts`. Dari sana, pilih akun dan gulir ke bawah ke "
"bagian :menuselection:`Control` di mana notifikasi ditangani. Di bawah "
"heading :guilabel:`Notify users`, ketik di field user mana yang harus diberi "
"notifikasi untuk channel WhatsApp tertentu ini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:878
msgid ""
"Once a conversation is initiated between a user and a customer, "
"notifications to all the users specified in the WhatsApp business account "
"configuration will not occur. Only notifications to the users in the "
"conversation occur. Should the user not respond within 15 days, the "
"customer's reply after the 15 days populates once again to all the users "
"specified in the WhatsApp configuration."
msgstr ""
"Setelah percakapan dimulai antara user dan pelanggan, notifikasi ke semua "
"user yang ditentukan dalam konfigurasi akun bisnis WhatsApp tidak akan "
"terjadi. Hanya notifikasi ke user dalam percakapan yang terjadi. Jika user "
"tidak merespons dalam 15 hari, balasan pelanggan setelah 15 hari akan muncul "
"lagi ke semua user yang ditentukan dalam konfigurasi WhatsApp."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:887
msgid "Add users to a chat"
msgstr "Menambahkan user ke chat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:889
msgid ""
"Users can be added to a WhatsApp chat by expanding the WhatsApp pop-up "
"window. WhatsApp conversations are located in the **Discuss** app. Select a "
"conversation, then click the :icon:`fa-user-plus` :guilabel:`(Add User)` "
"icon in the top-right, and a window appears to invite users to the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"User dapat ditambahkan ke chat WhatsApp dengan memperluas jendela pop-up "
"WhatsApp. Percakapan WhatsApp terletak di aplikasi **Diskusi**. Pilih "
"percakapan, kemudian klik ikon :icon:`fa-user-plus` :guilabel:`(Add User)` "
"di kanan atas, dan jendela muncul untuk mengundang user ke percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid ""
"Adding users to a WhatsApp conversation, with the add user icon highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan user ke percakapan WhatsApp, dengan ikon tambah user disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:900
msgid "WhatsApp API FAQ"
msgstr "FAQ API WhatsApp"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:905
msgid "Verification"
msgstr "Verifikasi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:907
msgid ""
"As of February 1, 2023, if the Meta app requires advanced level access to "
"permissions, a complete business verification may need to be completed. This "
"includes submitting office business documents to Meta. `See this "
"documentation <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/development/release/"
"business-verification>`__."
msgstr ""
"Sejak 1 Februari 2023, jika aplikasi Meta memerlukan akses tingkat lanjut ke "
"izin, verifikasi bisnis lengkap mungkin perlu diselesaikan. Ini termasuk "
"mengirimkan dokumen bisnis kantor ke Meta. `Lihat dokumentasi ini <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/development/release/business-verification>`__."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:913
msgid ""
"`Meta's WhatsApp access verification documentation <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/development/release/access-verification/>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentasi verifikasi akses WhatsApp Meta <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"docs/development/release/access-verification/>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:919
msgid "Cannot receive messages"
msgstr "Tidak dapat menerima pesan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:921
msgid ""
"If the business account cannot receive messages, check all of the webhook "
"configurations. Navigate to :menuselection:`WhatsApp Business Platform "
"documentation --> Resources --> API Reference --> WhatsApp Business Account "
"--> Subscribed Apps API --> POST /{Version}/{WABA-ID}/subscribed_apps`, or "
"click `here <https://developers.facebook.com/documentation/business-"
"messaging/whatsapp/reference/whatsapp-business-account/subscribed-apps-api/"
"#post-version-waba-id-subscribed-apps>`__. Log in to the business account if "
"necessary. Under the *Request Syntax* section, click :guilabel:`Try it` and "
"fill out the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Jika akun bisnis tidak dapat menerima pesan, periksa semua konfigurasi "
"webhook. Navigasi ke :menuselection:`WhatsApp Business Platform "
"documentation --> Resources --> API Reference --> WhatsApp Business Account "
"--> Subscribed Apps API --> POST /{Version}/{WABA-ID}/subscribed_apps`, atau "
"klik `di sini <https://developers.facebook.com/documentation/business-"
"messaging/whatsapp/reference/whatsapp-business-account/subscribed-apps-api/"
"#post-version-waba-id-subscribed-apps>`__. Login ke akun bisnis jika "
"diperlukan. Di bawah bagian *Request Syntax*, klik :guilabel:`Try it` dan "
"isi field berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:929
msgid ""
":guilabel:`authorization`: enter the :ref:`permanent access token "
"<productivity/whatsapp/token>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`authorization`: masukkan :ref:`permanent access token "
"<productivity/whatsapp/token>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:930
msgid ""
":guilabel:`WABA-ID`: enter the *WhatsApp Business Account ID (WABA ID)*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`WABA-ID`: masukkan *WhatsApp Business Account ID (WABA ID)*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:931
msgid ""
":guilabel:`override_callback_uri`: enter the :ref:`callback URL "
"<productivity/whatsapp/webhooks>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`override_callback_uri`: masukkan :ref:`callback URL <productivity/"
"whatsapp/webhooks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:932
msgid ""
":guilabel:`verify_token`: enter the :ref:`verification code <productivity/"
"whatsapp/webhooks>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`verify_token`: masukkan :ref:`verification code <productivity/"
"whatsapp/webhooks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:934
msgid ""
"To retrieve the *WABA ID*, navigate to :menuselection:`WhatsApp --> API "
"setup` in the left-hand side menu of the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__. The WABA ID is located in the *Send and "
"receive messages* section, under :guilabel:`Step 1: Select phone numbers`. "
"Once all the fields are filled out, click :guilabel:`Send request`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengambil *WABA ID*, navigasi ke :menuselection:`WhatsApp --> API "
"setup` di menu sisi kiri `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__. WABA ID terletak di bagian *Send and "
"receive messages*, di bawah :guilabel:`Step 1: Select phone numbers`. "
"Setelah semua field diisi, klik :guilabel:`Send request`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:942
msgid "Template errors"
msgstr "Error template"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:944
msgid ""
"Editing templates can cause tracebacks and errors unless :ref:`the exact "
"process is followed <productivity/whatsapp/templates>`."
msgstr ""
"Mengedit templat dapat menyebabkan traceback dan kesalahan "
"kecuali :ref:`proses yang tepat diikuti <productivity/whatsapp/templates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:950
msgid "Duplicate validation error"
msgstr "Error validasi duplikat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:952
msgid ""
"When syncing the templates there may be an instance when there are multiple "
"templates with the same name on Meta's business manager and in Odoo. This "
"causes a duplicate validation error. Odoo displays `Validation Error: The "
"operation cannot be completed: Duplicate template is not allowed for one "
"Meta account`. To correct this issue, rename the duplicate template name on "
"Odoo and :ref:`sync the templates once again <productivity/whatsapp/sync-"
"templates>`."
msgstr ""
"Saat menyinkronkan template, mungkin ada kejadian di mana ada beberapa "
"template dengan nama yang sama di business manager Meta dan di Odoo. Ini "
"menyebabkan error validasi duplikat. Odoo menampilkan `Validation Error: The "
"operation cannot be completed: Duplicate template is not allowed for one "
"Meta account`. Untuk memperbaiki masalah ini, ubah nama template duplikat di "
"Odoo dan :ref:`sinkronkan template sekali lagi <productivity/whatsapp/sync-"
"templates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid "Error message displayed in Odoo when a duplicate template exists."
msgstr "Pesan kesalahan yang ditampilkan di Odoo ketika templat duplikat ada."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:964
msgid "Token errors"
msgstr "Error token"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:969
msgid "User error 190"
msgstr "Kesalahan user 190"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:971
msgid ""
"If the temporary token is not replaced with a permanent token, Odoo displays "
"`User Error 190: Error validating access token: Session has expired`. To "
"correct this issue, :ref:`add a permanent token <productivity/whatsapp/"
"token>`."
msgstr ""
"Jika token sementara tidak diganti dengan token permanen, Odoo menampilkan "
"`User Error 190: Error validating access token: Session has expired`. Untuk "
"memperbaiki masalah ini, :ref:`tambahkan token permanen <productivity/"
"whatsapp/token>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid "Error message displayed in Odoo when the temporary token expires."
msgstr ""
"Pesan kesalahan yang ditampilkan di Odoo ketika token sementara kedaluwarsa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:981
msgid "User error 100"
msgstr "Kesalahan user 100"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:983
msgid ""
"If an :guilabel:`Employee` attempts to set up the permanent token, Odoo "
"displays `User Error 100: Unsupported get request`."
msgstr ""
"Jika seorang :guilabel:`Karyawan` mencoba mengatur token permanen, Odoo "
"menampilkan `User Error 100: Unsupported get request`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:986
msgid ""
"To correct this error, :ref:`create an Admin system user <productivity/"
"whatsapp/token>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbaiki kesalahan ini, :ref:`buat user sistem Admin <productivity/"
"whatsapp/token>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid ""
"Error message displayed in Odoo when an employee token is generated instead "
"of an Admin\n"
"user."
msgstr ""
"Pesan kesalahan yang ditampilkan di Odoo ketika token karyawan dibuat alih-"
"alih user Admin."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:1000
msgid "Template cannot be sent to multiple contacts"
msgstr "Template tidak dapat dikirim ke beberapa kontak"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:1002
msgid "Make sure the *Multi-Template* feature is enabled on the template."
msgstr "Pastikan fitur *Multi-Template* diaktifkan pada templat."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:1007
msgid "Message failed to send"
msgstr "Pesan gagal terkirim"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:1009
msgid ""
"Enable the *Failure Type* and *Failure Reason* columns "
"under :guilabel:`WhatsApp ---> Messages`."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan kolom *Failure Type* dan *Failure Reason* di "
"bawah :guilabel:`WhatsApp ---> Messages`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:1014
msgid "Other error codes"
msgstr "Kode kesalahan lainnya"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:1016
msgid ""
"For other errors, see Meta's Developer Suite for `WhatsApp Error Codes "
"<https://developers.facebook.com/documentation/business-messaging/whatsapp/"
"support/error-codes>`__."
msgstr ""
"Untuk error lainnya, lihat Developer Suite Meta untuk `WhatsApp Error Codes "
"<https://developers.facebook.com/documentation/business-messaging/whatsapp/"
"support/error-codes>`__."

